name: Toyota Crown Athlete
description:
It has a 2.5L V6 engine mated to a 6 speed auto transmission. The Crown Athlete is distinctively sporty with its agressive front grill, sleek body lines and larger multi spoke wheels. 
It features a rear wheel drive (RWD)for a more engaging deiving experience.

name: Mazda MPV
description:
The Mazda MPV (Multipurpose Passenger Vehicle)is a minivan manufactured by Mazda. 
It has a spacious interior and seats 7 people. Has a very reliable engine 
2.5L DOHC (Double Overhead Cam)V6 engine. Other variants come with the inline 4 but this specific unit has the V6 engine.
This is a great choice if you're looking for a family friendly vehicle with decent performance and reasonable fuel efficiency.

name: Nissan Skyline
description:
The 2011 Nissan Skyline blends performance and sophistication offering a dynamic driving experience with its sleek design and advanced technology.Equipped with a powerful engine, precise handling and cutting edge features, the Skyline delivers a smooth yet exhilarating ride making it standout in both style and performance. 
Ideal for those seeking a blend of luxury and sport, the 2011 model is a true testament to Nissan's engineering excellence.

name: 2024 Toyota Landcruiser Prado Adventure Plus (J250).
description:
This is the Toyota Landcruiser Prado Adventure Plus trim of the Prado J250 series that comes equipped with a 2.8L turbocharged diesel engine paired to a 6 speed automatic transmission and equipped with a full time 4WD system. 
The fuel tank is around 110 litres and comes with 7 seats.
It has a bigger 12 inch infotainment  screen and parking sensors all round.

name: Volkswagen Touareg
description: The Volkswagen Touareg has some similarities with the Porsche Cayenne. This one comes equipped with a 3000CC Diesel engine. Perfect for long trips and towing as well. Its is also equipped with an AWD system.

name: Toyota Succeed
description: This is a great commercial vehicle perfect for doing business in and out of town. It has a 1500CC engine and a 2WD drivetrain.

name: Toyota Noah
description: The Toyota Noah is a spacious and reliable minivan offering seating upto 8 passengers. Its an ideal choice for families seeking comfort and practicality.

name: Toyota Fortuner
description: 2.4GD spec , 2023 model in excellent condition with 27,000kms covered. Close derivative of the Hilux, the Fortuner offers more comforts making it more ideal for private usage.

name: Toyota Crown
description:
"athlete" spec which comes standards with spoilers, 19inch alloys, body kit and quad exhaust. 
S210 14th generation variant also equipped with a Hybrid engine for minimum fuel consumption.
Well kept unit with aftermarket rims edge detailing and heavy sound system

name: Volkswagen Tiguan
description: 2.0 Litre variant equipped with 4Motion all wheel drive and twin clutch DSG Gearbox. Excellent balance between practicality and edge of the seat perfomance.

name: BMW X3
description: Body in excellent condition but will require some exterior and mechanical touch ups. In driveable condition.

name: Range Rover Vogue
description: 4th generation, "L405" variant powered by a 4,400cc diesel V8 engine which is arguably one of the most realible and highly sort after engines in the Land rover line up. No expense has been spared in maintaining this particular unit and the starting price is pretty reasonable for a unit this clean.

name: Mitsubishi Pajero Shogun
description:
The Pajero was sold under the "shogun" name in Europe and features some unique equipment trims not standard on ex japan models. This include sunroof, multi lingual infotainment system, cruise control and satellite navigation.
Pictured model was shipped in Kenya circa 2013 and has only had one owner.

name: Toyota Crown
description:
Athlete package, includes unique sport features ie Sporty alloys, custom athlete grille and athlete body styling.
Users love the Crown for its smooth , comfortable drive thats derived from a 2.5 litre V6 motor mated to a 6 speed gearbox.

name: Nissan Patrol
description:
Excellent candidate for an offroad rig project. Runs great, aftermarket "robs magic suspension" , Custom bull bar  , Snorkel and all terrain tyres.
Originally sourced from the United Kingdom, this one of the best patrol deals you can get in the Kenyan market.

name: Mercedes ML350
description: Bluetech model diesel, exceptional condition and only one owner locally since importation. Excellent deal, won't last long!

name: Toyota Landcruiser 200 series
description:
Ex UK and has nice extras including sunroof, heated seats and rear climate controls.
Buyers will be guaranteed massive torque, superb offroad perfomance and an imposing spacious design.

name: Toyota Mark X
description: Our best selling vehicle of 2024, out of the hundreds of cars successfully delivered by kaiandkaro.com the Mark X accounted for over 10%

name: Volkswagen Sharan
description: The Sharan is a spacious 7 seater mini van that would work very well for many types of applications be it commercial or private. Pictured unit is in excellent condition and has been well used in Kenya.

name: Mazda Demio
description: Rare red upholstery on this 2015 Demio. Other extras include original Mazda Alloys and heated seats.

name: Toyota Fielder
description: Non hybrid 1,500cc petrol fielder variant. locally used but in great overall condition.

name: Honda civic
description:
With 30 million units sold globally, the Civic is Hondas best selling car with a solid reputation for being extremely realible.
The pictured unit is in running condition but will need a few exterior and interior touch ups.

name: Mercedes C220
description: Powered by a 2,200cc diesel engine, buyers of this C220 can expect excellent torque figures and suprisingly low fuel consumption. Historically, such diesel powered Mercedes benz models have found great use as executive taxis or corporate vehicle.

name: BMW X1
description: 18i sdrive, M sport trim equipped model with a 2,000cc turbocharged N20 engine mated to an 8 speed ZF gearbox. This unique combination was only available on late 2015 BMW X1s. Pictured unit is exceptionally maintained and won't be available for long!

name: Mercedes G350D
description: AMG Line equipped model featuring AMG alloys, AMG body Kit, AMG interior styling and sunroof. Despite the AMG inspired exterior, the G350D is powered by a manageable 3,000cc diesel engine giving it a unique blend of power and good fuel consumption.

name: Honda fit hybrid
description: Very rare Honda fit spec with some unique features including panoramic sunroof, cruise control, heated seats , steering audio controls and eco mode.

name: Toyota Vitz
description: When the vitz first appeared in Kenya circa 2007, it became an instant hit thanks to its low fuel consumption, affordability and simple design that made it the perfect urban hatchback. Alot has changed since then but the Vitz still remains the choice of vehicle for most people in the market for an affordable hatchback.

name: Subaru impreza
description: Subaru Impreza has been in production since 1982 and the pictured model is a 3rd generation "GH" model. Notable specs on this one include black alloy rims,aftermarket android infotainment unit, strong suspension and no cost has been spared in maintenance by previous owner

name: Toyota Mark X
description: This Mark X is in exceptional condition and has nice extras including aftermarket subwoofer ,pioneer radio and size 18 alloy wheels. Powered by a smooth 2.5 Litre V6, the Mark X is our best selling vehicle of 2024

name: Mercedes C200
description: The Mercedes C200 has been the best selling luxury saloon car in Kenya due to many factors including affordable running costs,excellent realibility and good resale values. We would highly recommend it!

name: Kawasaki Z900
description: The Kawasaki Z900 is a "standard" street motorbike powered by a 950cc naturally aspirated engine. Standard motorbikes are ideal for day to day commuting thanks to their "upright" stance, simple design and lack of complex body fairings.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: Fresh import , not locally used and comes equipped with a panoramic sunroof, leather upholstery with quilted finish , Genuine Toyota alloys and premium wood finish.

name: Toyota Crown Athlete
description: The 2008 Toyota Crown Athlete 2500cc is a comfortable, well-equipped sedan, ideal for those seeking a reliable luxury vehicle with solid performance and a refined driving experience.

name: Toyota Vanguard
description: The 2013 Toyota Vanguard  hosts a V6 engine providing more power and performance. It's a reliable SUV with excellent safety features, making it a good option for those needing a practical, versatile vehicle.

name: Toyota Kluger
description: The 2005 Kluger is known for its solid build quality, decent performance, and spacious interior. It is a good option for families looking for an affordable, comfortable, and safe vehicle.

name: Audi Q5
description: Audi Q5 is a luxury compact SUV offering a powerful engine , standard Quattro AWD, and a refined interior. With fuel efficiency of 12–16 km/L and advanced features like the Audi MMI infotainment and multiple safety systems, it balances performance, comfort, and practicality.

name: Subaru Impreza
description: Subaru impreza is valued for its AWD capability, sporty performance and durability making it a perfect choice for enthusiasts and everyday drivers.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI
description: Golf TSI offers excellent fuel efficiency at 20–22 km/L, making it economical for daily use. Maintenance is manageable, though parts and service may cost slightly more than average due to Volkswagen's premium build quality and reliance on specialized components.

name: Toyota Mark X
description: The Toyota Mark X is a reliable and durable sedan, known for its durable V6 engines, high build quality, and cost-effective maintenance. With proper care, it delivers long-term performance and comfort, making it a dependable choice for daily commute

name: Toyota Vitz
description: A well maintained car that offers practicality and above average fuel consumption,this Toyota Vitz has been properly used and maintained by the owner hence a condition score of 4/5,it is fitted with fabric seats,mechanical handbrake and brand new tyres.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado
description: TX models of the Toyota Prado offer a blend of rugged off-road capability and family-friendly features. Designed for versatility, the TX variant maintains the Prado’s renowned durability while providing a spacious and comfortable interior that can accommodate up to seven passengers. The cabin is equipped with essential modern conveniences, including a touchscreen infotainment system and multi-zone climate control, ensuring a pleasant driving experience. With advanced safety features such as stability control and hill-start assist, the TX model is as safe as it is practical. Whether for daily commutes or adventurous road trips, the Prado TX stands out as a reliable and capable SUV.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: The Subaru Forester SG5 Turbo, produced between 2002 and 2008, is a second-generation model that offers practicality and versatility. It features a manual transmission, allowing for an engaging driving experience, and comes with Subaru's symmetrical all-wheel-drive system, ensuring excellent handling and traction in diverse conditions. Its spacious interior, durable build, and adaptability make it a reliable choice for both urban and off-road use.

name: Toyota Landcruiser 80 Series
description: The Toyota Land Cruiser 80 Series, a rugged and capable SUV known for its off-road performance and durability. The specific features in this image, such as the snorkel, roof rack, and heavy-duty bumpers, indicate it is modified for off-road adventures. The 80 Series was produced between 1990 and 1997 and is highly regarded among enthusiasts for its reliable drivetrain and tough build. Let me know if you'd like more details about its specifications or capabilities!

name: Toyota Fielder
description: The Toyota Fielder Hybrid is a versatile station wagon that blends practicality with eco-friendly efficiency. Equipped with Toyota’s Hybrid Synergy Drive system, it delivers a smooth and quiet ride, ideal for both city commutes and longer trips. The spacious interior offers ample room for passengers and cargo, while its ergonomic design ensures comfort and functionality. Advanced safety features, modern infotainment options, and low running costs further enhance its appeal. The Fielder Hybrid is a reliable choice for those seeking an economical yet stylish family or utility vehicle. Let me know if you'd like more details on its performance or features!

name: Honda Vezel
description: Hybrid drivetrain technology is often seen as the future, and many appreciate the hybrid system in the Vezel, especially in today’s economic climate. The car excels in fuel efficiency, thanks to its impressive 1500cc naturally aspirated engine paired with a hybrid setup, making driving more convenient and economical even during fuel price hikes.

name: Mercedes Benz E250
description: The Mercedes-Benz E250 in the W213 generation is a luxury sedan that combines advanced technology, refined design, and exceptional comfort. Positioned in the E-Class lineup, it features an elegant exterior with aerodynamic styling and a spacious, premium interior crafted with high-quality materials. Standard features include advanced safety systems such as adaptive cruise control and lane-keeping assist, as well as a sophisticated infotainment system with a central display. The E250 offers a balance of performance and efficiency, with smooth handling and a focus on passenger comfort, making it ideal for both city driving and long-distance travel. Let me know if you'd like details on engine specs or trim options!

name: Toyota Noah
description: Toyota Noah is a very comfortable car. From experience and reviews, you can comfortably sit for long distances without tiring your back. The passengers have the same satisfactory reviews. And it is quite powerful giving sufficient torque.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado
description: The Toyota Prado is a mid-size SUV known for its strong off-road capabilities and refined on-road manners. It’s part of the Land Cruiser family, offering a blend of rugged durability and modern comfort. The Prado features a robust body-on-frame construction, advanced four-wheel-drive systems, and a range of powerful engines, typically including diesel and petrol options, making it well-suited for challenging terrains and long-distance driving. Inside, the Prado provides a spacious and well-appointed cabin with seating for up to seven passengers, advanced safety technologies, and modern infotainment features, making it a versatile choice for both family use and adventurous expeditions.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: The 2003 Subaru Forester XT is a sporty variant of the second-generation Forester, blending the utility of a compact SUV with the performance characteristics of a turbocharged vehicle. It features a robust design with all-wheel drive as standard, providing excellent handling and traction across various terrains. The Forester XT is notable for its turbocharged engine, which delivers strong acceleration and makes it one of the more performance-oriented options in its class during that era. Inside, the Forester XT offers a practical and comfortable cabin, with ample space for passengers and cargo, making it suitable for both daily commuting and adventurous trips. Its combination of rugged capability, sporty performance, and practicality made it a popular choice for drivers seeking a versatile and engaging compact SUV.

name: Nissan Note
description: The Nissan Note is a compact hatchback that combines practicality with modern features, making it ideal for city driving. Its design emphasizes spaciousness and efficiency, with a roomy interior that comfortably accommodates passengers despite its compact size

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: The Subaru Forester XT is a turbocharged variant of the Forester SUV, featuring a 2.0-liter turbocharged flat-four engine producing 250 horsepower and 350 Nm of torque. It comes with all-wheel drive and offers a balanced mix of performance and practicality. The Forester XT is known for its strong acceleration, rugged build, and capability in various driving conditions, including off-road. It also offers a spacious interior and a range of modern features, making it a versatile and reliable SUV.

name: Volvo XC60
description: The T5 version of the Volvo XC60 offers a blend of luxury and performance, showcasing the SUV's signature Scandinavian design and advanced features. Inside, the XC60 T5 boasts a spacious and well-crafted interior, featuring premium materials and the latest in infotainment and safety technology. Known for its smooth ride and exceptional safety systems, the XC60 T5 is equipped with Volvo's renowned driver-assistance features, making it one of the safest vehicles in its class. With its refined styling, comfort, and reliability, the XC60 T5 is a great option for those seeking a luxurious and secure driving experience.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The third-generation Mercedes-Benz C-Class (W204), produced from 2007 to 2014, is a luxury compact sedan that combines elegant design with sporty performance. It features a refined, muscular exterior with a bold front grille and a more dynamic stance. Inside, the cabin offers premium materials, comfortable seating, and advanced technology, including a user-friendly infotainment system and various driver assistance features. Known for its smooth ride and precise handling, the W204 offers a range of engine options focused on both performance and fuel efficiency, with the available 4MATIC all-wheel-drive system enhancing traction. This generation balances luxury, comfort, and performance, appealing to both everyday drivers and enthusiasts alike.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: The second-generation Toyota Harrier, produced from 2003 to 2013, was a luxury crossover SUV known for its refined design, comfort, and advanced technology. It featured a sleek, aerodynamic exterior and a high-quality interior with premium materials and modern amenities. Both front-wheel and all-wheel drive configurations were available, and a hybrid variant was introduced in 2005, blending performance with fuel efficiency. The Harrier stood out for its smooth ride, spacious cabin, and focus on safety, making it a popular choice among those seeking both luxury and practicality in an SUV.

name: Toyota Vitz
description: Toyota used the Vitz nameplate majorly for the Japanese market and the Yaris for international markets. As a direct consumer of the Japanese market, we got the Vitz nameplate. It has been a very popular car in a lot of markets achieving over 3.5 Million sales in excess of the projected number in over 70 countries. It still continues to be among the top selling hatchbacks by the Japanese Manufacturer.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: The Toyota Harrier is a stylish mid-size crossover SUV that expertly combines sophistication with practicality, making it a sought-after choice for those in need of a versatile vehicle. Its sleek, aerodynamic exterior is characterized by bold lines, a distinctive front grille, and elegant LED headlights, lending it a modern and upscale appearance. Inside, the Harrier boasts a spacious cabin adorned with high-quality materials, comfortable seating, and advanced technology, including an intuitive infotainment system and a comprehensive suite of safety features. With a focus on comfort, it offers ample legroom and cargo space, ideal for daily commutes and family adventures. Engine options typically include efficient petrol and hybrid powertrains, ensuring a smooth and responsive driving experience. Known for its reliability and the brand's commitment to quality, the Harrier is an excellent blend of performance and style for those who appreciate aesthetics without compromising functionality.

name: Toyota Fielder
description: The Toyota Fielder is the station wagon variant of the Toyota Corolla, offering practicality and versatility for everyday use. Known for its spacious interior and generous cargo capacity, it is a favorite among families and businesses. The Fielder features a modern design, with higher trims offering advanced technology such as a touchscreen infotainment system, navigation, and safety features like ABS and airbags. Its reputation for reliability, fuel efficiency, and low maintenance costs makes it a popular choice for those seeking a dependable and functional vehicle.

name: Mazda CX8
description: The Mazda CX-8 is a mid-size SUV designed to balance elegance, practicality, and performance. It features a three-row seating configuration, accommodating up to seven passengers, and a refined interior with premium materials such as leather upholstery and woodgrain accents in higher trims. The CX-8 boasts Mazda’s signature KODO: Soul of Motion design, with sleek lines and a sophisticated exterior. Equipped with advanced technology, it offers features like a responsive infotainment system, a suite of safety systems (i-Activsense), and efficient Skyactiv engines. Combining luxury, comfort, and versatility, the CX-8 is an ideal choice for families seeking a premium SUV.

name: Nissan Juke
description: Nissan Juke made a debut in 2010 as a production vehicle. In its first year of selling, it surpassed the manufacturer's expectation 10 fold and since then it has been received well in the market. It has been purchased in high numbers in Kenya also making it among best selling cars that some have criticised its shape, one that was inspired by a lot of history at Nissan. This unit comes with two-tone fabric seats, climate controls, android infotainment display screen, and a push to start button.

name: Honda Stream
description: The Honda Stream is a renown versatile station wagon, offering a combination of practicality and dynamic styling. It is loved for its practicality and reliability.

name: Mazda Demio
description: XD trim of the Mazda Demio emphasize luxury and sophistication, featuring premium upholstery and soft-touch finishes throughout the cabin. The trim includes advanced technology such as a modern infotainment system with a touchscreen interface, navigation, and smartphone connectivity. Stylish design elements like alloy wheels, LED lighting, and chrome accents enhance its upscale appeal. These features, combined with the refined comfort of the seats and advanced driver-assist systems, make the XD variant ideal for those seeking a compact car with a touch of elegance and modern convenience.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The Subaru Forester is a compact SUV known for its practicality, reliability, and off-road capability. It comes with Subaru's signature Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive (AWD), ensuring excellent traction and stability in various driving conditions. The vehicle offers spacious seating for five, a functional interior with ample cargo space, and advanced safety features like ABS and multiple airbags. Available engine options include both naturally aspirated and turbocharged versions of Subaru's Boxer engines, paired with either a manual or automatic transmission. Its balanced ride quality and robust build make it a strong contender for families and adventurers alike.

name: Toyota Axio
description: The Toyota Axio, also referred to as the Corolla Axio in some markets, is a compact sedan recognized for its reliability, practicality, and fuel efficiency. Ideal for both daily commuting and family use, it offers a comfortable and well-organized interior, featuring easy-to-use controls and ample passenger space. Its compact dimensions allow for easy maneuverability in tight city spaces, while still maintaining a comfortable ride on longer journeys. The Axio is equipped with essential modern features, including basic infotainment options and key safety systems, making it a trusted choice for those seeking an economical, low-maintenance vehicle with Toyota's renowned reliability.

name: Toyota Isis
description: The Toyota Isis is a compact MPV designed primarily for the Japanese market, offering practicality and versatility for families. It features a spacious interior with three-row seating, sliding rear doors for easy access, and various configurations for passenger and cargo needs. The Isis is equipped with advanced features for its time, including optional all-wheel drive, safety systems like ABS, and a comfortable driving experience. Its combination of efficiency, reliability, and practicality made it a popular choice for those seeking a functional family vehicle.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The Subaru Forester is a compact SUV renowned for its ruggedness, versatility, and all-wheel-drive capability. It offers a spacious interior with excellent cargo space, making it ideal for families and outdoor enthusiasts. Equipped with Subaru’s signature Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, the Forester provides superior handling and stability on various terrains, from city streets to off-road trails. It features a range of modern safety and technology options, ensuring a safe and comfortable driving experience. The Forester is well-regarded for its reliability, making it a practical choice for those seeking an adventurous yet dependable SUV.

name: Honda Odyssey
description: The Honda Odyssey is a family-friendly vehicle designed for practicality and comfort, offering spacious seating for 7–8 passengers and versatile interior configurations for various needs. Known for its smooth performance and reliability, the Odyssey features modern amenities such as advanced infotainment systems and premium materials in higher trims. It excels in safety with Honda's suite of driver-assist technologies, including adaptive cruise control and collision mitigation systems. With a reputation for long-term dependability and a focus on convenience, the Odyssey remains a top choice for families seeking a comfortable and versatile vehicle.

name: Mazda Demio
description: Mazda Demio is a very reliable and excellently performing car with the 1.5L turbo diesel engine giving sufficient power to carry up to 5 individuals and some cargo at the back. The seats have the heating functionality which is also a plus for the comfort aspect. It has a beautiful interior which gives it a different look from the traditional Demio.

name: Mitsubishi Pajero
description: Pajero is a full size SUV (Sport Utility Vehicle) that is very efficient in handling multiple terrains including offroad and urban setups. It runs a very capable engine and excellent drivetrain with locking diffs for offroad mode. It also works well for large family setups as a number of Pajeros come in 5 up to 7 seats!

name: Subaru Legacy
description: The Subaru Legacy station wagon is a rare blend of performance, practicality, and all-weather capability, making it highly sought after among enthusiasts and adventurers alike. Unlike typical wagons, the Legacy features Subaru’s iconic symmetrical all-wheel-drive system, giving it exceptional handling and stability, even in challenging conditions.

name: Mercedes Benz B180
description: The Mercedes-Benz B180 combines elegance, practicality, and modern features, making it a versatile choice for daily use. Its interior is thoughtfully designed with premium materials, comfortable seating, and ample storage options to suit a variety of lifestyles. The exterior boasts the signature Mercedes-Benz styling, with sleek lines and a polished appearance. Equipped with advanced safety technologies and a smooth driving experience, the B180 offers a balance of style and functionality that appeals to families and professionals alike.

name: Mercedes Benz GLA45 AMG
description: The Mercedes-AMG GLA 45 is a high-performance compact SUV that combines luxury, sportiness, and practicality. With its distinctive AMG styling, including an aggressive front grille, aerodynamic enhancements, and larger wheels, it exudes a bold presence. Inside, the cabin features AMG-specific details like sports seats, premium materials, and advanced technology, including the MBUX infotainment system with customizable displays. The GLA 45 delivers dynamic handling and exceptional performance, making it an exciting choice for those seeking a powerful yet versatile vehicle in the compact luxury segment.

name: Audi A7
description: The Audi A7 S line with a sunroof blends sleek coupe-like styling with advanced luxury and technology. The S line trim enhances its sporty appeal with distinctive features like a more aggressive body kit, upgraded wheels, and premium interior touches such as sport seats and brushed aluminum inlays. The panoramic sunroof adds an airy, open feel to the cabin, complementing the high-quality materials and cutting-edge tech like the MMI infotainment system and driver-assistance features. This model offers a perfect mix of elegance, comfort, and dynamic performance, making it a standout choice in the luxury fastback segment.

name: Volkswagen Beetle
description: The Volkswagen Beetle, one of the most iconic cars in automotive history, is celebrated for its distinctive rounded design and cultural significance. Originally conceived in the 1930s as an affordable, reliable vehicle, it gained worldwide popularity post-WWII and became a symbol of individuality and freedom during the 1960s. Over its generations, the Beetle evolved with modernized features while retaining its retro charm, culminating in a final production run in 2019. Known for its compact size, versatile interior, and unique style, the Beetle remains a beloved classic and a standout in the automotive world.

name: Nissan Wingroad
description: The Nissan Wingroad is a versatile compact wagon that balances practicality with a comfortable driving experience. It stands out for its spacious interior and flexible seating arrangements, allowing for easy adjustment between passenger seating and cargo space. Ideal for families or those needing extra storage, the Wingroad provides ample room while maintaining a compact, city-friendly size. Known for its reliable performance and fuel efficiency, it’s designed for everyday use, whether it's for commuting, road trips, or running errands. With a focus on utility and ease of driving, the Wingroad is a dependable choice for those who need both function and comfort in a small wagon.

name: Porsche Cayenne
description: The Porsche Cayenne Platinum Edition is a luxurious variant of the Cayenne SUV, featuring exclusive design elements and premium finishes. It comes with Platinum accents on the grille, rear lettering, and wheels, which add a sophisticated touch to its exterior. Inside, the cabin is meticulously crafted with high-quality materials, advanced technology, and comfort-focused features like a panoramic sunroof and ambient lighting. With seating for five, ample cargo space, and a range of driver-assistance systems, it offers a seamless blend of style, practicality, and cutting-edge technology tailored for a premium driving experience​

name: Lexus RX450h
description: The Lexus RX 450h is a luxury hybrid SUV that combines premium comfort with fuel efficiency and advanced technology. Known for its bold and elegant design, the RX 450h features sharp lines, a signature spindle grille, and striking LED headlights. Under the hood, it offers a hybrid powertrain that blends a V6 engine with electric motors, delivering a smooth, quiet, and efficient performance with reduced emissions. Inside, the RX 450h boasts a spacious, high-end interior with leather upholstery, cutting-edge infotainment, and a host of driver assistance features. Its smooth ride, luxurious amenities, and hybrid efficiency make it an attractive choice for those seeking a blend of environmental responsibility and luxury.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The Mazda CX-5 is a stylish and versatile compact SUV that seamlessly combines sporty performance with everyday practicality. Its sleek exterior showcases Mazda's Kodo design philosophy, featuring flowing lines, a bold grille, and striking LED headlights that create a dynamic and upscale look. Inside, the CX-5 offers a well-crafted cabin with high-quality materials, comfortable seating, and an intuitive infotainment system, making it perfect for both daily commutes and longer journeys. With a choice of efficient engines that deliver spirited performance and responsive handling, the CX-5 embodies Mazda's commitment to driving enjoyment. Its spacious interior provides ample cargo space and thoughtful storage solutions, appealing to families and outdoor enthusiasts alike, making the CX-5 a standout choice in the competitive compact SUV segment.

name: Toyota Vanguard
description: The Toyota Vanguard is a mid-size SUV that combines practicality, comfort, and performance. Introduced in 2007, it is essentially a longer and more spacious version of the Toyota RAV4, offering an optional third row of seats to accommodate up to seven passengers. It features a well-designed interior with high-quality materials, modern infotainment, and safety features like airbags and stability control. The Vanguard's balanced ride quality and all-wheel-drive options make it suitable for both city and off-road driving. Its versatility, reliability, and spacious cabin have made it a popular choice for families and adventurers.

name: Honda CBR600RR
description: The Honda CBR600RR is a high-performance supersport motorcycle featuring a 599cc inline four-cylinder engine. It delivers 113 horsepower and 63 Nm of torque, with precise engineering designed for track and road performance. Known for its lightweight and agility, the CBR600RR weighs approximately 186-196 kg, depending on the variant, and includes advanced features like a 6-axis IMU for cornering ABS, traction control, and multiple riding modes. With a focus on aerodynamics and handling, it incorporates race-inspired technology such as winglets, a quick-shifter, and high-spec suspension, making it a top choice for riders seeking both speed and precision.

name: Jeep Grand Cherokee
description: The Jeep Grand Cherokee is a midsize SUV known for its blend of luxury, off-road capability, and powerful performance. It offers a spacious and well-appointed interior with advanced technology and safety features, catering to families and adventurers alike. The Grand Cherokee stands out for its rugged 4x4 systems and towing capability, making it suitable for off-road trails and heavy-duty tasks. Its versatile lineup includes trims ranging from practical to high-performance, ensuring a fit for various preferences and needs.

name: Audi Q5
description: The Audi Q5 is a luxury compact SUV that seamlessly combines elegant design, advanced technology, and versatile performance. Known for its refined and spacious interior, the Q5 offers high-quality materials, modern amenities, and a comfortable ride for both driver and passengers. It comes equipped with a range of powerful and efficient engine options, including turbocharged and hybrid variants, all paired with Audi's quattro all-wheel-drive system for enhanced traction and stability. The Q5 also features cutting-edge technology, including a sophisticated infotainment system and a suite of driver assistance features, making it a top choice for those seeking a premium, well-rounded SUV that excels in both urban and long-distance driving.

name: Subaru Impreza
description: The Subaru Impreza hatchback stands out with its ensuring superior handling and stability. It features a modern and spacious interior equipped with advanced technology like a touchscreen infotainment system supporting Bluetooth and smartphone integration. Safety highlights include features like traction control and optional blind-spot monitoring. Practicality is enhanced by a roomy cargo area and foldable rear seats, making it an excellent choice for versatile use

name: Honda N Wagon
description: The Honda N-Wagon is a compact and practical kei car designed primarily for urban use. It offers a boxy design that maximizes interior space while maintaining a small footprint for easy maneuverability. Inside, the N-Wagon features a well-thought-out cabin with flexible seating configurations and modern tech amenities, making it comfortable for both driver and passengers. Its fuel-efficient engine is paired with either a CVT or automatic transmission, delivering smooth performance and excellent fuel economy. The N-Wagon is popular for its reliability, practicality, and affordability, appealing to drivers seeking a compact yet versatile vehicle for everyday commuting.

name: Nissan Juke
description: The Nissan Juke is a compact crossover SUV known for its bold design and agile handling. First introduced in 2010, it quickly gained attention for its unique styling, combining sporty and SUV-like elements. The Juke offers a comfortable cabin with modern technology features, catering to urban drivers who value practicality and individuality. With its compact dimensions, it excels in city driving while offering the versatility of a crossover. The Juke's appeal lies in its blend of standout design, nimble performance, and everyday usability.

name: Ford Ranger
description: The Ford Ranger is a versatile and reliable pick-up truck designed for both work and recreation. Known for its rugged build, it offers excellent off-road capability and a durable cargo bed for heavy-duty tasks. The interior is equipped with modern features, including comfortable seating and advanced infotainment options, making it suitable for long journeys. With its strong chassis and refined driving dynamics, the Ford Ranger delivers a balance of utility and comfort, appealing to drivers who need a tough yet practical vehicle.

name: Subaru Impreza
description: The Subaru Impreza G4 is a sedan version of the Impreza lineup, offering a sleek design and practical features. Known for its spacious cabin and advanced safety technologies, including Subaru's signature all-wheel-drive system, the G4 provides stable handling and versatility for various driving conditions. It features a compact yet refined design, catering to urban commuters and small families. The Impreza G4 balances comfort and functionality, making it a popular choice for those seeking reliability and value in a sedan

name: Nissan Note
description: The Nissan Note is a compact hatchback that combines practicality with modern features, making it ideal for city driving. Its design emphasizes spaciousness and efficiency, with a roomy interior that comfortably accommodates passengers despite its compact size.

name: Mitsubishi Colt
description: The Mitsubishi Colt is a compact hatchback that has gained popularity for its practicality, efficient use of space, and reliable performance. Known for its versatile design, the Colt provides a comfortable interior with seating for up to five passengers and offers a decent amount of cargo space for its size. Its compact dimensions make it ideal for city driving, while the range of fuel-efficient engines enhances its appeal as a cost-effective daily driver. Over its production years, the Colt has been offered with various trims and features, catering to a broad range of preferences and needs.

name: Mazda Demio
description: The Mazda Demio Diesel Sport offers a practical and fuel-efficient hatchback experience with sporty features. It combines modern styling and compact dimensions, making it well-suited for urban environments. The interior provides a comfortable cabin with advanced infotainment and safety technologies. Its diesel powertrain is known for exceptional fuel economy, while the sport trim adds dynamic touches such as sportier suspension and distinctive styling elements.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado
description: The Toyota Land Cruiser Prado J120, produced from 2002 to 2009, is a mid-size SUV renowned for its durability, off-road capability, and comfortable ride. Available in both three-door and five-door body styles, the J120 features Toyota's rugged body-on-frame construction and advanced 4WD system, making it highly capable on challenging terrain. Inside, it offers a spacious and refined interior with quality materials and practical features, suitable for families and adventurers alike. Its reliability and versatility have made it a popular choice in markets worldwide, balancing off-road prowess with everyday usability.

name: Honda Vezel
description: The Honda Vezel Hybrid RS combines sporty styling with impressive hybrid technology. It features the Honda Sensing suite, including advanced safety systems like collision mitigation, lane-keeping assist, and adaptive cruise control, making it a well-rounded option for urban and highway driving. The RS trim emphasizes sportiness with its distinctive exterior details and more dynamic suspension setup. Inside, it offers a premium feel with comfortable seating, modern infotainment, and ample cargo space. This hybrid model balances fuel efficiency with Honda's signature driving engagement, making it ideal for those seeking a stylish yet practical compact crossover.

name: Nissan Serena
description: The Nissan Serena is a highly practical multi-purpose vehicle (MPV) tailored for families, featuring a spacious interior and versatile seating that adapts to various needs. Its sliding doors facilitate easy access, while the flexible seating arrangement allows for multiple configurations, maximizing comfort for both passengers and cargo. Modern Serena models are equipped with Nissan’s ProPILOT technology, a semi-autonomous driving system designed to assist with highway driving, enhancing safety and ease on long trips. The Serena is available with a choice of hybrid or traditional gasoline powertrains, providing options for those focused on fuel efficiency. Known for its combination of practicality, advanced safety features, and family-friendly design, the Nissan Serena remains a popular choice for those seeking a reliable and adaptable vehicle.

name: Toyota Rav4
description: The Toyota RAV4 with a sunroof, particularly the panoramic option available in higher trims, enhances the driving experience by providing an open and airy feel to the cabin. The large glass panel allows natural light to flood the interior, creating a more spacious and luxurious ambiance. This feature is often paired with other premium upgrades, such as leather upholstery, advanced infotainment systems, and power-adjustable seating, making the RAV4 a versatile and upscale choice in the compact SUV segment. The sunroof option is perfect for drivers who appreciate added comfort and a connection to the outdoors during their journeys.

name: Subaru Forester
description: A well engineered, great powered SUV, with one of the best drivetrains in the world, the Subaru Forester. It is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, and heated front seats as some of its major specs.

name: Peugeot 208
description: Moonroof in the Peugeot 208 enhances the driving experience, flooding the cabin with natural light and creating an open, airy feel. This compact hatchback combines stylish design, advanced technology, and practicality, making it an excellent choice for urban and suburban driving. Inside, it offers a modern and comfortable interior, featuring Peugeot’s signature i-Cockpit with a compact steering wheel, high-mounted instrument cluster, and touchscreen infotainment system. With its dynamic handling and efficient engine options, the Peugeot 208 delivers a refined driving experience while maintaining excellent fuel economy, all wrapped in a sleek, contemporary package.

name: BMW 740e
description: The BMW 740e xDrive iPerformance is a plug-in hybrid luxury sedan that combines a 2.0-liter turbocharged petrol engine with an electric motor for a total system output of 326 horsepower and 500 Nm of torque. This hybrid setup allows the car to accelerate from 0 to 100 km/h in just 5.4 seconds, with a top speed electronically limited to 250 km/h. Its battery offers an all-electric range of 44-48 km, making it ideal for short commutes in electric mode. The 740e also boasts a spacious interior with advanced luxury features and is known for its smooth ride quality.

name: Audi Q3
description: The first-generation Audi Q3, produced from 2011 to 2018, is a compact luxury SUV that blends Audi's signature style with practicality and versatility. It features a sleek, sporty design, highlighted by a bold front grille, sharp headlights, and a compact yet muscular profile. Inside, the Q3 offers a premium cabin with high-quality materials, comfortable seating, and a user-friendly infotainment system, delivering the refined feel expected from Audi. Despite its compact size, it provides ample space for passengers and cargo, making it suitable for urban driving and longer journeys. The Q3 is also known for its smooth handling, efficient engines, and available all-wheel drive, ensuring a balanced driving experience that combines comfort with agility. Overall, the first-generation Audi Q3 offers a solid mix of luxury, performance, and practicality in a compact SUV package.

name: Toyota Rav4
description: The 2019 Toyota RAV4 marked the debut of its fifth generation, showcasing a complete redesign with a bold, rugged exterior inspired by Toyota's off-road vehicles. Built on the Toyota New Global Architecture (TNGA) platform, it offers improved driving dynamics, a stiffer chassis, and enhanced fuel efficiency. The 2019 RAV4 features a spacious and well-appointed interior with advanced technology, including Toyota’s Entune infotainment system and standard safety features under Toyota Safety Sense 2.0, such as adaptive cruise control and lane-keeping assist. With its versatile design and strong reputation for reliability, the 2019 RAV4 remains a top choice in the compact SUV segment.

name: Mazda CX3
description: XDL trim of the Mazda CX-3 stands out with a unique blend of sportiness and sophistication, aimed at drivers who want both style and substance. This trim level enhances the CX-3’s already sleek, compact SUV design with premium touches and additional features. The XDL offers upgraded interior materials, creating a more refined cabin experience, while its advanced infotainment system keeps drivers connected on the go. Known for its agile handling and fuel efficiency, the CX-3 XDL provides a smooth and engaging drive, ideal for urban commutes and weekend adventures alike.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: Sunroof in the Subaru Forester XT adds a touch of luxury and enhances the driving experience, allowing for natural light and fresh air to fill the cabin. This sporty version of the second-generation Forester is equipped with turbocharged performance, Subaru’s Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, and rugged practicality, making it versatile for both urban and off-road adventures. Its compact SUV design offers a spacious interior, with the sunroof adding an airy feel, and folding rear seats increase cargo flexibility. Combining performance, safety, and comfort, the 2008 Forester XT with a sunroof remains a popular choice for drivers seeking an engaging and functional compact SUV.

name: Mazda Demio
description: Mazda Demio is a very reliable and excellently performing car with the 1.5L turbo diesel engine giving sufficient power to carry up to 5 individuals and some cargo at the back. The seats have the heating functionality which is also a plus for the comfort aspect. It has a beautiful interior which gives it a different look from the traditional Demio.

name: Mazda CX3
description: XDL trim of the Mazda CX-3 stands out with a unique blend of sportiness and sophistication, aimed at drivers who want both style and substance. This trim level enhances the CX-3’s already sleek, compact SUV design with premium touches and additional features. The XDL offers upgraded interior materials, creating a more refined cabin experience, while its advanced infotainment system keeps drivers connected on the go. Known for its agile handling and fuel efficiency, the CX-3 XDL provides a smooth and engaging drive, ideal for urban commutes and weekend adventures alike.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado
description: TZ-G is the top-tier variant of the Toyota Land Cruiser Prado J151, known for its luxurious features and advanced off-road capabilities. This model combines ruggedness with elegance, showcasing a bold exterior with a distinctive grille and robust body lines. Inside, the TZ-G boasts high-quality materials, spacious seating, and a range of comfort and convenience features, including premium upholstery and advanced infotainment options. Its powerful engine, paired with a sophisticated four-wheel-drive system, ensures impressive performance both on and off the road, making it ideal for adventurous trips or daily driving. With an emphasis on safety and technology, the TZ-G variant includes numerous driver-assistance features, providing peace of mind for occupants. Overall, the Toyota Land Cruiser Prado J151 TZ-G is a perfect blend of luxury, capability, and reliability, appealing to those seeking a versatile SUV for various driving conditions.

name: Toyota Allion
description: The Toyota Allion is a compact sedan known for its sleek design, comfort, and reliability. It offers a balanced mix of practicality and style, making it ideal for both city driving and longer journeys. The interior is well-designed with ample space, comfortable seating, and intuitive controls. The Allion also features modern safety and infotainment systems, providing a dependable and comfortable driving experience for everyday use.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: The 2003 Subaru Forester XT is a sporty variant of the second-generation Forester, blending the utility of a compact SUV with the performance characteristics of a turbocharged vehicle. It features a robust design with all-wheel drive as standard, providing excellent handling and traction across various terrains. The Forester XT is notable for its turbocharged engine, which delivers strong acceleration and makes it one of the more performance-oriented options in its class during that era. Inside, the Forester XT offers a practical and comfortable cabin, with ample space for passengers and cargo, making it suitable for both daily commuting and adventurous trips. Its combination of rugged capability, sporty performance, and practicality made it a popular choice for drivers seeking a versatile and engaging compact SUV.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI
description: The Volkswagen Golf is a compact hatchback known for its refined design, high-quality build, and versatile performance. It offers a spacious and well-crafted interior, blending practicality with modern technology and comfort. The Golf is praised for its responsive handling, making it enjoyable to drive in both city and highway conditions. Available in various trims and engine options, it caters to a wide range of drivers, from those seeking efficiency to enthusiasts looking for sportier performance. With its solid reputation for reliability, safety features, and a premium feel, the Volkswagen Golf remains one of the most popular compact cars globally.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TX
description: TX models of the Toyota Prado offer a blend of rugged off-road capability and family-friendly features. Designed for versatility, the TX variant maintains the Prado’s renowned durability while providing a spacious and comfortable interior that can accommodate up to seven passengers. The cabin is equipped with essential modern conveniences, including a touchscreen infotainment system and multi-zone climate control, ensuring a pleasant driving experience. With advanced safety features such as stability control and hill-start assist, the TX model is as safe as it is practical. Whether for daily commutes or adventurous road trips, the Prado TX stands out as a reliable and capable SUV.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The third-generation Mercedes-Benz C-Class (W204), produced from 2007 to 2014, is a luxury compact sedan that combines elegant design with sporty performance. It features a refined, muscular exterior with a bold front grille and a more dynamic stance. Inside, the cabin offers premium materials, comfortable seating, and advanced technology, including a user-friendly infotainment system and various driver assistance features. Known for its smooth ride and precise handling, the W204 offers a range of engine options focused on both performance and fuel efficiency, with the available 4MATIC all-wheel-drive system enhancing traction. This generation balances luxury, comfort, and performance, appealing to both everyday drivers and enthusiasts alike.

name: Subaru XV
description: The Subaru XV is a compact crossover that blends rugged off-road capability with urban practicality. Known for its standard all-wheel-drive system and higher ground clearance, the XV is well-suited for a variety of terrains, making it a favorite for outdoor enthusiasts. Its compact size ensures easy maneuverability in city driving, while the spacious interior provides comfort for passengers and cargo alike. Equipped with Subaru’s EyeSight safety suite and advanced infotainment features, the XV offers a balance of modern technology and safety. With its reliable performance and versatility, the Subaru XV is an ideal choice for those seeking adventure without sacrificing everyday usability.

name: Mercedes Benz E200
description: Experience the luxuries of the E200. Wide display screen which displays the instrument cluster and the infotainment system and the Co-driver's seat controls from the driver's side is among the highlights of the E-Class experienced in the S-Class. You also get other premium features like powered multi-way adjustable seats, three-position memory seats for the front occupants, dual zone climate controls, leather bucket-styled front seats, and voice commands among other specs make up these marque.

name: Nissan Note
description: The Nissan Note is a compact hatchback that combines practicality with modern features, making it ideal for city driving. Its design emphasizes spaciousness and efficiency, with a roomy interior that comfortably accommodates passengers despite its compact size

name: Volkswagen Polo
description: The Volkswagen Polo is a compact hatchback admired for its blend of style, practicality, and German engineering quality. Known for its compact yet spacious design, it offers a comfortable interior with advanced tech features that are typically found in larger, more premium vehicles. The Polo is highly maneuverable, making it an excellent choice for city driving, while still providing stability and comfort for longer journeys. Volkswagen has equipped the Polo with efficient engines, making it economical on fuel while delivering a smooth, responsive driving experience. Its understated yet refined look, coupled with a focus on safety and reliability, makes the Volkswagen Polo a popular choice among drivers seeking a versatile, stylish, and economical small car.

name: Audi Q5
description: S line on the 2018 Audi Q5 adds a distinctive, sport-oriented flair to Audi's luxury compact SUV. This package enhances the Q5's appearance with exclusive exterior features like unique bumpers, S line badging, and stylish alloy wheels that emphasize a bolder, athletic look. Inside, the S line includes premium upgrades such as sport seats in leather and Alcantara, a multifunction S line steering wheel, and brushed aluminum inlays, creating a refined, driver-centric atmosphere. Paired with Audi’s quattro all-wheel-drive system, the Q5 S line blends luxury with a dynamic driving experience, appealing to those seeking both performance and sophistication in a compact SUV.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI
description: The MK7 Volkswagen Golf TSI combines sleek design with turbocharged efficiency, offering a refined yet practical driving experience. Its clean exterior lines, wide grille, and sharp headlights give it a modern and timeless look. Inside, the cabin is spacious and well-appointed with high-quality materials and intuitive controls. The turbocharged TSI engine provides a responsive and efficient performance, making it suitable for both city driving and longer trips. With its balanced handling, comfortable ride, and impressive fuel economy, the MK7 Golf TSI is a versatile compact hatchback that blends style, practicality, and performance.

name: Suzuki Alto
description: They Call it the perfect Urban car, Suzuki Alto is among the top cars in the top lists of highly fuel economical cars with tops of 20Kms a liter. Quite an Easy and reliable car!

name: Suzuki Swift
description: The Suzuki Swift RS is a sporty, enhanced version of the popular Swift hatchback, known for adding a blend of performance-focused features and refined styling. While retaining the Swift’s compact size and fuel efficiency, the RS variant typically showcases unique design elements, such as distinctive alloy wheels, a bold front grille, and other sporty accents. Inside, it offers upgraded materials and extra tech features, adding to driver comfort and convenience. The Swift RS is designed with slightly tuned suspension, enhancing handling and stability for a more agile drive. This model appeals to those seeking the practicality of the Swift with added style and a sportier, more dynamic driving experience.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The e-Boxer version of the Subaru Forester is a hybrid SUV that combines a 2.0-liter petrol engine with an electric motor for enhanced fuel efficiency and lower emissions. This hybrid system integrates seamlessly with Subaru’s signature Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, delivering the Forester's characteristic stability and off-road capability while being more eco-friendly. The e-Boxer model offers the same spacious and versatile interior as the standard Forester, along with advanced safety features and modern technology. It’s a great choice for those who want the reliability and ruggedness of the Forester, paired with the benefits of hybrid efficiency.

name: Honda N Box
description: The Honda N-Box is a compact, boxy kei car introduced in 2011, designed to offer maximum interior space and functionality within a small footprint. Its tall, squared design allows for a surprisingly roomy cabin, with ample headroom and legroom, making it comfortable for both drivers and passengers despite its small exterior. The N-Box is ideal for city driving, featuring a fuel-efficient engine and easy maneuverability, along with sliding rear doors that facilitate entry and exit, even in tight spaces. Honda has equipped recent models with advanced technology and safety features, such as the Honda Sensing suite, which includes adaptive cruise control and lane-keeping assistance. The N-Box is popular in Japan for its efficiency, practicality, and user-friendly design, making it a top choice for urban drivers seeking a versatile and economical vehicle.

name: Subaru Pleo
description: The Subaru Pleo is a compact, practical car introduced in 1998, designed to offer excellent maneuverability and fuel efficiency for urban driving. With its tall, boxy shape, the Pleo maximizes interior space, allowing for a surprisingly roomy cabin given its small exterior footprint. Often classified as a kei car, it is popular in Japan for its compact size, which benefits from tax and insurance incentives. The Pleo typically comes with a small, fuel-efficient engine and, in some models, Subaru’s all-wheel-drive (AWD) system, providing added stability in varying road conditions. Known for its affordability and ease of handling, the Pleo appeals to city dwellers looking for a budget-friendly, versatile vehicle.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado
description: TX models of the Toyota Prado offer a blend of rugged off-road capability and family-friendly features. Designed for versatility, the TX variant maintains the Prado’s renowned durability while providing a spacious and comfortable interior that can accommodate up to seven passengers. The cabin is equipped with essential modern conveniences, including a touchscreen infotainment system and multi-zone climate control, ensuring a pleasant driving experience. With advanced safety features such as stability control and hill-start assist, the TX model is as safe as it is practical. Whether for daily commutes or adventurous road trips, the Prado TX stands out as a reliable and capable SUV.

name: BMW X3
description: BMW X3 is based on the BMW 5 Series and classified as a Sports Activity Vehicle. This is where luxury has been fully invested by BMW. The reason BMW has fitted a lot of equipments on the X3 ranging from hill descent control, front & rear camera view, Autohold brake function, electric parking brake, Front heated seats, parking sensors, radar guided adaptive cruise control, ECO Pro modes, powered memory seats, to the multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Range Rover Sport
description: The first-generation Range Rover Sport, produced from 2005 to 2013, was designed to offer a more dynamic, performance-oriented option within the Range Rover lineup. It featured a sleek, modern design with a sloping roofline, giving it a sportier appearance compared to the traditional Range Rover. The Range Rover Sport was built on the same platform as the Land Rover Discovery 3, blending off-road capability with on-road handling. It came equipped with the brand's Terrain Response system, allowing the vehicle to adjust to various terrains, from rugged trails to city streets. Inside, the Sport offered a luxurious, high-tech cabin with premium materials and modern infotainment options, ensuring both comfort and convenience for passengers. The first-generation Range Rover Sport was highly regarded for its mix of luxury, performance, and off-road capability, making it a popular choice for those seeking a versatile and sophisticated SUV.

name: Subaru Impreza
description: The Subaru Impreza is a compact car known for its practical design, and solid performance. It offers a spacious interior and a comfortable ride. With its blend of power and fuel efficiency, the Impreza delivers a balanced driving experience. Modern features include a user-friendly infotainment system, advanced safety technologies, and a well-designed cabin. The Impreza stands out for its reliability and versatility, making it a strong choice for those seeking a dependable and capable compact vehicle.

name: Mercedes Benz B180
description: The Mercedes-Benz B180 is part of the B-Class lineup, which combines a compact design with the luxury and precision engineering that Mercedes-Benz is known for. It offers a unique balance between the practicality of a hatchback and the premium features typically found in larger models. The B180 is powered by an efficient engine, making it a good choice for urban driving and long-distance comfort. Inside, the B180 features a high-tech cabin with modern infotainment systems, plush materials, and ample cargo space, emphasizing a user-friendly experience. It's often appreciated for its blend of driving dynamics, comfort, and versatility, making it an appealing choice for those seeking a luxury compact car with plenty of room and functionality.

name: Toyota Hilux
description: The Toyota Hilux is a durable, high-performance pickup truck renowned for its rugged build quality, off-road capability, and reliability in demanding conditions. First introduced in 1968, the Hilux has evolved through multiple generations to become a popular choice worldwide for both personal and commercial use. Its design prioritizes robustness, featuring a high ground clearance, solid chassis, and dependable suspension, which make it ideal for rough terrains and challenging weather conditions.

name: Nissan Serena
description: The Nissan Serena is a highly practical multi-purpose vehicle (MPV) tailored for families, featuring a spacious interior and versatile seating that adapts to various needs. Its sliding doors facilitate easy access, while the flexible seating arrangement allows for multiple configurations, maximizing comfort for both passengers and cargo. Modern Serena models are equipped with Nissan’s ProPILOT technology, a semi-autonomous driving system designed to assist with highway driving, enhancing safety and ease on long trips. The Serena is available with a choice of hybrid or traditional gasoline powertrains, providing options for those focused on fuel efficiency. Known for its combination of practicality, advanced safety features, and family-friendly design, the Nissan Serena remains a popular choice for those seeking a reliable and adaptable vehicle.

name: Audi A6
description: The Audi A6 C7 (2011-2018) is a well-regarded fourth-generation executive sedan that combines luxury, technology, and performance. Known for its refined, modern design, the C7 A6 features a sharp exterior with Audi’s iconic grille, LED lighting, and a sleek, aerodynamic profile. Inside, it offers a high-end, tech-rich cabin, with available options like the MMI infotainment system, premium materials, and the Audi Virtual Cockpit in later models, creating a sophisticated driving environment. The A6 C7 comes with a variety of engine options, delivering a smooth, responsive drive with available quattro all-wheel drive on select models. Advanced safety features, including adaptive cruise control and lane-keeping assist, make it both a comfortable and secure choice, appealing to those seeking an elegant yet dynamic luxury sedan.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The Mazda CX-5 is a stylish and well-rounded compact SUV known for its sharp handling, elegant design, and high-quality interior. It combines Mazda's signature sporty driving dynamics with the practicality and versatility of an SUV, making it a popular choice for families and individuals alike. The CX-5 offers a comfortable and well-appointed cabin with modern technology and safety features, ensuring a pleasant and secure driving experience. Its sleek, aerodynamic design gives it a dynamic appearance, while the efficient engines provide a balance of performance and fuel economy. The Mazda CX-5 is an excellent option for those seeking a compact SUV that delivers both style and substance.

name: Toyota Vitz
description: Toyota used the Vitz nameplate majorly for the Japanese market and the Yaris for international markets. As a direct consumer of the Japanese market, we got the Vitz nameplate. It has been a very popular car in a lot of markets achieving over 3.5 Million sales in excess of the projected number in over 70 countries. It still continues to be among the top selling hatchbacks by the Japanese Manufacturer.

name: Nissan Tiida
description: The Nissan Tiida is a compact car known for its practicality, spacious interior, and fuel efficiency. Available in both sedan and hatchback body styles, the Tiida offers ample legroom and cargo space for its class, making it a comfortable option for daily commuting and small families. The car is equipped with modern features like air conditioning, a basic infotainment system, and essential safety technologies. Its smooth ride and easy handling make it well-suited for city driving, while its reliability and low running costs add to its appeal. The Nissan Tiida is a sensible choice for those seeking an affordable, no-frills compact car.

name: Audi A3
description: The A3 Sportback is specced with a 1.4L Turbocharged Petrol Engine driving the front wheels, Audi MMI infotainment system, Multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, and rear mounted spoiler.

name: Suzuki Swift
description: The Swift is a proper hatch that has been widely loved by a lot of enthusiasts. It is preferred for its well consuming engine, comfortable rides, and easy stretch on maintenance to the pockets.

name: Toyota Premio
description: The Toyota Premio G is a refined variant of Toyota’s Premio sedan, offering a blend of luxury, comfort, and reliability ideal for daily use. As an upgraded trim level, the Premio G often includes premium features such as wood accents, advanced infotainment options, and additional safety technologies, enhancing the driving experience compared to base models. Known for its smooth handling and a spacious, well-designed interior, the Premio G provides a comfortable ride for both driver and passengers. This model’s understated elegance and Toyota's renowned build quality make it a popular choice for those seeking a practical yet stylish sedan for urban and longer-distance driving.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado
description: The Toyota Prado is a mid-size SUV known for its strong off-road capabilities and refined on-road manners. It’s part of the Land Cruiser family, offering a blend of rugged durability and modern comfort. The Prado features a robust body-on-frame construction, advanced four-wheel-drive systems, and a range of powerful engines, typically including diesel and petrol options, making it well-suited for challenging terrains and long-distance driving. Inside, the Prado provides a spacious and well-appointed cabin with seating for up to seven passengers, advanced safety technologies, and modern infotainment features, making it a versatile choice for both family use and adventurous expeditions.

name: Mercedes Benz E220d
description: The Mercedes-Benz E220d, part of the E-Class lineup from 2009 to 2016, is a diesel luxury sedan known for its refined design, spacious interior, and advanced safety features. With a 2.1-liter, four-cylinder diesel engine, it achieves impressive fuel efficiency, typically around 20 km/l depending on driving conditions. The W212 generation brought a modern, angular exterior design and included innovative safety technologies such as Attention Assist and Pre-Safe, enhancing occupant protection and driver awareness. Inside, the E220d offers a high-quality cabin with premium materials, designed to provide comfort and luxury for both drivers and passengers. The E220d's combination of efficiency, safety, and elegance has made it a popular choice among luxury sedan enthusiasts.

name: BMW 320i
description: The BMW E90 is the fifth-generation BMW 3 Series sedan, produced from 2005 to 2013, and is known for its sharp handling, balanced design, and quality interior. This generation introduced a more modern, sportier look with distinct body styles: the E90 sedan, E91 wagon, E92 coupe, and E93 convertible. The E90 featured a range of powerful and efficient engines, including turbocharged options and, in the high-performance M3 version, a V8 engine—a unique offering in the M3 lineup. The interior was well-crafted, with BMW’s iDrive infotainment available on higher trims, giving drivers a tech-focused and premium experience. The E90 remains popular among enthusiasts for its engaging driving dynamics and solid engineering, embodying BMW’s reputation for performance-oriented luxury.

name: Subaru Legacy
description: The 4th generation Subaru Legacy (2009-2014) features a more refined design with a modern look and improved interior quality. This generation emphasized Subaru’s signature symmetrical all-wheel drive system, offering stability and traction in various driving conditions. It also introduced a spacious cabin with upgraded materials and advanced technology for improved comfort and usability. The Legacy included enhanced safety features, including standard all-wheel drive, contributing to its reputation as a reliable and practical choice for families and commuters. It competes well with other mid-size sedans like the Honda Accord and Toyota Camry, offering a solid balance of practicality and performance.

name: Toyota Rav4
description: The second-generation Toyota RAV4 (2000-2005) added space, style, and power, making it a stronger competitor in the compact SUV market. With a slightly larger, more rugged body and a facelift in 2004, it featured a bolder look with redesigned headlights and grille. Powered by a four-cylinder engine, it offered a balance of efficiency and versatility for both urban and light off-road driving. The interior was practical, with a foldable rear bench to expand cargo space, and safety was enhanced with anti-lock brakes and optional side airbags. Available in front-wheel and all-wheel drive, this generation maintained the RAV4’s reputation for reliability and adaptability, appealing to those seeking a compact, dependable SUV.

name: Audi A6
description: The Audi A6 is a luxury mid-size sedan that combines elegant design, advanced technology, and strong performance. Known for its smooth and refined ride, the A6 features a range of turbocharged engines and an option for Audi’s quattro all-wheel drive, enhancing handling and stability. Inside, it has a spacious, high-end cabin with dual touchscreens and Audi’s Virtual Cockpit, giving it a tech-forward feel. Competing with models like the BMW 5 Series, the A6 stands out for its premium materials, sophisticated infotainment, and extensive safety features, making it a top choice among luxury sedans.

name: Toyota Vitz
description: The 2017 Toyota Vitz facelift brought some notable updates to this popular compact hatchback, enhancing both its style and technology. Visually, the facelift included a refreshed front fascia with a larger grille and sleeker headlights, giving it a more modern, aggressive look. The interior received quality upgrades as well, with improved materials and an updated infotainment system, making it more comfortable and user-friendly. In terms of safety, Toyota added features like Vehicle Stability Control (VSC) and Traction Control (TRC) to improve handling and stability, particularly in challenging road conditions. Some versions also included the option for Toyota Safety Sense C, which offers pre-collision warning, lane departure alert, and automatic high beams. The 2017 facelift maintained the Vitz’s reputation for reliability and fuel efficiency, appealing to drivers looking for an economical, city-friendly car with modern features.

name: Subaru Legacy
description: The Subaru Legacy station wagon is a rare blend of performance, practicality, and all-weather capability, making it highly sought after among enthusiasts and adventurers alike. Unlike typical wagons, the Legacy features Subaru’s iconic symmetrical all-wheel-drive system, giving it exceptional handling and stability, even in challenging conditions. Certain rare models come with unique features like a twin-turbocharged engine, offering a level of power usually reserved for performance sedans. The spacious interior and versatile cargo area make it perfect for families or outdoor enthusiasts, with ample room for gear, bikes, or skis. A true rarity on the roads, the Legacy wagon combines the ruggedness of a Subaru with the style and versatility of a station wagon, appealing to those who value both function and form.

name: Nissan March
description: This Nissan March features a bold, custom bright red leather interior, giving the compact car a vibrant and sporty look. The seats are covered in two-tone leather, with a mix of bright red and darker maroon accents, adding a unique flair to the cabin. This striking color scheme enhances the visual appeal and gives the interior a more premium feel, setting it apart from standard upholstery options. This custom interior not only adds style but also provides a more comfortable and durable seating surface, making the Nissan March a stylish and eye-catching choice for urban driving.

name: Nissan Note
description: The Nissan Note e-Power is a compact hatchback that features an innovative hybrid powertrain, designed for efficiency and smooth driving. Unlike traditional hybrids, the e-Power system uses a gasoline engine solely to generate electricity, while an electric motor drives the wheels. This setup provides the feel of an electric car with the convenience of gasoline refueling. The Note e-Power offers quick acceleration, responsive handling, and impressive fuel economy, making it ideal for city driving. Inside, it’s equipped with a modern, spacious cabin, intuitive infotainment, and advanced safety features, delivering both practicality and a pleasant driving experience.

name: BMW X1
description: The X1 F48 series that came in is based on the Modular front-wheel drive based UKL2 platform that is used with BMW and MINI models, a modular meant to increase interior space and boot space in smaller size model cars. They are both available in front wheel and All Wheel drive systems with the front adopting the SDrive naming and the All Wheel adopting XDrive naming.

name: Renault Megane
description: The Renault Megane is a compact car that combines European style, advanced technology, and versatile performance. Available in various body styles, including hatchback, sedan, and estate, the Megane appeals to a wide range of drivers. Its exterior design features sleek lines, a distinctive front grille, and Renault’s signature C-shaped LED headlights, giving it a modern and elegant look. Inside, the Megane offers a well-designed cabin with quality materials, comfortable seating, and an intuitive infotainment system. Equipped with a range of efficient engines, including petrol, diesel, and hybrid options in recent models, the Megane balances power with fuel economy. Advanced safety features and driver assistance systems make it a reliable choice for both city and highway driving, appealing to those who seek a stylish yet practical compact car.

name: Honda Fit
description: The Mugen-kitted Honda Fit Hybrid combines the fuel efficiency and practicality of the Fit Hybrid with sporty aesthetics and unique styling elements from Mugen, Honda’s performance division. The Mugen kit enhances the car's appearance with a bold front bumper, side skirts, a rear spoiler, and exclusive Mugen badging, giving it a more dynamic and aggressive look. Additional features like custom alloy wheels and a sport exhaust further add to its visual appeal. This version of the Fit Hybrid is perfect for drivers who want an economical, eco-friendly vehicle with a distinct, performance-inspired design that stands out on the road.

name: Ashok Leyland Partner
description: The Ashok Leyland Partner is a versatile light commercial truck designed for urban and rural transport needs. It features a modern cab-forward design, providing better visibility and maneuverability, ideal for navigating tight spaces. Powered by a fuel-efficient diesel engine, the Partner offers a balance of power and economy, making it suitable for a range of applications like goods delivery, logistics, and specialized modifications. The truck includes a spacious, comfortable cabin with ergonomic seating and essential features for driver convenience. Known for its durability and low maintenance costs, the Ashok Leyland Partner is a popular choice for businesses seeking reliability in light commercial transportation.

name: Audi Q5
description: The 2018 Audi Q5 is a luxury compact SUV that combines sleek design, advanced technology, and dynamic performance. Its premium interior features high-quality materials, comfortable seating, and cutting-edge systems like the Audi Virtual Cockpit and intuitive MMI infotainment. Equipped with a turbocharged engine and Audi’s renowned Quattro all-wheel-drive system, the Q5 delivers a smooth and responsive driving experience with excellent traction, whether on city streets or rougher terrains. Offering a balance of sporty handling, comfort, and a suite of driver-assistance features, the 2018 Q5 is a versatile and refined choice for modern drivers.
