name: Mazda Axela
description: XDL is the top-tier trim of the Mazda Axela, also known as the Mazda3 in many markets. The Axela XDL stands out with its stylish design, premium features, and refined performance. The exterior features sleek lines, a bold front grille, and sporty detailing, giving it a dynamic presence on the road. Inside, the cabin is equipped with high-quality materials, offering comfort and convenience with features such as a touchscreen infotainment system, leather upholstery, and advanced safety technologies. The XDL trim typically comes with a more powerful engine, providing a smooth and responsive driving experience, while the overall design focuses on both practicality and luxury. The Axela XDL is an ideal choice for those seeking a compact car with a sophisticated edge.

name: BMW 750i
description: The BMW 750i is a luxurious sedan that combines refined elegance with cutting-edge technology. Its sleek, bold exterior design is matched by a plush interior, featuring high-quality materials, advanced infotainment, and a range of premium amenities for ultimate comfort. The cabin is spacious, offering luxurious seating and a quiet, serene environment. Equipped with state-of-the-art safety features and driver assistance systems, the 750i prioritizes convenience and security, providing a sophisticated, smooth driving experience. It's an ideal choice for those seeking luxury, comfort, and modern technology in a premium vehicle.

name: Lexus RX270
description: The Lexus RX270 is a luxury crossover SUV that blends style, comfort, and practicality. Featuring a sleek, aerodynamic exterior design with a prominent front grille and refined lines, the RX270 exudes sophistication. Inside, the cabin offers a high level of luxury, with premium materials, comfortable seating, and a user-friendly infotainment system. The RX270 is powered by a 2.7-liter engine, providing a smooth and efficient driving experience. Its spacious interior ensures ample room for passengers and luggage, while advanced safety features and Lexus' signature attention to detail make it an ideal choice for those seeking a blend of performance and luxury in their everyday drive.

name: Subaru Forester
description: Panoramic sunroof features prominently in the Subaru SJ5, offering an expansive, open-air driving experience. The SJ5, a versatile SUV, combines rugged performance with refined design, making it suitable for both urban and off-road adventures. Its exterior is sleek, with sharp lines and a distinctive front grille, while the interior is designed for comfort, with ample seating and premium materials. Equipped with advanced safety features and technology, the SJ5 provides a smooth, responsive drive, whether navigating city streets or tackling more challenging terrain. The panoramic sunroof enhances the feeling of openness and connection to the environment, making each drive more enjoyable.

name: Honda Insight
description: The Honda Insight is a sleek, hybrid sedan that combines fuel efficiency with modern style and a comfortable ride. Designed with a low-profile, aerodynamic body, the Insight stands out for its smooth lines and sophisticated look, offering an appealing alternative to traditional hybrids. Inside, it features a well-appointed cabin with quality materials, intuitive technology, and spacious seating, creating a comfortable environment for both driver and passengers. Honda’s hybrid system allows the Insight to deliver excellent fuel economy without compromising on performance, making it ideal for both city commutes and highway drives. Known for its reliability and eco-friendly engineering, the Honda Insight is a smart choice for drivers who want an efficient, stylish, and practical car with a touch of Honda’s signature innovation.

name: Nissan Note
description: The NISMO-spec Nissan Note takes the practical, everyday functionality of the standard Note and infuses it with a sporty, performance-focused edge. With aggressive styling elements, including a more aerodynamic body kit, sporty front bumper, and signature NISMO red accents, this variant stands out with a bold, athletic look. Enhanced suspension tuning and a recalibrated steering system provide sharper handling, making it not just a stylish upgrade but also more dynamic to drive. Inside, the NISMO version of the Note features sporty seats, unique trims, and a cockpit designed to enhance the driving experience. Ideal for those who seek a balance between practicality and a thrill on the road, the Nissan Note NISMO adds spirited performance to the everyday hatchback.

name: Nissan March
description: The Nissan March is a compact car that shines with its blend of practicality and personality, making it ideal for city living. Despite its small footprint, the March maximizes interior space, offering a surprisingly roomy cabin with thoughtfully designed storage and comfortable seating. Its compact size allows for easy parking and maneuverability, while its efficient engine keeps fuel costs low without sacrificing a peppy driving experience. The March’s sleek curves and stylish touches bring a sense of fun and individuality to a car that’s practical at heart. Known for its reliability and ease of maintenance, the Nissan March is a dependable and agile companion for navigating busy urban environments.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: The Toyota Harrier is a refined crossover that combines luxury with everyday practicality, making it a standout choice for those who value both style and functionality. Its sleek, sophisticated design exudes an upscale feel, while the spacious, comfortable interior is crafted with high-quality materials and intuitive technology. With smooth handling and a quiet ride, the Harrier is well-suited for urban commutes and long-distance travel alike. It also offers ample cargo space and a flexible rear seating arrangement, accommodating a variety of lifestyles, from family outings to weekend getaways. Built with Toyota’s reputation for reliability, the Harrier delivers a premium experience without compromising on durability and everyday usability.

name: Nissan NV200
description: The Nissan NV200 stands out as a smartly designed urban van, built to tackle city life with a compact footprint and impressive interior space. Its streamlined body may look modest, but inside it boasts a surprisingly spacious and flexible layout, with room for cargo or passengers in a highly adaptable cabin. Known for its ease of handling, the NV200 maneuvers through city streets and tight spots effortlessly. Features like wide-opening sliding doors and a low step-in height make loading hassle-free, while its efficient design focuses on keeping operating costs low. Perfect for small businesses, families, or adventurers, the NV200 delivers practicality without the bulk, making it an understated yet highly capable choice for versatile needs.

name: Toyota CHR
description: The Toyota C-HR is a compact crossover that breaks away from traditional SUV styling with its bold, edgy design and coupe-like profile. Designed for urban adventures, it combines the elevated ride height and practicality of an SUV with the agility and compact size of a city-friendly vehicle. Inside, the C-HR offers a driver-focused cockpit with modern technology and comfort features, making it both stylish and functional. With a focus on fuel efficiency, responsive handling, and advanced safety systems, the C-HR appeals to those who want a head-turning, efficient, and versatile ride suited for both city streets and beyond.

name: Nissan Wingroad
description: The Nissan Wingroad is a masterclass in practical design and versatility, tailored for those who live a dynamic lifestyle. Unlike typical wagons, the Wingroad combines a sleek, streamlined body with surprising cargo space, making it perfect for urban adventures and weekend getaways alike. Its compact dimensions make it agile and easy to maneuver, while its adaptable rear seat configurations offer unmatched storage flexibility for everything from sporting gear to groceries. With an emphasis on fuel efficiency and reliable performance, the Wingroad doesn’t just get you from point A to B—it does so with understated style and dependable ease. This is the ultimate choice for individuals who want a vehicle that’s as adaptable as they are, without compromising on comfort or utility.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The Mazda CX-5 is a compact crossover SUV that stands out for its stylish design and engaging driving experience. It features Mazda's distinctive "KODO: Soul of Motion" design language, which gives it a sleek and modern look. Inside, the cabin is well-designed with high-quality materials, comfortable seating, and an intuitive infotainment system.

name: Honda Jade
description: Honda Jade is a compact MPV first produced in 2013 mainly for the Chinese Market but has since penetrated other markets including the Japanese in 2015. It is a 5 door wagon with configurations of 5 or 4+2 individuals. Quite spacious and classy, and turns out to be a good consumer as well.

name: Jeep Grand Cherokee
description: The American Marque categorised in the mid-size SUV produced since 2010 to 2022. At the unveiling moment in New York's Auto Show, it received 30 awards. The Grand Cherokee 'BLACKHAWK' has definitely outperformed itself in all its years of production. It is a serious offroader and doubles up well as a presentable urban driving car. It features a four-wheel independent suspension which improves road handling. The engine option in this car is the 3.6L Pentastar V6 Petrol version with a power rating of 290hp. On the interior are comfy half leather seats, a premium surround sound system, a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, and a 4WD drive select system.

name: Audi Q7
description:

description: The Mercedes-Benz C230 W203, produced between 2000 and 2007, is a compact luxury sedan that balances performance, style, and comfort. This model is part of the second generation of the C-Class and features a refined design with sleek lines and a classy, understated look. Known for its solid build quality, the C230 offers a comfortable and well-appointed interior, with premium materials and ergonomic controls typical of Mercedes-Benz. The handling is agile and responsive, making it enjoyable for both city and highway driving, while safety features like multiple airbags and stability control enhance its appeal. Overall, the C230 W203 remains a stylish and reliable choice, embodying Mercedes-Benz’s legacy of quality and performance.

name: Nissan Serena
description: The Nissan Serena is a versatile and spacious family minivan designed for comfort and practicality. Known for its boxy shape and roomy interior, the Serena offers generous seating for up to eight passengers, making it ideal for larger families or groups. Its sliding doors provide easy access in tight parking spaces, and the cabin is thoughtfully designed with ample storage compartments and a flexible seating arrangement. In recent models, the Serena is equipped with advanced safety features, an efficient engine, and a smooth driving experience, ensuring reliability and peace of mind for long journeys. The Serena combines practicality with modern convenience, delivering a family-friendly solution for everyday travel needs.

name: Mazda CX3
description: XDL trim of the Mazda CX-3 stands out with a unique blend of sportiness and sophistication, aimed at drivers who want both style and substance. This trim level enhances the CX-3’s already sleek, compact SUV design with premium touches and additional features. The XDL offers upgraded interior materials, creating a more refined cabin experience, while its advanced infotainment system keeps drivers connected on the go. Known for its agile handling and fuel efficiency, the CX-3 XDL provides a smooth and engaging drive, ideal for urban commutes and weekend adventures alike.

name: Nissan NV200
description: The Nissan NV200 is a unique blend of compact practicality and urban versatility, designed to tackle both city streets and business needs with ease. Unlike traditional vans, the NV200 combines an agile, car-like handling with the spacious interior and functionality of a commercial vehicle. Its compact dimensions make parking and maneuvering in tight spaces effortless, yet inside it boasts a surprisingly roomy cargo area, thoughtfully configured to maximize storage capacity. Its sliding side doors and low floor height make loading and unloading a breeze, while the driver-centric cockpit ensures a comfortable and efficient workspace. With a focus on durability and reliability, the NV200 offers an understated, hardworking appeal, standing out as a rare find in the world of compact vans, ideal for businesses and individuals who need a vehicle as flexible as their lifestyle.

name: Toyota Mark X
description: The Toyota Mark X GRX120, produced from 2004 to 2009, is a mid-size sedan known for its balance of performance, comfort, and luxury. Designed primarily for the Japanese market, it features rear-wheel drive (with some all-wheel-drive options) and a sporty design inspired by Toyota's aim to offer an enjoyable driving experience. With a focus on high-quality interiors, it includes premium materials, ample seating space, and tech features aimed at enhancing comfort and convenience. The GRX120 series stands out for its dynamic handling and smooth ride, making it popular among drivers seeking a refined yet engaging sedan.

name: Mazda Axela
description: Mazda Axela offers a very good balance of efficiency, flexibility, and performance. Giving very efficient fuel consumptions and effective maintenance costs, flexible use scenarios in all kinds of environments, and good performance output.

name: Nissan Sunny
description: Nissan Sunny has its last gen, B15, that has been produced for about 40 years. The 2002 model was the 2nd last year of production as the production of the C11 Nissan Tiida and G11 BlueBird replaced the Sunny. This is a very clean unit with its internals, externals, and the engine being in optimal states.

name: Landrover Discovery 4
description: The Land Rover Discovery IV (also known as the LR4 in some markets) is a luxury off-road SUV that combines rugged capability with refined comfort. Known for its robust build and exceptional off-road performance, the Discovery IV features a spacious interior with seating for up to seven passengers, making it ideal for families and adventurers alike. It comes equipped with advanced off-road technologies like Terrain Response, adjustable air suspension, and permanent four-wheel drive, ensuring it can tackle challenging terrains with ease. Inside, the Discovery IV offers a premium experience with high-quality materials, modern infotainment systems, and a versatile cargo area. Its blend of luxury and off-road prowess makes it a standout in the SUV market.

name: BMW 523d
description: Luxury defines the BMW G30 523d, a sophisticated and refined sedan that blends elegance with impressive performance. This model offers a smooth and composed ride, featuring high-quality materials throughout the cabin, including premium leather upholstery and polished wood accents that create a serene, upscale atmosphere. Advanced technology enhances the driving experience, with a user-friendly infotainment system, digital driver display, and cutting-edge safety features. The G30 523d's efficient diesel engine provides a balance of power and fuel economy, making it ideal for long-distance drives as well as city commutes. With its timeless design and luxurious appointments, the BMW 523d luxury edition stands out as a refined choice in the executive sedan category.

name: Audi A3
description: The A3 is definitely worth your money. A versatile engine, relatively spacious interior, a powerful 1.4L turbocharged petrol engine, minimalistic sufficiently useful cockpit, and a classy subcompact sedan. The A3 works magic for a budget of less than 2.5M.

name: Mitsubishi Outlander
description: The Outlander is an excellent SUV that delivers the best of what Mitsubishi intended to give its consumers ranging from economy to occupancy. It features a 7 seats occupancy that has foldable third row seats that extends the boot space when the third row is not occupied. It drives all the 4 wheels which gives it an edge over any offroad terrains. It also has an eco mode that optimises fuel consumption.

name: Mazda CX3
description: Mazda CX-3 began sales in 2016 in all the major markets it was sold including Canada. A lot of individuals have responded well to this entry into the market. It was produced in the age of modern technologies and designs making it a good looking car since the first generation as consumere don't have any other thought of how Mazda looked or previously performed which gives it an advantage of having a positive face in the automotive sector.

name: Ford Ranger
description: Wildtrack edition of this Ford Ranger takes off-road capability and style to the next level. This heavily modified version showcases an aggressive front bumper equipped with red tow hooks and reinforced for durability, making it ideal for rough terrain. The oversized all-terrain tires and custom black-and-red wheels enhance both traction and visual impact. A roof-mounted cargo rack and rugged side steps add utility for outdoor adventures, while the matte green paint and bold “FORD” grille lettering give it a commanding presence on the road. This Wildtrak is built to handle the toughest trails with ease, combining ruggedness and flair for serious off-road enthusiasts.

name: Toyota Rav4
description: The Adventure trim of the 2017 Toyota RAV4 adds rugged styling and enhanced capability to this popular compact SUV, making it an appealing option for those with an active lifestyle. This model includes distinctive exterior features like larger wheels, unique badging, and enhanced ground clearance, giving it a more aggressive, off-road-ready appearance. Inside, it combines practicality with comfort, offering a spacious interior, durable materials, and ample cargo space. Equipped with Toyota's reliable all-wheel-drive system, the RAV4 Adventure handles a range of terrains, from city streets to light off-road paths, with ease. This blend of style, functionality, and dependability makes the 2017 RAV4 Adventure a versatile choice for drivers looking to balance everyday driving with weekend getaways.

name: Toyota Rav4
description: The Toyota RAV4 basing from its powerful Naturally Aspirated 2.4L engine producing 160 horsepower and 220Nm of torque and roof rails, it can do a lot One can carry heavy cargo and travel for long distances and the RAV4 would still handle pretty well. Fabric seats steering wheel controls, climate controls, and an android infotainment display screen complete this very reliable unit.

name: Mazda Axela
description: The second-generation Mazda Axela (known as the Mazda3 in other markets), produced from 2009 to 2013, is a sporty compact car that combines Mazda's signature "Zoom-Zoom" driving dynamics with practicality and style. This generation introduced Mazda's "Nagare" design language, with sleek lines and a bold front grille, giving the Axela a distinctive, dynamic look. Inside, it features a driver-oriented cabin with intuitive controls, quality materials, and ample space, making it comfortable for both driver and passengers. The second-gen Axela also improved on fuel efficiency and handling, with a well-tuned suspension that provides a smooth yet responsive ride. This model gained popularity for its reliability, fun-to-drive character, and practicality, making it a strong choice for those who want a compact car with a bit of flair.

name: Mitsubishi Galant
description: The Mitsubishi Galant is a classic sedan that combines Mitsubishi's engineering expertise with a timeless design, offering a smooth, comfortable, and reliable driving experience. Known for its roomy interior and well-crafted cabin, the Galant provides both driver and passengers with a relaxing ride suited for longer journeys and daily commutes alike. Depending on the generation, it features a range of engines, balancing efficiency with a degree of power that makes it versatile for city and highway driving. With a reputation for durability, the Mitsubishi Galant has been a dependable choice across several generations, appealing to those who value comfort, straightforward design, and long-lasting performance in a midsize sedan.

description: The Mazda Demio, known as the Mazda2 in some markets, is a subcompact hatchback praised for its agile handling and stylish design. It offers a compact footprint that makes it ideal for city driving, yet provides a surprisingly spacious and well-appointed interior for its size. The Demio features a high-quality cabin with modern technology and user-friendly infotainment options. Its efficient engines deliver a good balance of performance and fuel economy, while its precise steering and dynamic handling contribute to an engaging driving experience. The Mazda Demio is appreciated for its blend of practicality, efficiency, and driving enjoyment in the subcompact segment.

name: Mazda Demio
description: The Mazda Demio is a compact hatchback known for its blend of style, efficiency, and practicality. It features a sleek, modern design with a surprisingly roomy interior for its size. The Demio offers comfortable seating, intuitive controls, and a well-organized dashboard. Its compact dimensions make it ideal for city driving, while its efficient engines provide great fuel economy. With user-friendly technology and Mazda’s signature sporty handling, the Demio delivers a smooth and enjoyable driving experience, making it a popular choice for those looking for an affordable yet refined small car.

name: Nissan Xtrail
description: The Nissan X-Trail is a compact SUV that blends practicality with a sleek design. It features a more streamlined look compared to earlier models, with a modern, aerodynamic exterior. Inside, the X-Trail offers a spacious cabin with flexible seating for up to seven passengers in some trims. It also comes with updated technology, including a touchscreen infotainment system and optional features like a panoramic sunroof and advanced safety systems. Known for its comfortable ride and practical layout, the X-Trail is a solid choice for families and daily drivers alike.

name: Peugeot 208
description: The Peugeot 208 is a chic and nimble hatchback that marries French flair with clever engineering, creating a car that feels as stylish as it is functional. Its design embodies fluid, sculpted lines and an athletic stance, making it look in motion even when parked. Step inside, and you’re welcomed by Peugeot’s futuristic i-Cockpit layout, where a compact steering wheel, high-set digital dash, and intuitive infotainment screen create an immersive, driver-centric experience. Beyond aesthetics, the 208 is surprisingly versatile, with ample interior space despite its compact form, and it’s built to handle city streets and open roads with equal finesse. It’s the quintessential car for those who value artistry in everyday life, blending practicality and personality in a way only Peugeot can deliver.

name: Nissan Note
description: The Nissan Note Nismo is a sporty, performance-oriented variant of the popular Nissan Note, designed with both agility and style in mind. Enhanced by Nissan’s Nismo division, the Note Nismo features a sport-tuned suspension, refined steering, and upgraded brakes, providing a more responsive and engaging driving experience. The exterior boasts a bold design with aerodynamic upgrades, including a unique front grille, side skirts, and Nismo badging, all enhancing its sporty look. Inside, the Nismo edition includes sport seats, special trim, and a more driver-focused cockpit. This compact yet versatile car is perfect for those who want the practicality of a hatchback with the added thrill of a sportier performance and design.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The Subaru Forester SG5 was produced from 2002 to 2008. Equipped with Subaru’s signature symmetrical all-wheel-drive system, it delivers excellent traction and stability on various terrains, while the turbocharged engine provides strong acceleration and power, making it a favorite for those who enjoy both city driving and off-road adventures. The SG5 offers a spacious interior, high ground clearance, and rugged design, blending versatility and sporty performance. Its robust handling and reliability make it a standout choice in the compact SUV segment.

name: Toyota Ractis
description: Toyota Ractis gives an interior advantage to both passengers and cargo on its height from the car floor. It can comfortably sit any person of any height and even large size cargos as it has a high roof compared with other cars of similar class. It has side mirror indicators, fabric seats, climate controls, and android infotainment system among other specs.

name: Volvo S60
description: The T3 brings a balance of efficiency and refinement to the Volvo S60, offering a sophisticated and practical sedan. The S60 T3 features Volvo’s elegant design, with a focus on safety and quality. Inside, the cabin is well-crafted with comfortable seating, advanced technology, and premium materials, creating a serene and stylish environment that reflects Volvo’s commitment to luxury and attention to detail.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado
description: TX models of the Toyota Prado offer a blend of rugged off-road capability and family-friendly features. Designed for versatility, the TX variant maintains the Prado’s renowned durability while providing a spacious and comfortable interior that can accommodate up to seven passengers. The cabin is equipped with essential modern conveniences, including a touchscreen infotainment system and multi-zone climate control, ensuring a pleasant driving experience. With advanced safety features such as stability control and hill-start assist, the TX model is as safe as it is practical. Whether for daily commutes or adventurous road trips, the Prado TX stands out as a reliable and capable SUV.

name: Mazda CX3
description: The Mazda CX-3 is a compact crossover SUV known for its sporty design and engaging driving dynamics. As a petrol model, it typically features a responsive engine that delivers a balance of performance and efficiency. The CX-3’s sleek exterior design is complemented by a well-crafted interior, offering high-quality materials and a driver-focused layout that enhances the overall driving experience. With comfortable seating for passengers and a versatile cargo space, the CX-3 is practical for daily commutes and weekend adventures. Its Skyactiv technology contributes to a fun driving experience, making it an appealing choice for those seeking a compact SUV with a sporty edge.

name: Mercedes Benz E200
description: The 4MATIC all-wheel-drive system in the Mercedes-Benz W213 E200 provides enhanced traction and stability, making it ideal for various driving conditions. This model blends Mercedes’ luxury with a refined, athletic presence, featuring a turbocharged engine that ensures smooth acceleration and a composed driving experience. Inside, the E200 4MATIC boasts a premium cabin with high-quality materials, a sleek, modern dashboard, and intuitive controls for an upscale feel. With advanced safety features and cutting-edge infotainment, the E200 4MATIC offers a stylish, comfortable, and capable option for those seeking a luxurious driving experience with all-weather versatility.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The 4MATIC all-wheel-drive system in the Mercedes-Benz W205 C200 provides enhanced traction and stability, making it well-suited for a range of driving conditions. This model combines Mercedes’ luxurious design with a sporty edge, featuring a turbocharged engine that delivers responsive acceleration and a refined driving experience. Inside, the C200 4MATIC offers a premium cabin with high-quality materials, intuitive controls, and a clean, modern dashboard layout. Advanced safety features and infotainment options add convenience and peace of mind, making the C200 4MATIC a stylish and practical choice for those who want luxury with all-weather capability.

Equipped with Subaru's symmetrical all-wheel-drive system and a finely tuned suspension, the WRX STI provides exceptional traction, sharp handling, and stability on a variety of surfaces. The aggressive styling, with its signature hood scoop, wide fenders, and rear spoiler, signals its sporty intent. Inside, it features a driver-focused cockpit, bolstered sport seats, and STI-specific details. Powered by a turbocharged engine, the WRX STI delivers impressive acceleration and torque, making it a favorite among performance enthusiasts seeking both daily driving comfort and track-ready performance.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: The Subaru Forester XT is a turbocharged variant of the Forester SUV, featuring a 2.0-liter turbocharged flat-four engine producing 250 horsepower and 350 Nm of torque. It comes with all-wheel drive and offers a balanced mix of performance and practicality. The Forester XT is known for its strong acceleration, rugged build, and capability in various driving conditions, including off-road. It also offers a spacious interior and a range of modern features, making it a versatile and reliable SUV.

name: Toyota Kluger
description: The Toyota Kluger is a well-rounded SUV that balances rugged capability with a refined, family-friendly design. Blending the durability of an off-road vehicle with the comfort of a luxury SUV, it provides ample space, ideal for family adventures or road trips. The Kluger offers a smooth and composed ride, with an elevated driving position that ensures excellent visibility. Thoughtfully designed, its interior features intuitive technology and storage solutions that make everyday use convenient and enjoyable. Known for its reliability and low-maintenance appeal, the Kluger stands as a versatile option, catering to both urban and outdoor lifestyles.

name: Subaru Legacy
description: The Subaru Legacy is celebrated for its all-wheel-drive capability, making it a reliable choice for various driving conditions. Known for its spacious and comfortable interior, the Legacy offers ample legroom and cargo space, providing a pleasant experience for both drivers and passengers. Safety is a strong focus, with many models featuring advanced technologies such as the EyeSight driver assist system. The sedan also boasts competitive fuel efficiency, enhancing its appeal as a practical everyday vehicle. Additionally, models equipped with a sunroof offer a touch of luxury and an open-air driving experience, further elevating the Legacy's overall charm and functionality. Its reputation for reliability and durability ensures that the Legacy remains a popular choice among consumers looking for a dependable station wagon.

name: Honda CRV
description: The Honda CR-V is a popular compact SUV known for its blend of practicality, comfort, and reliability. It offers a spacious interior with ample cargo space and a comfortable ride, making it a strong choice for families and those needing extra room. The CR-V features a modern design with a high-quality cabin, including advanced technology like a touchscreen infotainment system and various driver assistance features. It is available with a range of engines, including efficient four-cylinder options, and provides good fuel economy and smooth handling. Overall, the Honda CR-V is celebrated for its versatility, practicality, and overall value.

name: Nissan Note
description: The Nissan Note is a compact hatchback that combines practicality with modern features, making it ideal for city driving. Its design emphasizes spaciousness and efficiency, with a roomy interior that comfortably accommodates passengers despite its compact size.

name: Toyota Vitz
description: The Toyota Vitz is a compact hatchback known for its practicality, efficiency, and reliability. Designed for urban driving, it offers a compact footprint that makes maneuvering and parking easy. The Vitz features a functional and well-organized interior with modern technology

name: Toyota Wish
description: The Toyota Wish Valvematic is a versatile MPV designed to offer a blend of space, efficiency, and smooth performance. Equipped with Toyota's Valvematic technology, which enhances fuel efficiency and power delivery by optimizing valve timing, the Wish provides a more responsive and fuel-efficient driving experience. With its three-row seating configuration, it comfortably accommodates up to seven passengers, making it ideal for families or groups. The interior is practical and spacious, with a flexible seating arrangement to maximize cargo space when needed. Known for its reliability, low maintenance, and user-friendly features, the Toyota Wish Valvematic is a popular choice among those seeking a practical and dependable family vehicle.

name: Landrover Discovery IV
description: The Land Rover Discovery IV (also known as the LR4 in some markets) is a luxury off-road SUV that combines rugged capability with refined comfort. Known for its robust build and exceptional off-road performance, the Discovery IV features a spacious interior with seating for up to seven passengers, making it ideal for families and adventurers alike. It comes equipped with advanced off-road technologies like Terrain Response, adjustable air suspension, and permanent four-wheel drive, ensuring it can tackle challenging terrains with ease. Inside, the Discovery IV offers a premium experience with high-quality materials, modern infotainment systems, and a versatile cargo area. Its blend of luxury and off-road prowess makes it a standout in the SUV market.

name: Mercedes Benz B180
description: The Mercedes-Benz B180 is a compact MPV that emphasizes practicality, comfort, and efficient performance, ideal for urban and family use. Known for its spacious interior and premium feel, the B180 combines a high seating position with ample headroom and legroom, providing a comfortable experience for both driver and passengers. The B180 features a modern, well-equipped cabin with advanced infotainment options and safety technologies, aligning with Mercedes-Benz’s focus on quality and innovation. With efficient performance and a compact design, the B180 is easy to maneuver in tight spaces while still offering the comfort and refinement expected from the brand.

name: Audi Q7
description: Creation of the Q7 by Audi favored large family consumers. Powered by a 3000cc Turbocharged Diesel V6 Engine producing 233 horsepower and 500Nm of torque.Its 7 seats have leather material and are powered. It also has a multifunctional 4 spoke steering wheel. Its ground clearance is excellent for offroading adventures as well!

name: Mercedes Benz ML350
description: The petrol-powered Mercedes-Benz ML350, equipped with a 3.5-liter V6 engine, delivers a smooth and refined driving experience with ample power for both city and highway driving. Known for its blend of luxury and capability, the ML350 features Mercedes-Benz's attention to detail, offering a comfortable, high-quality interior with advanced technology and safety features. Its responsive V6 engine provides solid acceleration, while the SUV’s well-tuned suspension ensures a smooth ride across various terrains. With ample cargo space and a sophisticated all-wheel-drive system, the ML350 combines practicality and luxury, making it a versatile choice for drivers who value comfort and performance.

name: Honda Fit
description: The Honda Fit is a compact hatchback known for its exceptional space efficiency, reliability, and fuel economy. With its clever "Magic Seat" system, the Fit allows for multiple interior configurations, maximizing cargo space and versatility for various passenger and cargo needs. Its compact size and nimble handling make it ideal for city driving, while the efficient design and smooth engine options deliver excellent fuel economy. Inside, the Fit offers a surprisingly roomy cabin with user-friendly features and high-quality materials for its class. This blend of practicality, efficiency, and Honda's reputation for durability has made the Fit a popular choice for drivers seeking a versatile, low-maintenance vehicle.

name: BMW X6
description: The xDrive35i variant of the BMW X6 combines sporty performance with the versatility of an SUV, creating a unique, coupe-styled vehicle with a bold presence. Powered by a turbocharged engine, the xDrive35i delivers strong acceleration and smooth power, while BMW's xDrive all-wheel-drive system ensures reliable traction and stability in various driving conditions. Inside, the X6 xDrive35i features a high-quality interior with comfortable seating, advanced infotainment, and modern driver-assistance features that reflect BMW's luxury standards. With its distinctive sloping roofline and agile handling, the X6 xDrive35i stands out as an option for those seeking a blend of style, performance, and SUV capability.

name: Toyota Landcruiser ZX
description: The Toyota Land Cruiser 200 ZX is the top-tier variant of Toyota's flagship SUV, designed to provide luxury, power, and off-road capability. Known for its robust build and advanced features, the ZX trim stands out with upscale additions such as leather upholstery, premium wood accents, and state-of-the-art technology, offering a high level of comfort and convenience. Equipped with Toyota's legendary 4WD system, the LC200 ZX is built for rugged terrains, featuring advanced suspension, crawl control, and various off-road assist systems that allow it to handle challenging conditions with ease. Despite its tough off-road capabilities, the ZX trim delivers a refined on-road experience, balancing power and luxury to create a vehicle that excels in both adventure and everyday driving.

name: Toyota IST
description: The Toyota Ist is a compact hatchback celebrated for its practicality, reliability, and efficiency, making it well-suited for urban driving. Launched in 2002 primarily for the Japanese market, the Ist features a boxy, modern design that maximizes interior space within a compact footprint. Its high roofline and hatchback layout provide ample room for passengers and cargo, while the straightforward interior offers comfort and functionality. Known for its durability and low maintenance needs, the Ist delivers solid fuel economy and dependable performance, making it a popular choice for those seeking a user-friendly and versatile vehicle for everyday use.

name: Toyota Auris
description: A fairly great car to own, the Toyota Auris! The Auris has always retained its worth over the years for its durability and reliability. With a few engine varieties, owners have really appreciated how they have been treated by the cars in general.

name: Volkswagen Passat CC
description: As Volkswagen calls it, the CC in Passat CC means Comfort Coupe which is a combination of its Coupe like body style and the comfort Passat offers. It features bucket-styled half-leather seats that are powered and have three-position memory seats. The seats are also heated and both the front occupants get to enjoy individual air conditioning via the dual zone climate controls. The analogue clock at the center of the dashboard gives the Passat a classy finish. Other specs include an android infotainment display system, traction control, electric parking brake Auto hold brake function steering wheel controls, paddle shifters, and an analogue cluster.

name: Audi S5
description: The Audi S5 B9, part of the second generation introduced in 2016, is a high-performance variant of the A5, known for its sleek design and powerful capabilities. Available as a coupe or sportback, the S5 B9 boasts a striking exterior with distinctive S-specific styling elements. Under the hood, it is powered by a 3.0-liter V6 turbocharged engine that produces around 354 horsepower and 500 Nm of torque, paired with Audi's Quattro all-wheel-drive system for exceptional traction and handling. This setup allows the S5 to accelerate from 0 to 100 km/h in approximately 4.7 seconds. Inside, the S5 features a luxurious cabin equipped with high-quality materials and advanced technology, providing a blend of comfort, style, and performance that appeals to driving enthusiasts and luxury buyers alike.

name: Nissan NV200
description: The Nissan NV200 is a compact van designed for urban mobility and commercial use, offering versatility, efficiency, and practicality. With its compact size, the NV200 is easy to maneuver in tight city streets while still providing ample cargo space for deliveries or transporting equipment. The interior is functional, with a spacious cargo area and a comfortable, straightforward cabin for the driver and passengers. Known for its reliability and fuel efficiency, the NV200 is ideal for small businesses or as a fleet vehicle. Its sliding doors and low load floor make it easy to load and unload cargo, enhancing its convenience for everyday use.

name: Audi A3
description: The Audi A3 is a premium compact car known for its sophisticated design, quality interior, and engaging driving dynamics. It offers a blend of luxury and performance, with a well-appointed cabin featuring high-quality materials, advanced technology, and a comfortable ride. The A3 comes in various body styles, including a sedan, hatchback (Sportback), and convertible, catering to different preferences. It’s equipped with efficient and responsive engines, delivering a balance of power and fuel efficiency. The Audi A3 also features advanced safety systems and driver assistance technologies, making it a popular choice for those seeking a compact car with a premium feel and modern features.

name: Volvo S60
description: The T4 variant of the Volvo S60, enhanced with a Heico body kit, combines efficient performance with a sportier, more aggressive look. The Heico upgrades, including modified bumpers, side skirts, and a rear diffuser, give the S60 a dynamic presence on the road. Inside, it retains Volvo's signature blend of safety and luxury, with a premium cabin that features high-quality materials and advanced technology. Offering responsive handling and solid performance, the T4 with Heico styling provides an ideal mix of Volvo's renowned comfort and practicality, paired with a more striking, athletic design.

description: The 2018 Audi Q5 is a luxury compact SUV that combines sleek design, advanced technology, and dynamic performance. Its premium interior features high-quality materials, comfortable seating, and cutting-edge systems like the Audi Virtual Cockpit and intuitive MMI infotainment. Equipped with a turbocharged engine and Audi’s renowned Quattro all-wheel-drive system, the Q5 delivers a smooth and responsive driving experience with excellent traction, whether on city streets or rougher terrains. Offering a balance of sporty handling, comfort, and a suite of driver-assistance features, the 2018 Q5 is a versatile and refined choice for modern drivers.

name: Honda Fit
description: The Honda fit Non hybrid version is powered by a 1300cc naturally aspirated engine that produces 97 horsepower and 130Nm of torque. In its interior are fabric seats, digital climate controls and an Eco drive mode that saves on fuel by reducing the engine performance.

name: Peugeot 308
description: The peugeot 308 came as a replacement of the 307. It sits below the 508 and just above the 208. It is powered by a 1200cc turbocharged petrol engine with 128hp and 230Nm of torque, a speedometer maxing at 250Km/h, cruise control, steering wheel controls, climate controls, android infotainment display system, and electric parking brake.

name: Mazda Axela
description: The Mazda Axela is a stylish and well-rounded compact car known for its sporty design, engaging driving dynamics, and high-quality interior. It delivers a good balance of performance and fuel economy, with a premium cabin featuring modern technology like a touchscreen infotainment system and advanced safety features. Available in both sedan and hatchback versions, the Axela offers practicality, comfort, and a connected driving experience, making it a popular choice for those seeking both style and substance in a compact car.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TX
description: TX models of the Toyota Prado offer a blend of rugged off-road capability and family-friendly features. Designed for versatility, the TX variant maintains the Prado’s renowned durability while providing a spacious and comfortable interior that can accommodate up to seven passengers. The cabin is equipped with essential modern conveniences, including a touchscreen infotainment system and multi-zone climate control, ensuring a pleasant driving experience. With advanced safety features such as stability control and hill-start assist, the TX model is as safe as it is practical. Whether for daily commutes or adventurous road trips, the Prado TX stands out as a reliable and capable SUV.

name: Jeep Wrangler
description: A Jeep Wrangler with off-road modifications takes its rugged capabilities to the next level, making it an ideal choice for serious off-road enthusiasts. Common upgrades include lift kits for increased ground clearance, larger all-terrain or mud tires for better traction, and enhanced suspension systems for superior handling on rough terrains. Many also add steel bumpers, rock sliders, and winches for extra protection and recovery options, while LED light bars and snorkels improve visibility and water-fording ability. These modifications elevate the Wrangler’s performance on challenging trails while maintaining its iconic, adventurous spirit.

name: Toyota Hilux
description: The seventh-generation Toyota Hilux, produced from 2004 to 2015, is celebrated for its rugged reliability and off-road prowess. It features a muscular design with a bold grille, larger headlights, and higher ground clearance, giving it a tough, commanding presence. Built for both work and adventure, it offers a spacious cargo bed and strong towing capabilities. Inside, the cabin is functional and comfortable, with user-friendly controls and varying levels of equipment depending on the trim. Powered by durable and powerful engines, the seventh-gen Hilux is known for its exceptional durability, making it a go-to choice in demanding environments worldwide.

name: Nissan Xtrail
description: The Nissan X-Trail is a compact SUV with a sleek design and a spacious, well-organized interior. It’s built for comfortable driving, offering a smooth ride and modern features like an intuitive infotainment system and advanced safety technologies. The cabin is roomy, with ample space for passengers and cargo, making it practical for family use or long trips. The X-Trail’s design focuses on delivering a comfortable and reliable driving experience, with both front-wheel and all-wheel-drive options available, making it a solid choice for everyday driving needs.

name: Lexus NX300H
description: The Lexus NX300h is a luxury compact hybrid SUV that combines eco-friendly technology with premium comfort and modern design. It features a hybrid system that pairs a gasoline engine with electric motors, delivering a smooth and quiet drive along with excellent fuel efficiency. The NX300h is equipped with Lexus' E-Four all-wheel-drive system, offering enhanced traction and stability for various road conditions. Inside, it boasts a high-end cabin with advanced infotainment, luxurious materials, and a suite of safety features through the Lexus Safety System+. Overall, the NX300h offers a refined, environmentally conscious driving experience without compromising on style or comfort.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TZG
description: TZ-G is the top-tier variant of the Toyota Land Cruiser Prado J151, known for its luxurious features and advanced off-road capabilities. This model combines ruggedness with elegance, showcasing a bold exterior with a distinctive grille and robust body lines. Inside, the TZ-G boasts high-quality materials, spacious seating, and a range of comfort and convenience features, including premium upholstery and advanced infotainment options. Its powerful engine, paired with a sophisticated four-wheel-drive system, ensures impressive performance both on and off the road, making it ideal for adventurous trips or daily driving. With an emphasis on safety and technology, the TZ-G variant includes numerous driver-assistance features, providing peace of mind for occupants. Overall, the Toyota Land Cruiser Prado J151 TZ-G is a perfect blend of luxury, capability, and reliability, appealing to those seeking a versatile SUV for various driving conditions.

name: Mazda Atenza
description: The Mazda Atenza XD-L(also known as the Mazda XD-L) is a mid-size sedan that stands out for its luxurious features, refined design, and engaging driving dynamics. It combines a sleek, modern exterior with a high-quality, spacious interior that includes premium materials and advanced technology. The XD-L variant typically features a 2.2-liter diesel engine, known for its strong torque and fuel efficiency, delivering a smooth and powerful driving experience. With its precise handling, comfort-focused design, and a range of safety and convenience features, the Atenza XD-L offers a compelling blend of style and performance.

name: BMW 320i
description: The BMW 320i F30 M Sport adds a sportier edge to the standard 320i, enhancing both its aesthetics and driving dynamics. The M Sport package includes a more aggressive body kit, larger alloy wheels, and distinctive M badging, giving the 320i a sleek, athletic appearance. Inside, the M Sport trim features sport seats, an M Sport steering wheel, and exclusive interior accents, creating a more performance-oriented atmosphere. The suspension is also upgraded for sharper handling, providing a more engaging driving experience. Overall, the 320i F30 M Sport combines luxury with a sporty flair, making it an appealing choice for those who value both style and performance.

name: Jeep Wrangler
description: This is the 3rd generation Jeep Wrangler that came into production in 2006 under the development of Daimler Chrysler and was developed under a clean-sheet design of the body, frame, and suspension. This generation came with power windows, remote power door locks, navigation, and electronically detachable sway bars on some models. The Wrangler carries the seriousness an offroader deserves. It also has an aftermarket Carbon steering wheel with engine revs display among other dash systems. A 4WD system and a high torque engine is all you need to fulfil your offroad adventures!

name: Subaru Forester
description: A well engineered, great powered SUV, with one of the best drivetrains in the world, the Subaru Forester. It is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, and heated front seats as some of its major specs.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The third-generation Mercedes-Benz C-Class (W204), produced from 2007 to 2014, is a luxury compact sedan that combines elegant design with sporty performance. It features a refined, muscular exterior with a bold front grille and a more dynamic stance. Inside, the cabin offers premium materials, comfortable seating, and advanced technology, including a user-friendly infotainment system and various driver assistance features. Known for its smooth ride and precise handling, the W204 offers a range of engine options focused on both performance and fuel efficiency, with the available 4MATIC all-wheel-drive system enhancing traction. This generation balances luxury, comfort, and performance, appealing to both everyday drivers and enthusiasts alike.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: The Toyota Harrier is a stylish mid-size crossover SUV that expertly combines sophistication with practicality, making it a sought-after choice for those in need of a versatile vehicle. Its sleek, aerodynamic exterior is characterized by bold lines, a distinctive front grille, and elegant LED headlights, lending it a modern and upscale appearance. Inside, the Harrier boasts a spacious cabin adorned with high-quality materials, comfortable seating, and advanced technology, including an intuitive infotainment system and a comprehensive suite of safety features. With a focus on comfort, it offers ample legroom and cargo space, ideal for daily commutes and family adventures. Engine options typically include efficient petrol and hybrid powertrains, ensuring a smooth and responsive driving experience. Known for its reliability and the brand's commitment to quality, the Harrier is an excellent blend of performance and style for those who appreciate aesthetics without compromising functionality.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado
description: The Toyota Prado is a mid-size SUV known for its strong off-road capabilities and refined on-road manners. It’s part of the Land Cruiser family, offering a blend of rugged durability and modern comfort. The Prado features a robust body-on-frame construction, advanced four-wheel-drive systems, and a range of powerful engines, typically including diesel and petrol options, making it well-suited for challenging terrains and long-distance driving. Inside, the Prado provides a spacious and well-appointed cabin with seating for up to seven passengers, advanced safety technologies, and modern infotainment features, making it a versatile choice for both family use and adventurous expeditions.

name: BMW X1
description: The BMW X1 S-DRIVE20i was largely accepted in the market for the three key things that it gave to its consumers. Efficiency, lower pricing on it because of the option of getting an All Wheel drive it being not available by default, and the smaller size which some of the consumers are very comfortable with. They are also reliable cars that demands less while giving more to its users. The comfort aspect is excellent as the seats are made of Alcantara material which are quite comfy.

name: Mercedes Benz C180
description: In the class of compact sedans, the C180 turns out to be an excellently engineered sedan, with this car probably being the best there is. It gives an executive taste with all in round class while delivering excellent performance and fuel economy. It runs a 1.6L turbocharged petrol engine with a descent horsepower of 156hp and 250Nm of torque driving you in comfortable front row-heated bucket styled leather seats with thigh support while regulating your cabin temperature from dual zone climate controls listening to music from a premium surround sound system.

name: Subaru XV
description: The third-generation Subaru XV, introduced in 2017, is a versatile compact crossover that blends Subaru's renowned off-road capability with modern design and technology. Built on Subaru’s Global Platform, it offers improved handling, safety, and comfort, while its Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive and elevated ground clearance ensure excellent performance on both city streets and rugged terrain. Inside, the XV boasts a tech-forward cabin with updated infotainment, driver-assistance systems, and plenty of cargo space. With its combination of practicality, off-road prowess, and reliability, the third-gen Subaru XV is a top choice for those seeking a capable and comfortable compact SUV.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: The second-generation Toyota Harrier, produced from 2003 to 2013, was a luxury crossover SUV known for its refined design, comfort, and advanced technology. It featured a sleek, aerodynamic exterior and a high-quality interior with premium materials and modern amenities. Both front-wheel and all-wheel drive configurations were available, and a hybrid variant was introduced in 2005, blending performance with fuel efficiency. The Harrier stood out for its smooth ride, spacious cabin, and focus on safety, making it a popular choice among those seeking both luxury and practicality in an SUV.

name: Porsche Cayenne
description: Porsche has been producing superior performing cars since the early years of the 20th century. They have shown their expertise and highly advanced engineering in their productions. The Cayenne is one of the marvels of Porsche engineering. The 2015 Petrol Platinum Edition variant is powered by a 3600cc petrol engine that does an impressive 300 horsepower at 6300 RPMs and 400Nm of Torque at 3000 RPMs. It does a lot more better than the diesel variant in the horsepower numbers, doing about 240 horses. We can all agree on the engine's reliability and maintenance. It has beige leather, multizone climate controls, Multifunctional tilt & telescopic steering wheel, Auto start stop feature, a premium surround sound system, and differential locks.

name: Nissan AD Van
description: This Nissan AD Van is a good enough unit to run errands involving small and large loads because of its large boot space that can also be extended by folding rear seats. It is powered by a 1500cc naturally aspirated engine with torque numbers of 134Nm. Its seats are in fabric materials that are quite good and comfortable.

name: Mitsubishi Pajero IO
description: The Mitsubishi Pajero iO is a compact SUV designed for both urban use and off-road adventures, offering a balance of practicality and rugged capability. Equipped with Mitsubishi's Super Select 4WD system, it handles a variety of terrains with ease, making it versatile for city driving and outdoor exploration. Despite its smaller size compared to the full-sized Pajero, the iO provides a comfortable and spacious interior for passengers and cargo. Known for its durability and reliability, the Pajero iO is a solid choice for those seeking a compact SUV that excels in both everyday driving and off-road performance.

name: Toyota Passo
description: The Toyota Passo is quite comfortable and stable at relatively high speeds. Giving great fuel consumption numbers to 20Kms a liter and close to zero breakdowns.

name: Volkswagen Golf GTI
description: The MK7 Golf GTI, launched in 2013, is a celebrated hot hatch known for its practicality and everyday usability. It features a sporty yet understated design, highlighted by a distinctive front grille with red accents, aggressive bumpers, and larger alloy wheels. Inside, the cabin offers a blend of comfort and sportiness with supportive plaid seats, a flat-bottomed steering wheel, and a user-friendly infotainment system equipped with smartphone connectivity and driver-assistance features. The MK7 GTI's spacious interior and versatile cargo space make it an ideal choice for both daily commuting and weekend adventures, appealing to those seeking a stylish and functional hatchback.

name: Audi A4
description: The Audi A4 B9 S line is a sporty variant of the B9 generation A4, introduced in 2015, and is celebrated for its blend of performance, luxury, and cutting-edge technology. The S line trim enhances the A4’s visual appeal with aggressive design elements like a bold front bumper, distinctive side skirts, and larger alloy wheels, while the interior features sport seats, high-quality materials, and unique badging that create a dynamic atmosphere. Typically equipped with efficient and powerful turbocharged engines, the A4 B9 S line delivers a spirited driving experience. Additionally, it boasts advanced technology, including Audi’s MMI infotainment system and virtual cockpit, along with a suite of driver-assistance features for enhanced safety and convenience. Overall, the Audi A4 B9 S line is an excellent choice for those seeking a premium compact sedan with a performance-oriented edge.

name: Honda Fit
description: One of the most durable hatches in the market, Honda Fit. The Hybrid system in Honda consists of a petrol powered engine and a lithium-ion battery pack that is charged by a generator powered by the engine that in turn powers the drive motor when the engine is not running. This is a very efficient fuel saving and power generation mechanism that makes Honda Fit Hybrid a very reliable model.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado
description: The Toyota Prado is a mid-size SUV known for its strong off-road capabilities and refined on-road manners. It’s part of the Land Cruiser family, offering a blend of rugged durability and modern comfort. The Prado features a robust body-on-frame construction, advanced four-wheel-drive systems, and a range of powerful engines, typically including diesel and petrol options, making it well-suited for challenging terrains and long-distance driving. Inside, the Prado provides a spacious and well-appointed cabin with seating for up to seven passengers, advanced safety technologies, and modern infotainment features, making it a versatile choice for both family use and adventurous expeditions.

name: Volkswagen Touareg
description: The 1st Gen of Touareg was first produced in 2002 and straight up won several awards for its among it for being the best in the 4×4 car category. It shares a lot of parts with the Cayenne and has it engine equipped with a 3.6L Petrol V6 engine. This is a go-to car for someone who wants to use it for several purposes including offroading and for urban setups.

name: Nissan Patrol
description: The 1998 Nissan Patrol is a rugged and reliable full-size SUV known for its off-road capabilities and durability. As part of the fourth generation (Y61 series), it features a sturdy body-on-frame construction, making it well-suited for challenging terrains and off-road adventures. The Patrol offers a spacious interior, capable of seating up to seven passengers, and comes with a range of features designed for comfort and utility. It is equipped with a robust suspension system and four-wheel-drive capabilities, ensuring stability and traction in rough conditions. The 1998 Nissan Patrol is widely respected for its reliability, making it a popular choice for both adventure enthusiasts and those seeking a dependable SUV for everyday use.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado
description: TX models of the Toyota Prado offer a blend of rugged off-road capability and family-friendly features. Designed for versatility, the TX variant maintains the Prado’s renowned durability while providing a spacious and comfortable interior that can accommodate up to seven passengers. The cabin is equipped with essential modern conveniences, including a touchscreen infotainment system and multi-zone climate control, ensuring a pleasant driving experience. With advanced safety features such as stability control and hill-start assist, the TX model is as safe as it is practical. Whether for daily commutes or adventurous road trips, the Prado TX stands out as a reliable and capable SUV.

name: Nissan Note
description: The first-generation Nissan Note, introduced in 2004, is a compact hatchback that emphasizes practicality and spaciousness. Its tall, boxy design provides ample interior room, offering generous headroom and legroom, especially for a car of its size. The rear seats are highly versatile, allowing for flexible cargo configurations, making it ideal for families or those needing extra storage. With a comfortable ride and excellent fuel efficiency, the Note is well-suited for city driving and daily commutes. Its straightforward, user-friendly technology adds to its appeal as an efficient, functional, and affordable compact car.

name: Mazda Premacy
description: The Premacy is an excellent alternative to it's competitors thanks to it's friendly price. Being a Mazda, you are assured of thorough reliability, especially with this 2000cc petrol engine powerded option.

name: Toyota LandCruiser Prado
description: Nothing better than a fully loaded J120 Series Toyota Landcruiser Prado with a range of premium specs including a Sunroof, powered seats made of leather material, 8 seats occupancy capacity, and a fully functional infotainment system. This was initially owned in the United Kingdom. The 1KD 3.0 Turbocharged engine is a moving magic that just carries anything thrown at it except bad maintenance. Family units very well fit the car and long distance trips or offroading eacapades are the best with this J120!

name: Toyota Fielder
description: Toyota Fielder is available in a station wagon body style which means you have more space both at passenger spaces and boot space. This gives the option of using this car for multiple tasks including commercially carrying cargo whose capacity is extended because of the car's body style, commercially for moving people from one point to another as it is a very capable car, and in a corporate using it to get to work and running official errands. An excellent multi-tasker!

name: Mazda Demio
description: The Mazda Demio is a subcompact hatchback that offers a blend of style, efficiency, and fun driving dynamics. It’s known for its sleek design, featuring Mazda's KODO design language, which gives it a modern and sporty appearance. The Demio is compact yet spacious, providing a comfortable interior with well-designed controls and practical storage space. It’s powered by fuel-efficient engines, making it ideal for city driving and longer trips with great fuel economy. With responsive handling and advanced safety features, the Mazda Demio is a popular choice for those seeking a practical yet stylish small car.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The XD-L trim of the 2017 Mazda CX-5 AWD is a luxury mid-sized SUV that combines a refined design with premium features and strong performance. Equipped with a 2.2-liter turbocharged diesel engine and all-wheel drive, it offers both power and excellent traction. The XD-L trim features a high-quality interior with advanced technology, comfortable seating, and a range of convenience features, delivering a sophisticated and versatile driving experience.

name: Mazda Demio
description: The Mazda Demio is a subcompact hatchback that offers a blend of style, efficiency, and fun driving dynamics. It’s known for its sleek design, featuring Mazda's KODO design language, which gives it a modern and sporty appearance. The Demio is compact yet spacious, providing a comfortable interior with well-designed controls and practical storage space. It’s powered by fuel-efficient engines, making it ideal for city driving and longer trips with great fuel economy. With responsive handling and advanced safety features, the Mazda Demio is a popular choice for those seeking a practical yet stylish small car.

A powerful engine, stylish and spacious, durable. and easy on the pockets. This would be an interesting choice to purchase for any long term use of a vehicle.

name: Nissan Xtrail
description: The Nissan X-Trail T32, introduced in 2013, is a modern compact SUV that combines sleek design with practicality. Offering seating for five or seven passengers, it features a spacious and comfortable interior with advanced tech like a touchscreen infotainment system and driver-assist features. Available in both front-wheel and all-wheel drive configurations, the T32 delivers a smooth driving experience, making it ideal for city driving as well as light off-road adventures. Known for its reliability, fuel efficiency, and family-friendly design, the T32 remains a popular choice among crossover SUV buyers.

name: E Bike
description: An e-bike, or electric bicycle, features a battery-powered motor that assists with pedaling, making it easier to ride over long distances or challenging terrain. It offers adjustable levels of assistance, allowing riders to control how much help they get from the motor, which is ideal for commuting, recreational riding, or even tackling hills with less effort. E-bikes come in various styles, from road to mountain models, and typically provide a range of 30 to over 100 km per charge, with top speeds around 25-45 km/h, depending on regulations. They offer an eco-friendly and convenient alternative to traditional transportation.

description: The Audi Q5 with a panoramic sunroof combines luxury and practicality in a stylish compact SUV. The panoramic sunroof enhances the cabin's spaciousness, creating an open, airy feel for all passengers. Inside, the Q5 offers a high-quality interior with seating for five and modern features, including an intuitive infotainment system and premium materials throughout. Powered by a 2.0L turbocharged engine with 220 hp and 350 Nm of torque, the 2016 Q5 accelerates from 0 to 100 km/h in around 7.1 seconds. Audi’s Quattro all-wheel drive ensures confident handling in various conditions, with a fuel economy of approximately 10-12 km/l.

The MK7.5 Volkswagen Golf, a facelift of the seventh-generation model, introduced in 2017, features updated styling with LED headlights, taillights, and redesigned bumpers. It comes with advanced tech upgrades, including a larger touchscreen infotainment system and, in some versions, a fully digital instrument cluster. Maintaining the Golf’s reputation for sporty yet refined handling, the MK7.5 offers a comfortable, practical ride with enhanced driving dynamics, especially in performance-oriented trims like the GTI and R, making it a versatile choice for both everyday driving and enthusiasts seeking a dynamic hatchback.

name: Suzuki Solio
description: The Suzuki Solio is a compact yet practical MPV designed for urban mobility, offering a spacious interior despite its small footprint. Its tall, boxy design maximizes cabin space, providing comfortable seating for five and a surprisingly generous amount of headroom and cargo space. The sliding rear doors make it convenient for passengers to enter and exit in tight parking spaces. Equipped with modern features like a touchscreen infotainment system and advanced safety technologies, the Solio is aimed at drivers looking for an efficient, easy-to-maneuver vehicle that excels in city environments while offering practicality for everyday use.

name: Toyota CHR
description: The CH-R is a compact crossover SUV produced by Toyota since 2016. It is produced in the same platform as the E210 Corolla Series and lies between Toyota Yaris and Corolla Cross in the same SUV lineup. In the Japanese market which we majorly source our cars from, the CH-R is powered a choice of either the 1.2L turbocharged petrol engine or the 1.8L hybrid variant. It comes in S, S-LED, G, S-T and G-T trims where the S, S-LED and G trims are powered with the 1.2-litre turbo while S-T and G-T trims run the 1.8L. It is one of the best crossovers by Toyota especially for individuals who are after fuel economy.

description: The American Marque categorised in the mid-size SUV produced since 2010 to 2022. At the unveiling moment in New York's Auto Show, it received 30 awards. The Grand Cherokee 'BLACKHAWK' has definitely outperformed itself in all its years of production. It is a serious offroader and doubles up well as a presentable urban driving car. It features a four-wheel independent suspension which improves road handling. The engine option in this car is the 3.6L Pentastar V6 Petrol version with a power rating of 290hp. On the interior are comfy half leather seats, a premium surround sound system, a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, and a 4WD drive select system.

name: Toyota Hilux
description: The seventh-generation Toyota Hilux, produced from 2004 to 2015, is celebrated for its rugged reliability and off-road prowess. It features a muscular design with a bold grille, larger headlights, and higher ground clearance, giving it a tough, commanding presence. Built for both work and adventure, it offers a spacious cargo bed and strong towing capabilities. Inside, the cabin is functional and comfortable, with user-friendly controls and varying levels of equipment depending on the trim. Powered by durable and powerful engines, the seventh-gen Hilux is known for its exceptional durability, making it a go-to choice in demanding environments worldwide.
