name: Jeep Wrangler
description: This is the one of the best offroad machines to ever appear in our markets, 3rd generation Jeep wrangler that came in, in 2006 under the development of Daimler Chrysler and was developed under a clean-sheet design of the body, frame, and suspension. This generation of Wrangler Unlimited Sports came with power windows, remote power door locks, navigation, and electronically detachable sway bars on some models. The Wrangler carries the seriousness an offroader deserves. A 4WD system and a high torque engine is all you need to fulfil your offroad adventures!

name: Mazda CX5
description: XD-L denotes the diesel variant of the Mazda CX-5, offering a blend of power and efficiency in a stylish and versatile SUV. With its sleek design and sporty lines, the CX-5 XD-L stands out on the road, while its spacious interior provides ample comfort and functionality for both passengers and cargo. The diesel engine delivers robust performance with impressive torque, ensuring a responsive driving experience, complemented by Mazda’s renowned handling dynamics. Inside, the cabin is well-appointed with high-quality materials, advanced technology, and a focus on driver comfort, making it ideal for both daily commutes and longer journeys. Overall, the CX-5 XD-L combines practicality with a touch of luxury, appealing to those seeking a refined yet capable SUV.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The Subaru Forester is a compact SUV renowned for its ruggedness, versatility, and all-wheel-drive capability. It offers a spacious interior with excellent cargo space, making it ideal for families and outdoor enthusiasts. Equipped with Subaru’s signature Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, the Forester provides superior handling and stability on various terrains, from city streets to off-road trails. It features a range of modern safety and technology options, ensuring a safe and comfortable driving experience. The Forester is well-regarded for its reliability, making it a practical choice for those seeking an adventurous yet dependable SUV.

name: Nissan Sylphy
description: Nissan Sylphy comes out as a very reliably efficient sedan with minimal to no challenges to its owners. Offering maximum comfort for this class and excellent fuel consumption to an average of 14Kms a Liter. It has good ride height which eases the stresses of maneuvering our roads. It is definitely a go-to car for a large number of Users.

name: Subaru Outback
description: The Subaru Outback is a versatile crossover SUV known for its rugged capability, standard all-wheel drive, and elevated ground clearance, making it ideal for both city driving and off-road adventures. Its spacious interior comfortably seats five, offering ample cargo space and modern tech features like a touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. With a focus on safety, it includes advanced driver-assistance systems such as adaptive cruise control and lane-keeping assist. The Outback delivers a smooth ride and dependable handling, appealing to those seeking both practicality and adventure.

name: Toyota Vitz RS
description: The Toyota Vitz RS is a sporty variant of the popular Vitz hatchback, celebrated for its compact size, agile handling, and vibrant design. Featuring a more aggressive front fascia, unique alloy wheels, and distinctive trim details, the Vitz RS enhances the sporty appeal of the lineup. Inside, it offers a driver-focused cabin with supportive seats, modern technology, and a well-organized dashboard that elevates the driving experience. Equipped with features such as a touchscreen infotainment system, Bluetooth connectivity, and various safety technologies, the Vitz RS is ideal for daily commuting and urban driving. With its responsive engine delivering lively performance and excellent fuel efficiency, the Toyota Vitz RS combines sporty styling, practicality, and advanced features, making it a compelling choice for those seeking a fun and economical hatchback.

name: Mazda Demio
description: The Mazda Demio is a compact hatchback known for its blend of style, efficiency, and practicality. It features a sleek, modern design with a surprisingly roomy interior for its size. The Demio offers comfortable seating, intuitive controls, and a well-organized dashboard. Its compact dimensions make it ideal for city driving, while its efficient engines provide great fuel economy. With user-friendly technology and Mazda’s signature sporty handling, the Demio delivers a smooth and enjoyable driving experience, making it a popular choice for those looking for an affordable yet refined small car.

name: Toyota Landcruiser ZX
description: The Toyota Land Cruiser LC200 V8 is a full-size SUV celebrated for its rugged durability and exceptional off-road capability, making it a preferred choice for adventure seekers and families alike. Launched in 2007, it boasts a commanding presence with bold design elements, high ground clearance, and robust body lines that reflect strength and reliability. Inside, the LC200 offers a luxurious and spacious cabin with seating for up to eight passengers, featuring high-quality materials and advanced technology, including leather upholstery, multi-zone climate control, and a premium sound system. Equipped with an advanced four-wheel-drive system and features like Multi-Terrain Select and Crawl Control, the LC200 is designed to tackle various terrains with ease. Overall, the Toyota Land Cruiser LC200 V8 strikes a remarkable balance between luxury and ruggedness, appealing to those who seek reliability and capability in an SUV.

name: Honda Fit Shuttle
description: The Honda Fit Shuttle is a practical and versatile compact car that combines the benefits of a hatchback and a wagon, making it ideal for those seeking extra cargo space in a compact footprint. Based on the Honda Fit (or Jazz), it features a sleek design with an extended rear for increased storage capacity, complemented by Honda's innovative Magic Seat system that allows for flexible seating configurations. Typically equipped with a fuel-efficient 1.5-liter inline-4 engine, the Fit Shuttle offers a balance of power and economy, averaging around 15-20 km/l. With various safety features, including airbags and stability control, it provides a secure driving experience, making it an excellent choice for families and individuals needing both comfort and utility in their daily transportation.

name: Peugeot 308
description: The peugeot 308 came as a replacement of the 307. It sits below the 508 and just above the 208. It is powered by a 1200cc turbocharged petrol engine with 128hp and 230Nm of torque, a speedometer maxing at 250Km/h, cruise control, steering wheel controls, climate controls, android infotainment display system, and electric parking brake.

name: Nissan Note
description: The Nissan Note Medalist is a stylish and compact hatchback known for its blend of practicality and modern design. With a sleek front fascia and refined interior features, the Medalist trim enhances the overall appeal of the Note lineup. Inside, it offers a spacious cabin with comfortable seating for up to five passengers and a versatile cargo area, all crafted with quality materials and equipped with advanced technology, including an infotainment system that supports smartphone connectivity and various driver-assistance features. Typically powered by a fuel-efficient engine, the Note Medalist strikes a good balance between performance and economy, making it an ideal choice for both city driving and longer journeys.

name: Subaru Pleo
description: The Subaru Pleo is a compact city car introduced in 1998, known for its efficient use of space and practicality as a kei car, making it ideal for urban environments. Featuring a boxy design that maximizes interior room, the Pleo comfortably seats four passengers and offers a versatile cargo area. Its functional dashboard layout provides easy access to instruments and controls, ensuring a straightforward driving experience. Typically powered by a small 0.7L engine, available in both naturally aspirated and turbocharged variants, the Pleo delivers adequate power for city driving while boasting impressive fuel efficiency, making it a reliable and economical choice for urban dwellers.

name: Nissan Elgrand
description: The Nissan Elgrand is a luxury MPV that combines spaciousness, comfort, and versatility, making it an ideal choice for families and those in need of ample passenger space. With a sleek, modern design characterized by a prominent front grille and large windows, the Elgrand offers a roomy interior that can accommodate up to eight passengers. Inside, it features high-quality materials and advanced amenities, including a sophisticated infotainment system, climate control, and multiple storage options, all designed for a premium experience. Typically powered by a 3.5L V6 engine, the Elgrand strikes a balance between performance and efficiency, solidifying its reputation as a practical yet luxurious vehicle.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The Subaru Forester is a compact SUV renowned for its ruggedness, versatility, and all-wheel-drive capability. It offers a spacious interior with excellent cargo space, making it ideal for families and outdoor enthusiasts. Equipped with Subaru’s signature Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, the Forester provides superior handling and stability on various terrains, from city streets to off-road trails. It features a range of modern safety and technology options, ensuring a safe and comfortable driving experience. The Forester is well-regarded for its reliability, making it a practical choice for those seeking an adventurous yet dependable SUV.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado
description: The Toyota Prado is a robust mid-size SUV known for its off-road capabilities and durability, making it a member of the legendary Land Cruiser family. Its distinctive boxy design features high ground clearance and prominent wheel arches, which enhance its rugged appearance. Inside, the Prado offers a practical and spacious cabin that can accommodate up to seven passengers, with durable materials designed for both comfort and resilience. It typically comes with various features like air conditioning and power accessories. Under the hood, the Prado often features a reliable 3.0L turbo diesel engine, providing a solid balance of power and efficiency, making it a popular choice for adventure seekers and families alike.

name: Toyota Mark X Zio
description: The Toyota Mark X ZiO. A mid-size MPV that was produced by Toyota from 2007 to 2013, to replace the Mark II Blit Station Wagon. They share the nameplate with Mark X, which it was sold alongside, sharing a number of features. Its chassis is from the MC Platform which the E150 Auris, XA30 RAV4, and T270 Avensis were based on. Its name, ZiO, was from the fact that it had a very spacious interior and increased cargo capacity. The modifications done on this unit are absolutely great, with a 360° camera view and a premium music system, this is a great choice for an SUV.

name: Mercedes Benz GLC 43 AMG
description: The Mercedes-AMG GLC 43 Coupe is a dynamic blend of performance and style, featuring a sloping roofline that gives it a sleek, coupe-like silhouette while retaining SUV practicality. Powered by a twin-turbo V6 engine, it delivers impressive acceleration and handling, paired with standard all-wheel drive for enhanced traction. Inside, the cabin is luxurious and driver-focused, with premium materials, advanced infotainment, and sporty accents throughout. The GLC 43 Coupe balances high performance with everyday usability, making it a standout in the luxury performance SUV category.

name: Toyota Mark X
description: The Toyota Mark X is a mid-size sedan known for its sporty performance, refined design, and rear-wheel-drive layout. It features a stylish, aggressive exterior and a well-appointed interior with high-quality materials and modern technology. The Mark X offers a smooth, comfortable ride with responsive handling, making it enjoyable for both daily commuting and spirited driving. Inside, it provides ample space for passengers, along with advanced infotainment and safety features. Popular in markets that favor performance-oriented sedans, the Mark X stands out for its blend of comfort, reliability, and engaging driving dynamics.

name: Range Rover Velar
description: The Range Rover Velar is a sleek and modern mid-size luxury SUV, known for its minimalist design with flush door handles and a floating roof. Inside, it features a high-tech, premium cabin with dual touchscreens, a digital driver display, and luxurious materials throughout. The Velar offers a refined driving experience, combining smooth on-road handling with off-road capability, thanks to Land Rover's Terrain Response system. It balances style, technology, and versatility, making it a distinctive choice in the luxury SUV market.

name: Range Rover Sport
description: The Range Rover Sport Autobiography is a luxury SUV that combines off-road capability with high-end comfort and a sporty driving experience. It features a bold design with large alloy wheels and a refined interior, complete with premium leather, wood accents, and advanced tech like navigation and climate control. The Sport version offers sharper handling while maintaining the off-road abilities that Range Rover is known for, thanks to its Terrain Response system. This model delivers a perfect balance of performance, style, and rugged versatility.

name: Audi Q7
description: The 2017 Audi Q7 3.0T is a luxury SUV powered by a 3.0-liter supercharged V6 engine, delivering 333 horsepower and 440 Nm of torque, allowing it to accelerate from 0 to 100 km/h in just 6.1 seconds. Equipped with Audi’s quattro all-wheel-drive system and an 8-speed automatic transmission, it offers excellent handling and a smooth ride across various terrains. Inside, the Q7 features a spacious and luxurious cabin with advanced technology, including Audi’s virtual cockpit and MMI infotainment system, accommodating up to seven passengers comfortably. With a blend of performance, comfort, and cutting-edge features, the 2017 Q7 3.0T is ideal for families seeking both luxury and practicality.

name: BMW 520i
description: The BMW 520i is a luxury sedan that offers a refined balance of performance, comfort, and technology. As part of the BMW 5 Series, the 520i features a sleek and elegant design, both inside and out. The driving experience is enhanced by BMW's precision engineering, providing smooth handling and responsive performance. The interior is equipped with high-quality materials, advanced infotainment systems, and a range of driver-assistance features to ensure both safety and convenience. With its blend of luxury and dynamic driving characteristics, the BMW 520i stands as an excellent choice for those seeking a premium sedan with a focus on comfort and sophistication.

name: Honda Fit Shuttle
description: The Honda Fit Shuttle is a practical and versatile compact car that combines the benefits of a hatchback and a wagon, making it ideal for those seeking extra cargo space in a compact footprint. Based on the Honda Fit (or Jazz), it features a sleek design with an extended rear for increased storage capacity, complemented by Honda's innovative Magic Seat system that allows for flexible seating configurations. Typically equipped with a fuel-efficient 1.5-liter inline-4 engine, the Fit Shuttle offers a balance of power and economy, averaging around 15-20 km/l. With various safety features, including airbags and stability control, it provides a secure driving experience, making it an excellent choice for families and individuals needing both comfort and utility in their daily transportation.

name: Toyota Hilux
description: The Toyota Hilux is a globally recognized pickup truck renowned for its durability, off-road capability, and reliability, making it a favorite among both professionals and outdoor enthusiasts. Known for its tough construction and high ground clearance, the Hilux can tackle rough terrains with ease, thanks to its robust suspension and available 4WD systems. It offers a range of powerful engine options, typically featuring fuel-efficient turbocharged diesel engines that provide excellent torque for towing and hauling. Inside, the Hilux combines practicality with comfort, often equipped with modern infotainment systems and safety features. Its high payload and towing capacity, along with a reputation for being nearly indestructible, solidify the Hilux's status as a versatile and dependable choice in the pickup truck segment.The Toyota Hilux is a globally recognized pickup truck renowned for its durability, off-road capability, and reliability, making it a favorite among both professionals and outdoor enthusiasts. Powered by efficient engines, the Tiida delivers solid performance for both city driving and longer journeys, making it a versatile and budget-friendly choice.

name: Toyota Mark II
description: The Toyota Mark II is a mid-size sedan that gained popularity for its blend of comfort, reliability, and rear-wheel-drive performance. Known for its smooth ride and solid build quality, the Mark II offers a spacious interior with refined features, making it a favorite for both daily driving and long-distance travel. It comes in various engine options, with the 2.0L and 2.5L engines providing a balance between performance and fuel efficiency. Enthusiasts particularly appreciate its rear-wheel-drive layout, especially in higher-powered versions, making it a versatile and durable choice in the mid-size sedan segment.

The Forester is well-regarded for its reliability, making it a practical choice for those seeking an adventurous yet dependable SUV.

name: Porsche Cayenne
description: The first-generation Porsche Cayenne, launched in 2002, was Porsche's bold move into the SUV market, blending luxury with the brand’s signature sports car performance. It offered impressive on-road agility and handling, rare for an SUV, while still maintaining off-road capability with advanced all-wheel-drive. The Cayenne featured a spacious, high-quality interior, delivering both comfort and practicality. It stood out for its versatility, providing a refined daily driving experience alongside the ability to tackle tougher terrains, all while upholding Porsche’s reputation for performance and reliability.

With its agile handling, smooth ride, and practical features, the 2016 S60 T3 stands out as an appealing option for those seeking a sophisticated yet accessible luxury sedan.

name: Toyota Raum

Its boxy design maximizes interior space, with sliding rear doors that provide easy access to the back seats, making it especially convenient in tight parking spaces. Known for its reliability and fuel efficiency, the Raum is ideal for city driving, offering easy handling and good maneuverability. Overall, the Toyota Raum is a practical and dependable choice for those seeking a compact vehicle with spaciousness and convenience.

High-quality materials, customizable ambient lighting, and a range of advanced safety features, such as adaptive cruise control and lane-keeping assist, enhance its contemporary character, making the 3008 a standout choice for those seeking a sleek and tech-forward SUV.

name: Nissan Xtrail

With its sporty design and premium interior, it offers a refined driving experience while maintaining the practicality needed for everyday use. Inside, the GLA features high-quality materials, advanced technology such as the MBUX infotainment system with voice control, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto, and a spacious cabin with flexible cargo options. It’s available with a range of efficient turbocharged engines and comes equipped with advanced safety features like active brake assist and lane-keeping assist, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a premium yet practical compact SUV.

name: Toyota Rav4
description: Adventure Offroad Package on the 2021 Toyota RAV4 enhances its rugged appeal, making it perfect for outdoor enthusiasts seeking both style and practicality. This package adds bold design elements, including an aggressive front grille, black fender flares, and 19-inch alloy wheels with all-terrain tires for a commanding off-road presence. It also includes increased ground clearance and a reinforced suspension to tackle rougher terrains with ease. Inside, the RAV4 Adventure offers a spacious and durable cabin equipped with modern tech, such as a touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. With advanced safety features and a tough, versatile design, this RAV4 variant is well-suited for both daily use and weekend getaways.

name: Toyota Estima
description: Aeras is the sporty trim of the Toyota Estima, a premium MPV that seamlessly combines style, spaciousness, and modern features, making it an excellent choice for families and those needing versatility. With its distinctive aerodynamic silhouette and eye-catching exterior details, including unique bumpers and alloy wheels, the Aeras variant stands out on the road. Inside, the Estima Aeras offers a roomy and well-appointed cabin, capable of comfortably seating up to seven passengers, with flexible seating configurations and ample cargo space to accommodate various needs. Equipped with advanced technology such as a touchscreen infotainment system and a comprehensive suite of safety features, it enhances the overall driving experience. Additionally, with efficient engine options, including hybrid variants, the Estima Aeras delivers a smooth ride and commendable fuel economy, making it a practical yet stylish vehicle for everyday use.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: The Toyota Harrier is a stylish mid-size crossover SUV that expertly combines sophistication with practicality, making it a sought-after choice for those in need of a versatile vehicle. Its sleek, aerodynamic exterior is characterized by bold lines, a distinctive front grille, and elegant LED headlights, lending it a modern and upscale appearance. Inside, the Harrier boasts a spacious cabin adorned with high-quality materials, comfortable seating, and advanced technology, including an intuitive infotainment system and a comprehensive suite of safety features. With a focus on comfort, it offers ample legroom and cargo space, ideal for daily commutes and family adventures. Engine options typically include efficient petrol and hybrid powertrains, ensuring a smooth and responsive driving experience. Known for its reliability and the brand's commitment to quality, the Harrier is an excellent blend of performance and style for those who appreciate aesthetics without compromising functionality.

name: Mazda Familia
description: The Mazda Familia is a compact car known for its reliability, practicality, and engaging driving experience, making it a popular choice for budget-conscious consumers. Featuring a sporty design with various body styles, including sedan, hatchback, and wagon, the Familia offers a comfortable interior with ample space for both passengers and cargo. Its range of fuel-efficient engines strikes a balance between performance and economy, while the car’s lightweight chassis and responsive steering enhance its nimble handling. With solid build quality and low maintenance costs, the Mazda Familia delivers a dependable and enjoyable ride, ideal for city driving and beyond.

name: Mercedes Benz E350
description: The 2010 Mercedes-Benz E350 (W211) is a luxury sedan known for its refined elegance, advanced technology, and strong performance. Powered by a 3.5-liter V6 engine, it produces 268 horsepower and 350 Nm of torque, providing smooth and responsive acceleration. The E350 balances comfort and power, accelerating from 0 to 100 km/h in around 6.5 seconds, making it both quick and composed. Its classic, understated exterior is complemented by a luxurious interior featuring high-quality materials, advanced infotainment, and a host of safety features. With its smooth ride, spacious cabin, and prestigious feel, the 2010 E350 offers a perfect blend of performance, comfort, and Mercedes-Benz reliability.

description: D4 refers to the 2.0-liter turbocharged diesel engine found in the Volvo V60 D4, offering a blend of efficiency and performance. Known for its smooth power delivery, this engine produces 190 horsepower and 400 Nm of torque, making it ideal for both highway cruising and city driving. The V60 D4 delivers excellent fuel economy, with figures typically around 20-22 km/l in combined driving conditions. Paired with Volvo's refined design, premium interior materials, and advanced safety features, the V60 D4 is a versatile and luxurious option for those seeking practicality and efficiency in a stylish package.

name: Nissan Bluebird
description: The Nissan Bluebird is a mid-size sedan that has built a reputation for its reliability, comfort, and practicality. Known for its understated design, the Bluebird offers a spacious and well-appointed interior, providing ample legroom and a comfortable ride for both driver and passengers. Its straightforward design focuses on functionality, making it a dependable choice for daily commuting and family use. Equipped with fuel-efficient engines, the Bluebird balances performance with economy, delivering a smooth driving experience. Over its various generations, the Bluebird has become synonymous with durability and low maintenance, appealing to those seeking a reliable and affordable sedan without compromising on comfort.

name: Toyota Fielder
description: The WXB version of the Toyota Corolla Fielder adds a sporty and upscale touch to the standard model, with distinctive black accents, unique alloy wheels, and sleek LED headlights that give it a bold, dynamic look. Inside, the WXB trim elevates the driving experience with premium materials, advanced technology, and added comfort features. Despite its stylish upgrades, the Fielder WXB retains its practical roots, offering a spacious cabin with flexible seating and generous cargo space, making it ideal for both everyday commutes and family trips. Powered by efficient engines, it delivers a smooth and reliable performance, combining the versatility of a wagon with the sleekness and sophistication of the WXB styling.

name: Peugeot  3008
description: The Peugeot 3008 is a stylish and refined compact SUV that stands out for its distinctive design, modern technology, and comfortable interior. Its bold exterior features sharp lines, a prominent front grille, and striking LED headlights, giving it a sophisticated yet dynamic look. Inside, the 3008 offers a premium cabin with high-quality materials, Peugeot’s innovative i-Cockpit, and a large touchscreen infotainment system, creating a futuristic and driver-focused experience. It provides ample space for passengers and cargo, making it practical for families or long trips. With efficient engine options and responsive handling, the Peugeot 3008 delivers a smooth and engaging driving experience, blending elegance with everyday practicality.

name: Toyota Rav4
description: The Toyota RAV4 is a versatile compact SUV that combines reliability, practicality, and modern design, making it a top choice for both urban driving and outdoor adventures. Its bold exterior features a strong front grille and sleek lines, while the spacious interior comfortably seats five and offers ample cargo space. Equipped with advanced technology, including an intuitive infotainment system and Toyota's Safety Sense features, the RAV4 ensures a safe and convenient driving experience. Powered by fuel-efficient engines and available in both front-wheel and all-wheel drive options, it delivers a smooth, balanced ride with the capability for light off-roading. Known for its dependability and low running costs, the RAV4 continues to be a go-to choice for those seeking a practical and reliable SUV.

name: Nissan Tiida
description: The Nissan Tiida is a practical and reliable compact car, available in both hatchback and sedan versions, known for its spacious interior and fuel efficiency. Its design emphasizes simplicity and functionality, with a tall roofline and large windows providing excellent visibility and ample headroom. Inside, the Tiida offers a surprisingly roomy cabin with comfortable seating, especially in the rear, making it ideal for families and daily commuters. Equipped with modern features like air conditioning and an intuitive infotainment system, it balances comfort with convenience. Powered by efficient engines, the Tiida delivers solid performance for both city driving and longer journeys, making it a versatile and budget-friendly choice.

name: Audi SQ5
description: The Audi SQ5 is a luxury performance SUV that blends sporty capabilities with premium comfort. It features a powerful 3.0-liter V6 turbocharged engine, delivering strong acceleration and a dynamic driving experience. The exterior is sleek and modern, with a distinctive Audi design that includes a bold grille and sharp LED lighting. Inside, the SQ5 offers a sophisticated cabin with high-quality materials, advanced technology, and spacious seating for five. It’s equipped with Audi’s Quattro all-wheel-drive system, ensuring confident handling in various driving conditions. Overall, the SQ5 is designed for those who seek a combination of performance, luxury, and practicality in their vehicle.

Its lightweight build ensures nimble handling and maneuverability, perfect for city commutes. While simple in terms of features, the Daihatsu Mira stands out for its reliability and cost-effective performance, appealing to budget-conscious drivers who prioritize practicality.

description: The second-generation Nissan X-Trail, produced from 2007 to 2013, is a versatile compact SUV that combines practicality with off-road capability. While retaining the rugged, boxy look of its predecessor, it introduces a more refined design with a larger grille, updated headlights, and smoother lines. Its high ground clearance and durable exterior make it well-suited for both urban driving and rough terrains. Inside, the X-Trail offers a spacious and flexible cabin, with foldable rear seats to expand cargo space and modern conveniences like an advanced infotainment system and climate control. Powered by efficient engines, the second-gen X-Trail delivers a balanced performance, offering both fuel efficiency and capability for adventurous drivers.

name: Toyota Hilux
description: The seventh-generation Toyota Hilux, produced from 2004 to 2015, is celebrated for its rugged reliability and off-road prowess. It features a muscular design with a bold grille, larger headlights, and higher ground clearance, giving it a tough, commanding presence. Built for both work and adventure, it offers a spacious cargo bed and strong towing capabilities. Inside, the cabin is functional and comfortable, with user-friendly controls and varying levels of equipment depending on the trim. Powered by durable and powerful engines, the seventh-gen Hilux is known for its exceptional durability, making it a go-to choice in demanding environments worldwide.

name: Lexus LX600
description: The Lexus LX600 is a luxury full-size SUV that masterfully blends off-road capability with refined comfort and advanced technology. Its bold exterior features Lexus' signature spindle grille and sharp LED headlights, giving it a commanding presence on the road, while its rugged design is complemented by elegant touches. Inside, the LX600 offers a premium cabin with high-quality materials, leather upholstery, and wood accents, ensuring a luxurious experience for all passengers. Equipped with cutting-edge technology, including a large infotainment system and a suite of safety features, it delivers a seamless driving experience. Powered by a robust engine, the LX600 offers smooth performance across all terrains, making it a top choice for those who seek luxury and adventure in one package.

name: Toyota Alphard
description: The first-generation Toyota Alphard, launched in 2002, is a luxury MPV that emphasizes comfort and versatility, making it an ideal choice for families and premium travel enthusiasts. Its distinctive boxy silhouette features a bold front grille and prominent headlights, contributing to its upscale appearance. Inside, the spacious cabin accommodates up to eight passengers, boasting high-quality materials and a range of amenities, including advanced audio systems and climate control for a pleasant journey. The flexible seating configurations allow for easy adaptation of the interior to suit both passenger and cargo needs. With a smooth ride and powerful engine options, the first-generation Alphard has earned a reputation as a well-rounded vehicle that seamlessly blends luxury with practicality.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The Mazda CX-5 is a stylish and versatile compact SUV that seamlessly combines sporty performance with everyday practicality. Its sleek exterior showcases Mazda's Kodo design philosophy, featuring flowing lines, a bold grille, and striking LED headlights that create a dynamic and upscale look. Inside, the CX-5 offers a well-crafted cabin with high-quality materials, comfortable seating, and an intuitive infotainment system, making it perfect for both daily commutes and longer journeys. With a choice of efficient engines that deliver spirited performance and responsive handling, the CX-5 embodies Mazda's commitment to driving enjoyment. Its spacious interior provides ample cargo space and thoughtful storage solutions, appealing to families and outdoor enthusiasts alike, making the CX-5 a standout choice in the competitive compact SUV segment.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado
description: Nothing better than a fully loaded J120 Series Toyota Landcruiser Prado with a range of premium specs including a Sunroof, powered seats made of leather material, 8 seats occupancy capacity, and a fully functional infotainment system. This was initially owned in the United Kingdom. The 1KD 3.0 Turbocharged engine is a moving magic that just carries anything thrown at it except bad maintenance. Family units very well fit the car and long distance trips or offroading eacapades are the best with this J120!

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI
description: The MK7 Volkswagen Golf TSI combines sleek design with turbocharged efficiency, offering a refined yet practical driving experience. Its clean exterior lines, wide grille, and sharp headlights give it a modern and timeless look. Inside, the cabin is spacious and well-appointed with high-quality materials and intuitive controls. The turbocharged TSI engine provides a responsive and efficient performance, making it suitable for both city driving and longer trips. With its balanced handling, comfortable ride, and impressive fuel economy, the MK7 Golf TSI is a versatile compact hatchback that blends style, practicality, and performance.

name: Toyota Probox
description: The first-generation Toyota Probox, launched in 2002, is a compact station wagon built for practicality and durability. Its boxy, utilitarian design maximizes interior space, making it ideal for commercial use or transporting goods. The simple front fascia with rectangular headlights and a flat rear enhances functionality, while the interior offers a no-frills, hard-wearing environment focused on utility. With foldable rear seats for expanded cargo space and a reputation for reliability and fuel efficiency, the first-generation Probox quickly became a favorite for businesses and individuals seeking a dependable, cost-effective workhorse.

Under the hood, it delivers peppy performance and nimble handling, making it fun and responsive for city driving, while maintaining excellent fuel efficiency. The Swift RS is an ideal choice for drivers who want a blend of style, practicality, and sporty flair.

name: Audi A3
description: The Audi A3 is a premium compact car known for its stylish design, advanced technology, and refined driving experience. Inside, it features a high-quality, well-appointed cabin with modern tech like Audi's MMI infotainment system. The A3 offers a range of efficient turbocharged engines, providing both performance and fuel efficiency, while its precise handling ensures a smooth and enjoyable drive.

name: Toyota Probox
description: The Toyota Probox is a compact, utilitarian station wagon designed for practicality and efficiency. Its boxy exterior maximizes cargo space, making it ideal for commercial use and transporting goods. Inside, the cabin is simple and functional, with easy-to-use controls and plenty of storage space. While it lacks luxury features, the Probox excels in reliability and fuel efficiency, offering a durable and cost-effective option for businesses or individuals looking for a dependable workhorse vehicle. Its straightforward design and low maintenance needs make it a popular choice for those prioritizing utility over style.

description: The Mazda Bongo is a versatile and practical van, popular for both commercial and personal use due to its spacious interior and flexible configurations. Known for its reliability and ease of handling, the Bongo offers ample cargo or passenger space, making it ideal for transporting goods or people. Its compact dimensions make it easy to maneuver in tight urban settings, while the sturdy build ensures durability and long-term usability. With various seating arrangements and options, the Bongo is a practical choice for businesses, families, or anyone needing a reliable and functional van for everyday use.

name: Subaru Impreza
description: The fifth-generation Subaru Impreza is a compact car known for its standard all-wheel drive, offering excellent traction and handling in various conditions. Built on Subaru's Global Platform, it delivers improved stability, comfort, and safety. Available in both sedan and hatchback variants, the Impreza features a modern, well-designed interior with advanced technology, including an intuitive infotainment system with smartphone integration. With available Subaru EyeSight driver assistance, the Impreza provides enhanced safety features like adaptive cruise control and lane-keeping assist. Combining practicality, reliability, and a smooth driving experience, it’s a versatile choice for both city commuting and weekend adventures.

name: Subaru XV
description: The Subaru XV is a compact crossover that blends rugged off-road capability with urban practicality. Known for its standard all-wheel-drive system and higher ground clearance, the XV is well-suited for a variety of terrains, making it a favorite for outdoor enthusiasts. Its compact size ensures easy maneuverability in city driving, while the spacious interior provides comfort for passengers and cargo alike. Equipped with Subaru’s EyeSight safety suite and advanced infotainment features, the XV offers a balance of modern technology and safety. With its reliable performance and versatility, the Subaru XV is an ideal choice for those seeking adventure without sacrificing everyday usability.

name: Nissan Wingroad

description: The Lexus RX 450h is a luxury hybrid SUV that combines premium comfort with fuel efficiency and advanced technology. Its smooth ride, luxurious amenities, and hybrid efficiency make it an attractive choice for those seeking a blend of environmental responsibility and luxury.

name: Toyota Passo
description: The Toyota Passo is a compact hatchback designed for city driving, offering practicality, efficiency, and ease of use. With its small footprint and tight turning radius, the Passo excels in navigating urban streets and parking in tight spaces. Despite its compact size, the interior is surprisingly spacious, providing comfortable seating for passengers and a versatile cargo area. Known for its fuel efficiency, the Passo is a cost-effective choice for daily commutes. Its simple yet functional design, coupled with Toyota's reputation for reliability, makes the Passo a popular option for those seeking an affordable and dependable city car.

description: XD-L denotes the diesel variant of the Mazda CX-5, offering a blend of power and efficiency in a stylish and versatile SUV. With its sleek design and sporty lines, the CX-5 XD-L stands out on the road, while its spacious interior provides ample comfort and functionality for both passengers and cargo. The diesel engine delivers robust performance with impressive torque, ensuring a responsive driving experience, complemented by Mazda’s renowned handling dynamics. Inside, the cabin is well-appointed with high-quality materials, advanced technology, and a focus on driver comfort, making it ideal for both daily commutes and longer journeys. Overall, the CX-5 XD-L combines practicality with a touch of luxury, appealing to those seeking a refined yet capable SUV.

name: Nissan Note
description: The first-generation Nissan Note, introduced in 2004, is a compact hatchback that emphasizes practicality and spaciousness. Its tall, boxy design provides ample interior room, offering generous headroom and legroom, especially for a car of its size. The rear seats are highly versatile, allowing for flexible cargo configurations, making it ideal for families or those needing extra storage. With a comfortable ride and excellent fuel efficiency, the Note is well-suited for city driving and daily commutes. Its straightforward, user-friendly technology adds to its appeal as an efficient, functional, and affordable compact car.

name: Audi A6
description: The Audi A6 is a luxury sedan that embodies sophistication, performance, and cutting-edge technology. With its sleek design featuring sharp lines and a bold front grille, the A6 makes a striking impression. Inside, the cabin is a blend of high-quality materials and advanced infotainment systems, offering a spacious and comfortable environment for both driver and passengers.

name: Mercedes Benz E280
description: The Mercedes-Benz W211, produced from 2002 to 2009, is the third generation of the E-Class and is celebrated for its blend of luxury, performance, and advanced technology. Its sleek, elegant design is complemented by a spacious, high-quality interior with modern features for its time, including optional air suspension and advanced safety systems like Pre-Safe. Offering a smooth and refined driving experience, the W211 came with a range of engines, catering to both comfort-focused drivers and performance enthusiasts. Known for its solid build quality and timeless appeal, the W211 remains a popular choice for those seeking a luxurious yet reliable sedan.

name: KPR200
description: The Skygo KPR200 is a lightweight sportbike that offers an affordable entry into the motorcycle market, particularly popular in regions like Southeast Asia. Equipped with a 200cc engine, it provides a balance of performance and fuel efficiency, making it suitable for both city commuting and light touring. The KPR200 features a sporty design, with aggressive styling and a sleek fairing that gives it a bold presence on the road. It also comes with essential features like digital instrumentation and disc brakes, ensuring a modern and safe riding experience. Overall, the Skygo KPR200 is a practical and stylish option for riders seeking a budget-friendly yet capable sportbike.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: Turbo diesel power defines this 2013 Subaru Forester, offering a strong balance of performance and efficiency. The turbocharged diesel engine delivers impressive torque, enhancing off-road capability and towing power while maintaining excellent fuel economy for its class. Combined with Subaru’s symmetrical all-wheel-drive system, the Forester ensures optimal traction and stability across various terrains, making it perfect for both city driving and outdoor adventures. Inside, it features a spacious and comfortable cabin with plenty of cargo room, making it a practical and reliable choice for those seeking versatility and rugged performance.

name: Suzuki Wagon R
description: The Suzuki Wagon R is a compact and practical hatchback designed with a focus on maximizing interior space and fuel efficiency. Its tall, boxy design allows for a surprisingly roomy cabin, offering excellent headroom and flexible seating configurations, making it ideal for urban driving and small families. Known for its easy maneuverability and impressive fuel economy, the Wagon R is perfect for city commutes and tight parking spaces. The simple, functional interior is complemented by basic but essential technology, ensuring comfort and convenience. Overall, the Wagon R is a reliable and affordable option for those seeking a compact car with practical benefits.

Known for its sleek yet understated design, it provides a spacious and comfortable interior with user-friendly technology and durable materials. The Allion delivers a smooth and quiet ride, making it ideal for both city commuting and long-distance journeys. Its strong reputation for reliability, combined with low maintenance costs and excellent fuel economy, makes it a popular choice for families and professionals alike, offering practicality and peace of mind in a refined package.

name: Toyota Alphard
description: The Toyota Alphard is a luxury minivan designed to provide top-tier comfort and refinement, and the version with a double sunroof elevates the experience even further. Known for its spacious and opulent interior, the Alphard offers plush seating for up to seven or eight passengers, depending on the configuration. The double sunroof floods the cabin with natural light, enhancing the sense of space and luxury. High-quality materials, advanced technology, and features such as reclining seats with ottomans in higher trims create a first-class travel experience. The Alphard combines a smooth, quiet ride with cutting-edge convenience, making it ideal for both family and executive transport.

name: Toyota Hilux
description: The 2013 Toyota Hilux Double Cabin is a rugged and reliable pickup truck known for its durability and off-road capability. With its spacious double-cabin configuration, it comfortably accommodates five passengers while still offering a practical cargo bed for hauling. The Hilux is designed for tough environments, featuring a robust chassis and high ground clearance, making it capable of handling rough terrain with ease. Inside, the cabin provides a no-nonsense, durable interior with modern conveniences, ensuring both comfort and functionality. The 2013 Hilux is a popular choice for both work and recreational use, thanks to its reliability, versatility, and proven performance in challenging conditions.

description: Hybrid drivetrain technology is often seen as the future, and many appreciate the hybrid system in the Vezel, especially in today’s economic climate. name: Nissan Murano
description: The Nissan Murano is a mid-size crossover SUV known for its bold styling, comfortable ride, and upscale interior. Designed with a sleek exterior and a spacious, luxurious cabin, it offers comfortable seating, high-quality materials, and intuitive technology, including a user-friendly infotainment system. Powered by a V6 engine, the Murano delivers smooth acceleration and is well-suited for both daily commuting and long road trips. While not built for off-roading, its available all-wheel-drive system provides added stability in various weather conditions. Overall, the Murano is ideal for those seeking a stylish, comfortable, and refined SUV.

Known for its fuel efficiency and smooth handling, the 2008 provides a stylish, practical option for those seeking a versatile crossover in a compact package.

name: Toyota Landcruiser VX
description: The Toyota Land Cruiser LC200 with a 4200cc V8 turbodiesel engine delivers excellent towing capacity and strong off-road performance, making it well-suited for rugged terrains. The LC200 accelerates smoothly, with its advanced four-wheel-drive system ensuring stability and traction in various conditions. It also features a spacious and luxurious interior, accommodating up to eight passengers, with high-quality materials and advanced technology. This blend of power, comfort, and capability solidifies the Land Cruiser LC200's reputation as a top choice for both off-road enthusiasts and families seeking a reliable SUV.

name: Nissan Xtrail
description: The Nissan X-Trail T30, produced from 2001 to 2007, is a compact SUV renowned for its practicality and off-road capability. Featuring a distinctive design and a high ride height, it offers a spacious interior that comfortably seats five passengers, along with versatile cargo space. Available with various engine options and both two-wheel and all-wheel drive, the T30 excels in diverse driving conditions. Its robust chassis and capable four-wheel-drive system enhance off-road performance, while the interior is designed for comfort and functionality with user-friendly technology. The X-Trail T30 is celebrated for its reliability and versatility, making it a popular choice among families and adventure seekers.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The Mercedes-Benz C200 with air suspension offers a luxurious driving experience, combining elegant design with advanced technology. Its sleek exterior features a chrome grille and sharp LED headlights, while the air suspension ensures a smooth ride over uneven surfaces, with adjustable ride height for various conditions. Inside, the cabin showcases high-quality materials, leather upholstery, and ambient lighting, creating a premium atmosphere. The C200 effectively blends performance, comfort, and style, setting a benchmark for refinement in the luxury sedan segment.

name: Audi Q5
description: This Audi Q5 exudes a sleek yet rugged aura, combining elegance with practicality. Its deep black paintwork gleams under the light, giving it a sophisticated yet imposing presence on the road. The bold, single-frame grille is flanked by angular, high-tech LED headlights, contributing to a sharp and assertive front profile. The slightly flared wheel arches house large, polished black alloy wheels with an intricate spoke design, hinting at its performance potential. The roofline has a subtle slope towards the rear, enhancing its aerodynamic silhouette, while the tinted windows and roof rails add a touch of utility. This Q5 blends modern luxury with a hint of adventure, perfect for those seeking refinement without sacrificing capability.

name: Volkswagen Polo
description: The Polo Vivo is a popular compact hatchback from Volkswagen, known for its affordability, reliability, and solid build quality. Designed as a more budget-friendly alternative to the standard Polo, the Polo Vivo retains Volkswagen's signature clean design and robust engineering. Its interior is practical and comfortable, offering decent space for passengers and cargo, with straightforward controls and features. The Polo Vivo is also praised for its fuel efficiency, making it an economical choice for daily commuting. Its combination of durability, low maintenance costs, and respectable performance makes it a popular choice in markets where affordability and reliability are key.

name: Mazda CX3
description: The Mazda CX-3 is a subcompact crossover that blends stylish design with a sporty driving experience. Its sleek exterior features Mazda’s signature "KODO" design language, giving it a modern and premium look despite its compact size. Inside, the CX-3 offers a well-crafted cabin with quality materials and a driver-focused layout, making it both comfortable and visually appealing. The CX-3 is also known for its responsive handling and smooth ride, standing out as one of the more dynamic options in its class. Its compact dimensions make it easy to navigate in city environments, while its fuel efficiency and tech features like a touchscreen infotainment system and advanced safety options round out its appeal as a practical yet fun crossover.

name: Ford Everest
description: The 2014 Ford Everest is a mid-size SUV known for its robust build and versatility, catering to both off-road enthusiasts and families. With its body-on-frame construction, the Everest offers impressive durability and off-road capability, making it suitable for various terrains. Inside, the cabin is spacious, providing comfortable seating for up to seven passengers, along with ample cargo space. The 2014 model features modern amenities, including an intuitive infotainment system and advanced safety features, enhancing its appeal for everyday use. Its powerful engine options deliver solid performance, whether navigating city streets or tackling rugged trails, making the Everest a reliable choice for those seeking adventure without sacrificing comfort.

name: Porsche Cayenne
description: The first-generation Porsche Cayenne, launched in 2002, was Porsche's bold move into the SUV market, blending luxury with the brand’s signature sports car performance. It offered impressive on-road agility and handling, rare for an SUV, while still maintaining off-road capability with advanced all-wheel-drive. The Cayenne featured a spacious, high-quality interior, delivering both comfort and practicality. It stood out for its versatility, providing a refined daily driving experience alongside the ability to tackle tougher terrains, all while upholding Porsche’s reputation for performance and reliability.

name: Toyota Mark X
description: The Toyota Mark X stands out as a sedan that offers a blend of luxury and a touch of performance often unexpected in its class. Beyond its stylish design, what sets it apart is its rear-wheel-drive platform, which gives it a more dynamic and sporty driving experience compared to typical front-wheel-drive sedans. The Mark X was crafted to appeal to drivers looking for a balance between comfort and agility, with precise handling that's almost reminiscent of a sports sedan. Its long-term reliability and high resale value have also made it a practical investment, appealing to those who desire a car that can serve both as a daily driver and as something special for spirited drives.

name: Audi A5
description: The Audi A5 is a premium compact coupe, known for its sleek design, refined driving dynamics, and high-quality interior. It combines sporty performance with everyday comfort, offering precise handling and a smooth ride. The A5 features a modern, minimalist interior with advanced technology, including a digital cockpit and high-end infotainment system. Its spacious cabin provides comfortable seating, and the build quality reflects Audi's attention to detail. The A5’s distinctive design, highlighted by its flowing lines and aggressive front grille, gives it an upscale presence on the road, making it a stylish and luxurious option in its segment.

name: Nissan Xtrail
description: The first-generation Nissan X-Trail, launched in 2000, is a compact SUV known for its blend of practicality, affordability, and off-road capability. It features a boxy design, offering good visibility and a spacious interior with ample cargo room. The X-Trail's all-wheel-drive system and rugged build make it suitable for light off-road adventures while remaining comfortable and easy to drive in urban settings. Reliability is a key strength, with owners praising its durability and low maintenance costs. Its combination of versatility, practicality, and affordability made it a popular choice for families and outdoor enthusiasts alike.

name: Toyota Corolla 110
description: The Toyota Corolla 110 is renowned for its exceptional reliability, often lasting hundreds of thousands of kilometers with routine maintenance. Its simple engineering and durable components make it easy and affordable to maintain, with parts readily available and relatively inexpensive. The Corolla 110's practicality extends to its comfortable seating, ample trunk space, and efficient use of fuel, making it a budget-friendly option for daily commuting or family use. Its low running costs, combined with its long-lasting nature, contribute to its reputation as one of the most affordable and dependable vehicles in its class.

name: Nissan Note
description: The Nissan Note is a compact hatchback that combines practicality with modern features, making it ideal for city driving. Its design emphasizes spaciousness and efficiency, with a roomy interior that comfortably accommodates passengers despite its compact size.

name: Range Rover Sport SVR
description: The Range Rover Sport SVR is a high-performance luxury SUV that blends powerful performance with sophisticated design and comfort. It features a bold exterior with aggressive styling and enhanced aerodynamic elements. Inside, the SVR offers a premium, sport-oriented interior with high-quality materials, supportive sports seats, and advanced technology. It includes a high-resolution infotainment system, premium audio, and a range of comfort features such as heated and ventilated seats. The SVR model is designed to deliver an exhilarating driving experience while maintaining the Range Rover's signature luxury and versatility

name: Bentley Bentayga
description: The Bentley Bentayga W12 is a luxurious high-performance SUV that exemplifies Bentley's commitment to opulence and power. It features a 6.0-liter W12 engine that delivers exceptional performance and acceleration. The Bentayga W12 boasts a richly appointed interior with top-tier materials, advanced technology, and extensive customization options, ensuring a highly refined driving experience. Combining powerful performance with unparalleled luxury, the Bentayga W12 is designed for those seeking both comfort and high-end performance in a premium SUV.

name: Mazda Bongo
description: The Mazda Bongo is a versatile van known for its practicality and spacious interior. It features a flexible layout, with sliding side doors for easy access and ample cargo space. Popular for both commercial use and as a family vehicle, the Bongo is compact enough for urban driving while offering comfortable seating and reliability, making it a functional choice for various needs.

name: Nissan Note
description: The Nismo trim in the Nissan Note focuses on efficiency while still offering sporty styling and handling. The Nismo trim features a sport-tuned suspension, distinctive exterior accents, and enhanced interior details for a sportier feel. It typically delivers good fuel economy, making it a practical choice for those seeking a fun driving experience in a compact package.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The Subaru Forester SK9 stands out with its rugged design and advanced safety features. It offers a spacious interior, all-wheel drive, and a robust 2.5-liter flat-four engine, delivering a blend of power and efficiency. A unique feature is its impressive off-road capability, enhanced by the X-MODE system, which optimizes traction on challenging terrain. The Forester also emphasizes eco-friendliness, with a focus on sustainable materials in its construction.

name: Porsche Cayenne
description: The Diesel Porsche Cayenne is a luxury SUV that combines performance with efficiency. Powered by a turbocharged diesel engine, it offers a balance of strong torque and fuel economy, making it ideal for long-distance driving. The Cayenne Diesel provides the sporty handling Porsche is known for, with responsive steering and smooth acceleration, while maintaining the practicality of an SUV. Inside, it features a premium cabin with high-quality materials, modern infotainment, and ample space for passengers and cargo. The Cayenne Diesel is appreciated for its blend of luxury, performance, and versatility, offering both driving excitement and everyday usability.

name: Mercedes Benz GLE350d
description: The Mercedes-Benz GLE350d is a luxury midsize SUV that offers a refined driving experience, combining comfort, advanced technology, and efficiency. Inside, the GLE350d features a premium cabin with high-quality materials, spacious seating for up to five passengers, and a large cargo area. It comes equipped with modern amenities, including a large touchscreen infotainment system and a suite of driver assistance features for added convenience and safety. With its blend of practicality and luxury, the GLE350d is well-suited for both daily commuting and long trips.

name: Audi S3
description: Audi S3 twins with the popular Volkswagen Golf R. It is a hot hatch version of the A3. This is the 3rd Gen, internally coded Typ 8V, produced from 2013 to 2020. This model uses the 3rd Gen EA888 2.0L I4 turbo engine with a power rating of 300hp mated to a 6 speed S Tronic dual clutch transmission. It has a 6-speed manual transmission and Quattro All Wheel drive system as standard. A facelift was done mid-2016 with the major changes being the taillights with dynamic indicators, angular headlights than before, visually appealing front and rear bumpers plus diffuser, and of course the big trade being the 10 more horsepower added post-facelift

name: Mercedes Benz E220d
description: The Mercedes-Benz E220d All-Terrain is a versatile and rugged estate car designed to handle both city roads and rougher terrain. It features SUV-like styling with increased ground clearance, body cladding, and all-wheel drive. Inside, it offers the luxury and advanced technology typical of Mercedes-Benz, along with a spacious and comfortable cabin. Ideal for those who need the practicality of an estate with added off-road capability.

name: Toyota Premio
description: The Toyota Premio is a mid-size sedan known for its reliability, comfort, and understated elegance. It offers a refined driving experience with a smooth ride, making it ideal for daily commuting and long-distance travel. The Premio features a spacious and well-designed interior, with high-quality materials and a range of modern amenities. It’s also recognized for its fuel efficiency and low maintenance costs, making it a practical choice for families or professionals seeking a reliable and comfortable vehicle. With a focus on comfort and simplicity, the Toyota Premio appeals to those who value functionality and refinement in a sedan.

name: VOLKSWAGEN GOLF GTI MK7.5
description: Golf GTI MK7.5 is a high-performance hatchback with a sporty design, featuring a 2.0-liter turbocharged engine producing about 245 horsepower. It has a driver-focused interior with sport seats and modern technology. Known for its agile handling and quick acceleration, it offers a 0-100 km/h time of around 6.2 seconds. The GTI MK7.5 also includes advanced safety and driver assistance features.

name: HONDA VEZEL HYBRID
description: The Vezel Hybrid is powered by a 1.5-liter Atkinson-cycle petrol engine paired with an electric motor. This hybrid powertrain provides a smooth and efficient driving experience, combining good fuel economy with responsive performance. The hybrid system is designed to optimize fuel efficiency while delivering a comfortable ride.

name: MAZDA CX-3 XD-L
description: CX-3 features Mazda's signature Kodo design language, with a sleek, aerodynamic profile and a prominent front grille. Its compact size makes it well-suited for urban driving, while its bold design elements give it a distinctive, sporty look.

name: VOLKSWAGEN TIGUAN
description: Volkswagen Tiguan is a compact SUV known for its stylish design, comfortable interior, and versatile features. It offers a range of engine options, including efficient petrol and diesel engines, and comes with a choice of front-wheel or all-wheel drive. Inside, it provides a spacious cabin with high-quality materials and advanced technology, including an infotainment system with smartphone integration. The Tiguan is praised for its refined handling, smooth ride, and practical cargo space, making it a popular choice for families and individuals seeking a well-rounded SUV.

name: Nissan Dayz
description: Nissan DAYZ is a very efficient car for running the daily constant errands as with the Uber business. It is a very spacious, Comfortable, and convenient car. This unit has beige fabric seats with a tone of brown color on its edges. Powered by a 660cc, consumption levels are extremely good in this unit with up to 20Kms a liter on the minimum.

name: AUDI A5 CABRIOLET
description: The Audi A5 Cabriolet is a luxury convertible with a sleek design and refined interior. It features a fully automatic soft-top roof, a high-quality cabin with leather upholstery, and advanced infotainment options. Engine choices include a 252-horsepower 2.0L TFSI petrol engine, offering a blend of performance and efficiency. The car is equipped with Audi’s Quattro all-wheel-drive and a 7-speed dual-clutch transmission for smooth driving. Safety features include multiple airbags and available driver assistance systems. The A5 Cabriolet combines stylish design with a comfortable and engaging driving experience.

name: TOYOTA AURIS
description: The Toyota Auris is a compact hatchback designed to offer a balance between practicality, efficiency, and a touch of sportiness. Positioned as a successor to the Toyota Corolla hatchback in many markets,It represents Toyota’s efforts to cater to the demands of modern drivers who seek a versatile vehicle for urban commuting as well as longer journeys.

name: AUDI A3

Its Quattro all-wheel drive system enhances traction and stability, making every drive both dynamic and confident. Inside, the S5 is a meticulously crafted interior with premium materials and advanced technology, including a state-of-the-art infotainment system and comprehensive driver assistance features. The sleek, sporty design of the S5 is complemented by its refined elegance, making it a standout choice for those who seek both performance and luxury.Audi S5 combines style, comfort, and excitement in one remarkable package.

Cargo and Towing: Provides substantial cargo space, especially when the third-row seats are folded down. It's capable of towing heavy loads, making it versatile for both family trips and towing needs.

name: VOLKSWAGEN TIGUAN ALLSPACE
description: The Volkswagen Tiguan Allspace is a mid-size SUV with three-row seating for up to seven passengers. It offers a turbocharged engine, spacious interior, advanced technology, and a comfortable ride, making it a family-friendly option.

name: RANGE ROVER SPORT AUTOBIOGRAPHY
description: The Range Rover Sport Autobiography is a luxury SUV known for class, premium interior, and advanced off-road capabilities. It blends performance and comfort, with high-end materials, customizable features, and advanced technology. The Autobiography trim adds extra luxury and refinement, making it a top choice for those seeking both sophistication and rugged capability.

name: Volkswagen Tiguan
description: The Volkswagen Tiguan sits between the Touareg and T-Roc which ranks it as an excellent crossover of this class. It offers a very good balance between comfort, performance, and luxury. This unit comes fitted with leather seats, Multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, android infor **** tainment display system, parking sensors, rear retractable mini-tables for the rear occupants, electric handbrake, and side mirror indicators.

name: Volvo XC60
description: The XC60 comes in a number of trims and variants that satisfy customers with different preferences. The T5 is one of them which is the petrol variant powered by a 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine with a power rating of 240hp. It is fitted with a polished metal trimming on the interior, leather seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, and cruise control among other features.

name: BMW X5 XDrive35d
description: The BMW X5 xDrive35d is a midsize luxury SUV known for its blend of performance, comfort, and practicality. The xDrive35d model features a robust 3.0-liter inline-six diesel engine with twin-turbocharging, delivering strong acceleration and impressive fuel efficiency. The xDrive all-wheel-drive system ensures excellent traction and stability in various driving conditions.

name: SUBARU OUTBACK
description: The Subaru Outback is a versatile and rugged midsize crossover SUV known for its blend of practicality and capability. It features a standard all-wheel-drive system, which enhances its performance in various weather conditions and off-road scenarios. The Outback is powered by a choice of engines, including a 2.5-liter four-cylinder and a more powerful 3.6-liter six-cylinder.

name: BMW X1 XDrive18dx
description: The BMW X1 xDrive18d is a compact luxury SUV known for its sporty handling and practical design. It features BMW's xDrive all-wheel-drive system, which enhances traction and stability in various driving conditions. The X1 xDrive18d is powered by a fuel-efficient 2.0-liter four-cylinder diesel engine, delivering a balance of performance and efficiency.

name: JAGUAR XJ
description: The Jaguar XJ is a luxury full-size sedan known for its striking design and refined performance. It features a sleek, aerodynamic exterior and a sophisticated, well-crafted interior with high-quality materials and advanced technology. The XJ offers a range of engine options, including a supercharged V6 and a powerful V8, providing a blend of dynamic driving and smooth comfort.

name: MERCEDES BENZ S560L
description: The Mercedes-Benz S560L is a luxury sedan that exemplifies opulence and advanced technology. As part of the S-Class lineup, it offers a refined driving experience with a powerful 4.0-liter twin-turbo V8 engine, delivering impressive performance and smooth acceleration. The "L" in the name signifies its extended wheelbase, providing additional rear-seat space for enhanced comfort.

name: RANGE ROVER SPORT SDV6
description: The Range Rover Sport is a luxury SUV that offers a balance of performance, style, and versatility. Known for its dynamic on-road handling and strong off-road capabilities, the Range Rover Sport features a sleek, muscular design. Inside, it boasts a premium cabin with high-quality materials, advanced technology, and comfortable seating. Engine options range from efficient to high-performance, catering to various driving preferences. With features like a dual touchscreen infotainment system and advanced driver assistance, the Range Rover Sport is designed for those who seek luxury without compromising on capability.

name: TOYOTA LANDCRUISER ZX
description: The Toyota Land Cruiser ZX is a top-of-the-line luxury SUV known for its rugged durability and off-road prowess, combined with high-end comfort and advanced features. It comes equipped with a powerful V8 engine, providing strong performance both on and off the road. The Land Cruiser ZX features a robust four-wheel-drive system, adaptive variable suspension, and various off-road driving aids, making it capable of handling challenging terrains with ease.

name: Range Rover Vogue Autobiography
description: The Range Rover Vogue Ultimate Edition 4.4L SDV8 is a pinnacle of luxury in the SUV segment. It features an exceptionally refined interior with high-quality leather upholstery, wood and metal accents, and advanced technology. The cabin is designed for ultimate comfort, with heated and ventilated seats, multi-zone climate control, and a panoramic sunroof. Rear passengers enjoy executive-style seating. The Ultimate Edition also includes unique exterior styling elements and exclusive finishes, making it a standout choice for those seeking a blend of luxury, comfort, and sophisticated design.

name: RANGE ROVER SPORT
description: The Range Rover Sport is a luxury SUV that combines off-road capability with high-performance on-road driving. It features a stylish and muscular design, with a well-appointed interior that includes premium materials and advanced technology. This model offers a variety of powerful engine options, ranging from a supercharged V6 to a high-performance V8, and even a fuel-efficient diesel option.

name: Volkswagen Alltrack
description: The Volkswagen Golf Alltrack is a versatile and rugged version of the Golf wagon, designed for those who need extra capability and cargo space. It features standard all-wheel drive, higher ground clearance, and protective body cladding, making it well-suited for light off-road use and all-weather driving. The interior offers a practical and comfortable layout with high-quality materials, supportive seats, and a user-friendly infotainment system. The Golf Alltrack also includes features like a panoramic sunroof, heated front seats, and advanced safety technologies. It combines the practicality of a wagon with added versatility for outdoor adventures.

name: Range Rover Vogue
description: The L405 is definitely an excellently engineered car. Thanks to Jaguar Landrover, it created a highly stylish and exquisite car. It is lighter compared to the older L322 because of the All-Aluminium monocoque unitary body structure. This unit features perforated leather seats, fixed glassroof, heated steering wheel, memory seats package, and Meridian premium surround sound system.

name: VOLVO XC90
description: Volvo XC90 is a luxury midsize SUV known for its elegant design, advanced safety features, and a spacious, high-quality interior. It offers three rows of seating, making it a practical choice for families. The XC90 comes with a range of engine options, including a fuel-efficient four-cylinder and a powerful hybrid variant. Notable features include a user-friendly infotainment system, a minimalist interior design, and advanced driver assistance systems, like adaptive cruise control and lane-keeping assist. The 2017 XC90 is highly regarded for its blend of luxury, safety, and performance.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The Mazda CX-5 is a compact crossover SUV that combines stylish design with practicality and performance. It features a sleek exterior with Mazda's Kodo design philosophy, emphasizing clean lines and an elegant profile. Inside, the CX-5 offers a high-quality cabin with modern materials, a user-friendly infotainment system, and comfortable seating for passengers. It is known for its engaging driving dynamics, with responsive handling and a smooth ride. The CX-5 also includes a range of advanced safety and technology features, making it a well-rounded choice for those seeking a blend of style, comfort, and driving enjoyment.

name: Mazda Atenza
description: The Mazda Atenza, also known as the Mazda6 in some markets, is a mid-size sedan known for its stylish design and engaging driving experience. It features a sleek exterior with dynamic lines and a modern, upscale interior. Inside, the Atenza offers a comfortable and well-appointed cabin with high-quality materials, a user-friendly infotainment system, and available features such as leather upholstery, dual-zone climate control, and advanced driver assistance technologies. The Atenza is praised for its balance of performance, comfort, and efficiency.

name: Subaru Impreza
description: Impreza GP3, the AWD 1.6L Spec, is an excellent hatch to utilize with that it can be used for family purposes and chilled motorsports activities. It runs a 1.6L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine which comfortably handles its payload. On the interior, it is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, android infotainment display system, Multifunctional steering wheel, and a spoiler.

description: The last of its generation. Carina's production ended in 2001 after 31 years of production. This model, produced in 1998, is a gem that has lasted for over 25 years in pristine condition. The 5A-FE engine will last you another long period of great maintenance!

name: Mercedes-Benz AMG GLE43
description: The AMG GLE43 features a luxury interior with high-quality materials, including leather upholstery and trim. It includes advanced technology such as a user-friendly infotainment system with a high-resolution display, navigation, and smartphone integration. The SUV also offers a range of comfort features, including heated and ventilated seats, a panoramic sunroof, and a premium sound system. The design is sporty yet refined, with distinctive AMG styling elements that add to its upscale appeal.

name: Peugeot  2008
description: The Peugeot 2008 GT-Line is a compact crossover SUV with a sporty and stylish design. It features distinctive GT-Line styling cues such as a sporty grille, chrome accents, and unique alloy wheels. Inside, the GT-Line trim offers a more upscale interior with sports seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and a range of modern amenities like a touchscreen infotainment system, Bluetooth connectivity, and advanced driver assistance features. The 2008 GT-Line combines a practical compact size with a more dynamic and refined appearance.

name: Suzuki Swift
description: The Suzuki Swift is a compact hatchback with a practical and functional design. It features a straightforward exterior and a simple interior with essential amenities such as air conditioning and a standard audio system. The cabin is designed to be user-friendly with comfortable seating and straightforward controls, making it a practical choice for daily urban driving and commuting.

name: Porsche Cayenne GTS
description: The Porsche Cayenne GTS features a refined and luxurious interior with high-quality materials and advanced technology. It includes premium amenities such as leather upholstery, a high-resolution infotainment system, and a range of comfort features like heated and ventilated seats. The Cayenne GTS also offers a sophisticated exterior design with distinctive Porsche styling cues, and it provides a spacious cabin with ample room for both passengers and cargo.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The CX5 still gets preferential treatment in the market as it has rose to be a very preferred mid-size SUV amongst many individuals it being offered with a wide range of equipments that are not tradionally offered in such an affordable SUV. It consumes well, drives impressively good, and is easy on its owners pocket wise.

name: Mitsubishi Pajero
description:
Mitsubishi Pajero is arguably one of the best offroad full-size SUV with one of the most aggressive off 4WD system. This unit gets a manual transmission gearbox, and in combination with the 4WD system, it becomes an unbeatable offroad machine. It also has the Altimeter Inclinometer dash display with the first measuring altitude and the inclinometer , angles of slope or elevation.
