name: Nissan Leaf
description: The Nissan Leaf with a 24 kWh battery features a basic interior with essential technology and comfort amenities. It includes a touchscreen infotainment system, Bluetooth connectivity, and standard driver assistance features. The interior is functional, with simple design elements and straightforward controls. The Leaf offers a practical option for those seeking an affordable electric vehicle with essential features and a compact footprint.

name: Audi SQ5
description: The SQ5 was produced as the performance version of the Audi Q5 that was first produced in 2008, coded Typ 8R. The previous versions of the SQ5 available in the Typ 8R generation used a 3.0L Supercharged V6 petrol engines, while these new generations SQ5s in the Typ 80A generations adopted a new 3.0L twin turbocharged petrol engine which turns out to be a much powerful version than the previous versions. The torque was increased to 500Nm of Torque from previously rated 469Nm of torque engine. Horsepower remained the same. Advancements are similar to what the new gen Typ 80A Audi Q5 received including a virtual instrument cluster, a de-cluttered interior making it more minimalistic, and improved leather seats with the exterior becoming more curvy and aesthetically beautiful than what was available in the previous generation. The new gen is definitely worth it!

name: Lexus LX600
description: The Lexus LX600 is a luxury full-size SUV known for its opulent features and off-road capability. It offers a powerful engine, sophisticated interior with high-quality materials, and a range of advanced technology and safety features. The LX600 is designed to provide a smooth and comfortable ride, combining luxury with rugged performance for various driving conditions.

name: Audi RS7
description: The Audi RS7 is a high-performance luxury sedan with a sleek design and powerful 4.0-liter twin-turbo V8 engine. It features a premium interior with advanced technology, including a dual touchscreen infotainment system and a virtual cockpit. The RS7 combines sporty handling with a comfortable ride, offering a blend of luxury and performance.

name: Audi A6
description: The Audi A6 Avant is a premium mid-size station wagon known for its stylish design and practicality. It features a sleek exterior with sporty lines and a spacious, high-quality interior. The cabin offers ample room for passengers and cargo, with a user-friendly infotainment system and advanced technology. The A6 Avant includes features such as leather upholstery, a panoramic sunroof, and a comprehensive set of driver assistance systems. It combines luxury with versatility, making it a versatile choice for those needing both performance and practicality.

name: Mercedes-Benz C180
description: This is the Coupe version of the C180 equipped with Powered seats, side mirror indicators, Push-Start ignition, Premium surround sound system, Multifunctional tilt & telescopic steering wheel, and electric parking brake.

name: Volkswagen Arteon

Bluetooth connectivity, All round parking sensors, Front & side mounted airbags, Hill hold assist, and Radar guided adaptive cruise control.

name: Mercedes-Benz AMG E43
description: The Mercedes-Benz AMG E43, produced between 2017 and 2018, is a high-performance variant of the E-Class sedan. It features a 3.0-liter twin-turbo V6 engine producing 396 horsepower and 520 Nm of torque. The AMG E43 comes with a sportier design, including AMG styling elements and enhanced performance features. It includes a sport-tuned suspension, a more aggressive exhaust system, and distinctive AMG badging. Inside, the E43 boasts luxury materials, advanced technology, and performance-focused upgrades like AMG sport seats and a unique steering wheel.

name: Subaru Outback
description: The Subaru Outback is a mid-size crossover SUV that blends practicality with rugged capability. It features a high ground clearance and standard all-wheel drive, making it suitable for various driving conditions. Inside, it offers a spacious, comfortable cabin with quality materials and a user-friendly infotainment system. The Outback also includes advanced safety features, such as adaptive cruise control and lane departure warning, enhancing its appeal as a reliable and versatile family vehicle.

name: Honda Accord
description: The Honda Accord 2.0 Hybrid is a midsize sedan that focuses on comfort, efficiency, and practicality. It features a spacious and well-designed interior with high-quality materials and a user-friendly layout. The cabin includes a touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, Bluetooth connectivity, and available navigation. For safety, the Accord 2.0 Hybrid is equipped with advanced features such as adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assist, and automatic emergency braking.

name: Toyota Axio
description: This is the new gen Toyota Axio with major redesigns worked on a lot of parts, the major one being the face, front bumper. It has dark fabric seats, climate controls, android infotainment display screen, and cup holders.

name: Toyota Landcruiser ZX
description: The Toyota Land Cruiser ZX V8 4.6L is a premium full-size SUV designed for both luxury and capability. It boasts a high-quality interior with plush leather upholstery and premium finishes, ensuring a comfortable and sophisticated driving experience. The vehicle features advanced technology, including a touchscreen infotainment system with navigation, Bluetooth, and smartphone integration. Additionally, it offers a range of comfort amenities such as power-adjustable and heated/ventilated front seats, dual-zone climate control, and a sunroof. The Land Cruiser ZX V8 4.6L combines luxury with practicality, making it a top choice for those seeking an upscale, well-equipped SUV.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TXL
description: The Toyota Landcruiser Prado TXL J150 Series, is an excellent SUV that is able to multitask its use from offroad activities which it does well with the 4WD drive system and a good clearance, to official activities as it is a highly presentable car.

name: Toyota CHR
description: The Toyota C-HR ST is a sporty trim of the compact crossover SUV, known for its distinctive design and stylish features. It includes sportier exterior elements, such as unique trim accents and a more aggressive front grille. Inside, the C-HR ST offers sport-oriented interior details, including sport seats and a range of convenience features. The vehicle emphasizes a modern, high-quality interior with advanced technology and comfort features, making it a stylish and practical choice in the compact SUV segment.

name: Toyota Estima
description: The Toyota Estima, also known as the Toyota Previa, is a versatile minivan designed with family comfort and practicality in mind. It features a spacious interior with three rows of seating, ample cargo space, and convenient power-sliding doors. The cabin is equipped with a range of comfort and technology features, including a touchscreen infotainment system, Bluetooth connectivity, and optional leather upholstery. The Estima also includes various safety features such as stability control and multiple airbags, making it a reliable choice for families seeking a practical and comfortable vehicle.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The Subaru Forester SJ5, produced from 2013 to 2018, is a compact crossover SUV that emphasizes practicality, reliability, and versatility. It features a robust all-wheel-drive system, which enhances traction and stability across various driving conditions. The Forester SJ5 offers a spacious interior with ample cargo space and comfortable seating, making it suitable for families and outdoor enthusiasts alike. It includes a range of technology and safety features, with higher trims offering advanced driver assistance systems. Overall, the SJ5 Forester is valued for its dependable performance, spacious cabin, and off-road capability.

name: Audi A4
description: The "B9" generation of the A4 is equipped with a 7 speed dual Clucth transmission, Multifunctional steering wheel, adaptive headlights, half leather S-LINE sports seats, daytime running LED lights, virtual instrument cluster, premium surround sound system, and Radar guided Adaptive cruise control.

name: Mark X
description: The Toyota Mark X with a 2.5-liter V6 engine is a mid-size sedan known for its performance and comfort. The Mark X offers a smooth driving experience with a well-appointed interior, making it a popular choice for those seeking a blend of luxury and performance.

name: Mercedes Benz C180
description: In the class of compact sedans, the C180 turns out to be an excellently engineered sedan, with this car probably being the best there is. It gives an executive taste with all in round class while delivering excellent performance and fuel economy. It runs a 1.6L turbocharged petrol engine with a descent horsepower of 156hp and 250Nm of torque driving you in comfortable front row-heated bucket styled leather seats with thigh support while regulating your cabin temperature from dual zone climate controls listening to music from a premium surround sound system.

name: Mercedes-Benz GLE350D
description: The Mercedes-Benz GLE 350d is a luxury mid-size SUV known for its refined performance and upscale features. It offers a sophisticated design with a spacious and well-appointed interior, providing a comfortable ride for passengers. The GLE 350d is powered by a 3.0-liter V6 turbocharged diesel engine, delivering strong performance while maintaining efficiency. Inside, it features high-quality materials, advanced technology, and a range of comfort options, making it a well-rounded choice for those seeking both luxury and practicality in an SUV. The GLE 350d combines performance, comfort, and technology, making it a competitive option in its segment.

name: Mitsubishi Outlander
description: The Mitsubishi Outlander PHEV is a plug-in hybrid SUV that offers a blend of electric and gasoline power. It features a practical design with a spacious interior and a focus on versatility. The vehicle allows for short trips on electric power alone, with an extended range when using the gasoline engine. It combines the benefits of hybrid efficiency with the practicality of an SUV, including a roomy cabin, advanced technology, and a range of comfort and safety features. The Outlander PHEV is well-suited for drivers seeking both eco-friendly driving and the flexibility of a traditional SUV.

name: Lexus NX300H
description: The Lexus NX 300h is a luxury compact crossover SUV that combines a sophisticated design with hybrid efficiency. It features a stylish exterior and a high-quality interior with premium materials and advanced technology. The NX 300h is known for its comfortable ride, refined handling, and fuel-efficient hybrid powertrain. Inside, it offers a range of comfort features, including supportive seating and modern infotainment options. The vehicle also includes various advanced safety and driver assistance technologies, making it a well-rounded choice for those seeking luxury, efficiency, and practicality in a compact SUV.

name: Mercedes Benz C250
description: The Mercedes-Benz C250 features a 2.0-liter turbocharged engine with 208 horsepower and 350 Nm of torque. It accelerates from 0 to 100 km/h in about 6.6 seconds. The C250 offers a refined interior with advanced tech, blending luxury with everyday practicality.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: Toyota Harrier Premium has some premium specs added to it including a sunroof, Premium sound system, Xenon Projector Lamps, cruise control, and memory height adjustment. Other specs include a multifunctional steering wheel, powered seats, and a Pre-collision warning safety system among other specs.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The Mazda CX-5 is a compact crossover SUV that combines stylish design with practicality and performance. It features a sleek exterior with Mazda's Kodo design philosophy, emphasizing clean lines and an elegant profile. Inside, the CX-5 offers a high-quality cabin with modern materials, a user-friendly infotainment system, and comfortable seating for passengers. It is known for its engaging driving dynamics, with responsive handling and a smooth ride. The CX-5 also includes a range of advanced safety and technology features, making it a well-rounded choice for those seeking a blend of style, comfort, and driving enjoyment.

name: BMW 318i
description: This is the 4th Gen of BMW 3 Series in the range of compact executive cars coded E46. They were produced between the years of 1997 and 2006 and succeeded the E36 series that stopped production in 2000. It came as an improvement from the previous E36 series as it was 70% more rigid than the E36. With better integrated electronics using CAN BUS system with engine, transmission, and stability control communicated via the CAN BUS. It runs a 2.0L N46B20 inline-4 petrol engine with a power rating of 200Nm of Torque.

name: Audi A7
description: The A7 is the four-door fastback version of the C7-series of Audi A6. It is based on the MLB Platform by Volkswagen Group. The major difference between the A6 and the A7 is the detail work in its interior that it has a unique panelwork and utilizes Aluminum for much of its front body structure. The first gen of the A7 coded 4G8 was produced in 2010 and the 2nd gen Typ 4K8 appearing in 2018. It came with a variety of engines consisting of the 2.0L TFSI beginning in 2014-2018, the popular 3.0L TFSI, the 2.8 FSI QUATTRO, and the 3.0TDI diesel engine. This unit utilizes the 2.0L engine option mated to a 7 speed automatic transmission gearbox. It has a power rating of 249hp.

name: Range Rover Sport SVR
description: The Range Rover Sport SVR is a high-performance luxury SUV that blends powerful performance with sophisticated design and comfort. It features a bold exterior with aggressive styling and enhanced aerodynamic elements. Inside, the SVR offers a premium, sport-oriented interior with high-quality materials, supportive sports seats, and advanced technology. It includes a high-resolution infotainment system, premium audio, and a range of comfort features such as heated and ventilated seats. The SVR model is designed to deliver an exhilarating driving experience while maintaining the Range Rover's signature luxury and versatility.

name: BMW 550i
description: The BMW 550i is a luxury sedan that blends powerful performance with high-end features and comfort. It features a sleek and sophisticated design, a spacious and well-appointed interior, and advanced technology. The 550i is equipped with a powerful engine and a smooth transmission, providing a dynamic driving experience. Inside, it offers premium materials, advanced infotainment systems, and a range of comfort features, including heated and power-adjustable seats, dual-zone climate control, and a premium audio system. The 550i stands out for its combination of performance, luxury, and technology, making it a compelling choice in the executive sedan segment.

name: Toyota Isis
description: The Toyota Isis Platana V is a practical and versatile multi-purpose vehicle (MPV) designed for families and those needing extra space. It offers a spacious interior with flexible seating configurations, allowing for up to seven or eight passengers. The vehicle is known for its user-friendly features and comfort-oriented design, including air conditioning and convenient storage options. The Isis Platana V focuses on providing a reliable and functional driving experience, making it well-suited for daily use and long trips.

name: BMW X6M COMPETITION
description: The BMW X6 M Competition is a high-performance luxury SUV that combines aggressive styling with exceptional power. It features a bold and sporty exterior design with distinctive M styling elements. Inside, the X6 M Competition offers a luxurious cabin with premium materials, advanced technology, and sporty touches, such as M-specific seats and trim. The vehicle is equipped with powerful engines, advanced suspension systems, and all-wheel drive, providing both exhilarating performance and a refined driving experience. It also includes a range of modern technology and comfort features, ensuring a dynamic yet comfortable ride.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TX-L
description: The Landcruiser Prado TX-L GDJ150, diesel variant, is equipped with a 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox, side steps, fog lights, front & side curtain airbags, and a multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Suzuki Swift
description: Suzuki Swift is a highly soughted after compact car by motorists for its agile handling, sporty design, fuel efficiency, a practical comfortable interior, and high safety measures including stability control feature. This comes with a choice of fabric seats, android infotainment display screen, and climate controls.

name: Mazda Axela
description: The Axela diesel variant with its great power from the Skyactiv-D 2.2L diesel engine, and a great balance of versatility and luxury, sells as one of the most preferred hatchbacks. It is specced with a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, cruise control, parking sensors, lane departure assist, and i-stop system.

name: Toyota Noah
description: The Toyota Noah is a multi-purpose vehicle (MPV) designed for family and commercial use. It features a spacious and flexible interior with seating for up to eight passengers, depending on the configuration. The Noah is known for its practicality, offering ample cargo space and versatile seating arrangements. It typically includes user-friendly technology such as a touchscreen infotainment system, climate control, and various driver assistance features. The vehicle’s design focuses on comfort and convenience, making it a popular choice for families and those needing a reliable and functional vehicle for daily use.

name: Toyota Auris
description: The Auris has an expensive feel to it from what another Toyota in its class would feel like. It is specced with the 1.5L 1NZ-FE petrol engine with a power rating of 116hp. On the interior it has half leather seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, and electric foldable mirros.

name: Mazda Demio
description: The Demio is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, fabric seats, android infotainment display system, and headlight range adjustment.

name: Audi S3
description: The Audi S3 Sedan is a sporty compact luxury sedan that blends performance with everyday usability. It features a sleek and aggressive design, emphasizing its sporty character. The S3 Sedan comes with a high-quality interior, including leather upholstery, advanced infotainment system, and supportive sports seats. The vehicle is equipped with Audi's Quattro all-wheel drive system and a sport-tuned suspension, ensuring a dynamic driving experience while maintaining comfort and practicality. The interior is well-appointed with modern technology and driver assistance features, offering a balance of luxury and performance.

name: Toyota Fortuner
description: This is the 2nd gen Toyota Fortuner since its first production in 2004. 2nd Gen production began in 2015 mid with new introductions being made as with the part time 4 by 4 system that improved on the cars fuel economy. The 2.8L diesel engine was also improved with a common direct injection in its fuel system and a direct nozzle turbocharging. This unit has 7 tan leather seats with the third row being foldable for extra cargo space. It also has excellent clearance for offroad driving. This is a rugged enough unit that will sustain all offroading adventures!

name: Mercedes Benz GLC 250
description: Mercedes GLC 250 replaced the GLK Class in 2015 for 2016 model years. It is a premium Compact SUV equivalent to the C Class sedan. It features a 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine, a multifunctional steering wheel, multi zone climate control, heated seats with memory function, ambient lighting, and active parking assist system among other specs.

name: Toyota Noah
description: Toyota Noah is a very comfortable car. From experience and reviews, you can comfortably sit for long distances without tiring your back. The passengers have the same satisfactory reviews. And it is quite powerful giving sufficient torque.

name: Lexus LX570
description: The Lexus LX570 is a luxury full-size SUV known for its opulent interior and off-road capability. It features a spacious and high-quality cabin with premium materials, including leather upholstery and wood trim. The LX570 offers a range of advanced technology and comfort features, such as a large touchscreen infotainment system, a premium audio system, and multiple-zone climate control. The SUV is equipped with advanced driver assistance systems and offers a smooth, refined ride. Its robust build and off-road capabilities make it suitable for various driving conditions, blending luxury with practicality.

name: Lexus NX200T
description: Lexus NX200t turns out to be the king in compact luxury crossover SUVs class sold by Lexus. The sporty nature of the car is complimented by the 2.0L 8AR-FTS turbocharged petrol engine that is one hell of a perfomer. It is also a very economical car attributed to by Lexus' Economy with Superior Thermal Efficient Combustion (ESTEC) direct injection with turbo (D-4ST) fuel injection. It is run by a 6-speed automatic transmission gearbox with a very smooth shift. Definitely a car you can't think twice of acquiring it.

name: Volkswagen Golf R
description: The Volkswagen Golf MK7.5 R is a high-performance hatchback that offers a blend of sporty design and practicality. It features a sleek and aggressive exterior, with sporty styling elements that set it apart from the standard Golf models. Inside, the Golf R includes a driver-focused cockpit with premium materials, advanced technology, and supportive sports seats. The vehicle is equipped with all-wheel drive for enhanced traction and stability, along with a sport-tuned suspension for a dynamic driving experience. The Golf MK7.5 R combines everyday usability with the excitement of a performance-oriented vehicle.

name: Porsche Panamera
description: Experience Excellence of Porsche with the UK Specced Porsche Panamera fitted with 8 Speed PDK, Powered seats, Black high gloss interior, heated front seats, Retractable spoiler, Two-zone automatic climate control, Two High-Resolution Instrument Cluster Display, Cruise control, rear mounted spoiler, Porsche Stability Management, and Porsche Side Impact Protection.

name: Audi TT RS
description: The TT RS Coupe is equipped with an 7 speed dual-clutch S Tronic transmission gearbox, catalunya red paint, alcantara steering wheel, leather sports seats, powered seats, premium surround sound system, digital instrument cluster, lane keep assist, matrix LED headlights, and Traction control.

name: Nissan GTR
description: The GTR speaks for itself in all it can do from tarmac races to adventurous cruises. It is powered by a 3.8L V6 engine mated to a 6 speed dual clutch automatic transmission gearbox. Its power figures are horsepowers North of 564 and torque of 628Nm. It also has an All Wheel drive setup, bucket styled leather seats, Multifunctional steering wheel, infotainment system control screen and a 11-Speaker BOSE premium surround sound system.

name: BMW 740i
description: The BMW 740i is a luxury sedan that emphasizes comfort and advanced technology. It features a high-quality interior with premium materials such as leather upholstery and wood trim. The sedan includes a sophisticated infotainment system with a large touchscreen, navigation, and smartphone integration. It offers a range of comfort features, including multi-zone climate control, power-adjustable seats with memory settings, and advanced driver assistance systems. The 740i is designed to provide a smooth and luxurious driving experience, making it a refined choice in the luxury sedan segment.

name: BMW X4
description: The BMW X4 is a luxury compact SUV that combines sporty design with practical features. It offers a sleek, coupe-like exterior with a bold front grille and aerodynamic lines. Inside, the X4 features a high-quality cabin with premium materials, a user-friendly infotainment system, and advanced technology. It includes comfortable seating, a variety of driver assistance features, and a range of customizable options. The X4 provides a smooth and dynamic driving experience, with several engine choices available, depending on the market and trim level.

name: Bentley Continental GT
description: The Bentley Continental GT is a luxury grand tourer that offers a combination of elegance, comfort, and advanced technology. It features a beautifully crafted interior with high-quality materials such as leather, wood, and metal accents. The Continental GT includes a sophisticated infotainment system with a large touchscreen, navigation, and premium audio. It provides a smooth and refined driving experience with a focus on comfort and luxury. The car's design includes distinctive Bentley styling elements, such as a prominent grille and sleek lines, ensuring it stands out in the luxury vehicle market.

name: Bentley Flying Spur
description: The Bentley Flying Spur is a luxury sedan renowned for its exceptional comfort and opulent interior. It features a spacious cabin with high-quality materials, including leather upholstery, wood veneer, and advanced technology. The Flying Spur is equipped with a sophisticated infotainment system, including a large touchscreen, navigation, and premium audio options. It offers a smooth and refined ride, with attention to detail in its design and craftsmanship. The sedan also provides a range of customizable features to enhance comfort and personalize the driving experience, making it a symbol of luxury and elegance.

name: BMW X1
description: The X1 XDrive 18d "F48" is specced with a multifunctional steering wheel, all wheel drive system, daytime running LED lights, Premium surround sound system, and traction control.

name: Mercedes Benz GLE350D
description: This GLE 350D is equipped with Powered Nappa seats, active parking assist system, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, Mercedes Comand Infotainment system, Mercedes speedtronic cruise control, Premium surround sound system, downhill speed regulation, Sunroof, and Ambient lighting.

name: BMW X5
description: The BMW X5 M is a high-performance luxury SUV that combines aggressive styling with powerful performance. It is equipped with a 4.4-liter twin-turbocharged V8 engine that produces 600 horsepower and 750 Nm of torque. The X5 M features a sporty design, with distinct exterior styling, large wheels, and a performance-oriented suspension. Inside, it offers a luxurious and tech-filled cabin with high-quality materials, advanced infotainment, and a range of comfort features. The X5 M is designed to deliver both thrilling driving dynamics and everyday usability. Fuel consumption averages around 8-10 km/l.

name: Audi A5
description: This "B9" generation of the A5 is equipped with a sunroof, 7 speed dual Clucth transmission, Multifunctional steering wheel, adaptive headlights, daytime running LED lights, virtual instrument cluster, premium surround sound system, and Adaptive cruise control.

name: Mercedes Benz GLC 250
description: The Mercedes-Benz GLC 250 is a luxury SUV that features a high-quality interior, advanced technology, and a refined driving experience. It includes a spacious cabin with premium materials, the latest infotainment systems, and a range of comfort and safety features. The GLC 250 offers a smooth and comfortable ride, with a focus on luxury and practicality, making it a strong choice in the luxury SUV market.

name: Range Rover Sport
description: The Range Rover Sport HSE is equipped with a Rain sensing windscreen wipers, Electronic air suspension setup, Terrain Response management system, electric locking differentials, smartphone integration, panoramic sunroof, daytime running LED Lights, and a Meridian premium surround sound system.

name: Jaguar XF
description: The Jaguar XF R-Sport is a luxury sedan that blends elegant design with sporty styling cues. It features a sleek exterior with distinctive R-Sport elements like a more aggressive front bumper, side skirts, and unique wheels. Inside, the XF R-Sport offers a premium cabin with high-quality materials, comfortable seating, and advanced technology. The interior is designed for comfort and convenience, with features such as Jaguar’s InControl infotainment system and a range of safety technologies. The XF R-Sport combines luxury with a sportier appearance, making it a stylish choice in the luxury sedan market.

name: Audi Q8
description: The Audi Q8 is a luxury SUV that combines coupe-like styling with the practicality of an SUV. It features a bold design with a wide stance, a spacious and high-tech interior, and advanced technology. The Q8 offers a premium experience with a luxurious interior, featuring high-quality materials, advanced infotainment, and a range of comfort and safety features. Audi’s Quattro all-wheel-drive system ensures confident handling in various conditions. The Q8 stands out for its blend of style, luxury, and cutting-edge technology, making it a top choice in the luxury SUV segment.

name: Volkswagen Golf GTI
description: The Volkswagen Golf GTI, tuned by Cox, is a high-performance variant of the iconic hot hatch, enhanced with a range of specialized aftermarket parts. The tuning includes Cox Racing brakes and DBA brake rotors for improved stopping power, alongside a Cox stainless steel muffler and exhaust chamber for better exhaust flow and sound. The Interster power enhancement and Cox turbo pipe kit increase engine performance, while the Cox original spring kit and stabilizer set improve handling and stability. Additionally, Cox performance air filters (G-type) ensure optimized air intake, making this GTI a finely tuned machine that offers superior performance and driving dynamics.

name: Nissan Note
description: DIG-S, notably seen in the Nissan Note, means Direct Injection Gasoline-Supercharged. The Supercharger in this unit makes quite a difference in the power the Nissan Note makes. 147Nm of torque and 97hp compared to the NA version making 78hp and 106Nm does some magic in this Note DIGS Spec!

name: Mazda CX5 AWD
description: The CX-5 2.5S-L Package is specced with daytime running lights, Multifunctional tilt & telescopic steering wheel, BOSE Premium surround sound system, side impact airbags, Traction control system, and Adaptive frontlight system.

name: Volkswagen Golf Variant R
description: The heart of Golf R reflects in its station wagon variant for family units that need more space on the interior especially the boot. It houses a 2.0L turbocharged EA888 engine that has been one of the best performing engines in recent times especially on track. This units also gets rear entertainment screens describing a proper family orientation. This particular unit comes with some modifications. They include 19 inch pretoria 5 spoke rims,and a Pedal box /Race chip that guarantees upto 80 horsepower.

name: Audi A5
description: The Audi A5 B9, introduced in 2016, is the second-generation model available in coupe, sportback, and convertible versions. It features a sleek design with a wider stance and an upscale interior made with premium materials. The A5 B9 includes advanced technology like Audi's Virtual Cockpit, a fully digital instrument cluster, and a user-friendly infotainment system. Known for its balance of sporty handling and comfortable ride, the A5 B9 offers a refined driving experience that appeals to luxury car enthusiasts.

name: Audi Q3
description: An excellent crossover that blends practicality with performance and luxury as standard. It is a good choice for someone seeking a relatively small engine that ultimately performs well, and enough clearance that gives the feel of an SUV.

name: BMW 530i
description: The BMW 530i is a luxury sedan that blends performance, comfort, and technology. It offers a refined driving experience with a well-tuned suspension and precise handling. Inside, the 530i boasts a high-quality interior with advanced tech, including a large infotainment screen, premium materials, and numerous driver assistance features. Its blend of power, comfort, and cutting-edge technology makes it a strong contender in the luxury sedan market.

name: Range Rover Sport
description: The Range Rover Sport SVR is powered by a 5.0L V8 AJ133 Supercharged Petrol engine that does 575 Horsepowers and 702 Nm of Torque. It is mated to an 8 speed-shiftable ZF8HP automatic transmission gearbox. Other features include Powered two tone sports seats, heated front & rear seats, Terrain response management system, adaptive cruise control, Meridian premium surround sound system, Electric tailgate, and Traction control system.

name: Porsche Cayenne Turbo
description: The Porsche Cayenne Turbo is a high-performance luxury SUV powered by a 4.0-liter twin-turbocharged V8 engine, producing 541 horsepower and 770 Nm of torque. It accelerates from 0 to 100 km/h in just 3.9 seconds with the Sport Chrono package. The Cayenne Turbo offers a blend of thrilling performance, advanced technology, and premium comfort, making it one of the top choices in the luxury SUV segment.

name: Range Rover Vogue Autobiography
description: The Range Rover Vogue Autobiography is a luxury SUV featuring a premium interior with leather, wood, and metal finishes. It offers heated and ventilated seats, a panoramic sunroof, and a dual touchscreen infotainment system. The Autobiography trim adds massaging seats, a Meridian sound system, and advanced driver assistance features.

name: Mercedes Benz AMG E43
description: The Mercedes-Benz E43 AMG is a performance-focused luxury sedan with a 3.0-liter twin-turbo V6 engine producing 396 horsepower. It features sporty AMG styling, a high-quality interior with advanced technology, and sport-tuned handling for a blend of comfort and dynamic driving.

name: Porsche Cayenne
description: The Porsche Cayenne is a luxury mid-size SUV known for its sporty performance and high-quality interior. It features a sleek design with a distinctive front grille and aerodynamic lines. Inside, the Cayenne offers a premium cabin with high-grade materials, advanced technology, and spacious seating. Key features typically include a touchscreen infotainment system, leather upholstery, and a range of driver assistance technologies. The Cayenne balances practicality with Porsche’s signature driving dynamics, making it a versatile choice in the luxury SUV segment.

name: Range Rover Evoque
description: Range Rover Evoque was, in 2011, first produced by Land Rover LTD until 2012 and the other production years done by Jaguar Land Rover from 2013. It is a subcompact luxury crossover SUV meant for both urban and off-road experiences. It performs well in the city and excels as well offroading as Land Rover has done well in creating a reliable most efficient Terrain Response system including Grass, Gravel, Snow, and Sand modes. It has specially tweaked comfort to the standards Land Rover has maintained over the years and delivers great performance!

name: Audi SQ5
description: The SQ5 3.0T is equipped with an 8 speed automatic transmission gearbox, powered seats, premium surround sound system, Tri-zone climate controls, digital instrument cluster, lane keep assist, and Traction control.

name: Toyota Hiace
description: A very spacious multiple purpose Van. It has been used for Tourist Services and hence the well maintained state with an occupancy of 9 passengers. The seats are made of fabric material.

name: Mitsubishi Pajero
description: The Pajero is a full size SUV (Sport Utility Vehicle) that is very efficient in handling multiple terrains including offroad and urban setups. It runs a very capable engine and excellent drivetrain with locking diffs for offroad mode. It also works well for large family setups as a number of Pajeros come in 5 up to 7 seats!

name: Peugeot  3008
description: The 3008 is a compact crossover SUV that shares its platform with the 308 which is its smaller counterpart. This unit is the 2nd Generation Peugeot 3008, P84, that succeeded the T84 that ended production in 2015. P84 did a lot of improvements beginning with Peugeot's iCockpit featuring a virtual instrument cluster. The 8 inch display screen with a touch functionality is the center hub of all the car controls. Car controls were designed angularly towards the driver which eases the driver's focus when selecting any control feature. It is also offers a thrilling driving experience. It has a number of features including lane assist, Blindspot assist, and an exhilarating quick drive

name: Volkswagen Arteon
description: The Volkswagen Arteon is a sleek and stylish midsize sedan known for its upscale design and advanced technology. It features a sporty, fastback profile with a distinctive front grille and high-quality interior materials. Inside, the Arteon offers a spacious and comfortable cabin with a modern infotainment system, including a touchscreen interface, navigation, and smartphone integration.

name: Audi A6
description: Audi A6 C7 series, designated Typ 4G by Audi, began production in 2011 to 2018. It drew a lot of design inspiration from the A8 and has the similar powertrain, the Modular Longitudinal platform, that longitudinal front based engines were constructed under, interior and exterior features. In 2016, sales of the C7 facelift, C7.5 began with this model being among the first to be sold. It features improved exterior styling with design curves that reduced drag effect as with the C7, advanced Matrix LED lights, improved processing capabilities of the Audi MMI infotainment system, a polished metal trimming, and on its drivertrain, holds a 2.0L turbocharged inline 4 cylinder engine with a Dual clutch, famously S-Tronic, 7 speed automatic transmission. The dual clutch transmission system performs extremely well with sporty driving as it transmits without its torque being interrupted as the clutches are just ready to engage the next gears seamlessly, better than a manual transmission!

name: Mazda CX8
description: The Mazda CX-8 is a mid-size SUV offering a refined design and a spacious three-row interior. It features high-quality materials, a modern infotainment system, and ample cargo space. Comfort and safety are enhanced with features such as dual-zone climate control and advanced driver assistance technologies.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The Subaru Forester (SKE) is a compact SUV known for its practicality, reliability, and excellent all-wheel-drive system. This model is known for good handling and stability, especially in challenging road conditions thanks to Subaru's Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive. The Forester SKE is also equipped with a spacious interior, offering ample cargo space and comfortable seating for five passengers.

name: Porsche Macan GTS
description: The Porsche Macan GTS is a luxury compact SUV featuring a high-quality interior with leather and Alcantara upholstery, sport seats, and a sleek design. It includes advanced infotainment with a touchscreen, dual-zone climate control, and a panoramic sunroof. The exterior is sporty and elegant, with distinctive GTS styling.

name: Audi A7
description: The Audi A7 is a luxury sedan with a distinctive design that combines elegance with practicality. It features a sleek, coupe-like profile with a sharply sloping roofline and a wide, bold front grille. Inside, the A7 offers a refined and spacious cabin, equipped with high-quality materials, including leather and wood trim. The car includes advanced technology such as a dual touchscreen infotainment system, a digital driver display, and numerous driver assistance features. Its rear seats are comfortable and can be folded to expand the cargo space, making the A7 a versatile choice for both daily driving and longer journeys. The A7 is celebrated for its stylish design, premium interior, and cutting-edge technology.

name: Audi A8
description: The Audi A8 50 TDI is a luxury sedan that combines elegant design with advanced technology and a powerful 3.0-liter V6 diesel engine. Known for its smooth and refined ride, the A8 offers a spacious, high-quality interior with cutting-edge features. Audi's Quattro all-wheel-drive system ensures confident handling, making the A8 50 TDI a sophisticated choice for those seeking a blend of luxury and performance.

name: Volvo XC60
description:
The Volvo XC60 T6 R-Design is a luxury midsize SUV that combines Scandinavian design with sporty performance. The R-Design trim adds a sportier touch with unique exterior styling, including a more aggressive front grille, special alloy wheels, and R-Design badging.

Inside, the XC60 T6 R-Design offers a premium interior with leather sport seats, a digital driver display, and a 9-inch touchscreen infotainment system with features like Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. It also includes Volvo's renowned safety suite, with advanced features such as Pilot Assist, adaptive cruise control, and collision avoidance. The XC60 T6 R-Design is known for its blend of style, performance, and cutting-edge safety technology.

name: BMW X3
description: The BMW X3 xDrive20d (G01) is a luxury compact SUV that offers a blend of premium features and practicality. It comes with BMW's xDrive all-wheel-drive system, ensuring stable handling in various driving conditions. The interior is designed with high-quality materials, featuring comfortable seating, a user-friendly iDrive infotainment system, and advanced connectivity options. The X3 xDrive20d also includes a range of safety features, such as parking sensors, a rearview camera, and optional driver assistance systems. The 2017 X3 is appreciated for its refined design, spacious cabin, and versatility, making it a solid choice for those seeking a premium SUV experience.

name: Audi Q3
description: Typ 8U Audi Q3 is at its 2nd gen with the 1st Gen being produced at 2011. The Q3 received a LCI in 2014 for cars sold in 2015. Another update was done in 2015 with improvements of front and rear parking sensors, full LED lights, and improvements in front lights and grille. The 2.0L Quattro spec takes its load easily as it runs power figures of 197hp and 280Nm of torque to all 4 wheels

name: BMW 530I
description: The BMW 530i G30 is a luxury sedan that blends performance, comfort, and technology. It offers a refined driving experience with a well-tuned suspension and precise handling. Inside, the 530i boasts a high-quality interior with advanced tech, including a large infotainment screen, premium materials, and numerous driver assistance features. Its blend of power, comfort, and cutting-edge technology makes it a strong contender in the luxury sedan market.

name: Toyota Caldina
description: Toyota Caldina has been in production for 15 years ending in 2007. It was available in both front and four wheel drive systems with the four-wheel drive system gaining popularity in Australia and Russia among other countries. Its name is Italian inspired meaning essential. It was very essential in a number of households in the earlier years with a majority loving it. It is powered by the 2.0L 1AZ-FSE Naturally Aspirated petrol engine producing 153hp.

name: Mercedes Benz E300
description: After careful design considerations and works that began in 2003, the final design was produced in 2009 with the unveiling happening at the North American International Auto Show. The E300 featured a 3.0L V6 naturally aspirated petrol engine that running power figures of 228hp and 300Nm of torque. This model also features a sunroof which definitely makes the E300 more interesting.

name: Nissan Xtrail
description: The Nissan X-Trail is a versatile compact SUV known for its spacious interior and practicality. It offers seating for up to seven passengers with flexible seating arrangements, including a fold-flat rear seat configuration for increased cargo space. The X-Trail features a user-friendly infotainment system, with options for touchscreen navigation, Bluetooth connectivity, and smartphone integration. It also includes a range of safety features, such as multiple airbags, stability control, and advanced driver assistance systems, providing a secure and comfortable driving experience. The X-Trail is well-regarded for its family-friendly design and everyday usability.

name: Porsche 911 GT3
description:
The Porsche 911 GT3 is a high-performance sports car designed for driving enthusiasts. It is powered by a 4.0-liter naturally aspirated flat-six engine that produces 502 horsepower and 470 Nm of torque. The 911 GT3 accelerates from 0 to 100 km/h in just 3.4 seconds and has a top speed of around 318 km/h. 

This model is renowned for its precise handling, thanks to its rear-wheel-drive layout, lightweight construction, and advanced aerodynamics, including a large rear wing. The 2021 GT3 also features a track-tuned suspension and offers the option of a 6-speed manual transmission or a 7-speed PDK automatic, providing an engaging driving experience. Inside, it combines luxury with sportiness, featuring Alcantara and carbon-fiber accents. The 2021 911 GT3 is celebrated for its raw performance and connection to Porsche’s racing heritage.

name: Toyota Rav4
description: The Toyota RAV4 is specced with a Reverse camera with all round sensors, Emergency braking assist, Multifunctional tilt & telescopic steering wheel, Toyota infotainment system, Premium sound system, Daytime running LED lights, Smartphone integration, and Side impact airbags.

name: Lexus NX300H
description: The Lexus NX 300h F Sport is a luxury hybrid SUV with a 2.5-liter engine and electric motor, producing 194 horsepower. It offers sporty styling, enhanced suspension, and delivers about 15 to 17 km/l. The F Sport trim adds unique design elements and advanced tech features, blending performance with fuel efficiency.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TZ-G
description:
The Toyota Land Cruiser Prado TZ-G is powered by a 2.8-liter turbocharged diesel engine that produces 174 horsepower and 450 Nm of torque, offering robust performance for both on-road and off-road driving.

Inside, the TZ-G trim is equipped with luxury features such as leather seats, a premium sound system, and advanced safety technologies like adaptive cruise control and lane departure warning. The Prado TZ-G is known for its durability, off-road capability, and comfort, making it a versatile choice for various driving conditions.

name: Lexus LX600
description:
The Lexus LX 600 Executive Package is the top-tier luxury SUV offering in the LX lineup. Powered by a 3.5-liter twin-turbo V6 engine producing 409 horsepower and 650 Nm of torque, it delivers robust performance both on and off-road. The Executive Package focuses on ultimate luxury, featuring a plush interior with high-quality materials, including semi-aniline leather seats, real wood trim, and a host of advanced technology.

Key features include a rear-seat entertainment system, massaging rear seats, four-zone climate control, and a Mark Levinson premium sound system. The LX 600 also boasts Lexus's advanced safety suite, offering features like adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assist, and a 360-degree camera. The 2022 LX 600 Executive Package is designed for those who seek a blend of power, luxury, and cutting-edge technology in a full-size SUV.

name: Honda Vezel
description: The Honda Vezel Hybrid features a 1.5-liter engine paired with an electric motor. It delivers excellent fuel efficiency, around 20 to 24 km/l. The Vezel Hybrid offers a stylish design, modern interior, and advanced safety features, making it a practical and efficient choice for daily driving.

name: Mercedes-Benz AMG S63L
description: A powerhouse! A Mercedes Benz S63 AMG 4.0 BITURBO V8 with a 9 speed AMG SPEEDSHIFT automatic transmission and a sliding panoramic sunroof. The engine produces 603hp and 900Nm of torque. Other specs include powered two-tone Nappa leather seats, heated seats, AMG performance steering wheel, ventilated brake discs, THERMOTRONIC luxury dual dual automatic climate control, Active parking assist with Parktronic and 360° camera, Electronic differential locking, Heads Up Display, and AMG-SPORTS Exhaust.

name: Toyota Hilux
description: The better cargo truck option, The Toyota Hilux Double Cabin! A very rugged and agile pickup truck with manual transmission. It is still in perfect condition with all the seats well knitted together and body in good shape. It serves consumers who operate relatively heavy loads with the big space at the back and a powerful 2.5L 2KD Diesel engine.

name: Mazda Demio
description: Mazda Demio is a very reliable and excellently performing car with the 1.3L petrol engine giving sufficient power to carry up to 5 individuals and some cargo at the back. The seats have the heating functionality which is also a plus for the comfort aspect. It has aftermakert rims which give it a different look from the traditional Demio look.

description:

name: BMW X5
description: BMW X5 is a mid-size luxury SUV categorised by BMW as Sports Activity Vehicle (SAV) instead of SUV. It is available in an All wheel drive system that features torque-split. The E70 came in next after the E53 in 2006. The current listed F15 gen car came in later in 2013 featuring the same chassis and wheelbase as the E70. The F15 came with an introduction of an increased number of engine choices including the XDrive 40d, XDrive 35i, XDrive 25d, and SDrive 25d. This unit features a 3.0L N57 straight-6 diesel engine with a power rating of 560Nm of torque. It is fitted with heated seats that are powered, head up display, hill descent control, and an electric tailgate among other specs.

name: Range Rover Sport
description: The Range Rover Sport SVR is powered by a 5.0L V8 AJ133 Supercharged Petrol engine that does 575 Horsepowers and 702 Nm of Torque. It is mated to an 8 speed-shiftable ZF8HP automatic transmission gearbox. Other features include Powered two tone sports seats, heated front & rear seats, Terrain response management system, adaptive cruise control, Meridian premium surround sound system, Electric tailgate, and Traction control system.

name: Mitsubishi Outlander
description: The Mitsubishi Outlander PHEV is specced with a 4 wheel drive system, Infotainment system control screen, Multifunctional steering wheel, LED tail lights, foglamps, paddle shifters, and rear mounted spoiler.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TZ-G
description:
The Toyota Land Cruiser Prado TZ-G with the Aero Package is a premium version of the popular mid-size SUV. It is powered by a 2.8-liter turbocharged diesel engine that produces 174 horsepower and 450 Nm of torque, offering robust performance for both on-road and off-road driving. The Aero Package adds sporty styling elements, including a unique front bumper, side skirts, and rear spoiler, giving the Prado a more dynamic and aggressive look.

Inside, the TZ-G trim is equipped with luxury features such as leather seats, a premium sound system, and advanced safety technologies like adaptive cruise control and lane departure warning. The Prado TZ-G is known for its durability, off-road capability, and comfort, making it a versatile choice for various driving conditions.

name: Mazda Atenza
description:
SKYACTIV is a series of technologies that Mazda intended that they increase engine output and fuel efficiency. The Mazda Atenza uses a Skyactiv-D engine which is a group of diesel engines that are turbocharged. The Atenza uses SH-VPTS engine with a displacement of 2191cc. This engine was first used in CX-5s. In the Atenza, it produces 173hp and 420Nm of torque which gives the Atenza an edge over other cars in the same class.

name: Volvo XC90 D5
description: The 2nd Generation Volvo XC90 made a debut in 2014 before officially launching in 2015. 1st Edition of an all-new XC90 units were produced in 2014 with a total of 1927 numbered cars selling out in only 47hours. The First edition models featured an Onyx black finish and every other feature Volvo could offer. This 2017 model also features a number of features which are a big deal including a panoramic sunroof, leather seats with third row-seating capacity with both the front and rear occupants having a heating functionality, Premium surround sound system that makes the cabin feel like a large Orchestral theatre, steering wheel controls, and all the safety systems Volvo have ever come up with including City safety and Run-off-road protection package that controls the seats comfort level and belts adjustment to deliver a comfortable offroading experience.

name: Audi A4 Allroad
description: The Audi A4 Allroad is a versatile wagon that combines the practicality of an estate with the rugged capability of an SUV. It features a 2.0-liter turbocharged inline-4 engine that produces 252 horsepower and 370 Nm of torque, paired with Audi's Quattro all-wheel-drive system. This setup allows the A4 Allroad to handle a variety of road conditions with confidence. The Allroad version includes increased ground clearance, protective cladding, and a refined suspension for light off-roading. Inside, it offers a high-quality interior with advanced technology, including Audi’s Virtual Cockpit and a user-friendly infotainment system. The 2017 A4 Allroad is ideal for those seeking a blend of luxury, practicality, and off-road capability.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI
description: Volkswagen Golf MK7 falls under the Compact executive hatchback segment. The 7 in the name 'Mk7' denotes the 7th generation that this model is produced under. It was produced under the MQB platform that it shares with 3rd Gen Audi A3 and Skoda Octavia. This is a perfect executive car tha consumes like a 1.0L Toyota car. Performance and consumption are at its peak with prices highly favourable for such a fast executive car.

name: Mazda CX3
description: This is the leather package CX-3 XD specced with Infotainment system control screen with Mazda connect system, Multifunctional tilt & telescopic steering wheel, Premium surround sound system, adaptive frontlight system, and traction control system.

description:
This is the 5th Gen Subaru Impreza that was revealed in March 2016. It became the first model based on the Subaru Global Platform which became the new standard for Subarus produced after then. What was visible when sales began in Japan towards the end of 2016 is that sales rocketed four-fold monthly which represented a 51% surge to this brand from other brands. With major revamps happening in its body, the engine was also revised. Suspension and rigidity were all improved making it even more reliable and attractive!

description: The Mercedes-AMG C43 is a performance-oriented version of the C-Class sedan, featuring a 3.0-liter twin-turbocharged V6 engine that produces 362 horsepower and 520 Nm of torque. This power allows the C43 to accelerate from 0 to 100 km/h in about 4.7 seconds. It comes with Mercedes' 4MATIC all-wheel-drive system, ensuring excellent grip and handling. The C43 also offers sporty design elements, including AMG-specific styling, a refined interior with high-quality materials, and advanced technology. It strikes a balance between everyday usability and performance, making it a compelling choice in the compact luxury sports sedan category.

name: Porsche Cayenne Turbo
description: The Porsche Cayenne Turbo is a high-performance luxury SUV powered by a 4.0-liter twin-turbocharged V8 engine, producing 541 horsepower and 770 Nm of torque. It accelerates from 0 to 100 km/h in just 3.9 seconds with the Sport Chrono package. The Cayenne Turbo offers a blend of thrilling performance, advanced technology, and premium comfort, making it one of the top choices in the luxury SUV segment.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TZ-G
description: The Landcruiser Prado TZ-G GDJ151, diesel variant, is equipped with a 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox, side steps, fog lights, front & side curtain airbags, and a multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Toyota FJ Cruiser
description: The FJ Cruiser has been in production from 2006 to 2022. It is available in two configurations one driving the rear wheels and the other four wheels. It is a very rugged SUV meant for the offroads and comfortable for on-road. It uses a high-mounted double wishbone front suspension and stabilizer bar, and a 4-link rear suspension with lateral rod with coil springs and stabilizer bar A perfect build for an offroad car. The engine is a high power engine running a 4.0L 1GR-FE V6 petrol engine fitted with Dual VVT-i technology producing 260hp and 367Nm of torque. This power gets stopped by 'powered' front four-piston and rear two-piston disc brakes. To keep it safe as it is made on the body-on-frame chassis, it is equipped with Anti-lock brake system, Electronic brakeforce distribution, Brake assist, and Vehicle Stability control.

name: Range Rover Velar
description: The Range Rover Velar D180 S is a luxury compact SUV that blends sleek design with advanced technology. It is powered by a 2.0-liter turbocharged diesel engine that produces 180 horsepower and 430 Nm of torque. The Velar D180 S offers a smooth and refined driving experience, with good fuel efficiency for its class. The "S" trim level includes premium features such as a dual-touchscreen infotainment system, leather upholstery, and advanced driver assistance systems. Known for its stylish design and modern interior, the Velar D180 S provides a balance of elegance, performance, and practicality.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: This Toyota Harrier Hybrid is specced with an automatic transmission gearbox, powered seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, rear mounted spoiler, front & side mounted curtain airbags, and electric tailgate.

The Vogue Autobiography trim offers a plush interior with premium materials, including leather upholstery, wood veneers, and a host of advanced features like a panoramic sunroof, heated and cooled seats, and state-of-the-art infotainment systems. Known for its off-road capabilities and on-road comfort, the Range Rover Vogue Autobiography 4.4L V8 is a blend of luxury, power, and versatility.

description: The Audi RS Q8 is a high-performance luxury SUV powered by a 4.0-liter twin-turbocharged V8 engine, producing 591 horsepower and 800 Nm of torque. The RS Q8 combines Audi's Quattro all-wheel-drive system with sporty handling, making it one of the fastest SUVs in its class. name: Toyota Harrier

The bike is known for being economical and straightforward, with minimal features, making it a budget-friendly option. Fuel efficiency is typically good, averaging around 35-40 km/l, which makes it an affordable choice for daily transportation.

name: Audi Q2

The interior is well-crafted, offering comfort and advanced technology, while its compact size ensures easy maneuverability in urban environments.

description: The 2021 Mercedes-AMG GLE 53 is a performance-oriented luxury SUV powered by a 3.0-liter inline-6 turbocharged engine with mild hybrid EQ Boost technology. It delivers 429 horsepower and 520 Nm of torque, allowing it to accelerate from 0 to 100 km/h in about 5.3 seconds. The GLE 53 combines sporty performance with a refined and spacious interior, featuring advanced technology, including the MBUX infotainment system, and a range of driver assistance features. It offers a dynamic driving experience, with air suspension for comfort and agility, making it suitable for both everyday driving and spirited performance.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TZ-G
description: The Toyota Land Cruiser Prado TZG with the 2.8-liter turbo-diesel engine delivers about 174 horsepower and 450 Nm of torque. This engine provides a good balance of power and fuel efficiency, with fuel consumption averaging around 10-12 km/l. The Prado TZG is equipped with a luxurious interior, advanced technology, and strong off-road capabilities, making it a versatile choice for both city driving and off-road adventures.

name: Audi SQ5
description: The 2020 Audi SQ5 TDI is a performance-oriented SUV powered by a 3.0-liter V6 turbo-diesel engine producing 347 horsepower and 700 Nm of torque. It accelerates from 0 to 100 km/h in about 5.1 seconds. This model combines strong performance with diesel efficiency, offering around 13-15 km/l. The SQ5 features sporty styling, a luxurious interior, and advanced technology, making it a dynamic yet comfortable choice for both daily driving and spirited adventures.

name: Landrover Defender 110
description: The 2020 Land Rover Defender 110 "Double 0" Edition with the 2.0-liter petrol engine is a special variant known for its blend of rugged capability and modern luxury. This model features a turbocharged 4-cylinder engine that produces 300 horsepower and 400 Nm of torque, enabling it to accelerate from 0 to 100 km/h in about 7.6 seconds. It offers a fuel consumption of around 9-11 km/l. The "Double 0" Edition stands out with unique styling elements and advanced off-road technology, making it both a capable adventure vehicle and a comfortable daily driver.

name: Audi Q5
description: The Typ 80A Audi Q5 S-LINE. It is equipped with Quattro All wheel drive system, Multifunctional steering wheel, daytime running LED lights, Premium surround sound system, digital instrument cluster, adaptive cruise control, and Blindspot monitoring assist.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TZ-G
description: The Landcruiser Prado TZ-G GDJ151, is equipped with a 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox, side steps, fog lights, front & side curtain airbags, and a multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Mercedes Benz GLE450H
description: This gorgeous Mercedes Benz GLE450H is specced with Heated seats, Air suspension setup, Multifunctional, tilt & telescopic steering wheel, Mercedes MBUX infotainment system, Downhill speed regulation system, Active parking assist sytem, Ambient lighting, Headlights with range adjustment functionality, Panoramic sunroof, Multiple climate zones, and Smartphone integration.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI
description: The Golf TSI is an excellent consumer, a good performer, low on maintenance costs, and high on its social standards, this is a good option as an entry car into the VAG Group of cars.

name: Nissan Note
description: This Nissan Note is specced with a gorgeous two-tone fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, anti-collision warning system, lane departure warning system, Traction control, and Auto start stop among other features.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The 2019 facelifted Mercedes-Benz C200 (W205) features a 1.5-liter turbocharged 4-cylinder engine paired with a mild hybrid system, producing around 184 horsepower. It offers a refined driving experience with improved fuel efficiency, averaging about 14-16 km/l. The 0 to 100 km/h time is approximately 7.7 seconds. The facelift brought updated styling, enhanced interior technology, and advanced driver assistance systems, making it a balanced blend of luxury, performance, and modern tech.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado J120
description: Nothing better than a fully loaded J120 Series Toyota Landcruiser Prado with a range of premium specs including a Sunroof, powered seats made of leather material, 7 seats occupancy capacity, and a fully functional infotainment system. This was initially owned in the United Kingdom. The 1KD 3.0 Turbocharged engine is a moving magic that just carries anything thrown at it except bad maintenance. Family units very well fit the car and long distance trips or offroading eacapades are the best with this J120!

name: Mazda Atenza
description: Atenza adopts Mazda's philosophy of Stylish, Insightful, and spirited design. It is hats off one of the best sedans to hit the market. A powerful engine, stylish and spacious, durable. and easy on the pockets. This would be an interesting choice to purchase for any long term use of a vehicle.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TZ-G
description: The Landcruiser Prado TZ-G GDJ151, diesel variant, is equipped with a 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox, side steps, fog lights, front & side curtain airbags, and a multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Mercedes Benz GLC 220
description: The GLC 220d AMG-LINE is specced with 4 MATIC All Wheel Drive, Powered Nappa leather seats, heated seats, Mercedes Speedtronic cruise control, Mercedes Command Infotainment system, Premium surround sound system, Smartphone integration, downhill speed regulation, active parking assist system, ambient lighting, and multiple climate zones.

name: Audi Q2
description: The 2017 Audi Q2 1.0 TFSI is a compact SUV powered by a 1.0-liter turbocharged engine that delivers 116 horsepower. It's known for its stylish design, efficient performance, and practical features, making it a great option for city driving. The interior is well-crafted, offering comfort and advanced technology, while its compact size ensures easy maneuverability in urban environments.

name: Mercedes Benz GLC 250
description: Mercedes GLC 250 replaced the GLK Class in 2015 for 2016 model years. It is a premium Compact SUV equivalent to the C Class sedan. It features a 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine, a multifunctional steering wheel, multi zone climate control, heated seats with memory function, ambient lighting, and active parking assist system among other specs.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The Subaru Forester, SJ5 is equipped with Eyesight adaptive cruise control, symmetrical AWD setup, electric parking brake, Multifunctional steering wheel, auto headlights, and Anti-collision brake assist.

name: Range Rover Sport
description: The Range Rover Sport is equipped with a Rain sensing windscreen wipers, Electronic air suspension setup, Terrain Response management system, electric locking differentials, smartphone integration, panoramic sunroof, daytime running LED Lights, and a Meridian premium surround sound system.

name: Mercedes Benz A180
description: The sporty stance of the A180 is seen even better with a bodykit on it. This bodykit includes both front and rear bumpers. It is an excellent alternative to Mercedes B Class. It is more dynamic and tends to favour younger owners.

name: Range Rover Vogue
description: The L405 is definitely an excellently engineered car. Thanks to Jaguar Landrover, it created a highly stylish and exquisite car. It is lighter compared to the older L322 because of the All-Aluminium monocoque unitary body structure. This unit features perforated leather seats, fixed glassroof, heated steering wheel, memory seats package, and Meridian premium surround sound system.

name: Subaru Levorg
description: Subaru Levorg introduced in 2014 has proven to give owners an excellent ownership experience with good performance from the 'small' 1600cc Turbocharged Petrol Engine. 'Small' is an understatement! Underrating a Levorg on the road might not turn out so well.

name: Bentley Continental GTC
description: The Continental GTC 4.0L V8 is specced with a concealable infotainment display screen, Naim by Bentley Premium Surround sound system, adaptive cruise control, four zone climate controls, Adaptive cruise control, and a Breitlig analog cabin clock.

name: Lexus RX200T
description: RX 200T appears slightly larger than then NX200T that they share an engine. It is bold and beautiful in all aspects. It has a nicely complimenting interior and exterior with the interior consisting of red leather seats, very spacious and comfy, an analogue clock, a heated steering wheel and seats that are also cooled, heated rear seats & 3-position memory seats, Head-Up Display, adaptive cruise control, and Anti-collision warning system among other equipments. The sporty nature of the car is complimented by the 2.0L 8AR-FTS turbocharged petrol engine that is one hell of a perfomer. It is also a very economical car attributed to by Lexus' Economy with Superior Thermal Efficient Combustion (ESTEC) direct injection with turbo (D-4ST) fuel injection. It is run by a 6-speed automatic transmission gearbox with a very smooth shift.

name: Audi A8
description: The A8 is equipped with Quattro All wheel drive system, Multifunctional steering wheel, daytime running LED lights, Premium surround sound system, digital instrument cluster, parking assist with parking aid plus, headlight washers, absorption control, radar guided adaptive cruise control, and Blindspot monitoring assist.

name: Lexus LX570
description: This is not the run-of-the-mill Lexus LX570. This is the Black Sequence edition and it is a Special Edition package with black outer mirrors, a black rear diffuser, and a black front grille.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: Toyota Harrier Premium has some premium specs added to it including a sunroof, Premium sound system, Xenon Projector Lamps, cruise control, and memory height adjustment. Other specs include a multifunctional steering wheel, powered seats, and a Pre-collision warning safety system among other specs.

name: Volkswagen Golf R
description: Having won a number of drag races or appeared on the top of drag performers, many know what this car is capable of. The R indicates a high performance car as Volkswagen refers it to. The EA888 3rd Gen inline-four petrol engine has a re-engineered cylinder head, exhaust valves, valve seats, pistons, injection valves, and a modified intercooler. This enables it handle high power demands of 296hp stock power. In its drivetrain, it uses the fifth Gen Haldex 4MOTION All Wheel drive system that decouples and couples the rear wheels on demand. This unit also comes with the Dynamic Chassis Control which enables one to choose from three suspension modes; Comfort, Normal, and Race adjusting suspension damping. The bucket-styled seats holds you in place and makes a very comfortable ride.

name: Toyota Landcruiser ZX
description: Toyota Landcruiser ZX is what a Toyota with everything feels like. With a Sunroof, 7 seats occupancy, front heated leather seats, an automatic transmission gearbox, side steps which is a standard equipment for this series, roof rails, fog lights, and the Old money interior trimming of wood, this is the epitome of Toyota's luxury in the actual Toyota nameplate. Driving this unit gives you more understanding of why an example of politicians really adore this car.

name: Range Rover Sport
description: The listed Autobiography is specced with powered seats, terrain response management system, perforated seats, Electric locking differentials, and Meridian Premium surround system.

name: Toyota Fielder
description: This is not the ordinary Toyota Fielder. It is the WXB trim, the highest trim there is and it comes fully specced. From half-leather seats to pre-collision braking assist systems, there is nothing you'd want and not get in this Axio. Moreover, being a hybrid, you are assured of excellent fuel consumption.

name: Mercedes Benz AMG S63L
description: A powerhouse! A Mercedes Benz S63 AMG 4.0 BITURBO V8 with a 9 speed AMG SPEEDSHIFT automatic transmission and a sliding panoramic sunroof. The engine produces 603hp and 900Nm of torque. Other specs include powered two-tone Nappa leather seats, heated seats, AMG performance steering wheel, ventilated brake discs, THERMOTRONIC luxury dual dual automatic climate control, Active parking assist with Parktronic and 360° camera, Electronic differential locking, Heads Up Display, and AMG-SPORTS Exhaust.

name: Mercedes Benz S320
description: One of the more iconic Mercedes Benz S Class models built. In most movies, it is depicted as a car that was owned by mafia bosses and the wealthy businesses people. It has old money aura around it and earns a lot of respect wherever you go.

name: Ford Ranger Raptor
description: Offroad king in a very sophisticated design that is an eyecatcher at a glance. Offroading tires, side steps, offroad modes, comfortable rides in offroad fitted suspensions and half leather seats on the interior, and a high torque 2000cc twin turbocharged diesel engine.

name: Audi A5
description: This Audi A5 is equipped with a 7 speed dual Clucth transmission, Multifunctional steering wheel, adaptive headlights, daytime running LED lights, virtual instrument cluster, premium surround sound system, and Adaptive cruise control.

name: Mercedes Benz GLE350D
description: This GLE 350D is equipped with Powered Nappa seats, active parking assist system, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, Mercedes Comand Infotainment system, Mercedes speedtronic cruise control, Premium surround sound system, downhill speed regulation, Sunroof, and Ambient lighting.

name: Range Rover Sport
description: The Range Rover Sport SVR is powered by a 5.0L V8 AJ133 Supercharged Petrol engine that does 575 Horsepowers and 702 Nm of Torque. It is mated to an 8 speed-shiftable ZF8HP automatic transmission gearbox. Other features include Powered two tone sports seats, heated front & rear seats, Terrain response management system, adaptive cruise control, Meridian premium surround sound system, Electric tailgate, and Traction control system.

name: Peugeot  3008
description: The 3008 GT-LINE is fitted with focal premium surround sound system, Electric parking brake, daytime running LED lights, keyless entry, dual front and side mounted airbags, and alloy rims.

name: Ferrari Carlifonia
description: One of the best exotics to have, Ferrari California, specced with a 7 speed dual clutch automatic transmission, Rear wheel drive, Powered, heated beige leather seats, Apple Car Play, Bucket styled sport seats, Daytime running LED lights, 8-way electrically adjustable seats, Engine start button on steering wheel, Tyre reparation emergency kit, Tyre pressure & temperature monitoring system, Hardtop convertible, Traction control system, Quad sports exhausts, and Electronic stability control.

name: Nissan Skyline
description: A partnership between Nissan and Daimler between 2014 and 2019 gave birth to this amazing engineering piece, the Skyline 200Gt-t. The car operated Daimler's 2.0L M274 DE20 turbocharged direct injection 4 cylinder petrol engine with a power rating of 208hp and 350Nm of torque and is mated to Daimler's 7G-Tronic auto with manual shift mode. Nissan also did well in the body design of Skyline creating a curvy sharp line body that is sport oriented as seen also with the dual-tip exhaust tailpipes. You get leather seats with the front seats having heating functionality, dual zone climate controls, Multifunctional steering wheel, and cup holders.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: Timeless, that's exactly what this Mercedes Benz C200 here is. This generation is also known to be thoroughly reliable. Couple that to the fact that it has had only two owners in Kenya and you have yourself a goldmine.

name: Subaru Impreza
description: Versatile compact car by Subaru that subtly satisfies individuals who would like to use this brand model for family use. It has a 5 seats occupancy capacity and a sufficient boot space. It has a powerful enough 1.5L NA and it looks very pretty

name: Toyota Aqua
description: A 1500cc petrol hybrid engine on a car that is almost weightless makes the Toyota Aqua the perfect blend of performance and fuel efficiency

name: Ford Ranger Wildtrack
description: The Ranger WILDTRAK 3.2TDCi is specced with two tone half leather seats, terrain response management system, locking differentials, side steps, and powered seats as some of its equipments.

name: Mercedes Benz AMG GLE 53
description: The GLE 53 AMG 4 MATIC is equipped with Mercedes speedtronic cruise control, Heated seats, ventilated brake discs, downhill speed regulation, active parking assist system, Burmester premium surround sound system, ambient lighting, heated wind screen, linguatronic voice control, AMG Sports exhausts, electronic locking diffs, and four wheel electronic traction system.

name: Mazda CX5
description: This CX-5 is specced with daytime running lights, Multifunctional tilt & telescopic steering wheel, Premium surround sound system, side impact airbags, Traction control system, and Adaptive frontlight system.

name: BMW X1
description: The X1 XDrive 25i "F48" is specced with a multifunctional steering wheel, all wheel drive system, daytime running LED lights, Premium surround sound system, and traction control.

name: Porsche Cayenne GTS
description: The GTS is equipped with an 8-speed automatic transmission, powered seats, daytime running LED lights, BOSE premium surround sound system, Porsche Active suspension setup, analog cabin clock, metallic paddle shifters, cruise control, engine immobilizer, hill descent assist, and Porsche Traction Management system.

name: Audi Q3
description: This the 2WD Spec Q3 fitted with a 1400cc turbocharged petrol engine, bucket styled seats, premium sound system, Multifunctional steering wheel, rear mounted spoiler, side impact airbags, and engine immobilizer.

name: Mercedes Benz GLC 250
description: Mercedes GLC 250 replaced the GLK Class in 2015 for 2016 model years. It is a premium Compact SUV equivalent to the C Class sedan. It features a 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine, a multifunctional steering wheel, multi zone climate control, heated seats with memory function, ambient lighting, and active parking assist system among other specs.

name: BMW X1
description: The X1 F48 series that came in is based on the Modular front-wheel drive based UKL2 platform that is used with BMW and MINI models, a modular meant to increase interior space and boot space in smaller size model cars. They are both available in front wheel and All Wheel drive systems with the front adopting the SDrive naming and the All Wheel adopting XDrive naming. This unit is an SDrive 18i meaning it runs a 1.5L B38 straight-3 turbocharged engine and drives the power to front wheels.

name: Toyota Axio
description: This is not the ordinary Toyota Axio. It is the WXB trim, the highest trim there is and it comes fully specced. From half-leather seats to pre-collision braking assist systems, there is nothing you'd want and not get in this Axio. Moreover, being a hybrid, you are assured of excellent fuel consumption.

name: Toyota Hilux
description: The Toyota Hilux is a jack of all trades. From hauling, carrying cargo, and attending serious meetings, it is a wonderful car to have by your side. From its interior, you see 5 leather seats, climate controls, an manual transmission gearbox, and steering wheel controls. It also has both front and rear bullbar and sufficient carrying capacity on the covered cargo space. It is also a diesel powered car which defines its durability with tough work!

name: Mazda CX5
description: Mazda CX-5 2.2L AWD, a new generation that was sold as from 2017 just after the 1st generation began in 2012. It features a totally new design and an improved set of technologies that made the CX-5 more beautiful and highly loved by consumers. There are a number of engines ranging from the 2.0L and 2.5L petrol engine & a 2.2L diesel turbocharged engine, all with Skyactiv technologies. The unit listed features the 2.2L Turbo Diesel engine that is easy going in this class, it is also equipped with a good number of technologies that make it very convenient for consumers!

name: Porsche Cayenne
description: Porsche has been producing superior performing cars since the early years of the 20th century. They have shown their expertise and highly advanced engineering in their productions. The Cayenne is one of the marvels of Porsche engineering.
