The 2015 Petrol Platinum Edition variant is powered by a 3600cc petrol engine that does an impressive 300 horsepower at 6300 RPMs and 400Nm of Torque at 3000 RPMs. It does a lot more better than the diesel variant in the horsepower numbers, doing about 240 horses. We can all agree on the engine's reliability and maintenance. It has beige leather, multizone climate controls, Multifunctional tilt & telescopic steering wheel, Auto start stop feature, a premium surround sound system, and differential locks.

name: Mercedes-Benz C200
description: This Mercedes Benz W205 with gorgeous aftermarket rims is equipped with a 7 speed automatic transmission gearbox, powered seats, daytime running LED lights, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, side mirror indicators, adaptive cruise control with lane keep assist, blindspot monitoring & emergency braking system, premium surround sound system, and traction control.

name: Nissan Note
description: This Nissan Note is specced with a gorgeous two-tone fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, anti-collision warning system, lane departure warning system, Traction control, and Auto start stop among other features.

name: Toyota Wish
description: A 5-door station wagon that's a proper Family car from Toyota. With its production lasting for 14 years since 2003, the 7 seater occupancy capacity and the 2ZR-FAE 1800CC Petrol engine, this is all you need for your family from Toyota.

name: Volvo XC60 T6 AWD
description: The XC60 comes in a number of trims and variants that satisfy customers with different preferences. The T6 is one of them which is the petrol variant powered by a 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine with a power rating of 300HP. It is fitted with a polished metal trimming on the interior, leather seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, and cruise control among other features.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The Mercedes Benz W205 is equipped with a 7 speed automatic transmission gearbox, powered seats, daytime running LED lights, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, side mirror indicators, adaptive cruise control with lane keep assist, blindspot monitoring & emergency braking system, premium surround sound system, and traction control.

name: Subaru XV
description: The Subaru XV Hybrid, an economical version of the Non-hybrid XV. It was introduced in 2013, using a permanent magnet AC synchronous motor rated 13 hp and 65 Nm, Lineartronic CVT, Nickel hydride batteries, and gets equipped with 225/55 R17 tires. It can runs up to 1.6Kms going at a max speed of 40km/hr. The generator-motor is built into the Lineartronic CVT, similar to the "turbo-parallel-hybrid" system that was used in Subaru B5 TPH Concept car.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The Mercedes Benz W205 is equipped with a 7 speed automatic transmission gearbox, powered seats, daytime running LED lights, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, side mirror indicators, adaptive cruise control with lane keep assist, blindspot monitoring & emergency braking system, premium surround sound system, and traction control.

name: Toyota Fielder
description: This Toyota Fielder runs a 1.5L petrol engine, an automatic transmission gearbox, leather seats, climate controls, and a reverse camera.

name: BMW X5
description: This is the 2nd gen of the X5 which was launched in 2006 for the 2007 model year. It featured a torque split capable XDrive All wheel drive system which comes as a big advantage in maneuvering terrains. It uses a 3.0L petrol engine with a power rating of 302hp. Quite a powerful engine option.

name: Subaru Legacy
description: Being the makers flagship car, Subaru was committed to building a non-problematic fun, safe, and reliable car. It features symmetrical AWD Setup which is standard in the Legacy. Running from 1989, it has been known to be a powerful and durable car that a lot of enthusiasts have thoroughly enjoyed. It features a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, cruise control, and fabric seats.

name: Mitsubishi ASX
description: Mitsubishi ASX, ASX for Active Sports Crossover, is the ultimate crossover SUV for any owner looking to get a fuel efficient, reliable, and convenient SUV for a relatively good price. The Nameplate ASX was used to sell Mitsubishi RVR in a lot of markets except from Japan, South Korea, and Canada where it is known as the RVR. It runs the bigger 4B11 2.0L NA petrol engine from the smaller Japanese 1.6L.

name: Audi A3
description: The A3 Sportback is specced with a 1.4L Turbocharged Petrol Engine driving the front wheels, Audi MMI infotainment system, Multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, and rear mounted spoiler.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The Subaru Forester SK9! It is specced with Eyesight adaptive cruise control, Front & side canera views, Snow Dirt & Snow Mud modes, symmetrical AWD setup, half leather seats, heated front seats, metallic pedals, auto start stop for fuel efficiency, and Anti-collision brake assist.

name: Volvo XC60
description: Volvo's torque house, the XC60, D4, which has a D4204T15 turbocharged diesel engine producing 400Nm of Torque. The petrol variant has 350Nm of torque. It is specced with leather seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, a wood trimming, sunroof, and powered seats with memory function.

name: Nissan Bluebird
description: Nissan Bluebird has been widely known for its durability and reliability over the years of marketing and production since 1955. It is a very comfy car, good consumer, and very easy to operate and maintain. A 1.8L well powered with power rating of 118 horsepowers, mechanically comfortable seats and spaces, and convenient equipments that eases both the driver's and occupants rides consist of what the BlueBird has to offer.

name: Toyota Axio
description: The Toyota Axio specced with fabric seats, FM RADIO system, climate controls, and a reliable 1NZ-FE 1.5L engine.

name: Mazda Demio
description: The Demio is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, fabric seats, android infotainment display system, and headlight range adjustment.

name: Mercedes Benz GLC 220d
description: The GLC 220d AMG-LINE is specced with 4 MATIC All Wheel Drive, Powered Nappa leather seats, heated seats, Mercedes Speedtronic cruise control, Mercedes Command Infotainment system, Premium surround sound system, Smartphone integration, downhill speed regulation, active parking assist system, ambient lighting, and multiple climate zones.

name: Mercedes Benz G350d
description: The G350d is equipped with 9 speed automatic transmission gearbox, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, Harman kardon premium surround sound system, roof rails, dual front & side impact curtain airbags, Bi-xenon headlights with range adjustment functionality, and attention assist system.

name: Mercedes Benz S400
description: The S400 is specced with Powered Nappa leather seats, head up display, 12.3" infotainment display screen, Burmester premium surround sound system, ambient lighting, 360° camera view, panoramic sunroof, analogue dashboard clock, ambient lighting, and 4 zone climate controls.

name: Volkswagen Golf GTI
description: The MK7.5 GTI with DCC(Dynamic Chassis Control) PACKAGE is specced with an uprated 3rd Gen EA888 engine, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, side mirror indicators, premium surround sound system, digital instrument cluster, and traction control.

name: Volkswagen Golf R
description: The facelift of the MK7, MK7.5, with a new digital instrument cluster and an uprated engine with the Dynamic Chassis Control system that controls the driving especially in Sports Mode. It also features a heated front seats, launch control, HALDEX based 4MOTION all wheel drive, side mirror indicators, Dynaudio premium surround sound system, and Adaptive cruise control.

name: Audi A5
description: This "B9" generation of the A5 is equipped with a 7 speed dual Clucth transmission, Multifunctional steering wheel, adaptive headlights, daytime running LED lights, virtual instrument cluster, premium surround sound system, and Adaptive cruise control.

name: Audi A7
description: The A7 is equipped with Quattro All wheel drive system, Multifunctional steering wheel, daytime running LED lights, Premium surround sound system, digital instrument cluster, radar guided adaptive cruise control, and Blindspot monitoring assist.

name: Audi Q5
description: The Typ 80A Audi Q5 S-LINE. It is equipped with Quattro All wheel drive system, Multifunctional steering wheel, daytime running LED lights, Premium surround sound system, digital instrument cluster, adaptive cruise control, and Blindspot monitoring assist.

name: Volkswagen Golf R
description: On the MK7 generation, this Golf R comes specced with Dynamic Chassis Control, powered seats, launch control, daytime running LED lights, HALDEX based 4MOTION all wheel drive system, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, side mirror indicators, and Dynaudio premium surround sound system.

name: Lexus LX570
description: The WALD EDITION LX570 is equipped with an 8 speed automatic transmission with manual mode, daytime running LED lights, powered seats, wireless phone charging functionality, Mark Levinson Premium surround sound system, roof rails, hill start & descents assist, smartphone integration, and terrain response management system.

name: Volkswagen Golf GTI
description: One of the most aggressive hatchbacks we have had in the car scene. A 2.0L EA888 engine in the hood mated to a 6-speed DSG gearbox. Its power rating stands at 220hp, similar to what an Audi Q5 does. Its interior has original GTI fabric seats with armrests both in the front and the rear. The entertainment system is Volkswagen's factory setup that comes with a premium sound system. Other specs include a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters for aggressive driving, dual zone climate controls, and the claw-design Foglights.

name: Jeep Wrangler
description: This is the 3rd generation Jeep Wrangler that came into production in 2006 under the development of Daimler Chrysler and was developed under a clean-sheet design of the body, frame, and suspension. This generation came with power windows, remote power door locks, navigation, and electronically detachable sway bars on some models. The Wrangler carries the seriousness an offroader deserves. It also has an aftermarket Carbon steering wheel with engine revs display among other dash systems. A 4WD system and a high torque engine is all you need to fulfil your offroad adventures!

name: Toyota Wish
description: Toyota Wish is an MPV(Multipurpose Vehicle) with a lot to offer. 7 seats occupancy capacity with the seats made of fabric, a powerful 1.8L 2ZR-FAE petrol engine, a large enough cargo space that can also be extended by folding the 3rd row seats, and a generally reliable car in all aspects.

name: Mitsubishi Lancer
description: This is a local spec Mitsubishi Lancer specced with a 1.6L 4A92 I4 NA Petrol engine. This is a refreshed model done in 2016 with the option of a 1.6L 4A92 and a 2.0L 4B11 engine. It has a 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox, fabric seats, and a multifunctional steering wheel. The EX badging was introduced to differentiate it from the previous generation sold alongside this Lancer EX.

name: Mazda Axela
description: The Hybrid version of Mazda Axela was unveiled in 2013 at the Tokyo International Motor Show. It has the Skyactiv-G 2.0 engine with 14:1 compression and electric-petrol drive. It makes it one of the most unique versions of the Axela giving it an edge also in terms consumption and performance.

name: Volvo V40
description: Volvo V40 T3 utilizes the 1.6L I4 with 148hp power rating. Leather seats, dual zone climate controls, a multifunctional steering wheel, polished metal trimming, and adpative cruise control consists its specs.

name: Subaru Impreza
description: Impreza GP3, the AWD 2.0L Spec, is an excellent hatch to utilize with that it can be used for family purposes and chilled motorsports activities. It runs a 2.0L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine which comfortably handles its payload. On the interior, it is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, android infotainment display system, Multifunctional steering wheel, and a spoiler.

name: Subaru Legacy
description: Subaru Legacy, in its class, offers very good performance. With just a 2.5L engine, it performs well among other cars of the same class. And with Subaru's standard Symmetrical All Wheel Drive, you get to easily play around with traction when other road users might be struggling with theirs. It is very spacious and comfortable for both short and long distance travels.

name: Volkswagen Touareg
description: The 1st Gen of Touareg was first produced in 2002 and straight up won several awards for its among it for being the best in the 4×4 car category. It shares a lot of parts with the Cayenne and has it engine equipped with a 3.6L Petrol V6 engine. This is a go-to car for someone who wants to use it for several purposes including offroading and for urban setups.

name: Toyota Aqua
description: Toyota Aqua has a 1500cc naturally aspirated engine and a hybrid setup that saves a lot when it comes to fuel economy This unit is specced with two tone fabric seats, climate controls, and cup holders.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI
description: Volkswagen Golf TSI with its great German lifestyle! If you are looking for a great budget car that goes easy on your pockets both on fuel and maintenance & excels in delivering reliability with durability, this is the place. The 1.2L turbocharged petrol engine is a fast one and quickly dashes whenever prompted. It is also easy to maintain with a few services to be done during its service periods. It is very descent one as well with practical sense in both office and recreational activities.

name: Mazda Atenza
description: The Atenza is specced with 6 speed automatic transmission, Infotainment system control screen, Daytime running lights, fabric seats Multifunctional tilt & telescopic steering wheel, premium sound system, Push-Start ignition, Cruise control, Dual zone climate controls, Keyless entry, Side impact airbags, reverse camera, and rear mounted spoiler.

name: Audi SQ5
description: Based on the Audi Q5, the SQ5 is a much powerful version of the Q5 that runs a 3.0L V6 Supercharged Petrol Engine producing 354hp and 470Nm of torque which is way higher than what the 2.0L Q5 produces. It has the Quattro All Wheel Drive system which comes in handy in delivering optimal driving experience. This is where the thrill lies!

name: Subaru Forester
description: A well engineered, great powered SUV, with one of the best drivetrains in the world, the Subaru Forester. It is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, and heated front seats as some of its major specs.

name: BMW X3
description: BMW X3 is based on the BMW 5 Series and classified as a Sports Activity Vehicle. This is where luxury has been fully invested by BMW. The reason BMW has fitted a lot of equipments on the X3 ranging from hill descent control, front & rear camera view, Autohold brake function, electric parking brake, Front heated seats, parking sensors, radar guided adaptive cruise control, ECO Pro modes, powered memory seats, to the multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Toyota Fortuner
description: This is the Fortuner from the 1st Generation the began production in 2004 to 2015 when the 2nd Gen began. This was available with the 3.0L 1KD-FTV common rail variable geometry turbocharged diesel engine that was common in a lot of high torque Toyota models. It has a functional scoop on its hood being a common rail turbo intercooled. It has 7 seats occupancy capacity, excellent clearance, and a automatic transmission gearbox as some of its major specs.

name: Toyota Hilux Surf
description: Toyota Hilux Surf, in other markets know as the Toyota 4 Runner, received this naming because of its 4 wheel drive ability and also being able to operate in any terrain. The Japanese market was sold only 4 generations of Hilux Surf until 2009 when it was only continued for the American market in its 5th generation. This is the last of this gem in the Kenyan Market. It is built on the same platform as the Toyota Tacoma. This is a well maintained unit with leather seats, roof rails, and side steps among other specs.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The Forester is equipped with fabric seats, climate controls, and a tilt and telescopic steering wheel amongst other specs.

name: Toyota Mark X
description: This Toyota Mark X is fitted with 5 fabric seats, dual zone climate controls, interior wood trimming, steering wheel controls, android infotainment display screen, armrests, and fog lights.

name: Toyota RAV4
description: The Toyota RAV4 basing from its powerful Naturally Aspirated 2.4L engine producing 160 horsepower and 220Nm of torque and roof rails, it can do a lot One can carry heavy cargo and travel for long distances and the RAV4 would still handle pretty well. Fabric seats steering wheel controls, climate controls, and an android infotainment display screen complete this very reliable unit.

name: Volkswagen Passat
description: Volkswagen passat B7 gen came with some improvements majorly consisting of the body panels, grille, and headlights. The face of the Passat keeps on getting better with the advancements in generations. This unit is specced with leather seats, an analogue cabin clock, interior wood trimming, Multifunctional steering wheel, and powered seats with memory function.

name: Toyota Landcruiser ZX
description: Toyota Landcruiser ZX, Bruno Edition, is what a Toyota with everything feels like. With a Sunroof, 7 seats occupancy, front heated and cooled leather seats, heated steering wheel, an automatic transmission gearbox, side steps which is a standard equipment for this series, roof rails, fog lights and the Old money interior trimming, this is the epitome of Toyota's luxury in the actual Toyota nameplate Driving this unit gives you more understanding of why an example of politicians really adore this car.

name: Volkswagen Tiguan
description: The Volkswagen Tiguan 1.4L TSI is specced with Dynaudio premium surround sound system, 360° view camera, all round proximity sensors, side impact airbags, rear mounted spoiler, lane keep assist, and parking sensors.

name: Mercedes Benz E400
description: The W213 Mercedes Benz, produced from 2016 and sold from 2017, is the 5th Gen of the E Klasse. This is the Convertible Spec, sharing its platform with the  station wagon which wasn't so earlier with the W212. The 2017 being the most technologically advanced car Mercedes had made at the time puts the 2019 E400 Cabriolet way ahead of its time. The E400 uses the 3.0L M276 V6 Twin Turbo Petrol with a power rating of 362hp.

name: Mercedes Benz S350
description: The S350 W211, a full-size sedan produced from 2005 to 2013 as the 5th Gen of the S Class Mercedes Benz. This generation brought in a wave of new developments by Mercedes from safety to convenience. Safety: Brake Assist, Electronic stability program, speedtronic adjustable speed limiter, distronic plus radar controlled cruise control which is optional, pre-safe and pre-safe plus for those with distronic plus, Bi-Xenon headlights with Active Light Function swivelling curve light, and night view assist which is optional. Suspension: Airmatic air suspension paired with adaptive damping system, hydropneumatic Active Body Control standard in some cars including S600, S63, and S65 and Tele Aid used for emergency assistance provision. Comfort & convenience: Rain-sensing windshield wipers with two sensitivity settings, Fully automatic climate control system, Speed sensitive parameter steering, Electrically adjustable, folding, heated mirrors, Electrically folding rear head restraints, Electrically adjustable steering column, Infrared reflecting glass & noise insulating glass, garage door opener integrated in the interior rear view mirror, and Bi-Xenon headlights with Active Light Function swivelling curve light. This is just a few of what an S Class entails.

name: Landrover Discovery Sport
description: The Discovery Sport SE Si4 is specced with 5 seats carrying capacity, Multifunctional steering wheel, Meridian premium surround sound system, hill descent control, and heated rear and front windshields among other specs.

name: Audi Q3
description: This the 2WD Spec Q3 fitted with a 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox(S-Tronic), bucket styled seats, premium sound system, Multifunctional steering wheel, rear mounted spoiler, side impact airbags, and engine immobilizer.

name: Mini cooper
description: Mini Cooper S Clubman marketed and sold under BMW’s Mini Marque as its manufacturer as well. It is in the class of subcompact executive car. It first came into the market in 2007 and the 2nd Gen began in 2015. This is the 2nd gen that is based on BMW’S UKL2 Platform that features more space than the 1st gen. It features a special access to the cargo space via bi-parting rear doors called barn or split doors which made it unique at the time of its entry into the market. This unit features a 2.0L B48 Petrol engine with a power rating of 190hp. The engine is mated to an 8 speed automatic transmission gearbox.

name: Mercedes Benz E220d
description: Mercedes has always been the leading in terms of class, safety and looks. From its eye-catching sleek exterior design to its luxurious interior, with features such as leather seats, it is the perfect car for anyone looking for a reliable vehicle that offers a comfortable driving experience and impressive performance.

name: Subaru Legacy
description: Subaru Legacy outdoes itself in its class by offering very good performance. With just a 2.5L engine, it performs well among other cars of the same class. And with Subaru's standard Symmetrical All Wheel Drive, you get to easily play around with traction when other road users might be struggling with theirs. It is very spacious and comfortable for both short and long distance travels.

name: Suzuki Swift
description: Suzuki Swift is powered by a 1200cc naturally aspirated engine which is quite powerful in the hatchback. It also consumes well as the engine can with no strain run all the car components and accelerate easily.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The Subaru Forester is equipped with Eyesight adaptive cruise control, symmetrical AWD setup, electric parking brake, Multifunctional steering wheel, auto headlights, and Anti-collision brake assist.

name: Honda Vezel
description: The Vezel RS Hybrid is specced with a 1.5L petrol engine with a complimentary hybrid system, daytime running lights, Infotainment system display screen, lane departure warning assist, Anti-collision brake assist, reverse camera, Multifunctional steering wheel, and foglamps.

name: Toyota Fielder
description: Still fresh into the Kenyan Market, Toyota Filder ,coded NZE161, runs the 1.5L 1NZ-FE Naturally Aspirated petrol engine with a power rating of 109hp. There are other engine variants such as the 1.8L found in the S Trim. It is also specced with some fabric seats, Auto start-stop system, traction control, climate controls, and an android infotainment system among other specs.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: Mercedes Benz C200 ELEGANCE! It is the middle level trim with Avantgarde being the highest while Classic being the base. Elegance trim featured standard leatherette upholstery with optional leather. It also retained the traditional Mercedes-Benz grille, with horizontal chrome bars and standing hood emblem. The engine features a 1.8L turbocharged M271 CGI Inline-four engine with power rating of 270Nm of torque.

name: Toyota Kluger
description: As bulletproof as we always praise the Kluger for, it lives to that. From 2003, the car still drives super easy and super reliable. Body is in good shape and the engine is in good condition, just beginning its adventures.

name: Mercedes Benz C250
description:
EN ROUTE TO THE PORT OF MOMBASA! EXPECTED TIME OF ARRIVAL 6th AUGUST, 2024.

It is equipped with a 9 speed automatic transmission gearbox, powered seats, daytime running LED lights, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, side mirror indicators, adaptive cruise control with lane keep assist, blindspot monitoring & emergency braking system, premium surround sound system, and traction control.

name: Audi A5
description:
EN ROUTE TO THE PORT OF MOMBASA! EXPECTED TIME OF ARRIVAL 6th AUGUST, 2024.

It is equipped with a 7 speed dual Clucth transmission, Multifunctional steering wheel, adaptive headlights, daytime running LED lights, virtual instrument cluster, premium surround sound system, and Adaptive cruise control.

name: Jaguar XF
description: Jaguar is a classy car known for its use in the upper class. It is admired for the richness of technologies and elegance it carries. It is specced with an 8 speed ZF8HP automatic transmission gearbox, a Multifunctional steering wheel, adaptive headlights, daytime running LED lights, Meridian premium surround sound system, and Adaptive cruise control.

name: BMW X4
description: The X4 began production in 2014 as a compact luxury SUV marketed as a sports activity coupè. Its styling is similar to that of a two door coupè especially in its roof lining. The first gen was coded as the F26 and models included the XDrive 20i, XDrive 28i, 35i, 35d, 20d, all being XDrive versions. The M Performance version, the M40i came in to the market in 2016 with a power rating of 335hp. It shares it powertrain with the X3 with the I4 and I6 engine configurations. This runs the 2.0L N20B20 I4 turbocharged petrol engine with a power rating of 241hp.

name: Landrover Discovery V
description: The Discovery V is specced with Terrain response management system, 7 seats carrying capacity, Rear Entertainment screens, Electric locking differentials, perforated leather seats, multiple way Electrically Adjustable seats, Meridian premium surround sound system, and memory seats package among other specs.

name: Nissan Note
description: This is the Nissan Note DIG-S which means Direct Injection Gasoline-Supercharged. The Supercharger in this unit makes quite a difference in the power the Nissan Note makes. 147Nm of torque and 97hp compared to the NA version making 78hp and 106Nm does some magic in this Note DIGS Spec!

name: Toyota Auris
description: A fairly great car to own, the Toyota Auris! The Auris has always retained its worth over the years for its durability and reliability. With a few engine varieties, owners have really appreciated how they have been treated by the cars in general. This unit runs the 1.5L version, and has fabric seats among other specs.

name: BMW X5
description: BMW X5 is a mid-size luxury SUV categorised by BMW as Sports Activity Vehicle (SAV) instead of SUV. It is available in an All wheel drive system that features torque-split. The E70 came in next after the E53 in 2006. The current listed F15 gen car came in later in 2013 featuring the same chassis and wheelbase as the E70. The F15 came with an introduction of an increased number of engine choices including the XDrive 40d, XDrive 35i, XDrive 25d, and SDrive 25d. This unit features a 3.0L N57 straight-6 diesel engine with a power rating of 560Nm of torque. It is fitted with heated seats that are powered, head up display, hill descent control, and an electric tailgate among other specs.

name: Mitsubishi RVR
description: The RVR is your perfect crossover. With just the right body lenght and width, you can comfortably carry 5 passengers and go into any kind of squeezed road and still burn just enough fuel while going low on maintenance costs!

name: Honda Vezel
description: The Vezel RS Hybrid is specced with a 1.5L petrol engine with a complimentary hybrid system, daytime running lights, Infotainment system display screen, lane departure warning assist, Anti-collision brake assist, reverse camera, Multifunctional steering wheel, and foglamps.

name: Toyota Probox
description: Toyota Probox came to the market as a commercial vehicle that makes it very efficient in conducting business between various towns and long distances. It has a 2 wheel drive drivertrain that sends power, received from a 1500cc engine, to 2 Wheels all the time. It is fitted with fabric seats with the rear seats having leather material. Other features include an android infotainment display screen, climate controls powered windows, and a foot brake that is powerful compared to the handbrake.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TX
description: The J120 series were very good choices of Landcruiser Prados. For a daily driver who moves short distances, this is the best choice. Long distances would still work although the diesel brother works best for such trips. This unit has 7 seats with the 3rd row being foldable. Its engine is the 2.7L 2TR with 167hp power rating.

name: Mazda CX3
description: Mazda did a 2.0L Petrol option also on the CX3, an option that was avaliable on high end cars. Mazda Connect infotaiment system, a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, leather seats all spaced well especially for the rear occupants, and Traction Control system consist of the premium specs in this listing.

name: Volkswagen Tiguan
description: This is one of the cleanest Volkswagen Tiguans we have in the market. Excellent body state, well maintained interior with the beige leather seats sitting perfectly, a panoramic sunroof, a 2.0L engine in a mechanically sound condition, and an All Wheel drive system. It is listed with a good price giving it an edge in the market.

name: BMW 530i
description: The G30 is the 7th generation sedan of BMW 5 series. The G31 is the wagon or touring version. It is based on BMW’s Modular Cluster Architecture Platform (CLAR) that was first used in the G11 7 series. Its chassis is made from a mixture of steel and aluminium. The suspension system utilizes a double-wishbone front suspension and 5-link rear suspension. The Wagon variant uses self-levelling rear air suspension. The steering system is rack and pinion with electric power assistance. Its powertrain utilizes a 2.0L B48 Inline-4 turbo petrol engine.

name: BMW 116i
description: The BMW 116i is powered by a 1.6L inline 4 turbocharged engine. It drives only the rear wheels which is unique to the F20 and the F21 series as other models mostly drive front wheels. It has 5 alcantara seats, climate controls, and BMW'S iDrive infotainment system which is quite advanced and very detailed in the number of car controls it holds. Other specs include the multifunctional steering wheel and nice BMW alloy rims.

name: Volvo V60
description: Volvo V60 T4 is a trim of Volvo's 1st Gen. It has three engine versions run on this trim, two being a 1.6L and one being a 2.0L. The engine code of this variant is the B4164T with a power rating of 178hp. This is the facelift that came in 2014 with it being more sleek and appealing. This unit comes fitted with heated seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, a premium surround sound system that's arguably one of the best, and dual exhaust tailpipes.

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: The XTRAIL AUTECH Trim is equipped with great offroad features beginning with the 4WD drive system that is optional with the 2WD system being standard, a good ride height to easily crawl through uneven terrain systems, roof rails that creates a platform for a roof rack, and a powerful enough 2.0L Petrol engine. It also has a sunroof, cruise control, and ECO Mode to regulate fuel consumption.

name: Mercedes Benz A180
description: The Mercedes Benz A180 is an excellent German subcompact executive car. Being Mercedes' entry level car, it was well received in the market and has been widely purchased over the 4 generations it has been produced in. This is the 2nd Gen internally coded as W169 produced from 2004. Runs a 1.5L M266 I4 Petrol engine and accomodates upto 5 individuals.

name: Mazda Demio
description: The Demio is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, fabric seats, android infotainment display system, and headlight range adjustment.

name: Lexus RX450h
description: In matters reliablity, convenience, and class, the RX450h gets the good score! Many of its users have appreciated how good the Lexus has been. It comes with dark leather seats, climate controls, multifunctional steering wheel, and amrests.

name: Volkswagen Golf R
description:
EN ROUTE TO THE PORT OF MOMBASA! EXPECTED TIME OF ARRIVAL 1st AUGUST, 2024.

The Golf R MK7 comes specced with Dynamic Chassis Control, powered seats, launch control, daytime running LED lights, HALDEX based 4MOTION all wheel drive system, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, side mirror indicators, and Dynaudio premium surround sound system.

name: Nissan Juke
description: Nissan Juke made a debut in 2010 as a production vehicle. In its first year of selling, it surpassed the manufacturer's expectation 10 fold and since then it has been received well in the market. It has been purchased in high numbers in Kenya also making it among best selling cars that some have criticised its shape, one that was inspired by a lot of history at Nissan. This unit comes with two-tone fabric seats, climate controls, android infotainment display screen, and a push to start button.

name: Daihatsu Mira
description: Produced since 1980, Daihatsu Mira was produced for commercial purposes as a city vehicle. Its usage with Uber and Bolt cases are the perfect examples of its commercial use. The engine also is an excellent use case, with a 660cc displacement capacity, fuel consumption levels are at its best.

name: Mazda CX5
description: Mazda CX-5 2.2L AWD, a new generation that was sold as from 2017 just after the 1st generation began in 2012. It features a totally new design and an improved set of technologies that made the CX-5 more beautiful and highly loved by consumers. There are a number of engines ranging from the 2.0L and 2.5L petrol engine & a 2.2L diesel turbocharged engine, all with Skyactiv technologies. The unit listed features the 2.2L Turbo Diesel engine that is easy going in this class, it is also equipped with a good number of technologies that make it very convenient for consumers!

name: Mazda Atenza
description: Atenza adopts Mazda's philosophy of Stylish, Insightful, and spirited design. It is hats off one of the best sedans to hit the market. A powerful engine, stylish and spacious, durable. and easy on the pockets. This would be an interesting choice to purchase for any long term use of a vehicle.

name: Nissan Rich
description: Nissan Rich is a pickup truck and an SUV produced through a joint venture of Chinese Auto Dongfeng and Nissan. It is based on the Nissan F-Alpha Platform meaning a pickup with a long roof bed cover. It uses a petrol engine with a 2.4L Rating mated to a 5 speed manual gearbox.

name: Volkswagen Tiguan
description: This is a Special Edition Volkswagen Tiguan Allspace. It is the LWB version of the Tiguan, also advertised as Tiguan L. This version accomodates up to 7 individuals whose 3rd row is foldable. It holds a Special "OFFROAD" badging on the door pillar being an Offroad edition produced for the European market. Its Characteristic design for the Offroad edition has it specced with a unique bumper design with skid plates, black chrome window trim strips, black roof rails and side mirror covers. The interior has centre storage compartment wrapped in fabric, black headliner, gear knob wrapped in leather, rubber floor mats, and an Active Control System that one can select between Onroad, Offroad, and Snow modes.

name: Landrover Defender 110
description: Land Rover Defender X, P400 MHEV coded L663, a performance variant of the base Defender, is a 4-Wheel-drive off-road luxury manufactured by Jaguar Land Rover. It is a new engineering done by Land Rover on their new generation Landrovers. This new gen replaced the original generation Land Rover Defender that were produced from 1983-2016. Some highlights of its equipments include a permanent all-wheel drive, electronic active locking differentials with torque vectoring by braking, and a two-speed transfer case. Air suspension comes as a standard feature on this unit different from Defender 90 with which coil springs are standard. Its choice of engines come from a list of JLR Ingenium engines including the D200 having a 2.0L Diesel engine of power rating 196bhp, D240 with a 2.0l diesel engine of power rating 237bhp, P300 with a 2.0L Petrol, P400 with a 3.0L 6-cylinder turbo Petrol mild hybrid of 395bhp, and the P400e only available in the 110 with power rating of 398bhp. Its interior gets to be minimalistic with what welcomes you being a 10.0 inch infotainment system, gear lever along the center console, a few dials and the whole space for oneself.

name: BMW 523i
description: This is among the first models of the F10 Series BMW 523i that was first sold in 2011 with the series in general coming with major improvements that included dual Clucth transmission as used with the M5, 8 speed automatic transmission gearbox, and the turbocharged V8 engine as with the S63 engine among other specs. This unit is specced with 5 leather seats, parking sensors, Autohold brake function, auto start stop feature, and a 2.0L N20B20 inline-four turbocharged engine that was comparatively better than the N52/N53 NA six cylinder engines.

name: Mazda 6
description: What a better Saloon than the Mazda 6 popularly known as the Atenza! The Mazda 6 has an engaging drive with its agile driving and linear steering style. The Skyactiv tech petrol engine with a capacity of 2000cc impressively pushing torque figures of 213Nm. Quite a classy sedan!

name: Mazda CX5
description: The CX-5 is specced with daytime running lights, Multifunctional tilt & telescopic steering wheel, BOSE Premium surround sound system, side impact airbags, Traction control system, and Adaptive frontlight system.

name: Volkswagen Tiguan
description: Volkswagen Tiguan has been, overally, the best selling SUV in the Volkswagen Group, with over 900,000 units being produced in 2019 alone. It is an excellent compact crossover with the best offer from this car being the efficiency of the 2.0L TSI engine with a power rating of 197hp and consuming excellently.

name: Mercedes Benz E250
description: The E250 is specced with a 9 speed 9G-Tronic automatic transmission gearbox, bucket styled seats, daytime running LED lights, Multifunctional steering wheel, side mirror indicators, front & side impact curtain airbags, premium surround sound system, and tyre pressure monitoring system.

name: BMW 118i
description: BMW 118i M-SPORT, F20, was produced from 2011 to 2019. It is powered by a 1.5L B38 inline 3 turbocharged engine. It drives only the rear wheels which is unique to the F20 and the F21 series as other models mostly drive front wheels. It has 5 alcantara seats, dual zone climate controls BMW'S iDrive infotainment system which is quite advanced and very detailed in the number of car controls it holds. Other specs include the multifunctional steering wheel and nice BMW alloy rims.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: This might just be the best good looking Forester XT in our stock. With the unique maroon colour, you definitely get an eyecatcher Being an XT, you get the best of performance both on road and offroad. The XMODE feature S#(Sport Sharp), S(Sport), and I(Intelligent) modes all work to ensure you have a seamless and enjoyable car experience.

name: Toyota Noah
description: The Toyota Noah is specced with Fabric seats, android infotainment display screen, climate controls, lane departure warning system, Anti-collision braking system, side mirror indicators, powered doors, Antilock Braking system, and fog lights.

name: Ford Ranger
description: One of the great builds every Ford deserves! Aftermakert modifications done on this car makes it the best aftermarket mod car. The highlight is a stage one tune to the 3.2L 6 speed auto with a DPF & EGR delete which gives it a rating of 250hp and 500Nm of Torque. Some more specs done on this car include a Pioneer underseat subwoofer, Straight pipe, BF goodrich, Forged Fuel Custom rims including spare Custom sidesteps, bullbars Wheel arches, Ironman Lift kit suspension, Ironman lights, Chameleon tint, Led bar light, and Tuffcap boot cover.

name: Honda Fit Shuttle
description: Honda Fit Shuttle Hybrid is one of the best sub-compact station wagon cars to own that give an average of 34Kms a Liter as per a report by Honda. The shuttle hybrid is based on the Fit Hybrid which its smaller brother. This amazing fuel economy is achieved by reducing rolling resistance with front braking, reduced engine friction, improved control efficiency of the hybrid system, ECON mode to minimise fuel consumption, and improved aerodynamics.

name: Mazda CX3
description: Mazda CX-3 began sales in 2016 in all the major markets it was sold including Canada. A lot of individuals have responded well to this entry into the market. It was produced in the age of modern technologies and designs making it a good looking car since the first generation as consumere don't have any other thought of how Mazda looked or previously performed which gives it an advantage of having a positive face in the automotive sector.

name: Honda Fit
description: The Honda fit is powered by a 1300cc naturally aspirated engine that produces 97 horsepower and 130Nm of torque. In its interior are fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, android infotainment display screen, and an Eco drive mode that saves on fuel by reducing the engine performance.

name: Honda Vezel
description: The Vezel Hybrid is specced with a 1.5L petrol engine with a complimentary hybrid system, daytime running lights, Infotainment system display screen, reverse camera, Multifunctional steering wheel, and foglamps.

name: Ford Ranger
description: This is a local spec Ford Ranger specced with a 3.2L Diesel Turbo Engine mated to an automatic transmission with locking differentials, an android infotainment system, climate controls, 5 leather being a double cabin spec, and a tow hatch among other specs. Being a XLT, it is an Extra Luxurios Truck as it appears and as XLT actually means.

name: Mazda Atenza
description: SKYACTIV is a series of technologies that Mazda intended that they increase engine output and fuel efficiency. The Mazda Atenza uses a Skyactiv-D engine which is a group of diesel engines that are turbocharged. The Atenza uses SH-VPTS engine with a displacement of 2191cc. This engine was first used in CX-5s. In the Atenza, it produces 173hp and 420Nm of torque which gives the Atenza an edge over other sedans of the same class.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: A Turbo Spec Toyota Harrier! With the new generation of the Harrier, new technologies have been introduced that make the car more convenient than ever before. This unit has a wide premium range of equipments from a premium JBL sound system, Auto Brake Hold, Camera View, auto dimming light, automatic start stop system, traction control, and tail gate height adjustment among other equipments. It is a premium unit which is also a great deal of a purchase!

name: Audi Q3
description: This the 2WD Spec Q3 fitted with a 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox(S-Tronic), bucket styled seats, premium sound system, Multifunctional steering wheel, rear mounted spoiler, side impact airbags, and engine immobilizer.

name: Toyota Hiace
description: This Toyota Hiace runs the 3.0L 1KD engine which is a very durable and powerful engine. A durable van that doubles as a private and a commercial car. It gets to be a serious money maker for any type of properly idealized and executable business. It has a seating capacity of 12 occupants with very spacious and comfortable seats and a free space as well one can turn it into any good usable space. It is in excellent condition!

name: Subaru Impreza
description: This is the 2014 Subaru Impreza, fitted with an AWD drive system that comfortably handles our roads. Its interior has fabric seats, an android infotainment display system, Multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, lane assist, cruise control, and Anti-collision brake assist.

name: Toyota Hilux
description: Toyota Hilux Single Cab 2.4L diesel engine is fitted with a 5 speed manual transmission gearbox, 2 leather seats, and light intensity control among other specs.

name: Audi S3
description: Audi S3 twins with the popular Volkswagen Golf R. It is a hot hatch version of the A3. This is the 3rd Gen, internally coded Typ 8V, produced from 2013 to 2020. This model uses the 3rd Gen EA888 2.0L I4 turbo engine with a power rating of 300hp mated to a 6 speed S Tronic dual clutch transmission. It has a 6-speed manual transmission and Quattro All Wheel drive system as standard. A facelift was done mid-2016 with the major changes being the taillights with dynamic indicators, angular headlights than before, visually appealing front and rear bumpers plus diffuser, and of course the big trade being the 10 more horsepower added post-facelift.

name: Mitsubishi Triton
description: Mitsubishi Triton, popularly known as the L200 or the Strada has been produced since 1978. This is the 5th Gen produced from 2015. It shares its platform with the rebadged Fiat Fullback produced for the European and Middle East Markets. For the 2019 model year, it was refreshed giving it a new face from the earlier models of the 2nd gen. The bew updates include a teardrop taillight design as in the Pajero, and the fascia as well being inspired by the Eclipse Cross.

name: Smart Forfour
description: Smart Forfour has been marketed by Smart in two production generations from 2004 to 2021 with the 2nd Gen beginning in 2014. The 1st gen adopted a front-engine configuration and while sharing its platform with Mitsubishi Colt, it was majorly marketed in Europe. The 2nd gen took a different turn basing its platform on Renault Twingo, as it was jointly produced with Renault, adopting a rear-engine configuration. The forfour was internally designated as W543. They are offered in a choice of a manual transmission or double-clutch automatic. Initially, they were also offered in a Getrag automated manual transmission but was discontinued for this generation. The Brabus Xclusive Spec listed gets an increased power configuration in its Inline-3 turbocharged engine. It is important to note that Internal Combustion Engines of Forfour ended in 2019 before fully switching to EVs until 2021 when Smart# 1 Crossover took over!

name: Jeep Renegade
description: Jeep Renegade has been in production since 2014 and it came as the smallest vehicle marketed by Jeep before Avenger began production. It comes standard with front wheel drive and front engine layout. Other specs include an android infotainment display system, climate controls, and steering wheel with steering wheel controls among other specs. It adopts a generally unique stance from other sub compact SUVs.

name: Toyota Fielder
description: This Toyota Fielder Hybrid runs a 1.5L petrol engine with a hybrid setup, an automatic transmission gearbox, leather seats, climate controls, and a reverse camera.

name: Mercedes Benz CLA 250
description: Mercedes Benz CLA falls under the class of luxury compact executive cars that have been in production since 2013. This is the 1st gen produced as a 4-door sedan based on the W176 A-Class and W246 B-Class' platform with the latter being marketed as a four-door coupè. A station wagon was later produced in 2015 and marketed as the shooting brake because of its body style. The CLA 250 comes with the Inline-4 turbo M270 engine with a power rating of 208hp.

name: Nissan Note
description: This is the Nissan Note E-Power in Nismo spec. Combining the beauty and the perfomance of a Nismo with consumption efficiency of an e-Power, this is one of the best hatches by Nissan! The Note e-Power was introduced later in 2016 bringing to life the hybrid series in the Nissan Note line. It consists of a 1.2L three-cylinder gasoline engine coded HR12DE and an electric traction motor coded EM57, similar to what Nissan Leaf's motor has. The motor has a 1.5 kWh rating. The whole power system works by charging the battery while the motor generates the car's traction. The motor outputs 110hp and 240Nm of torque which typically gets to be the highest power rating of the car as one of the power sources between the engine and the motor gets to power the car one at a time.

name: Toyota Wish
description: Toyota Wish adopts a high design production giving its consumers excellent satisfaction having in mind that it accomodates between 5 and 7 individuals whose travel distances vary from short to long trips. The fabric seats are well accomodating with ergonomic seats that are adjustable as the third row seats can be folded for additional boot space.

name: Mercedes Benz E250
description: Mercedes has always been the classy top of class kid that has been everyone's favorite. It has never stopped holding its position and has truly lived up to its legacy. This unit is equipped with a 7-Speed automatic transmission gearbox, popularly 7G-Tronic, well-maintained leather seats, and a 1.8L Turbo petrol engine.

name: Ford Ranger
description: This is the facelifted version of the 1st gen Ford Ranger with the new platform, the facelift came in 2015 with redesigns adopting Ford's kinetic design, the major one being a three-bar grille. Ford Ranger made a debut in 1982 in North America with the first market being intended only for the North American market. Ford later considered the rest of the World with the 1st gen of Ford intended for the World Market being first produced in 1998. In 2011, the body size was increased to a midsize pickup truck from a compact truck before. The unit listed is the First Gen of Ford Ranger T6, P375. It underwent an LCI in 2015 with the interior undergoing major changes. This is Raptor kitted with the True Raptor having the Ford logo in Bold Letters, a wider body, and a more aggresive face as seen in the body kit. Raptor, the true Ford version, was meant for markets outside the US that never received the F150 models.

name: Range Rover Sport
description: Range Rover Sport is the ultimate SUV with top of class equipments that improves Range Rover's preference to any other SUV of its class. It has an improved suspension system that improves comfort and stability at high speeds and when engaging corners, an All Wheel Drive system with the drivetrain including terrain response management system and multiple offroad modes, and an eight speed automatic transmission gearbox. The infotainment system was upgraded with a 10-inch Touchscreen for convenience of car specs access with safety features including automatic emergency braking system, lane keep assist, and a blind spot warning sytem.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: The Toyota Harrier is specced with an automatic transmission gearbox, powered seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, rear mounted spoiler, front & side mounted curtain airbags, and electric tailgate.

name: Peugeot 308
description: The 308 GT-Line is where the sports element of Peugeot comes in. It is powered by a 1200cc turbocharged engine that's quite powerful doing over 230Nm of Torque. It has half leather seats, steering wheel controls, paddle shifters, climate controls, android infotainment display screen, and side mirror indicators. It also has a premium Denon sound system. It is quite spacious and very comfortable.

name: Honda Fit
description: One of the most durable hatches in the market, Honda Fit. The Hybrid system in Honda consists of a petrol powered engine and a lithium-ion battery pack that is charged by a generator powered by the engine that in turn powers the drive motor when the engine is not running. This is a very efficient fuel saving and power generation mechanism that makes Honda Fit Hybrid a very reliable model.

name: Toyota Hiace
description: The Toyota Hiace powered by the famous powerful 1KD engine with 3000cc engine displacement producing 188hp and 300Nm of torque has a carrying capacity of 14 seats. It has been very well maintained. Get to purchase this for your commercial or private adventures.

name: Audi Q5
description: The Typ 8R S-Line Audi Q5! It is equipped with Quattro All wheel drive system, S-Line sports seats, Multifunctional steering wheel, daytime running LED lights, Premium surround sound system, digital instrument cluster, adaptive cruise control, and Blindspot monitoring assist.

name: Mercedes Benz GLC 250
description: A GLC with an Air Suspension system? Just the best deal we have! Its other specs include a 9 speed automatic transmission gearbox, powered Nappa seats, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, Premium surround sound system, daytime running LED lights, downhill speed regulation system, active parking assist system, ambient lighting, smartphone integration, and Anti theft alarm.

name: Mazda CX8
description: The CX8. It is Mazda's flagship car in Japan. It is also sold in Oceania, SouthEast Asia, and China. It was unveiled in September 2017 becoming the only three-row SUV offered by Mazda after they discontinued Mazda Premacy and Biante. It was initially offered with a 2.2 L Skyactiv-D diesel engine but later in 2018, a choice of two I4 petrol engines was added: a 2.5L Skyactiv-G (PY-VPS) from the CX-5 and a turbocharged version of the same engine from the CX-9. It is definitely a better bargain for any three-row SUV.

name: Peugeot 208
description: The 208 is specced with a 1.2L petrol engine, comfy fabric seats, and is a generally easy car generous on fuel and maintenance.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: With the Subaru Forester XT, you get the best of performance both on road and offroad. The XMODE feature, S#(Sport Sharp), S(Sport), and I(Intelligent) modes all work to ensure you have a seamless and enjoyable car experience.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI
description: Volkswagen Golf MK7 falls under the Compact executive hatchback segment. The 7 in the name 'Mk7' denotes the 7th generation that this model is produced under. It was produced under the MQB platform that it shares with 3rd Gen Audi A3 and Skoda Octavia. This is a perfect executive car tha consumes like a 1.0L Toyota car. Performance and consumption are at its peak with prices highly favourable for such a fast executive car.

name: BMW 523i
description: The BMW 523i, still in perfect condition, is specced with Powered seats, Multifunctional steering wheel, heated front seats, premium surround sound system, cruise control, and traction control.

name: Toyota Fortuner
description: This is the 2nd gen Toyota Fortuner since its first production in 2004. 2nd Gen production began in 2015 mid with new introductions being made as with the part time 4 by 4 system that improved on the cars fuel economy. The 2.8L diesel engine was also improved with a common direct injection in its fuel system and a direct nozzle turbocharging. This unit has 7 tan leather seats with the third row being foldable for extra cargo space. It also has excellent clearance for offroad driving. This is a rugged enough unit that will sustain all offroading adventures!

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: This is the Mercedes Benz C200 AVANTGARDE which is the top trim Mercedes Benz marketed the C200 with. It was offered with Liverpool fabric/leatherette seats and optional leather. It used a different sport grille that had three wide matt-finish horizontal bars and a central Mercedes emblem that appeared boldy at the middle. An optional AMG Bodykit was also available. Upgraded sports suspension and brake piston callipers. The engine features a 1.8L turbocharged M271 CGI Inline-four engine with power rating of 270Nm of torque.

name: Suzuki Escudo
description: Suzuki Escudo is the name Suzuki Vitara is marketed under in Japan and a number of other markets. It has been produced as an SUV since 1988 in different body capacities from a mini SUV to a subcompact crossover SUV. It has been produced in configurations of front-engine, rear-wheel drive between 1988-2017, front-engine, front-wheel drive from 2015 and a four-wheel drive configuration available as an option since 1988. This is the 4th gen that was produced from 2015 adopting a lightweight unibody platform that it shares with the S×4 S-Cross. It now gets a transverse all-wheel drive layout being the AllGrip variant meaning it intelligently drives all the 4 wheels. It still scores to be a good offroad companion!

name: BMW 320i
description: This is a manual spec BMW 320. It was produced as a 5 door sedan 320i series from the year 2004 internally coded as E90. It succeeded the E46 that was produced until 2006 for 9 years and later was succeeded by F30 and F31 series as from 2012 although the 5th Gen 3 series ended production in 2013. This unit features leather seats, Dual zone climate controls, BMW iDrive infotainment system, multifunctional steering wheel, push-start ignition, and of the highlights a 6-speed manual transmission gearbox.

name: Volkswagen Touareg
description: This is the 2nd gen of the Touareg that made a debut in 2010 adopting some new technologies such as the Dynamic Light assist that continually adjusts its pattern and beam intensity to protect other drivers from the high beam illumination while intensely illuminating its surrounding: Something Prado should copy. It offroad capabilities are also some of its highlights as the 4Motion All Wheel drive setup gives it excellent capability to manoeuvre offroad terrains. This is also coupled by sufficient clearance.

name: Jaguar F PACE
description: Jaguar holds automotive pride with its rich history spanning many years since production. Its collaborations with Landrover and the beautiful time pieces this collaboration has led into keeps it at the top of its leagur. The F-Pace, listed, is fitted with Powered leather seats, heated front & rear seats, terrain response management system, adaptive cruise control, panoramic sunroof, multizone climate controls, Jaguar premium surround sound system, and collision avoidance system.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The CX-5 is specced with daytime running lights, Multifunctional tilt & telescopic steering wheel, Premium surround sound system, side impact airbags, Traction control system, and Adaptive frontlight system.

name: Toyota Sienta
description: The Toyota Sienta is a premium minivan produced now in three generations from 2003 with the 3rd beginning in 2033. This is the 2nd gen that began in 2015 adopting a new design like that of trekking shoe from ita original box design. It is specced with a 1.5L NA Petrol engine, climate controls, and a 5 seating capacity among other specs.

name: Range Rover Vogue
description:
The Range Rover Vogue SE!
With the developments done on the L405, new series of the Range Rover from 2012, sales have improved as a good number of luxury lovers have inclined to this generation. Upgrades include a new terrain response system called Terrain Response 2. It has 5 engine options but with this, we have a 3.0L V6 Turbocharged diesel engine doing 600Nm of torque. Landrover created a fancy gear Selector that is rotary in nature which some tend to confuse with the volume knob but doesn't happen because it locks when the car has gained momentum. Definitely every money man's choice!

name: BMW X6
description: Production of the 2nd Gen BMW X6 began in 2014 with sales being done same year towards the end. It came with new improvements including a new 8 speed automatic transmission gearbox and a larger luggage compartment. The X6 became the first BMW to use Dynamic Performance Control system which works together with XDrive All Wheel Drive. Dynamic Performance Control is a drivetrain and chassis control system that work to regulate traction and correct over and understeer by actively spreading out drive forces across the rear axle. Torque vectoring happens laterally between the front and rear wheels and also from side to side at the rear which improves agility and stability. It runs a 3.0 N55 Straight 6 turbocharged petrol engine.

name: Porsche Cayenne
description: The Cayennes from the 1st generation show the durability their builds had. Durable long lasting engines, body builds, interior parts, and reliable systems in general are the hallmark of what Porsche represents. Porsche will always make the best there is in the market!

name: Nissan Sunny
description: This Nissan Sunny Super Saloon is a decent sedan from the late 90s that still runs perfectly well and is still in a good condition. It has fabric seats, functional climate controls, and a 4-spoke steering wheel as some of its specs.

name: Audi Q5
description: As the production of the 1st gen Audi Q5, Typ 8R, ended as the year 2016 elapsed, the 2nd Gen, Typ 80A, made its debut. It comes as a total redesign from the previous Typ 8R Q5 that began production in 2009. It features a range of new technologies that makes it a favourite of many Audi Consumers. A digital instrument cluster, redesigned steering wheel, dashboard, and center console with the design being more minimalistic than the previous model. Exterior designs became more sharper lowering drag coefficient. Both front and rear lights were also redesigned giving the car a much better admired fascia. It also was uprated just with the EA888 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine to 252hp and 370Nm of torque from the previous 222hp and 350Nm of torque.

name: Mercedes Benz GLC 250
description: Mercedes GLC 250 replaced the GLK Class in 2015 for 2016 model years. It is a premium Compact SUV equivalent to the C Class sedan. It features a 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine, a multifunctional steering wheel, multi zone climate control, heated seats with memory function, ambient lighting, and active parking assist system among other specs.

name: Audi A3
description: The highlight of this A3 is in its virtual instrument cluster which is a new technology and puts together the car's display systems by putting a number of controls in the cluster that one can switch to and from. Other specs include a 1.4L Turbocharged Petrol Engine driving the front wheels, Audi MMI infotainment system, Multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, and rear mounted spoiler.

name: Nissan NV 250
description: The Nissan NV250, slightly smaller than the NV350, its larger counterpart, utilizes its body space in a commercially appropriate way. One can convert it to a cargo car or one to carry passengers as in a "Matatu". It has a 1.6L petrol engine with power rating of 152Nm of torque mated to an automatic transmission gearbox. It has already been pre-installed with 8 seats, two for the front occupants, and 6 for the rear passengers.

name: Porsche Cayenne
description: The Cayenne, diesel variant, is specced with heated steering wheel, multiple way electrically adjustable front seats, BOSE premium surround sound system, and dual front & side mounted curtain airbags.

name: Toyota Voxy
description: Toyota Voxy is a Minivan loved for its comfort and convenience. It has two rear sliding doors opening up a 7 seats occupancy with both the third and 2nd row seats being foldable. Comfort is what sells more in this minivan. The seats have fabric seats well angled for maximum sitting comfort, and the space between the floor and the car's roof allows it to accomodate all heights of individuals.

name: Nissan Juke
description: Nissan Juke is arguably one of those highly aerodynamically designed cars. With the hatch or coupe design like at the back, air flows in an airplane-wing like orientation and adding to a spoiler evens helps more with drag effect from air flow. Arguably, that is one of the reason why the Juke-R with the GTR 3.8L V6 engine was produced in just the same design as the famous Juke.

name: Volvo V40
description: Volvo V40 at launch was produced with two petrol engine options one being the 1.6L EcoBoost I4 with 150hp and 180hp power ratings, and the 2.5L B525 I5 doing 254hp. This unit uses the 1.6L I4 with 180hp power rating. Has leather covered seats, dual zone climate controls, a multifunctional steering wheel, polished metal trimming, and adpative cruise control consists its specs.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: This C200 is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, aftermarket android infotainment display system, four-spoke steering wheel, and a mechanical footbrake.

name: Volvo S60
description: The T5, by Volvo, is powered by a 2.0L B420T turbocharged inline-4 petrol engine with power rating of 241hp. The amount of investment Volvo does to make their consumers comfortable is amazing: comfy bucket-styled seats with heating function and 3-position memory seats with high quality leather material, top of class premium surround sound system, and quite an accomodating interior.

name: Lexus RX300
description: If you loved Toyota Harrier and the Venza of earlier production years up to late 2012, and would have liked to have a luxurious counterpart of the same manufacturer, then the Lexus RX300 is for you. Produced by Lexus which is the Luxury division of Toyota, you get to enjoy premium features and associate oneself with a high class car.

name: Mercedes Benz E200
description: Experience the luxuries of the E200. Wide display screen which displays the instrument cluster and the infotainment system and the Co-driver's seat controls from the driver's side is among the highlights of the E-Class experienced in the S-Class. You also get other premium features like powered multi-way adjustable seats, three-position memory seats for the front occupants, dual zone climate controls, leather bucket-styled front seats, and voice commands among other specs make up these marque.

name: Subaru XV
description: The XV AWD is specced with symmetrical all wheel drive system, leather seats, electric parking brake, Multifunctional steering wheel, auto headlights, Anti-collision brake assist, and alloy rims.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: One would say a Harrier is just a Harrier, well, the new market of this car has brought us premium looks to the Toyota Harrier we were not used to. With new technologies and new body designs especially with the colors, Harriers have never been this attractive. This unit is specced with an automatic transmission gearbox, powered seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, rear mounted spoiler, automatic brake hold, auto start-stop system, front & side mounted curtain airbags, and electric tailgate.

name: BMW 118i
description: BMW 118i, F20, was produced from 2011 to 2019. It is powered by a 1.5L B38 inline 3 turbocharged engine. It drives only the rear wheels which is unique to the F20 and the F21 series as other models mostly drive front wheels. It has 5 alcantara seats, dual zone climate controls BMW'S iDrive infotainment system which is quite advanced and very detailed in the number of car controls it holds. Other specs include the multifunctional steering wheel and nice BMW alloy rims.

name: Volvo XC60
description: Volvo's torque house, the XC60, D4, which has a D4204T15 turbocharged diesel engine producing 400Nm of Torque. The petrol variant has 350Nm of torque. It is specced with beige leather seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, a polished metal trimming, and powered seats with memory function.

name: Toyota Aqua
description: Aqua is a very practical sub compact car that has a 1500cc naturally aspirated engine and a hybrid setup that saves a lot when it comes to fuel economy This unit is specced with two tone fabric seats, climate controls, and cup holders.

name: Mercedes Benz GLE 350d
description: A physical stunner! Excellent piece of engineering! The GLE 350D is equipped with Powered Nappa seats, active parking assist system, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, Mercedes Comand Infotainment system, Mercedes speedtronic cruise control, Premium surround sound system, downhill speed regulation, Sunroof, and Ambient lighting.

name: Toyota Axio
description: The Toyota Axio Hybrid runs a 1.5L petrol engine with a hybrid setup, an automatic transmission gearbox, fabric seats, climate controls, and a reverse camera.

name: Subaru Impreza
description: The Subaru Impreza fitted with a 2WD drive system that comfortably handles our roads. Its interior has leather seats, an android infotainment display system, Multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, lane assist cruise control, and Anti-collision brake assist.

name: Honda Odyssey
description: Honda Odyssey is a minivan that has been in production since 1994. This is the 4th Gen produced since 2008 with its engine and transmission remaining the same as the 3rd gen Odyssey. It runs a 2.4L engine mated to a 5-Speed automatic transmission. It is quite a reliable minivan spacious enough to handle 7 individuals with the 3rd row being foldable.

name: Mercedes Benz E200
description: Stepping into an E Class feels like an immersion into a classical theatre of luxury and elegance. The wide display screen which displays the instrument cluster and the infotainment system and the Co-driver's seat controls from the driver's side is among the highlights of the E-Class experienced in the S-Class. You also get other premium features like powered multi-way adjustable seats, three-position memory seats for the front occupants, dual zone climate controls, leather bucket-styled front seats, and voice commands among others.

name: Lexus RX450H
description: Lexus RX450h is specced with a 3.5L petrol V6 engine with a complimentary hybrid setup, automatic transmission, powered seats with memory function, heated steering wheel, daytime running LED lights, Mark Levinson Premium surround system, tilt & telescopic multifunctional steering wheel, rear mounted spoiler, head up display, 360° view camera, and electric tailgate.

name: Volkswagen Golf GTI
description: How admirable the GTI is! Its original GTI rims, plaid seats, and the stature the GTI presents holds it at near top of the list of high performance hatches by Volkswagen. 220 horses to the rear wheels, adaptive cruise control and emergency braking systems, a virtual instrument cluster, and a traction control system, has the GTI as one of the most admirable hatches!

name: Toyota Crown
description: The Royal Crown really appears a classy premium sedan made by Toyota in the line of mid-size luxury sedans. It has a very bold outlook with the center console bulging out with a large display screen and a number of feature selection buttons and touch-screen access. The seats are largely accomodating with Multiple-way adjustable electric controls. It runs a 2.5L 4GR-FSE V6 petrol engine mated to a 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox and driving the 4 wheels on demand.

name: Range Rover Vogue
description: Let's see what this 4th generation Rover Vogue has to offer. L405 is what it was internally coded and it lasted from 2012 to 2021 where from the beginning, a new unitary monocoque body shell was adopted which resulted in a lighter design car because of the use of aluminium in the car's structure. Upgrades include a new terrain response system called Terrain Response 2. It has 5 engine options but with this, we have a 3.0L V6 Turbocharged diesel engine doing 600Nm of torque. Landrover created a fancy gear Selector that is rotary in nature which some tend to confuse with the volume knob but doesn't happen because it locks when the car has gained momentum. The unit has black leather seats with a sunroof as some of its specs.

name: Volkswagen Arteon
description: Volkswagen Arteon falls under large family car category and is available in five-door liftback or estate body styles. This is the liftback body style. Arteon is based on the MQB platform that was first used in Golf MK7 back in 2012. It directly succeeds the CC and is heavily based on a concept Volkswagen Arteon revealed in 2015. It came in with new design aspects from the body to the interior and gets very appealing. It runs a 2.0L TSI Petrol engine with power rating of 276hp. With its design inspirations, it is able to do a 0-100kph in 5.6s. It has a sunroof, leather seats, and a multifunctional steering wheel among other specs.

name: Nissan DAYZ
description: Nissan DAYZ is an excellent urban cruiser that's produced solely by Nissan to help you preserve your finances both on fuel and maintenance. It is also very spacious and classy with the bright interior giving it a touch of excellent taste and generally a worthy competition to its competitors such as the Alto.

name: Mazda Atenza
description: The Atenza has an engaging drive with its agile driving and linear steering style. The Skyactiv tech petrol engine with a capacity of 2000cc impressively pushing torque figures of 213Nm. Quite a classy sedan!

name: Toyota Auris
description: Toyota Auris drives as the Volkswagen Golf does which actually Toyota target that it competes with. The Golf and the Ford Focus in the medium cars segment are its main competitors despite the performance these two cars display. It carries some class with a lot of capability for serious racing as with the variant running the 1.2L turbocharged 8NR-FTS engine. It is the engine this car runs and is produced in the line of NR inline-four engines. It is also well spaced and quite comfortable.

name: Toyota Axio
description: The unit listed is a hybrid spec Toyota Axio which being a highly fuel efficient car without the hybrid system now becomes a highly efficient car easy on the pockets. This is an excellent car in A1 state ready to explore the roads.

name: Nissan Lafesta
description: Nissan Lafesta began production in 2004 sharing its platform with Renault Megane. It succeeded Nissan Liberty giving competition to Toyota Isis, Honda Stream, Toyota Wish, Subaru Exiga, and Mazda Premacy. The 2nd gen Lafesta commenced production in 2011, coded B35. It was supplied to Nissan by Mazda based on the 3rd gen Mazda Premacy. It was produced all the way to March 2018 when the Premacy was discontinued.

name: KIA Sportage
description: KIA Sportage began production in 1993 before the 2nd gen began in 2004 after a 2-year break. In the 2nd gen, Sportage used car-based platform instead of the body-on-frame chassis used in the 1st Gen. The car-based platform had it produced alongside Hyundai Tucson as a crossover SUV. Its powertrains were from a choice of two petrol engines and one diesel engine. This unit uses the 2.0 L D CRDI I4 engine with power rating of 140hp. Its drivetrain has a 4WD system making it very competitive as a SUV.

name: Nissan Fuga
description: The Nissan Fuga 250Gt is a premium sedan by Nissan with top equipments that make the car classy and highly sought after. Getting into the dash gives one a precious feel from its super comfy leather seats with lower limb support for the front passenger, climate controls with all individuals able to regulate their own cabins, a classy wooden finish to the interior, and a powerful engine to comfortably pull the car through.

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: The XTRAIL Hybrid version is equipped with a complimentary hybrid setup, automatic transmission, daytime running lights, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, and traction control.

name: Toyota Vitz
description: This is a 1.0L NA petrol version which is the smaller brother to the bigger 1.3L NA engine. It has leather seats, climate controls, android infotainment display screen, and a central dash.

name: Subaru WRX S4
description: WRX was initially based on Impreza that was produced for World Rally Championship in 1992. STI means Subaru Technica International while the WRX means World Rally eXperimental. You probably have seen the older models bearing the name Impreza STI while the newer models just have the name WRX S4. In 2015, models in the WRX line were separated from Impreza and hence the name Subaru WRX S4.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The Mercedes Benz W205 with a highlight of Cranberry Red Interior, is equipped with a 7 speed automatic transmission gearbox, powered seats, daytime running LED lights, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, side mirror indicators, adaptive cruise control with lane keep assist, blindspot monitoring & emergency braking system, premium surround sound system, and traction control.

name: Ford Ranger
description: Ford Ranger is a torque star that excels in cargo carriage or long distance travels. Its 2.2L turbo diesel engine has been rated at 375Nm of torque which gives excellent power to haul cargo of large capacities. It is meant for the tough roads and tough journeys and gets to be very affordable as well.

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: The Nissan XTRAIL, Hybrid, is equipped with a complimentary hybrid setup, automatic transmission, daytime running lights, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, and traction control.

name: Toyota Hiace
description: A very spacious multiple purpose Van. It has been used for Tourist Services and hence the well maintained state with an occupancy of 9 passengers. The rear seats are made of fabric material with the front seats encompassing leather and fabric materials. It runs a 2.7L 2TR-FE petrol engine driving 2 wheels.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: Toyota Harrier Premium has some premium specs added to it including a Premiums sound system, Xenon Projector Lamps, cruise control, and memory height adjustment. Other specs include a multifunctional steering wheel, powered seats, and a Pre-collision warning safety system among other specs.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The C200 has highly attractive looks to it already classy stature. It is specced with a sunroof, heated leather seats that are powered, a multifunctional steering wheel, analogue cabin clock, and a panoramic sunroof among other specs.

name: Mercedes Benz GLE
description: The GLE 350D is equipped with Powered Nappa seats, active parking assist system, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, Mercedes Comand Infotainment system, Mercedes speedtronic cruise control, Premium surround sound system, downhill speed regulation, Sunroof, and Ambient lighting.

name: Subaru Impreza
description: Impreza GP3 is an excellent sedan to utilize with that it can be used for family purposes and chilled motorsports activities. It runs a 1.6L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine which comfortably handles its payload. On the interior, it is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, android infotainment display system, Multifunctional steering wheel, and a spoiler.

name: Range Rover Vogue
description: The Range Rover Vogue 3.0L SE is equipped with a Terrain Response management system, electric locking differentials, perforated seats, heated steering wheel, multiple way electrically adjustable front seats, daytime running LED Lights, and a Meridian premium surround sound system.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado VX
description: The VX is one of the top trims available in the Landcruiser Series. It runs the famous 3.0L 1KD diesel engine making it a very competitive SUV of its class. It has a 7 seats occupancy capacity and a sunroof as some of its premium specs. Adjustable ride height controls, Multi-terrain system control, CRAWL Mode, Sports Mode, and differentials lock are its major features.

name: Mitsubishi Outlander
description: The Outlander is an excellent SUV that delivers the best of what Mitsubishi intended to give its consumers ranging from economy to occupancy.
