It features a 7 seats occupancy that has foldable third row seats that extends the boot space when the third row is not occupied. It drives all the 4 wheels which gives it an edge over any offroad terrains. It also has an eco mode that optimises fuel consumption.

name: Nissan NV100 Clipper
description: Nissan Clipper is a nameplate used by Nissan in its commercial vehicles of kei trucks body types. They are commercially efficient for both cargo carriage and passenger utilisation. It uses a 660cc petrol engine with a power rating of 63hp.

name: Volkswagen Passat CC
description: As Volkswagen calls it, the CC in Passat CC means Comfort Coupe which is a combination of its Coupe like body style and the comfort Passat offers. It features bucket-styled half-leather seats that are powered and have three-position memory seats. The seats are also heated and both the front occupants get to enjoy individual air conditioning via the dual zone climate controls. The analogue clock at the center of the dashboard gives the Passat a classy finish. Other specs include an android infotainment display system, traction control, electric parking brake Auto hold brake function steering wheel controls, paddle shifters, and an analogue cluster.

name: Nissan Note E Power
description: The Note e-Power was introduced later in 2016 bringing to life the hybrid series in the Nissan Note line. It consists of a 1.2L three-cylinder gasoline engine coded HR12DE and an electric traction motor coded EM57 similar to what Nissan Leaf's motor has. The motor has a 1.5 kWh rating. The whole power system works by charging the battery while the motor generates the car's traction. The motor outputs 110hp and 240Nm of torque which typically gets to be the highest power rating of the car as one of the power sources between the engine and the motor gets to power the car one at a time.

name: Subaru Legacy
description: The 4th Gen of Subaru Legacy adopted a new design that began development early in 1999 while production began in 2003. With the chassis being stiffened, a more aggresive and a better handling car especially with sharp corners. The Japanese market received a 500cc less capacity engine from the North American market that recived 2.5L turbocharged engines. The Japanese market received a 2.0L with power figures of 240hp and 345Nm of Torque.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: The Forester XT is equipped with heated seats for the front occupants, XMODE for offroading, roof rails, memory height adjustment, tailgate memory height adjustment, and Blindspot monitoring assist amongst other specs.

name: Mercedes Benz Viano
description: Viano CDI22 is a classic Van by Mercedes with a premium setup of two-three seats occupancy facing each other being very spacious and having the possibility of being used for meetings. It has a powerful 2.1L diesel engine that comfortably handles the cars payload. It beats the standard travel style by upgrading it to a premium style.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The CX-5 XDL has an extra range of equipments not available in the basic spec CX5. It is specced with daytime running lights, Multifunctional tilt & telescopic steering wheel, Premium surround sound system, side impact airbags, Bose premium surround sound system, Traction control system, and Adaptive frontlight system.

name: Porsche Cayenne
description: Cayenne was a major leap for Porsche as it had spent a lot of years focusing on performance and luxury sedans leaving out offroading and mid & full size luxury cars. Sharing its platform, body frame, and electronics with the Touareg and Q7, it allows VAG Group enthusiasts have a wide range of SUVs to choose from. From official activities to family and road trips, Porsche Cayenne serves all purposes excellently!

name: Landrover Discovery IV
description: This is the second generation (L319), Discovery 4, also known as LR4, which was produced from 2009 to 2016. This unit is the last of its generation. Powered by a 3.0L turbocharged SDV6 diesel engine producing 600Nm of torque. It was much upgraded in 2012 to include powerful brakes from Ranger Rover Sport, thicker anti-roll bars for better road handling and a better stability control system that handles issues with understeer as soon as it occurs. It still has fully independent air suspension and electronically locking differentials.

name: Subaru XV
description: The XV AWD is specced with symmetrical all wheel drive system, half leather seats, electric parking brake, Multifunctional steering wheel, auto headlights, Anti-collision brake assist, and alloy rims.

name: Mercedes Benz C300
description: With the latest hot sedan we have at our disposal, the C300 is here to make a statement. Its 2.0L M274 DE20 LA Petrol engine has a power tune of 242 horses from the factory. The practicality of this power is displayed by the G-Force measure in its virtual display. Definitely an exciting time to be alive to experience this C Class with 4 MATIC All Wheel Drive System. Its interior is practically satisfying. Modern systems, comfortable and pleasurable drives, and exciting features to explore makes this car the best choice in the list of affordable C-Klasse. The 4 MATIC seems to have some influence over how this feels. You should try it out!

name: Mazda CX5
description: We have the 2.0L Petrol version of the CX5 well pampered with aftermakert front and rear bumpers & side skirts giving it a unique premium look. It is specced with lane departure system, traction control system, adaptive frontlight system, and i-stop function among other specs.

name: Nissan Note
description: The Note is an excellent hatch by Nissan that gives a very good value for money with the features it offer as with the spacious interior, and a very generous maintenance cost.

name: Toyota Auris
description: The Toyota Auris is specced with a 1.5L NA Petrol engine. Among other specs are fabric seats, steering wheel controls, android infotainment system, mechanically controlled handbrake, and climate controls.

name: Jeep Grand Cherokee
description: Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited is what Jeep calls the 'step-up' trim of Grand Cherokee which succeeded what was in its level, the Laredo X. All the equipments available in the Laredo X including leather seats, powered front seats, a touch-screen infotainment system, a 9-speaker 506-watte Alpine surround-sound audio system, Bluetooth connectivity, were present in the Limited trim but additional options including heated front and rear seats & ventilated front seats, driver's memory system, and Nappa leather seats were offered. It runs the famous 3.6L V6 Pentaster petrol engine that has been known to be a bulletproof engine! The instant power from the Naturally Aspirated V6 makes this car one of the best non-problematic SUVs for all-round terrain handling.

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: The XTRAIL Hybrid version is equipped with a complimentary hybrid setup, automatic transmission, daytime running lights, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, and traction control.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: Bodykits seriously spice up the beauty of the Toyota Harrier. A new look for the front and rear bumpers which is definitely a change maker in this car and its fascia brings up a whole new other unit. Automatic transmission gearbox, powered seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, rear mounted spoiler, auto start-stop system, front & side mounted curtain airbags, auto brake hold, cruise control and electric tailgate consists of its other specs.

name: BMW 320i
description: BMW 320i GT, Gran Turismo, is a 5-door fastback in the 3 series class of BMW Series. It has a hatchback design on the rear with a retractable spoiler. It runs an N20B20 2.0L producing 181hp and 270Nm of torque. The rear spoiler comes in handy in increasing aerodynamic flow accelerating to 100Km per hour in 7.9 Seconds. It is styled with leather seats with the front seats being heated, dual zone climate controls, a multifunctional steering wheel, and BMW’s i-Drive infotainment system.

name: Range Rover Vogue
description:
A one of few Spectral Light Blue RR VOGUE AUTOBIOGRAPHY!! 
The 4th Gen, L405, of Range Rover lasted from 2012 to 2021 where from the beginning, a new unitary monocoque body shell was adopted which resulted in a lighter design car because of the use of aluminium in the car's structure. Upgrades include a new terrain response system called Terrain Response 2. It has 5 engine options but with this, we have a 4.4L V8 Twin-Turbocharged diesel engine doing 740Nm of torque. Landrover created a fancy gear Selector that is rotary in nature which some tend to confuse with the volume knob but doesn't happen because it locks when the car has gained momentum. The unit has beige leather seats with a sunroof as some of its specs

name: Subaru Outback
description: The Subaru Outback is powered by a 2.5L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine, fabric seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, android infotainment display system, dual zone climate controls, and a Symmetrical All Wheel Drive setup.

name: Nissan Note E Power
description: The Note e-Power was introduced later in 2016 bringing to life the hybrid series in the Nissan Note line. It consists of a 1.2L three-cylinder gasoline engine coded HR12DE and an electric traction motor coded EM57 similar to what Nissan Leaf's motor has. The motor has a 1.5 kWh rating. The whole power system works by charging the battery while the motor generates the car's traction. The motor outputs 110hp and 240Nm of torque which typically gets to be the highest power rating of the car as one of the power sources between the engine and the motor gets to power the car one at a time.

name: Toyota Mark X ZiO
description: Well in, the Toyota Mark X ZiO. A mid-size MPV that was produced by Toyota from 2007 to 2013, to replace the Mark II Blit Station Wagon. They share the nameplate with Mark X, which it was sold alongside, sharing a number of features. Its chassis is from the MC Platform which the E150 Auris, XA30 RAV4, and T270 Avensis were based on. Its name, ZiO, was from the fact that it had a very spacious interior and increased cargo capacity. The modifications done on this unit are absolutely great, with a 360° camera view and a premium music system, this is a great choice for an SUV.

name: Mercedes Benz GLE 350d
description: The GLE 350D is equipped with Powered Nappa seats, active parking assist system, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, Mercedes Comand Infotainment system, Mercedes speedtronic cruise control, Premium surround sound system, downhill speed regulation, Sunroof, and Ambient lighting.

name: Honda Fit
description: The Honda fit Non hybrid version is powered by a 1300cc naturally aspirated engine that produces 97 horsepower and 130Nm of torque. In its interior are fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, android infotainment display screen, and an Eco drive mode that saves on fuel by reducing the engine performance.

name: Toyota Axio
description: This Toyota Axio Hybrid runs a 1.5L petrol engine with a hybrid setup, an automatic transmission gearbox, fabric seats, climate controls, and a reverse camera.

name: Subaru Forester
description: The Forester is equipped with fabric seats, climate controls, and a tilt and telescopic steering  wheel amongst other specs.

name: Toyota Hiace
description: This is the 9L Toyota Hiace that is an excellent commercial passenger car or for private use. It has a 12 seats occupancy capacity that is adjusted based on the consumers needs. It uses the 2.7L 2TR-FE petrol engine mated to an automatic transmission gearbox.

name: Audi A5
description:
UNDERGOING CUSTOMS CLEARANCE AT THE PORT OF MOMBASA!

Specs include a Quattro All wheel drive, powered leather seats with memory function, heated seats, Multifunctional steering wheel, virtual instrument cluster, engine immobilizer, all round parking sensors, hill hold assist, radar guided adaptive cruise control, and Bluetooth connectivity.

name: Toyota Auris
description: The Toyota Auris features a 1.5L NA Petrol engine with a Smart Stop Feature as its highlight equipment. Among other specs are fabric seats, steering wheel controls, android infotainment system, mechanically controlled handbrake, and climate controls.

name: Subaru Outback
description: This is the latest model of the Outback produced by Subaru in its 6th Generation beginning in the year 2020. Major changes are visible on its design that make it a very admirable SUV with insane offroading capabilities one being its ground clearance that begins at 220mm. Its powerful 2.5L NA FB25D Boxer engines chucks 245Nm of torque through an 8 speed lineartronic gearbox. Get to experience what the new generation of the Outback brings at an impressively good price!

name: Peugeot 208
description: A supermini car that came to replace Peugeot 207 in 2012 when the 208 began production. It was constructed under the PSA PF1 platform which is a subcompact platform for cars by Peugeot in the subcompact body class. It came with an increased space at the boot and in its legroom. It gets specially designed bucket seats that make the car appear sporty complimented by the moonroof that extends a bit to the back.

name: Hyundai HD65
description: Hyundai HD Series falls under the category of light to medium duty trucks. It does a number of tasks including stowage. Working on its engine is quite easy now with the new cab tilting tech of up to 50°. It is termed as one of the most ergonomic cabs because of its driver convenience features, one being the curved control panel layout. It runs a 3.6L Naturally Aspirated Diesel engine capable of handling the 3.2T load capacity.

name: Honda CR Z
description: The CR-Z is a sport compact car with a hybrid setup. It is marketed by Honda as a sport hybrid coupe as it utilizes a hybrid gasoline-electric powertrain and on its design adopting the elements of a tradional sports car. Its sport element has had it develop a lot of liking amongst many individuals. It resembles the CR-X and scores as one of the best least polluting hybrid car rated as an Advanced Technology Partial Zero Emissions Vehicle (AT-PZEV). It has a four-occupancy capacity with some markets like the North America having only 2 in the front. It served the market well till mid 2016 where it was discontinued for the production of Honda Accord Hybrid and Clarity.

name: BMW 320i
description: This is a 5-door sedan of the E90 series from the year 2004. It succeeded the E46 that was produced until 2006 for 9 years and later was succeeded by F30 and F31 series as from 2012 although the 5th Gen 3 series ended production in 2013. This unit features fabric seats, Dual zone climate controls, BMW iDrive infotainment system, multifunctional steering wheel, push-start ignition, and a speedo clock of up to 260Km/h.

name: BMW 520i
description: This is the 6th gen of BMW 5 Series coded the F10. They were produced since 2010. The 5 series shares its platform with the F01 Gen of the 7 Series that is in the category of full-size sedan and also with the F12 6 Series executive-sized grand tourers. This generation came with major improvements that included dual Clucth transmission as used with the M5, 8 speed automatic transmission gearbox, and the turbocharged V8 engine as with the S63 engine among other specs. This unit is specced with 5 leather seats, parking sensors, Autohold brake function, auto start stop feature, and a 2.0L N20B20 inline-four turbocharged engine that was comparatively better than the N52/N53 NA six cylinder engines.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The C200 is a premium saloon that is becoming a favorite of a lot consumers. It is specced with leather seats that are powered and heated, a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, and 3-position memory seats make up some of this car's specs Beautifully designed exterior curves, analogue clock at the dash center, and an array of equipments make the C200 a car to behold!

name: Toyota Fielder Hybrid
description: Hybrid Synergy Drive, a new tech adopted by Toyota to supplement the power from its Internal Combustion Engine and to cut down on fuel costs especially in urban driving as it includes increased starts and stops because of road traffic. This is extreme convenience from what the car actually offers in its interior. This is just the right car for reliable and highly convenient drives!

name: Daihatsu Begu
description: Also called Toyota Rush, Daihatsu Bego is a very good Mini SUV. A good multi purpose SUV that serves a lot of tasks. It is available in a 1.3L or 1.5L with the 1.5L being available with a 2WD or 4WD drivetrain system. It has fabric seats and a rear spare tyre with side steps as some of its specs.

name: Volvo XC60
description: The 2nd gen of the XC60 was unveiled in 2017 at the Geneva Motor Show. Based on the same Scalable Product Architecture platform as the S90, V90, and the XC90, this is one of the great four-cylinder engines by Volvo with impressive power tunes. The XC60 D4 runs on the D4204T14 engine with two turbochargers having a torque rating of 400Nm. Apart from its engine, Volvo's has an excellent exterior and interior design with the highlight being its Thor Hammer lights with Full LED system.

name: Volkswagen Tiguan
description: Volkswagen Tiguan is a perfect Crossover that sits between the Touareg and T-Roc. It offers a very good balance between comfort, performance, and luxury. This unit comes fitted with fabric seats, Multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, android infotainment display system, parking sensors, rear retractable mini-tables for the rear occupants, electric handbrake, and side mirror indicators.

name: Renault Megane
description: Renault Megane is a small family car produced by Renault since 1996. It is offered in three or five-door hatchback, saloon. coupè, convertible, and estate bodystyles. This is the 4th gen Megane offered in a 5-door hatchback produced since 2016. Its design is similar to that seen in Clio IV. It uses Renault's MR16DDT turbocharged and intercooled engine with twin variable valve timing control that is on intake and exhaust valves. It has 5 driving modes one can choose from that also changes the car's setup. The GT being the high performance version based on the hatchback version of Megane has 4Control, four-wheel steering system, and dual clutch automatic transmission gearbox as standard. It is a whole new level of thrill!

name: Lexus LS460
description: Lexus LS is a full-size luxury sedan that serves as the flagship model of Lexus. The first 4 generations were offered with V8 engines and a rear wheel drive setup and as the 5th gen came in 2017, an all-wheel drive setup, hybrid, and long-wheelbase variants were offered. The LS460, listed above, comes with a 4.6L 1UR-FSE engine with a power rating of 386hp. It has an 8 speed automatic transmission gearbox with an impressive acceleration of 5.7 seconds.

name: Landrover Discovery V
description: The Discovery V HSE has to be a very interesting car that took a very different turn in terms of its design that is different from the LR4. The rear of Disco V is very unique to that of Discovery IV. It is also very light to the Disco IV by about 480Kg all attributed to a new material structure. It is also highly specced with Terrain response management system, Electric locking differentials, perforated leather seats, multiple way Electrically Adjustable seats, and memory seats package among other specs.

name: Daihatsu Mira
description: Daihatsu Mira was produced for commercial purposes as a city vehicle. Its usage with Uber and Bolt cases are the perfect examples of its commercial use. The engine also is an excellent use case, with a 660cc displacement capacity, fuel consumption levels are at its best.

name: BMW 116i
description: BMW 116i, F20, was produced from 2011 to 2019. It is powered by a 1.6L inline 4 turbocharged engine. It drives only the rear wheels which is unique to the F20 and the F21 series as other models mostly drive front wheels. It has 5 fabric seats, climate controls, and BMW'S iDrive infotainment system which is quite advanced and very detailed in the number of car controls it holds. Other specs include the multifunctional steering wheel and nice BMW alloy rims.

name: Audi Q5
description: The Typ 8R Audi Q5! It is equipped with Quattro All wheel drive system, S-Line sports seats, Multifunctional steering wheel, daytime running LED lights, Premium surround sound system, digital instrument cluster, adaptive cruise control, and Blindspot monitoring assist.

name: Volkswagen Passat
description: This is the B7 gen of Volkswagen passat that came with some improvements majorly consisting of the body panels, grille, and headlights. The face of the Passat keeps on getting better with the advancements in generations. This unit is specced with semi leather seats, an analogue cabin clock, interior polished metal trimming, and a Multifunctional steering wheel among other specs.

name: Toyota Hilux Surf
description: The Hilux Surf is a very aggressive SUV with amenities that serve different purposes from offroading to official duties. It has a rugged drivetrain combined with a powerful 2.7L 3RZ-FE Petrol engine with a torque rating of 207Nm. With a 5 seating occupancy capacity, one comfortably pull a large group offroading escapade.

name: Toyota Carina
description: The Carina is definitely a one durable sedan by Toyota that has seen better years of reliability and efficiency. The 3S-FE engine has proven to be an all-round all-year engine and has a guaranteed record of constantly starting all the day whenever needed.

name: Mazda CX5
description: Quite a super good deal on this 2.0L Petrol variant of the CX-5. It is specced with lane departure system, traction control system, adaptive frontlight system, and i-stop function among other specs.

name: Subaru Outback
description: Subaru Outback has been a big preference to a lot of individuals who have always wanted the raw power and the capabilities this car bears. It carries a lot of features including Subaru's Eyesight feature that makes Adaptive cruise control possible and additionally lane keep assistance, Traction control, Symmetrical AWD which is the best in the world, highly sufficient legroom and roof height, and 920 liters of boot space expandable to over 2000 liters when the back seats are folded.

name: Range Rover Vogue
description: Precious deals at kaiandkaro.com! This Range Rover Vogue TDV8 is a special one, a 4.4L V8 turbocharged diesel engine with pure 700Nm of torque that makes this car pull away so easily. Its engine is the biggest highlight of this unit. Comfort and luxury are not a bargain, leather seats with heating functionality, spacious and classy!

name: Suzuki Swift
description: Suzuki Swift is a highly soughted after compact car by motorists for its agile handling, sporty design, fuel efficiency, a practical comfortable interior, and high safety measures including stability control feature. This comes with a choice of fabric seats, android infotainment display screen, and climate controls.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: We cannot ignore the fact that the C200 is way way classy in the compact executive class of Mercedes C Class. A 2000cc turbocharged engine doing 180 horsepower matches the comfy semi leather interior with a polished metal trimming complimented by the Mercedes Command Infotainment system that's very detailed. Very brief and detailed as the C200 shows. With the best of price deals!

name: Mercedes Benz C250
description: As the new prices come a bit pricey than what majority of consumers expect, getting the older model might just be another good alternative. This is still as good as the owner with well kept half leather seats, a sunroof, Multifunctional steering wheel, climate controls, polished metal trimming, and the poweful 2.1L I4 turbocharged diesel engine which was quite something in the C250 as it made it very competitive.

name: Ford Ranger
description: Ford Ranger made a debut in 1982 in North America with the first market being intended only for the North American market. Ford later considered the rest of the World with the 1st gen of Ford intended for the World Market being first produced in 1998. In 2011, the body size was increased to a midsize pickup truck from a compact truck before. The unit listed is the First Gen of Ford Ranger T6, P375. It underwent an LCI in 2015 with the interior undergoing major changes. This is Raptor kitted with the True Raptor having the Ford logo in Bold Letters, a wider body, and a more aggresive face as seen in the body kit. Raptor, the true Ford version, was meant for markets outside the US that never received the F150 models. Adventures in these vehicle are definitely interesting!

name: Honda Freed
description: Honda Freed, introduced in 2008, has been a very practical car with its impressive carrying capacity of 7 seats and torque of 148Nm. It has a 1500cc naturally aspirated petrol engine producing 118 horsepower. This is Facelifted version of the First generation of Honda Freed with fabric seats, cup holders, an android infotainment display screen, and climate controls.

name: Volvo V60
description: The best deal Volvo V60 we have! The T3. The V60 was first introduced into the market in 2010 with the second generation beginning in 2018. It underwent a facelift in 2014 with the newer version being more sleek and appealing. This unit comes fitted with heated seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, a premium surround sound system that's arguably one of the best, and dual exhaust tailpipes.

name: Subaru Forester
description: We have a great deal on this Non Turbo Subaru Forester specced with half leather seats, heated front seats, steering wheel controls, Subaru S-Drive feature, dual zone climate controls, fog lights, side mirror indicators, and roof rails.

name: Nissan Note
description: DIG-S, notably seen in the Nissan Note, means Direct Injection Gasoline-Supercharged. The Supercharger in this unit makes quite a difference in the power the Nissan Note makes. 147Nm of torque and 97hp compared to the NA version making 78hp and 106Nm does some magic in this Note Autech DIGS Spec!

name: Suzuki Swift
description: Suzuki Swift runs a 1.2L NA petrol engine which is quite powerful in the hatchback. It also consumes well as the engine can with no strain run all the car components and accelerate easily.

name: Subaru Impreza
description: Subaru Impreza, the third generation, was revealed in 2007 with both the Naturally Aspirated and the Turbocharged WRX versions coming into the market then. It is internally designated as GH being a five-door hatchback. This body version replaced the wagon variant in the previous generation. This new gen was slightly longer in its wheelbase as Subaru at the same time worked on regulating the weight of the chassis although they didn't succeed on it as the weight remained the same with the previous gen. Its suspension system featured a MacPherson strut setup in the front and double wishbone suspension at the rear. In the Naturally Aspirated engine series of the Impreza, this unit is equipped with a 1.5L EL15 H4 engine mated to a 5 speed manual transmission gearbox with a power rating of 109hp. The other options in that line included a 2.0L EJ20 G4, 2.5L EJ25, among other options.

name: Subaru Levorg
description: The Levorg is equipped with one of the world's best symmetrical All Wheel Drive system, Adaptive cruise control, hill descent assist, lane keep assist, and a proper 2.0L turbocharged and intercooled direct injection flat four engine.

name: Audi A5
description: The A5 has been produced under the B-Platform family of cars including the A4 and the Q5. The first generation, Typ 8T, falls under the B8 series while the 2nd Generation, Typ 8W6, falls under the B9 series. The third generation is yet to commence production where Audi seeks to replace the A4/S4 sedan with the A5/S5 fastback series. It is a very reliable and durable sedan that most Audi consumers choose to go for.

name: Volvo XC60
description: Sales of the XC60 first gen began in 2008 in Europe and has been Volvo's best selling car since 2009. Volvo was created with a tune of Landrover's offroading capabilities and Volvo's technologies. This makes it one of the best Multipurpose, in the sense of one can operate them at different terrains and for different events, and it will never let one down. The aesthetics are on point, extremely well done, safety earns is a solid 5 star rating from both official tests and consumer reports, and performance is top notch, a marvel. The unit listed is the 2nd Gen that began production in 2017. An Inscription T5 AWD Setup Volvo XC60, quite a beauty to look at. It runs a B4204T 2000cc engine doing 251 horsepowers and 350Nm of torque in an engine orientation of inline 4 plus a turbocharger.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: The Toyota Harrier has a wide range of specs including is an automatic transmission gearbox, powered seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, rear mounted spoiler, automatic brake hold, auto start-stop system, front & side mounted curtain airbags, and electric tailgate.

name: Mitsubishi Outlander
description: The Outlander delivers the best of what Mitsubishi intended to give its consumers ranging from economy to occupancy. It features a 7 seats occupancy that has foldable third row seats that extends the boot space when the third row is not occupied. It drives all the 4 wheels which gives it an edge over any offroad terrains. It also has an eco mode that optimises fuel consumption.

name: Volkswagen Passat
description: Volkswagen passat B7 gen came with some improvements majorly consisting of the body panels, grille, and headlights. The face of the Passat keeps on getting better with the advancements in generations. This unit is specced with fabric seats, an analogue cabin clock, interior polished metal trimming, and a Multifunctional steering wheel among other specs.

name: Toyota Axio
description: Here is an excellently maintained Toyota Axio specced with fabric seats, FM RADIO system, climate controls, and a reliable 1NZ-FE 1.5L engine.

name: Nissan Note
description: Nissan gets better year by year with all the classes of their production cars. The Nissan Note has been advancing with the designs getting better and better. This 2017 model gets a flat-bottomed steering wheel, Anti-collision brake assist, lane departure assist, and Traction control as some of its major specs. It is as comfy as it appears with the two-tone fabric seats.

name: Toyota Isis
description: The Toyota Isis is specced with 7 seats occupancy capacity having the 3rd row being foldable, fabric seats, side mirror indicators, steering wheel controls, and polished metal trimming.

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: A highly durable SUV that has been widely used by a lot of consumers for its versatility  and reliability. It is equipped with an automatic transmission, daytime running lights, 4WD Select, and heated seats among other specs.

name: Volkswagen Golf GTI
description: One can never tire admiring this hot hatch by VAG Group. The Wolverine-designed front lamps plus a similar design addition at the rear of this unit are an eyecatcher. Aftermakert RAYS Rims handling what a seriously uprated EA888 third gen engine pumps, bucket-styled leather seats, rear amrest that doubles as cupholders, and a virtual instrument cluster make the Volkswagen  GTI one of the best offers by the group.

name: Toyota Harrier
description:
UNDERGOING CUSTOMS CLEARANCE AT THE PORT OF MOMBASA.

Specs include an automatic transmission gearbox, powered seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, rear mounted spoiler, front & side mounted curtain airbags, and electric tailgate.

name: Nissan Note
description:
UNDERGOING CUSTOMS CLEARANCE AT THE PORT OF MOMBASA.

Specs include fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, Traction control, Anti-collision brake assist, lane keep assist, and Auto start stop.

name: Mercedes Benz GLA 45
description: GLA 45 AMG 4 MATIC gets something different from the GLA models we are accustomed to. The concept car was unveiled in 2013 at Los Angeles Auto Show. It came as a performance version of the GLA. The highlight of it is the 2.0L 4-cylinder twin-scroll turbocharged petrol engine mated to an AMG Speedshift DCT 7-Speed transmission. One can shift to manual mode control with paddle shifters. What's better than the sweet rumbles of an AMG Sports Exhaust system with an electronically controlled variable vane system that controls the exhaust note! Apart from AMG Badgings, the GLA 45 gets AMG Sports suspensions with specially tuned damper units, optimised elastokinematics & bigger Anti-roll bars, electromechanical AMG speed-sensitive sports steering, high performance braking system from AMG, 3-Stage ESP with "Sport Handling" mode, and ESP Dynamic Curve Assist. The exterior has AMG printings with its specs quite visible.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: This Toyota Harrier has been properly pampered. It has an all new leather stitching on the interior that is bright in colour making the car look all new by itself, an aftermarket music system, all terrain tyres fitted on it, and a nice paint it wears. Any 2nd gen Harrier better than this?

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The C200 is equipped with a 1.8L Supercharged M271 engine mated to 7G-Tronic Plus automatic transmission gearbox. Its comfort specs feature fabric seats, climate control, Multifunctional steering wheel, Mercedes Comand Infotainment system, and a polished-metal trimming.

name: Toyota Allion
description: This is the 1.8L variant of the Allion specced with an automatic transmission gearbox, Multifunctional steering wheel, side mirror indicators, tinted rear windows, air con climate control, powered windows, and Foglights.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: The Forester XT is equipped with heated seats for the front occupants, XMODE for offroading, roof rails, memory height adjustment, tailgate memory height adjustment, a sunroof and Blindspot monitoring assist amongst other specs.

name: Toyota Hilux
description: The Hilux is equipped with a 2.5L 2KD Turbo Diesel engine, 5 seats occupancy capacity, cruise control, and a manual transmission gearbox which is a great fit for such an offroad high load pickup among other specs.

name: Ford Ranger
description: Ford Ranger is a tough pickup made for the tough terrains and heavy cargo carriage. It has a 2.2L diesel engine with an engine option of a 3.2L engine. It has a 5 seating occupancy capacity and an enclosed cargo space.

name: Ford Ranger
description: This is a locally assembled Ranger, in its T6 platform, in which this car is built on has been in use since 2011. It accomodated all mid-size pickup trucks that were manufactured and sold by Ford. It carries the name of Ford well in what it meant to achieve as the trucks and the SUVs made in this platform are tough and handle the terrains with ease. With the 3.2L engine coupled to a 6 speed manual transmission gearbox, one gets to enjoy the fullness of Ford.

name: Mitsubishi Galant Fortis
description: In 2007, Mitsubishi launched the Galant Fortis in an aim to produce a new style sedan that has a sporty design and a well balanced mix of other features as safety and comfort. It runs a 2.0L engine giving exceptional power with the car giving an excellent stability and response on the road. Its engine is mated to a 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox that gives a very good gear balance making it a competitive car on the road.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: The aggressive version of the Forester by Subaru, the XT, equipped with heated seats for the front occupants, XMODE for offroading, roof rails, memory height adjustment, tailgate memory height adjustment, a sunroof and Blindspot monitoring assist amongst other specs.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: This C200 is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, aftermarket android infotainment display system, four-spoke steering wheel, and a mechanical footbrake.

name: Suzuki Alto
description: They Call it the perfect Urban car, Suzuki Alto is among the top cars in the top lists of highly fuel economical cars with tops of 20Kms a liter. Quite an Easy and reliable car!

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: The XTRAIL is equipped with an automatic transmission, daytime running lights, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, and traction control.

name: Porsche Cayenne
description: Cayenne was a major leap for Porsche as it had spent a lot of years focusing on performance and luxury sedans leaving out offroading and mid & full size luxury cars. Sharing its platform, body frame, and electronics with the Touareg and Q7, it allows VAG Group enthusiasts have a wide range of SUVs to choose from. From official activities to family and road trips, Porsche Cayenne serves all purposes excellently!

name: Toyota Vanguard
description: The Toyota Vanguard is equipped with Fabric seats, dual zone climate controls, cup holders, and a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters.

name: Volkswagen Tiguan
description: Volkswagen Tiguan, a preferred crossover in the class of mid-size SUVs as it is classified in Europe. They are available in three engine options from a 2.0 diesel engine, 2.0TSI Petrol, and a 1.4L petrol variant. This has the 2.0L TSI S-Line variant with power rating of 197hp. It is equipped with fabric and dual zone climate controls among other specs.

name: Subaru Forester
description: A well engineered, great powered SUV, with one of the best drivetrains in the world, the Subaru Forester. It is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, and heated front seats as some of its major specs.

name: Toyota Hilux
description: These locally assembled pickups are taking up the industry by a storm. With the most durable bodies, rugged drivetrain, and powerful engines, this is pickup every heavy activity individual with the need of an automobile should consider.

name: Toyota Fielder
description: Toyota Filder G coded NZE161 runs the 1.5L 1NZ-FE Naturally Aspirated petrol engine with a power rating of 109hp. There are other engine variants such as the 1.8L found in the S Trim. It is also specced with some fabric seats, climate controls, and an android infotainment system among other specs.

name: Subaru Impreza
description: This is the 2015 Subaru Impreza, fitted with a 2WD drive system that comfortably handles our roads. Its interior has leather seats, an android infotainment display system, Multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, lane assist, cruise control, and Anti-collision brake assist.

name: Toyota Crown
description: Toyota Crown falls under the categorily of mid-size sedans. From the extreme comfort the car's occupants receive to the comfortable driving modes, this could be rated as the S-Class of Toyota in its category. The Smooth driving in the Crown Royal Saloon is facilitated by the Driving Response and Acceleratiom Management System and jointly with the 2.5L V6 petrol engine, you get to experience a poweful drive. The smooth gearbox transmission is courtesy of the Super-Intelligent electronically controlled 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox called the Super 6 ECT.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: The Forester XT is equipped with heated seats for the front occupants, XMODE for offroading, roof rails, memory height adjustment, tailgate memory height adjustment, a sunroof and Blindspot monitoring assist amongst other specs.

name: Mazda CX3
description: Mazda CX-3 is one of the best compact crossover SUVs Mazda has ever produced. Beginning sales in 2016 in all the major markets it was sold including Canada, a lot of individuals have responded well to this entry into the market. It was produced in the age of modern technologies and designs making it a good looking car since the first generation as consumere don't have any other thought of how Mazda looked or previously performed which gives it an advantage of having a positive face in the automotive sector.

name: Mercedes Benz E43
description: The E43 is one proper AMG Model by Mercedes AMG Division. Coming into the market in 2016 before its exciting 2-year tenure before the E53 AMG came in that space, it packs a big deal of features. To begin with, the marvelous 3.0L BITURBO M276 V6 Petrol engine sumptuously delivers 396 brake horse power which is definitely not a walk in the park. Its acceleration? 4.6 good seconds of adrenaline! Unfortunately, the top Speed isn't achieved even with this spirited acceleration. You get 250Kmh for what electronics limits. As the engine thrills, the leather bucket styled seats with heating functionality deliver maximum comfort. The driver also gets to control the Co-driver's seats through controls next to the heating button. This is the most practical mid-size sedan one can ever get for good money without having to pay too much nor sacrifice comfort and luxury!

name: Mini Cooper
description: Mini Cooper Clubman marketed and sold under BMW’s Mini Marque as its manufacturer as well. It is in the class of subcompact executive car. It first came into the market in 2007 and the 2nd Gen began in 2015. This is the 2nd gen that is based on BMW’S UKL2 Platform that features more space than the 1st gen. It features a special access to the cargo space via bi-parting rear doors called barn or split doors which made it unique at the time of its entry into the market. This unit features a 2.0L diesel engine with a power rating of 330Nm of torque. The engine is mated to an 8 speed automatic transmission gearbox.

name: Landrover Defender 110
description: Land Rover Defender, P400 MHEV coded L663, is a 4-Wheel-drive off-road luxury manufactured by Jaguar Land Rover. It is a new engineering done by Land Rover on their new generation Landrovers. This new gen replaced the original generation Land Rover Defender that were produced from 1983-2016. Some highlights of its equipments include a permanent all-wheel drive, locking differentials in the centre and the rear, and a two-speed transfer case. Air suspension comes as a standard feature on this unit different from Defender 90 with which coil springs are standard. Its choice of engines come from a list of JLR Ingenium engines including the D200 having a 2.0L Diesel engine of power rating 196bhp, D240 with a 2.0l diesel engine of power rating 237bhp, P300 with a 2.0L Petrol, P400 with a 3.0L 6-cylinder turbo Petrol mild hybrid of 395bhp, and the P400e only available in the 110 with power rating of 398bhp. Its interior gets to be minimalistic with what welcomes you being a 10.0 inch infotainment system, gear lever along the center console, a few dials and the whole space for oneself. A rich space we call!

name: Volvo XC60 T5
description: The XC60 comes in a number of trims and variants that satisfy customers with different preferences. The T5 is one of them which is the petrol variant powered by a 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine with a power rating of 240hp. It is fitted with a polished metal trimming on the interior, leather seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, and cruise control among other features.

name: Lexus RX450h
description: This is the 3rd gen of Lexus RX450H produced between 2008 and 2015 before the 4th gen began production same year. It has an updated transmission that can lock up its torque converter from 2nd through 6th gears to improve fuel economy. The drag coefficient was decreased, exterior dimensions increased with cargo room getting an increment as well. Smart Access, keyless entry and start system, and UV reducing exterior glass were some of the features made standard. Safety was improved with twin chamber front passenger airbags, side torso airbags for the front row, side curtain airbags for front and rear rows, knee airbags for front row, and active headrests, to protect the passengers from whiplash injuries used to protect the passenger. Hill Assist control that prevents the car from rolling back on a steep incline is standard.

name: Volvo V60 T6
description: The T6 of Volvo V60 is the 2nd highest spec Volvo produced apart from the Polestar spec which stands at the top of the list. The V60 is a compact executive station wagon by Volvo cars which is the station wagon version of the S60 that is an executive sedan. First released in 2010 and done a facelift in 2014, it has scored to be an excellent station wagon. The engine option in the T6 features a very sharp, instant, and powerful Inline-4 2000cc VEA B4204T9 engine with a power rating of 302hp. This is a good deal of power for such a light hatchback. Adding on it is the R-Design spec which makes the car look aesthetically sportier! Volvo never ceases to amaze its consumers.

name: Toyota Fortuner
description: This is the Fortuner from the 1st Generation the began production in 2004 to 2015 when the 2nd Gen began. This was available with the 3.0L 1KD-FTV common rail variable geometry turbocharged diesel engine that was common in a lot of high torque Toyota models. It has a functional scoop on its hood being a common rail turbo intercooled. It has 7 seats occupancy capacity, excellent clearance, and a manual transmission gearbox as some of its major specs.

name: BMW 320i
description: BMW 320i 'F30' is the sedan version that used the N20B20 engine replaced by the B48B20 from 2015 to 2019. This is an M-Sport version has better looks with M-Sport badging on the seats, door-frame floor, and front side fendors. It is fitted with Powered alcantara seats with memory function, dual zone climate controls, Multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, BMW iDrive infotainment system, and different drives modes to choose from including Sport and Eco mode.

name: Toyota Mark X
description: This Toyota Mark X is fitted with 5 half leather seats, dual zone climate controls, interior wood trimming, steering wheel controls, android infotainment display screen, armrests, and fog lights.

name: BMW 530i
description:
EN ROUTE TO THE PORT OF MOMBASA! EXPECTED TIME OF ARRIVAL 28th JUNE, 2024.

Specs include Leather seats, heated seats, Multifunctional steering wheel, adaptive LED lights, multiple ambient colour lighting options, Harman Kardon premium surround sound system, dual zone climate controls, head up display, cruise control, and traction control.

name: BMW 530i
description:
EN ROUTE TO THE PORT OF MOMBASA! EXPECTED TIME OF ARRIVAL 28th JUNE, 2024.

Specs include a Leather seats, heated seats, Multifunctional steering wheel, adaptive LED lights, multiple ambient colour lighting options, Harman Kardon premium surround sound system, dual zone climate controls, head up display, cruise control, and traction control.

name: Mercedes Benz C200 AVANTGARDE
description: Avantgarde is the top trim Mercedes Benz marketed the C200 with. It was offered with Liverpool fabric/leatherette seats and optional leather. It used a different sport grille that had three wide matt-finish horizontal bars and a central Mercedes emblem that appeared boldy at the middle. An optional AMG Bodykit was also available. Upgraded sports suspension and brake piston callipers. The engine features a 1.8L turbocharged M271 CGI Inline-four engine with power rating of 270Nm of torque.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado J120
description: The J120 series, 3rd Gen of Landcruiser Prado that was sold from 2002 after the 2nd Gen J90 ended production. Toyota improved Prado's suspension in this model year that also improved its reliability from the previous Gen. Earlier models of the J120 until 2004 used the 2.7L 3RZ-FE which was replaced by the famous 2TR-FE in late 2004. This unit has been very well maintained with its leather seats still at good condition and all the other parts in perfect condition.

name: Lexus RX200T
description: RX 200T appears slightly larger than then NX200T that they share an engine. It is bold and beautiful in all aspects. It has a nicely complimenting interior and exterior with the interior consisting of red leather seats, very spacious and comfy, an analogue clock, a heated steering wheel and seats that are also cooled, heated rear seats & 3-position memory seats, Head-Up Display, adaptive cruise control, and Anti-collision warning system among other equipments. The sporty nature of the car is complimented by the 2.0L 8AR-FTS turbocharged petrol engine that is one hell of a perfomer. It is also a very economical car attributed to by Lexus' Economy with Superior Thermal Efficient Combustion (ESTEC) direct injection with turbo (D-4ST) fuel injection. It is run by a 6-speed automatic transmission gearbox with a very smooth shift.

name: Peugeot 208
description: A perfect French starter car, Peugeot 208. A 1.2L petrol engine, comfy fabric seats, and a generally easy car generous on fuel and maintenance.

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: The XTRAIL has been a very popular SUV used since 2000 by a large number of individuals. It is a very capable offroader as it is fitted with optional 4WD select that enables one to drive on only two wheels to save on fuel, leather seats that are super comfortable, Nissan pure drive for environmental friendly drives, and heated seats for warming up during the cold. The hybrid system also saves up on fuel consumption and betters the consumption of this SUV.

name: Audi A7
description: The A7 is the four-door fastback version of the C7-series of Audi A6. It is based on the MLB Platform by Volkswagen Group. The major difference between the A6 and the A7 is the detail work in its interior that it has a unique panelwork and utilizes Aluminum for much of its front body structure. The first gen of the A7 coded 4G8 was produced in 2010 and the 2nd gen Typ 4K8 appearing in 2018. It came with a variety of engines consisting of the 2.0L TFSI beginning in 2014-2018, the popular 3.0L TFSI, the 2.8 FSI QUATTRO, and the 3.0TDI diesel engine. This unit utilizes the 2.0L engine option mated to a 7 speed automatic transmission gearbox. It has a power rating of 249hp.

name: Mazda CX5
description: This petrol variant of the CX-5 is specced with fabric seats, i-stop by Mazda, Adaptive frontlight system, Traction control system, dual zone climate controls, and Multifunctional steering wheel among other specs.

name: Toyota Axio
description: This is the new shape Toyota Axio with major redesigns worked on a lot of parts, the major one being the face, front bumper. It has bight fabric seats, climate controls, android infotainment display screen, and cup holders.

name: Mazda CX5
description: Quite a hassle to get this 2.0L Petrol variant of the CX-5. This is a great deal. It is specced with Rear Vehicle Monitoring system, traction control system, adaptive frontlight system, i-stop function, and a petrol engine variant among other specs.

name: Renault Lutecia TROPHY
description: Renault Lutecia IV is the 4th gen of Lutecia that made a debut in 2012. It has been upgraded with improvements including an extended wheelbase touching also the car's width. The RS(Renault Sport) version similarly was launched in 2012 with a number of adaptations being made including the use of 6-speed EDC(Efficient Double Clucth) instead of a manual transmission, a 1.6L DIG-T Nissan MR16DDT inline four engine doing 200hp and 240Nm of torque. The unit listed is an RS Trophy version with an uprated engine doing 217bhp and 280Nm of torque. Interior features include Renault R-Link 7 inch infotainment system that incorporates Android OS and TomTom Tech system that provides navigation assistance. This is now a proper French Hatchback!

name: Mazda CX3
description: This is one great subcompact crossover SUV that's looks minimalistically powerful but gets to offer a lot from power output to drivetrain and comfort. With an AWD Setup, you still get to triumph over any kind of surface while getting maximum comfort from the heated leather seats.

name: Nissan Tiida
description: The Nissan Tiida Latio came to the market fo fill a unique gap of reliable and highly fuel efficient engines. It has 5 fabric seats, climate controls, and side panel indicators that compliment the front and rear positioned indicators among its specs

name: Subaru Outback
description: The Subaru Outback is equipped with a 2.5L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine, heated leather seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, android infotainment display system, dual zone climate controls, and a Symmetrical All Wheel Drive setup.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TX
description: The Landcruiser Prado TX TRJ150, is equipped with a 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox, side steps, a sunroof, fog lights, front & side curtain airbags, and a multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Toyota Spade
description: Toyota Spade, also called Porte, is a mini Multipurpose Van developed by Toyota, minimalistic and simple, being an excellent comfortable car with a high roof line and a very spacious legroom. The interior design we give it to Toyota for giving a classy and minimalistic design that is very welcoming. You might as well love this car by just looking at the interior. It also shines in its cost effective performance with engine options of 1.3L and 1.5L giving figures of up to 18Kms a liter!

name: Volvo S60
description: Volvo S60 T3, powered by B4164T3 1600cc inline four turbocharged engine producing 148 horsepower and 240Nm of torque, is an excellent unit to use in any kind of activity from office errands to farm stuff. Very comfortable with bucket shaped leather seats and a Premium surround sound system.

name: Subaru Forester
description: Subaru introduced the 4th Generation Forester, coded SJ, in 2014, with a lot of interest going to the interior and the comfort its consumers would experience. The passenger and rear bench seats were positioned higher than before, its sound system was improved, and the transmission system as well. The EyeSight Driver Assist System fitted in 2014 consists of Pre-Collision Braking system, Pre-Colision Throttle Management, Adaptive cruise control, and Lane Departure & Sway warning. It is a highly recommended Compact Crossover SUV.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: Never seen a better kitted Toyota Harrier. It has been done an upgrade of the Front grill, front and rear bumpers, has aftermarket fitted quad exhaust tailpipes for aesthetics, and has a sunroof. Want to separate yourself from the crew? And shine among all? Look no further than this listed Harrier!

name: Volkswagen Golf Variant GTI
description: One of those rare occasions where you get to find the rare highly soughted after engines. This is a Volkswagen Golf GTI with a 2.0 Turbo engine. Great power yet it looks mean with its power, definitely qualifies to be a sleeper. That, is a big deal!

name: Nissan NP300 Hardbody
description: This variant of NP 300 runs the 3.0L Diesel engine. With the 3.0L Turbocharged diesel engine, it handles all the difficult tasks one has. This is a high torque car that is majorly used commercially and can accomodate upto 5 passengers. It is mated to a manual transmission gearbox with locking differentials.

name: Mercedes Benz E250
description: This is one of the best designed E Class models. With a wide display screen which displays the instrument cluster and the infotainment system and the Co-driver's seat controls from the driver's side is among the highlights of the E-Class experienced in the S-Class. You also get other premium features like powered multi-way adjustable seats, three-position memory seats for the front occupants, dual zone climate controls, leather bucket-styled front seats, and voice commands among others.

name: Mazda Axela
description: With great power from the Skyactiv-D 2.2L diesel engine, and a great balance of versatility and luxury, Mazda Axela sells as one of the most preferred hatchbacks. It is specced with a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, cruise control, parking sensors, lane departure assist, and i-stop system.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TX
description: The Landcruiser Prado TX GDJ150, diesel variant, is equipped with a 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox, side steps, 7 seats occupancy capacity, a sunroof, fog lights, front & side curtain airbags, and a multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Toyota Premio 260
description: This is the facelifted version of Toyota Premio. Premio 260 came into the market to fill the gap Camry left from Corolla. From the engine to body size. Premio has been bought by a very wide range of people from those who want the 1.5L, 1.8L, to 2.0L. This is a 1.8L version 2ZR-FE producing 138hp and 173Nm of torque. It has powered fabric beige seats, interior wood trim, and android infotainment system as some of its specs.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: This is a spiced up Modellista kitted Toyota Harrier which makes this car look much bolder than the regular Harriers. The Modellista bodykit includes both front and rear diffusers & side skirts that definitely gives it a substantial look. This unit also gets to be equipped with a Premium surround sound system, powered boot, leather seats, cruise control, Anti-collision brake assist, and lane assist as some of its features.

name: Mitsubishi RVR
description: Mitsubishi RVR is your excellent subcompact crossover choice. With just the right body lenght and width, you can comfortably carry 5 passengers and go into any kind of squeezed road and still burn just enough fuel while going low on maintenance costs!

name: Mazda Axela
description: This is the third generation of Mazda Axela since its first Gen production models in the year 2003, it has undergone a lot of changes with the major one being the Skyactiv chassis that replaced Ford's C1 platform. This unit has a 1500cc naturally aspirated petrol engine with a 2WD drivetrain. Fabric seats,climate controls, android infotainment display system, steering wheel controls, and cup holders make up the interior.

name: Toyota Vitz Jewela
description: Toyota Vitz, 3rd Gen XP130, features a much spacious interior compared to the previous generation, the XP90. This gives it a bonus in the comfort it offers to all of its occupants. It also looks a bit sportier as much as it is not a fully sports car as the Vitz RS variant is. The seats in this are made of fabric material, has steering wheel controls, and auto start stop among other features.

name: Toyota Roomy
description: Toyota Roomy is a Mini MPV manufactured by Daihatsu and sold by Daihatsu, Subaru, and Toyota. A big deal on this unit is its 1000cc 1KR-VET Turbo with a good deal of 97 horsepowers. It has sliding doors as one of its major spec. It is based on the M700 Series Boon with a 5 seating capacity. In the categories of small cars in Japan, this did not qualify to be a Kei car because of its exterior dimensions and has a slightly larger engine for a Kei Car. It was introduced in 2016 and has been running production until date.

name: Volkswagen Touareg
description: The 1st Gen of Touareg was first produced in 2002 and straight up won several awards for its among it for being the best in the 4×4 car category. It shares a lot of parts with the Cayenne and the engine is their biggest similarity with it being equipped with a 3.6L Petrol V6 engine. This is a go-to car for someone who wants to use it for several purposes including offroading and for urban setups.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TX
description: The Toyota Landcruiser Prado TX is an excellent SUV that is able to multitask its use from offroad activities which it does well with the 4WD drive system and a good clearance, family use with the sunroof, to official activities as it is a highly presentable car.

name: Audi Q3 2.0T QUATTRO
description:
Typ 8U Audi Q3 is at its 2nd gen
with the 1st Gen being produced
at 2011. The Q3 received a LCI
in 2014 for cars sold in 2015.
Another update was done in 2015
with improvements of front and
rear parking sensors, full LED
lights, and improvements in
front lights and grille. The
2.0L Quattro spec takes its load
easily as it runs power figures
of 197hp and 280Nm of torque to
all 4 wheels

name: Jeep Cherokee Limited 3.2L V6
description: Jeep, Since 1944. Jeep has been making tough cars since then. And depending on the engine types, one identifies the versatility of the car and the power they need for whatever kind of excursion they wish to participate in. This unit has the 3.2L V6 petrol engine with power rating of 286hp. It is heavily equipped with a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, a panoramic sunroof, an auto start-stop system, Multi Terrain select with Auto, Snow, Sport, Sand/Mud, and an android infotainment system.

name: Mercedes Benz E200
description: The E-Class sells as one of DAIMLER AG's favourite with all the developments they've done on this car from when they did a facelift to later adopting designs of the S-Class. The wide display screen which displays the instrument cluster and the infotainment system and the Co-driver's seat controls from the driver's side is among the highlights of the E-Class experienced in the S-Class. You also get other premium features like powered multi-way adjustable seats, three-position memory seats for the front occupants, dual zone climate controls, leather bucket-styled front seats, and voice commands among others.

name: Mitsubishi Colt
description: This is probably the cleanest Mitsubishi Colt we have received at our Market Place. An excellently maintained body, well kept interior, optimally performing engine, and the general drivetrain. This works as a great car to begin the vehicle ownership. A non problematic easy consuming MPV!

name: Mercedes Benz SLK 200 WALD
description: This is perfectly clean Convertible spec SLK 200 with Wald Black Bison Body Kit. A stunner we can call. It runs a 2.0L 7G-Tronic automatic transmission gearbox with a power rating of 215hp. It has heated leather seats, a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, Fender extensions from Germany, GT style front grill, Roof module from Germany installed, to enable roof opening and closing while driving upto a speeds of 60kph, Original sports rims from Germany, and Wheel spacers installed to give a broader look

name: Volkswagen Arteon
description: Volkswagen Arteon falls under large family car category and is available in five-door liftback or estate body styles. This is the liftback body style. Arteon is based on the MQB platform that was first used in Golf MK7 back in 2012. It directly succeeds the CC and is heavily based on a concept Volkswagen Arteon revealed in 2015. It came in with new design aspects from the body to the interior and gets very appealing. It runs a 2.0L TSI Petrol engine with power rating of 276hp. With its design inspirations, it is able to do a 0-100kph in 5.6s. It has a sunroof, leather seats, and a multifunctional steering wheel among other specs.

name: Volvo V60 T3
description: Volvo V60 was first introduced into the market in 2010 with the second generation beginning in 2018. It underwent a facelift in 2014 with the newer version being more sleek and appealing. This unit comes fitted with heated seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, a premium surround sound system that's arguably one of the best, and dual exhaust tailpipes.

name: Range Rover Vogue 3.0 TDV6
description: The 2019 Facelift looks a little more interesting on the 2015 Range Rover Vogue. A little leap into the future doesn't hurt, in fact, it tells more about the vehicles capability to handle whatever the future of driving has. It is equipped with a Terrain Response management system, electric locking differentials, perforated seats, heated steering wheel, multiple way electrically adjustable front seats, daytime running LED Lights, and a Meridian premium surround sound system.

name: Mitsubishi Outlander
description: PHEV (Plug in Hybrid Electric Vehicle) comes with a lot of benefits with the major one being low fuel bills. The 2.0L petrol engine and the electric system gets to achieve a combined 59Kms a Liter which is excellently great for both city and highway driving. This might just be the perfect mid-size SUV for family purposes and can actually go offroad without a hussle as it has the 4WD drivetrain system.

name: Landrover Defender 110
description: Defenders have always defended their titles of being the best durable cars that last a dime when kept well. Their engines are durable and their body materials last forever. One can keep pampering it over the years to keep it modern as the ages go by. They are excellent in offroading and takes pride in being one of the best overlanders with the modifications done by its owners.

name: Honda Fit Shuttle Hybrid
description: The shuttle hybrid is based on the Fit Hybrid which its smaller brother. This amazing fuel economy is achieved by reducing rolling resistance with front braking, reduced engine friction, improved control efficiency of the hybrid system, ECON mode to minimise fuel consumption, and improved aerodynamics.

name: Toyota Auris Hybrid
description: With how good Toyota's Hybrid Synergy drive system is, we can already know the value it gives to this Toyota Auris. As silent as it appears, is as it drives. With up to 34Kms a Liter of consumption, this is value for money. It is a 2017 model meaning it gets new technologies and design aspects. It has leather seats colored in two tones that get very appealing.

name: Mazda CX5
description: Anything better than a fully loaded CX-5, none we can think of. The new age of new generation CX-5s came with highly equipped cars with a wide range of specs and in this unit having premium specs including heated steering wheel, head up display, heated seats both for the front occupants and the rear, two-position memory seats, Blindspot monitoring assist, auto start stop system, parking sensors, and and lane departure assist.

name: BMW 320i Luxury
description: BMW 320i, is a 5-door sedan in the 3 series class of BMW Series. It runs an N20B20 2.0L producing 181hp and 270Nm of torque. With a good design that increases aerodynamic flow, it accelerates to 100Km per hour in 7.9 Seconds. It is styled with fabric seats, dual zone climate controls, a multifunctional steering wheel, and BMW’s i-Drive infotainment system.

name: Nissan NP300 Hardbody
description: The tough pickup by Nissan! Specced with a 3.0L Turbocharged diesel engine, this is one for the difficult tasks one has. This is a high torque car that is majorly used commercially and can accomodate upto 5 passengers. It is mated to a manual transmission gearbox with locking differentials.

name: Mercedes Benz C180
description: The durability of these old gens Benz was great. Cars were build with all the might and would live through the years. This C180 all the way from 1998 is still in perfect condition and would sustain another good number of years. It has a 1.8L petrol engine with its interior in fabric.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The new era of the CX-5 came with two famous engine in which the diesel engine has been the go-to by many consumers. The 2.5L petrol engine is a good option for those who would prefer a petrol choice to the diesel one. It has a power rating of 187hp which is quite descent for this SUV. It has some specs including auto start stop system, parking sensors, and and lane departure assist.

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: This is the 3rd gen of Nissan XTRAIL Mode-Premier AUTECH that has been widely used in the Kenyan Market since the entry of the first generation NT30 in 2000. It is a very capable offroader as it is fitted with optional 4WD select that enables one to drive on only two wheels to save on fuel, leather seats that are super comfortable, Nissan pure drive for environmental friendly drives, dual tip exhaust tailpipes, and heated seats for warming up during the cold.

name: Mercedes Benz ML 320
description: The ML 320 is a mid-size luxury SUV produced by Mercedes since 1997 with this being the 1st Gen internally known as the W163. It has the body-on-frame design and has a permanent 4Matic four-wheel drive system. It runa a 3.2L V6 petrol engines with power rating of 215hp. It has leather seats with the 3rd row seating being foldable. It displays the might of Germans with it strong durable build.

name: Volkswagen Golf R
description: Having won a number of drag races or appeared on the top of drag performers, many know what this car is capable of. The R indicates a high performance car as Volkswagen refers it to. The EA888 3rd Gen inline-four petrol engine has a re-engineered cylinder head, exhaust valves, valve seats, pistons, injection valves, and a modified intercooler. This enables it handle high power demands of 296hp stock power. In its drivetrain, it uses the fifth Gen Haldex 4MOTION All Wheel drive system that decouples and couples the rear wheels on demand. This unit also comes with the Dynamic Chassis Control which enables one to choose from three suspension modes; Comfort, Normal, and Race adjusting suspension damping. The bucket-styled seats holds you in place and makes a very comfortable ride.

name: Volkswagen Golf 1.4L TSI
description: Golf TSI could win the award of being the most non problematic, fast, reliable, spacious, and classy hatch. One would only dispose for an upgrade. It runs a 1.4L turbocharged petrol engine that drives power to the front wheels. Its seats are made of Alcantara material which are very comfy, has dual zone climate controls, auto brake hold, Multifunctional steering wheel, and apple carplay among other specs.

name: Toyota Vitz
description: A unique coloured Toyota Vitz! Not a bad shot. For anyone who wants specifics in this efficient JDM, this unit is a good choice. Specced with a 1.3L NA Petrol engine, fabric seats, and an overally spacious interior all the way to the boot, one can comfortably go for this unit.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: The Forester XT has been fitted a number of equipments including heated seats both in the front and the rear, XMODE for offroading, roof rails, memory height adjustment, SRH(Steering Responsive Headlights) to improve visibility at night by lighting where the steering directs to, and Blindspot monitoring assist amongst other specs.

name: Jeep Cherokee Sport
description: A decent urban SUV with the ruggedness and toughness the bigger brothers Wrangler and Grand Cherokee has. It was produced in 2013 for the 2014 model year. It sits below the bigger Grand Cherokee and above the smaller Jeep Compass. It runs a 2.4L petrol engine which is well powered for multiple uses.

name: Toyota Fielder
description: Hybrid Synergy Drive, a new tech adopted by Toyota to supplement the power from its Internal Combustion Engine and to cut down on fuel costs especially in urban driving as it includes increased starts and stops because of road traffic. This is extreme convenience from what the car actually offers in its interior. This, Toyota Fielder Hybrid WXB, is just the right car for reliable and highly convenient drives!

name: Toyota Crown Royal Saloon
description: Toyota Crown in general excels in the luxury saloons category in the mid-size category of cars. From the extreme comfort the car's occupants receive to the comfortable driving modes, this could be rated as the S-Class of Toyota in its category. The Smooth driving in the Crown Royal Saloon is facilitated by the Driving Response and Acceleratiom Management System and jointly with the 2.5L V6 petrol engine, you get to experience a poweful drive. The smooth gearbox transmission is courtesy of the Super-Intelligent electronically controlled 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox called the Super 6 ECT.

name: Subaru Forester
description: A versatile mid-size SUV by Subaru! Powered by a 2000cc Naturally aspirated petrol engine, this is the best bet for a non-problematic SUV that comfortably handles offroad and onroad use. XMODE handles offroad well and the Symmetrical AWD handles onroad even in wet conditions extremely good. The space in its interior is a good one, enough roof-height and legroom, and generally a comfy welcoming interior.

name: Peugeot 308
description: Peugeot 308 scored a very good reliability score among reviewers and users. It is very reliable with good maintenance and will with no doubt take you miles. It is powered by a 1200cc turbocharged engine that's quite powerful doing over 230Nm of Torque. It has fabric seats, steering wheel controls, paddle shifters, climate controls, android infotainment display screen, a moonroof, and side mirror indicators. It is quite spacious and very comfortable.

name: Toyota Allion 1.5L
description: Toyota Allion comes in different engine variants and one most economical variant is the 1NZ-FE 1.5L NA petrol engine which is very forgiving on your pockets. This car has been much pampered and styled well one would already buy before viewing it!

name: Toyota Axio
description: The newer models of Toyota Axio look very good compared to the older models. The redesigns worked on a lot of parts, the major one being the face, front bumper. It has bight fabric seats, climate controls, and android infotainment display screen.

name: Mitsubishi Outlander PHEV
description: Mitsubishi Outlander PHEV (Plug in Hybrid Electric Vehicle) comes with a lot of benefits with the major one being low fuel bills. The 2.0L petrol engine and the electric system gets to achieve a combined 59Kms a Liter which is excellently great for both city and highway driving. This might just be the perfect mid-size SUV for family purposes and can actually go offroad without a hussle as it has the 4WD drivetrain system.

name: Mazda Atenza
description: A full spec Atenza! Heated steering wheel, heated seats, sunroof, and a heavy torque engine! The Atenza has an engaging drive with its agile driving and linear steering style. The Skyactiv tech diesel engine with a capacity of 2200cc impressively pushing torque figures of 418Nm. Quite a classy sedan!

name: Volkswagen Tiguan
description: Tiguan sits between the Touareg and T-Roc which ranks it as an excellent crossover of this class. It offers a very good balance between comfort, performance, and luxury. This unit comes fitted with leather seats, Multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, android infotainment display system, parking sensors, rear retractable mini-tables for the rear occupants, electric handbrake, and side mirror indicators.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: One of the best good-looking cars in the market, the W205 Generation of the C200. This unit has dark leather seats that are bucket-styled with thigh support. The interior has also been modernised with the dash having a wide Mercedes Command infotainment display, analogue cabin clock, a touchscreen center console display control, flat-bottomed steering wheel, and 3-circular air vents.

name: Nissan March
description: Nissan March is one of the simplest get-in and driver car. A push to start ignition, climate controls, radio control that also provides phone connectivity, and comfortable fabric seats, all offered at the best deal.

name: Mercedes Benz C180
description: In the class of compact sedans, the C180 turns out to be an excellently engineered sedan, with this car probably being the best there is. It gives an executive taste with all in round class while delivering excellent performance and fuel economy. It runs a 1.6L turbocharged petrol engine with a descent horsepower of 156hp and 250Nm of torque driving you in comfortable front row-heated bucket styled leather seats with thigh support while regulating your cabin temperature from dual zone climate controls listening to music from a premium surround sound system.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: The best of Toyota Harrier there is, the G's, a premium SUV by Toyota that accomodates consumers who still love Toyota but would want extras of a comfortable and convenient SUV. From powered seats, eco mode that by far saves on fuel by reducing engine performance and maximising on fuel efficiency, Auto start stop feature, high clearance, dual zone climate controls, a multifunctional steering wheel, push to start button, and Traction control that is practical in handling multiple terrains. The seats are laced with Alcantara material and the G's badging. And being the G's version, it appears more sportier than other versions of Toyota Harriers. The G's is badged nearly all over the car which makes the car even more appealing.

name: Toyota Vitz
description: Here is one well maintained 2nd gen Toyota Vitz that was produced between 2005 and 2010 in a five-door hatchback body style. It is fitted with 5 fabric seats, climate controls, android infotainment system, and key-ignition a some of its specs.

This spec, internally coded 4G15, runs a 1.5L turbocharged Inline 4 petrol engine producing 148hp to the rear wheels and making a quick 100Kmh run in 7.7s only. It is ready for any track or daily as one chooses!

It can comfortably sit any person of any height and even large size cargos as it has a high roof compared with other cars of similar class. It has side mirror indicators, fabric seats, climate controls, and android infotainment system among other specs.
