name: Toyota Kluger
description: Toyota Kluger is also known as Highlander in some markets. Running a 3.5L 2GR-FKS V6 bulletproof engine, it's descent enough to produce 361Nm of torque and 237hp when used with gasoline of 87 octane rating. It also serves as a descent family car carrying 7 occupants in a very spacious interior with the seats being all leather. The rear occupants also get to enjoy themselves with rear entertainment screens!

name: Range Rover Sport
description: Range Rover Sport is the ultimate SUV with top of class equipments that improves Range Rover's preference to any other SUV of its class. It has an improved suspension system that improves comfort and stability at high speeds and when engaging corners, an All Wheel Drive system with the drivetrain including terrain response management system and multiple offroad modes, and an eight speed automatic transmission gearbox. The infotainment system was upgraded with a 10-inch Touchscreen for convenience of car specs access with safety features including automatic emergency braking system, lane keep assist, and a blind spot warning sytem.

name: Jeep Grand Cherokee
description: The American Marque categorised in the mid-size SUV produced since 2010 to 2022. At the unveiling moment in New York's Auto Show, it received 30 awards. The Grand Cherokee 'BLACKHAWK' has definitely outperformed itself in all its years of production. It is a serious offroader and doubles up well as a presentable urban driving car. It features a four-wheel independent suspension which improves road handling. The engine option in this car is the 3.6L Pentastar V6 Petrol version with a power rating of 290hp. On the interior are comfy half leather seats, a premium surround sound system, a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, and a 4WD drive select system.

name: Toyota Fortuner
description: This is the second generation of Toyota Fortuner since its first production in 2004. 2nd Gen production began in 2015 mid with new introductions being made as with the part time 4 by 4 system that improved on the cars fuel economy. The 2.8L diesel engine was also improved with a common direct injection in its fuel system and a direct nozzle turbocharging. This unit has 7 tan leather seats with the third row being foldable for extra cargo space. It also has excellent clearance for offroad driving. This is a rugged enough unit that will sustain all offroading adventures!

name: Volkswagen Passat Variant 1.4L
description: Volkswagen passat B7 gen came with some improvements majorly consisting of the body panels, grille, and headlights. The face of the Passat keeps on getting better with the advancements in generations. This unit is specced with fabric seats, an analogue cabin clock, interior wood trimming, Multifunctional steering wheel, and powered seats with memory function.

name: Toyota Mark II Regalia
description: Regalia was produced as a special edition by Toyota for Mark II as it marked 35 years anniversary since the use of Mark II nameplate. The Mark II has been in the market for quite a long time since 1968 all the way to the years of 2007 with the Mark II Blit being the last in the production line. It was first produced as a compact sedan and later sold as a midsize sedan. It is probably one of the best clean cars we have ever received in our markets. We have never seen any Mark II that is not that clean regardless of the production year. They are very durable and reliable.

name: Audi Q5
description: The Typ 80A Audi Q5 features a range of new technologies that makes it a favourite of many Audi Consumers. A digital instrument cluster, redesigned steering wheel, dashboard, and center console with the design being more minimalistic than the previous model. Exterior designs became more sharper lowering drag coefficient. Both front and rear lights were also redesigned giving the car a much better admired fascia. It also was uprated just with the EA888 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine to 252hp and 370Nm of torque from the previous 222hp and 350Nm of torque.

name: Audi A4 2.0T QUATTRO
description: The A4 runs a 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine and drives all the 4 wheels on demand via Audi's All Wheel Quattro system which is arguably one of the best systems. It has leather seats that are powered, AUDI MMI infotaiment system, Multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters and a premium sound system among other specs.

name: Volvo XC90
description:
This 2017 model of the XC90 T5
features a number of equipments which are a big deal including a panoramic sunroof, leather seats with third row-seating capacity with both the front and rear occupants having a heating functionality, Premium surround sound system that makes the cabin feel like a large Orchestral theatre, steering wheel controls, and all the safety systems Volvo have ever come up with including City safety and Run-off-road protection package that controls the seats comfort level and belts adjustment to deliver a comfortable offroading experience.

name: Mazda CX8
description: The CX8 is a Midsize crossover SUV produced by Mazda. It is Mazda's flagship car in Japan. It is also sold in Oceania, SouthEast Asia, and China. It was unveiled in September 2017 becoming the only three-row SUV offered by Mazda after they discontinued Mazda Premacy and Biante. It was initially offered with a 2.2 L Skyactiv-D diesel engine but later in 2018, a choice of two I4 petrol engines was added: a 2.5L Skyactiv-G (PY-VPS) from the CX-5 and a turbocharged version of the same engine from the CX-9. It is definitely a better bargain for any three-row SUV.

name: Nissan Murano 3.5L V6
description: Big engines are the best in what it offers, from being one of the best sounding engine to delivering optimum power choices. This is the 2nd gen Murano produced in 2008 for 2009 model year, in effect skipping the 2008 model year in preparation for this 2009 model year. It came with major updates including a revised 3.5L V6 petrol engine and a revised Continuously Variable Transmission with Adaptive Shift Control. Brake assist, electronic stability control, and ABS are some of its standard safety features. It is equipped with a sunroof which is an optional equipment!

name: Mitsubishi Pajero GLX
description: Mitsubishi Pajero is arguably one of the best offroad full-size SUV with one of the most aggressive off 4WD system. This unit gets a manual transmission gearbox, and in combination with the 4WD system, it becomes an unbeatable offroad machine. It also has the Altimeter Inclinometer dash display with the first measuring altitude and the inclinometer , angles of slope or elevation. With a very strong build as seen with its durability, it can last a lifetime. Clocking nearly half a million Kilometres since production in 2006, the journey is yet to begin!

name: Mazda CX5
description: The CX-5 comes with a wide range of specs a mid-size SUV is supposed to have. From heated leather seats that are powered and have memory function. It has a sunroof convenient for adventures and an All Wheel Drive system convenient for all terrains especially offroad. It is spacious enough for 5 occupants and has sufficient cargo space. It has the best deal on it!

The Crossovers favored individuals who loved the brand but wanted something they could even go on official business with, without looking out of place in such setups.

description: Volvo V40 at launch was produced with two petrol engine options, one being the 1.6L EcoBoost I4 with 148hp and 178hp power ratings, and the 2.5L B525 I5 doing 254hp. This unit uses the 1.6L I4 with 148hp power rating. Leather seats, dual zone climate controls, a multifunctional steering wheel, polished metal trimming, and adpative cruise control consists its specs.

Its seating capacity also extends to the third row totally accommodating 7 individuals. And with any kind of weather, it is the best performer.

On the interior, leather seats with heating functionality, dual zone climate controls, Multifunctional steering wheel, and carbon fibre trimming carry the day. Such a magnificent piece.

description: Your best offroading partner! A 4T winch combined with aftermarket suspension system and excellent ground clearance make this a perfect match. It is one of the best offroad machines to ever appear in our markets, 3rd generation Jeep wrangler that came in, in 2006 under the development of Daimler Chrysler and was developed under a clean-sheet design of the body, frame, and suspension. This generation of Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sports came with power windows, remote power door locks, navigation, and electronically detachable sway bars on some models. The Wrangler carries the seriousness an offroader deserves. A 4WD system and a high torque engine is all you need to fulfil your offroad adventures!

It gets to be a serious money maker for any type of properly idealized and executable business. It has a seating capacity of 9 occupants with very spacious and comfortable seats. It is in excellent condition!

One would not mind this becoming their daily drive choice.

It also has heated seats and X-Mode for offroading adventures.

The drag coefficient was decreased, exterior dimensions increased with cargo room getting an increment as well. Smart Access, keyless entry and start system, and UV reducing exterior glass were some of the features made standard. Safety was improved with twin chamber front passenger airbags, side torso airbags for the front row, side curtain airbags for front and rear rows, knee airbags for front row, and active headrests, to protect the passengers from whiplash injuries used to protect the passenger. Hill Assist control that prevents the car from rolling back on a steep incline is standard.

Heated steering wheel and heated seats for maximum heat comfort in any kind of weather, complimented by climate controls, Mazda Connect infotaiment system, a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, leather seats all spaced well especially for the rear occupants, two-position memory seats, and Adaptive front light system consist of the premium specs in this listing.

The XMODE feature, S#(Sport Sharp), S(Sport), and I(Intelligent) modes all work to ensure you have a seamless and enjoyable car experience.

It originally uses a four cylinder 1.4L 4G41 OHV I4 naturally aspirated engine but this unit has been swapped a Datsun's 1.2L NA Engine. Do not under-estimate how powerful this actually is. This generation was available only in a rear wheel configuration as the 4WD versions became available in Japan in 1982. You can never go wrong with such bulletproof model cars!

name: Audi Q5
description: The Q5s are definitely bold show makers. Having an S-Line even makes it better as it is much more aesthetically equipped. Its body has S-LINE badging to the interior where the steering wheel is still badged. You get half leather seats and a panoramic sunroof which makes this unit even worth more. It is a low mileage car which gives its users another plus!

name: Subaru Forester XT with ROOF CARGO KIT
description: Need to carry some extra load on the XTs roof, this might just be the perfect Subaru Forester for the job. Going out off-town has never been this easy with the roof cargo box and a ladder to access the roof. The XT being the turbocharged version of Subaru Forester, gives a plus assurance when overtaking because of its powerful 2.0L petrol engine that does an impressive quick acceleration from 0 to 100kmh in 7.5s according to official results from Subaru. It handles all terrains with total ease having been equipped with Subaru's All Wheel Drive system.

name: Subaru Legacy 2.0L
description: Subaru Legacy, the 4th Gen, adopted a new design that began development early in 1999 while production began in 2003. With the chassis being stiffened, a more aggresive and a better handling car especially with sharp corners. The Japanes market received a 500cc less capacity engine from the North American market that recived 2.5L turbocharged engines. The Japanese market received a 2.0L with power figures of 165hp and 187Nm of Torque.

name: BMW X5 XDrive35d "F15" / PANO SUNROOF
description: BMW X5 made a debut in 1999 with the first model being coded as E53. It is a mid-size luxury SUV categorised by BMW as Sports Activity Vehicle (SAV) instead of SUV. It is available in an All wheel drive system that features torque-split. The E70 came in next after the E53 in 2006. The current listed F15 gen car came in later in 2013 featuring the same chassis and wheelbase as the E70. The F15 came with an introduction of an increased number of engine choices including the XDrive 40d, XDrive 35i, XDrive 25d, and SDrive 25d. This unit features a 3.0L N57 straight-6 diesel engine with a power rating of 560Nm of torque. It is fitted with heated seats that are powered, head up display, hill descent control, and an electric tailgate among other specs.

name: Volkswagen Polo
description:

name: Range Rover Evoque
description: Range Rover Evoque, HSE SD4, a subcompact luxury crossover SUV meant for both urban and off-road experiences. It performs well in the city and excels as well offroading as Land Rover has done well in creating a reliable most efficient Terrain Response system including Grass, Gravel, Snow, and Sand modes. It has specially tweaked comfort to the standards Land Rover has maintained over the years and delivers great performance!

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The W205 Benz C200 comes equipped with leather seats with heating functionality and memory seats, a flat-bottomed multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, an analogue cabin clock, dual zone climate controls, Mercedes Comand Infotainment system, lane keep assist, and an adaptive cruise control.

name: Hyundai Sante Fe
description: Hyundai Santa Fe was named after the city of Mexico, Santa Fe, by the South Korean automobile manufacturer. This is the SR Spec meaning it is the sporty version of the Santa Fe. They were produced in two short wheel or long wheel bas variants which also varied with the market. Some were marketed as 7 seater units while some as 5 seater capacity units. This unit came with 7 seats all in leather and a panoramic sunroof as some of the rare equipments of this unit in the Kenyan market. It has heated and cooled front seats. You also get electronic locking differential and adaptive cruise control as some of its premium specs.

name: Audi Q5
description: A very clean low mileage Audi Q5 Typ 8R that has been in production since 2008. A unique color in its interior and body.The EA888 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine and the versatility it carries with it is unbeatable. Based on the sedan A5 series, they correlate in a number of factors one being how much these cars are sought after for its performance that is rated at 350Nm of torque for both and equally great fuel economy which averages 13Kms a liter with good driving habits.

name: Volkswagen Tiguan
description: Volkswagen Tiguan has been, overally, the best selling SUV in the Volkswagen Group, with over 900,000 units being produced in 2019 alone. It is an excellent compact crossover with the best offer from this car being the efficiency of the 1.4L TSI engine with a power rating of 148hp and consuming close to what a Mazda Demio does.

name: Jincheng JC400 5
description: Jincheng JC400-5 is a 400cc Sports bike produced by the Chinese manufacturer Jincheng Group. With a rev counter of up to 15000 RPMs you get top speeds of close to 200Kms per hour. It has 6 speed manual transmission gearbox and disc brakes both on the front and the back. It has a one cylinder four-stroke engine that is air-cooled. Its fuel tank fills up with 18ltrs of gasoline.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The C-Class by Mercedes Benz was intensely redesigned as the generations went by, and in the 4th generation, we saw a major change in the shape, sharpness, and technological advancements. It resembles the S-Class more as DAIMLER AG did not want it becoming more of an entry level sedan in the C-Class, giving the CLA the title. You basically get to feel like in the S-Class while you pay less for it. This unit is fitted with a Panoramic sunroof,bucket-styled leather seats, and a flat-bottomed multifunctional steering wheel as some of its specs.

name: Range Rover Evoque SD4
description: Range Rover Evoque was, in 2011, first produced by Land Rover LTD until 2012 and the other production years done by Jaguar Land Rover from 2013. It is a subcompact luxury crossover SUV meant for both urban and off-road experiences. It performs well in the city and excels as well offroading as Land Rover has done well in creating a reliable most efficient Terrain Response system including Grass, Gravel, Snow, and Sand modes. It has specially tweaked comfort to the standards Land Rover has maintained over the years and delivers great performance!

name: BMW 530i
description: The G30 is the 7th generation sedan of BMW 5 series. The G31 is the wagon or touring version. It is based on BMW’s Modular Cluster Architecture Platform (CLAR) that was first used in the G11 7 series. Its chassis is made from a mixture of steel and aluminium. The suspension system utilizes a double-wishbone front suspension and 5-link rear suspension. The Wagon variant uses self-levelling rear air suspension. The steering system is rack and pinion with electric power assistance. Its powertrain utilizes a 2.0L B48 Inline-4 turbo petrol engine.

name: Volkswagen Golf GT
description: Volkswagen Golf GT gets a choice of 1.4L petrol twincharger engine, a 2.0L TDI Diesel engine, or a 2.0L FSI direct injection engine. This unit gets the 1.4L variant coupled with a DSG(Direct-Shift Gearbox). The GT has been known to be a very durable car with a good number of users this car has got reviews from. This unit is still in a good solid state which would go on to the next good couple of years with good maintenance.

name: Mazda Bongo
description: Mazda Bongo is a Multipurpose Van that consumers can turn it into a commercial vehicle for cargo or passenger purposes. It nearly all the times come with just the front seats leaving the rear space for the consumer's decision. A number would convert it for passenger services while some use it for cargo. However you want it to be, this unit gives you the chance.

name: Range Rover Vogue 3.0 TDV6 SE
description:
To many, it defines excellence,

Definitely an all rounder!

name: Toyota Royal Crown i-Four
description: Royal Crown is a group of Saloons primarily made by Toyota in the line of mid-size luxury sedans. It has a very bold outlook with the center console bulging out with a large display screen and a number of feature selection buttons and touch-screen access. The seats are largely accomodating with Multiple-way adjustable electric controls. It runs a 2.5L 4GR-FSE V6 petrol engine mated to a 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox and driving the 4 wheels on demand.

name: Honda Stepwagon
description: Honda Stepwgn has been in production since 1996 and falls in the category of minivans. It is stylized as Honda STEPWGN despite it being pronounced as "Stepwagon". This is the 4th gen that was produced between the years of 2009 and 2015. It is now able to carry up to 8 individuals instead of 7. In 2012, it received a minor facelift including a new front grille, front bumper, rear lights, and wheels. A parking camera was also added as standard.

name: Volvo XC60
description: Volvo, XC60 T5 Inscription 'AWD', holds a lot of magic in its production vehicles. From squeezing over 250 horsepower in a 2.0L engine in such a big SUV to being the safest vehicle there is, it is definitely worth every dime!

name: Volvo XC60
description: With the concept car appearing in 2007, sales of the XC60 first gen began in 2008 in Europe and has been Volvo's best selling car since 2009. Volvo was created with a tune of Landrover's offroading capabilities and Volvo's technologies. This makes it one of the best Multipurpose, in the sense of one can operate them at different terrains and for different events, and it will never let one down. The aesthetics are on point, extremely well done, safety earns is a solid 5 star rating from both official tests and consumer reports, and performance is top notch, a marvel. The unit listed is the 2nd Gen that began production in 2017. An Inscription T5 AWD Setup Volvo XC60, quite a beauty to look at. It runs a B4204T 2000cc engine doing 251 horsepowers and 350Nm of torque in an engine orientation of inline 4 plus a turbocharger. Volvo is your next home!

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The W205 Benz C200 comes equipped with leather seats with heating functionality and memory seats, a flat-bottomed multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, an analogue cabin clock, dual zone climate controls, Mercedes Comand Infotainment system, lane keep assist, and an adaptive cruise control.

name: Mitsubishi  eK Wagon
description: Mitsubishi eK Wagon is defined as an excellent minicar in the kei class, the smallest car segment, with excellent space on the interior and quite comfy fabric seats with armrests in the front, climate controls, and side mirrror indicators as some of its specs.

name: Mitsubishi Outlander PHEV
description: Mitsubishi Outlander PHEV (Plug in Hybrid Electric Vehicle) comes with a lot of benefits with the major one being low fuel bills. The 2.0L petrol engine and the electric system gets to achieve a combined 59Kms a Liter which is excellently great for both city and highway driving. This might just be the perfect mid-size SUV for family purposes and can actually go offroad without a hussle as it has the 4WD drivetrain system.

name: Nissan Latio
description: The Nissan Latio is another very easy to-go-to car. Fitted with 5 fabric seats, climate controls, side mirror indicators, and alloy rims, this is one of those cars you can comfortably daily be it to errands or office.

name: BMW X1
description: The X1 F48 series that came in, in 2016. It is based on the Modular front-wheel drive based UKL2 platform that is used with BMW and MINI models, a modular meant to increase interior space and boot space in smaller size model cars. They are both available in front wheel and All Wheel drive systems with the front adopting the SDrive naming and the All Wheel adopting XDrive naming. This unit is an SDrive 18i meaning it runs a 1.5L B38 straight-3 turbocharged engine and drives the power to front wheels.

name: Nissan Sylphy
description: Nissan Sylphy comes out as a very reliably efficient sedan with minimal to no challenges to its owners. Offering maximum comfort for this class and excellent fuel consumption to an average of 14Kms a Liter. It has good ride height which eases the stresses of maneuvering our roads. It is definitely a go-to car for a large number of Users.

name: Smart Forfour
description: Smart Forfour has been marketed by Smart in two production generations from 2004 to 2021 with the 2nd Gen beginning in 2014. The 1st gen adopted a front-engine configuration and while sharing its platform with Mitsubishi Colt, it was majorly marketed in Europe. The 2nd gen took a different turn basing its platform on Renault Twingo, as it was jointly produced with Renault, adopting a rear-engine configuration. The forfour was internally designated as W543. They are offered in a choice of a manual transmission or double-clutch automatic. Initially, they were also offered in a Getrag automated manual transmission but was discontinued for this generation. The Brabus Xclusive Spec listed gets an increased power configuration in its Inline-3 turbocharged engine. It is important to note that Internal Combustion Engines of Forfour ended in 2019 before fully switching to EVs until 2021 when Smart# 1 Crossover took over!

name: Audi A6 2.8L FSI QUATTRO C7 S-LINE
description: The A6 is a versatile and practical Premium Sedan by Audi. With a 2.8L NA petrol engine, you get to experience both ends of performance and perfect cruise both in the city and road trips. On the interior is a very comfortable space with leather seats that are adjustable and powered. It appears very sleek and definitely impresses!

name: Volkswagen Touareg 3.6L V6
description: Volkswagen Touareg 7P, 2nd gen of the Touareg made a debut in 2010 adopting some new technologies such as the Dynamic Light assist that continually adjusts its pattern and beam intensity to protect other drivers from the high beam illumination while intensely illuminating its surrounding: Something Prado should copy. It offroad capabilities are also some of its highlights as the 4Motion All Wheel drive setup gives it excellent capability to manoeuvre offroad terrains. This is also coupled by sufficient clearance.

name: Volkswagen Citi Golf 1.4i
description: Volkswagen Citi Golf has been in the market between the years of 1984 to 2009. It came as a facelift of the 1st Gen Volkswagen Golf MK1. It is marketed as a 5-door right-hand drive hatchback that has had a lot of use even in South African Police. It was only produced in South Africa in 3 body style with the 5-door hatchback being marketed as Citi Golf, 4-door sedan as Fox, 2-door Coupè marketed as Caddy. Citi Golf was a special one where after ending production in 2009, a Celebratory model called Citi MK1, was produced in 1000 specially designed units having lowered suspension and 15" alloys among other specs!

name: Mitsubishi Outlander PHEV
description: This is a Plug In Hybrid variant of the Outlander. It is an excellent SUV that delivers the best of what Mitsubishi intended to give its consumers ranging from economy to occupancy. It features a 5 seats occupancy capacity which is the case with Plug in variants. It drives all the 4 wheels which gives it an edge over any offroad terrains. It also has an eco mode that optimises fuel consumption.

name: Mercedes Benz ML350 / SUNROOF
description: The ML350 was meant for the offroading sect of its line of SUVs in Mercedes production lineup as it is with its successor, the GLE. It has better clearance for offroading and an All Wheel Drive system to tackle any terrain. Its 3.5L NA Petrol engine can easily pull the car with its proper torque rating of 350Nm. The occupants also get to enjoy leather seats and a sunroof among other technologies Mercedes did on this car at that time.

name: Toyota LiteAce GL "S402"
description: Toyota LiteAce is a light duty commercial and derivative passenger van. This model falls under the S400 series that began production in 2008. It has a semi cab-over engine body meaning flat-faced with the engine mounted under the front seats. It has a low roof with the truck, S412 offering high roof. The S402M which is the van listed has rear wheel drive as standard while the optional 4WD came in the S412 in 2010. It is fitted with a 1.5L 3SZ-VE engine and five-speed manual or optional four-speed automatic. It also has 5 seats with a cargo space on the rear.

name: Toyota Fielder
description: Hybrid Synergy Drive, a new tech adopted by Toyota to supplement the power from its Internal Combustion Engine and to cut down on fuel costs especially in urban driving as it includes increased starts and stops because of road traffic. This is extreme convenience from what the car actually offers in its interior. This is just the right car for reliable and highly convenient drives!

name: BMW X1
description: BMW X1 began its first production in 2009 with the E84 model code. It is currently at its 3rd generation after the 2nd gen ended production in 2021. It is based on the Modular front-wheel drive based UKL2 platform that is used with BMW and MINI models, a modular meant to increase interior space and boot space in smaller size model cars. They are both available in front wheel and All Wheel drive systems with the front adopting the SDrive naming and the All Wheel adopting XDrive naming. This unit is an SDrive 18i meaning it runs a 1.5L B38 straight-3 turbocharged engine and drives the power to front wheels.

name: Volvo V40 T5 AWD 'Cross-Country' Spec
description: Volvo V40 Cross Country was produced from 2013 to 2019. It is different from the normal V40 in terms of engine size and body design. It has protective body panels, bigger wheels and tyres with an increased ride height. Some variants of the V40 Cross Country feature 2-wheel drive. The T4 and T5 variants of V40 Cross Country features Haldex Gen-5 All Wheel Drive as an optional feature along with Hill descent control. It runs a 2.0L of model code B4204T11 with power rating of 245hp and 350Nm of torque. You would look at it and think this is one good performer!

name: Honda Fit
description: Honda Fit is a go to hatchback for anyone looking for a fast yet reliable and spacious hatch. It scored a reliability score of 85 which makes it in the top 85th percentile. A convenient one at that!

name: Nissan Teana XL
description: The Teana XL is equipped with the 2.5L NA Petrol engine and is specced with Fabric seats, android infotainment display screen that is fitted with the touch screen features easing its use, dual zone climate controls gives the Co-Driver power to tune the AC as they wish, and steering wheel controls reduces distractions while driving by allowing the driver to control some of the car's features from the steering.

name: Volvo XC60 D4
description: Volvo's torque house, the XC60, D4, which has a D4204T5 turbocharged diesel engine producing 400Nm of Torque. The petrol variant has 350Nm of torque. It is specced with black leather seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, a polished metal trimming, and powered seats with memory function.

name: Audi Q5 2.0T
description: Audi Q5 Type 8R is the first generation of the Q5 that began production in 2008 with the 2nd Generation beginning in 2017. The first generation was done a facelift in 2012 and carried through all the models after then to 2016. Front and rear lights were redesigned and the engines uprated with the increasing need for power and efficiency. The unit listed has half leather seats that are powered, a multifunctional steering wheel, Audi MMI infotainment system that was updated in the facelift.

name: Audi Q5 2.0T QUATTRO S-LINE
description: Quattro, All Wheel Drive, equipped in the Q5, is the kind of drivetrain system you need in any form of terrain. Quattro distributes power to all wheels depending on their power needs. This feature by Audi prevents skidding in the a wet terrain. The unit has half leather seats, dual zone climate controls, hill descent control, a multifunctional steering wheel among other features.

name: BMW 320i "F30"
description: BMW 320i "F30" began sales in 2012 after the first few models including the 328i, 335i, 330i, and 340i that were produced in 2011. The F30 is the sedan version that used the N20B20 engine replaced by the B48B20 from 2015 to 2019. This is an M-Sport version has better looks with M-Sport badging on the seats, door-frame floor, and front side fendors. It is fitted with Powered leather seats with memory function, dual zone climate controls, Multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, BMW iDrive infotainment system, and different drives modes to choose from including Sport and Eco mode.

name: Lexus RX450H
description: Lexus RX450H, the unit listed, falls under the third generation which was produced between 2008 and 2015 before the 4th gen began production same year. It has an updated transmission that can lock up its torque converter from 2nd through 6th gears to improve fuel economy. The drag coefficient was decreased, exterior dimensions increased with cargo room getting an increment as well. Smart Access, keyless entry and start system, and UV reducing exterior glass were some of the features made standard. Safety was improved with twin chamber front passenger airbags, side torso airbags for the front row, side curtain airbags for front and rear rows, knee airbags for front row, and active headrests, to protect the passengers from whiplash injuries used to protect the passenger. Hill Assist control that prevents the car from rolling back on a steep incline is standard.

name: Toyota Hilux D CAB
description: The Toyota Hilux is a jack of all trades. From hauling, carrying cargo, and attending serious meetings, it is a wonderful car to have by your side. From its interior, you see 5 leather seats, climate controls, an automatic transmission gearbox, and steering wheel controls. It also has both front and rear bullbar and sufficient carrying capacity on the covered cargo space. It is also a diesel powered car which defines its durability with tough work!

name: Audi Q5
description: A uniquely colored Audi Q5 that is sleek and modern with its luxurious design features. From the exterior to the interior, the Q5 is designed to impress and is equipped with advanced safety and technology features. This includes adaptive cruise control, a rearview camera, and Audi pre-sense basic.

name: Smart Fortwo
description: This variant of Smart Fortwo is equipped with fabric seats that are in two-tone and bucket-styled, and has a moonroof. It is a city car produced by Mercedes Benz since 1998 until the year 2024. It is now in its third generation that began in 2014 and is available as a 3-door 2-seater internally designated as the C453 and a 5-door 4-seater internally designated the W453. The C453 is marketed as Fortwo while the W453 as Forfour. This car was jointly produced with Renault and was powered by a choice of two 1.0L or a 0.9L turbo petrol engine. This runs the 0.9L engine option with a power rating of 89bhp. It runs a "twinamic" dual-clutch automatic transmission different from the "soft touch" used previously. It also got to fulfil Kei Cars class requirements in Japan despite it being a non-Japanese car.

name: Smart Fortwo
description: Here is a Brabus Exclusive Smart Fortwo which is a city car produced by Mercedes Benz since 1998 until year 2024. It is now in its third generation that began in 2014 and is available as a 3-door 2-seater internally designated as the C453 and a 5-door 4-seater internally designated the W453. The C453 is marketed as Fortwo while the W453 as Forfour. This car was jointly produced with Renault and was powered by a choice of two 1.0L or a 0.9L turbo petrol engine. This runs the 0.9L engine option with a power rating of 89bhp. It runs a "twinamic" dual-clutch automatic transmission different from the "soft touch" used previously. It also got to fulfil Kei Cars class requirements in Japan despite it being a non-Japanese car.

name: Smart Fortwo
description: With a Sunroof, the two occupants of this car get to enjoy even more in this premium city car Mercedes produced, Smart Fortwo Passion. This car was jointly produced with Renault and runs the 0.9L engine option with a power rating of 89bhp. It runs a "twinamic" dual-clutch automatic transmission different from the "soft touch" used previously. It also got to fulfil Kei Cars class requirements in Japan despite it being a non-Japanese car.

name: Mitsubishi Outlander PHEV
description: This is a Plug In Hybrid variant of the Outlander. It is an excellent SUV that delivers the best of what Mitsubishi intended to give its consumers ranging from economy to occupancy. It features a 5 seats occupancy capacity which is the case with Plug in variants. It drives all the 4 wheels which gives it an edge over any offroad terrains. It also has an eco mode that optimises fuel consumption.

name: Mitsubishi Outlander / 7 SEATS
description: The Outlander is an excellent SUV that delivers the best of what Mitsubishi intended to give its consumers ranging from economy to occupancy. It features a 7 seats occupancy that has foldable third row seats that extends the boot space when the third row is not occupied. It drives all the 4 wheels which gives it an edge over any offroad terrains. It also has an eco mode that optimises fuel consumption.

name: Mazda CX5
description: Mazda CX-5 2.0L, a new generation that was sold as from 2017 just after the 1st generation began in 2012. It features a totally new design and an improved set of technologies that made the CX-5 more beautiful and highly loved by consumers. There are a number of engines ranging from the 2.0L and 2.5L petrol engine & a 2.2L diesel turbocharged engine, all with Skyactiv technologies. The unit listed features the 2.0L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine that is easy going in this class, it is also equipped with a good number of technologies that make it very convenient for consumers!

name: Honda Vezel "RS" Hybrid
description: The Vezel RS Hybrid is specced with a 1.5L petrol engine with a complimentary hybrid system, daytime running lights, Infotainment system display screen, reverse camera, Multifunctional steering wheel, and foglamps.

name: Mercedes Benz GLE 350D
description: One of the best mid-size SUVs by Mercedes, the GLE350d Coupe. It comes specced with leather seats with heating functionality both in the front and the rear, memory seats function, Mercedes speedtronic cruise control system, active parking assist system, ambient lighting, multiple climate controls, and engine immobilizer among other features.

name: BMW X3 XDrive 20d M-SPORT / PANORAMIC SUNROOF
description: BMW X3 is classified as a Sports Activity Vehicle. This is where luxury has been fully invested by BMW. The reason BMW has fitted a lot of equipments on the X3 ranging from hill descent control, front & rear camera view, Autohold brake function, electric parking brake, Front heated seats, parking sensors, radar guided adaptive cruise control, ECO Pro modes, powered memory seats, to the multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: Harrier is premium SUV by Toyota that accomodates consumers who still love Toyota but would want extras of a comfortable and convenient SUV. Toyota Harrier offers that. From powered seats, hybrid Synergy drive that by far saves on fuel by utilizing its hybrid system and maximising on fuel efficiency, high clearance, dual zone climate controls, a multifunctional steering wheel, push to start button, and Traction control that is practical in handling multiple terrains.

name: Toyota CH-R
description: The CH-R is a compact crossover SUV produced by Toyota since 2016. It is produced in the same platform as the E210 Corolla Series and lies between Toyota Yaris and Corolla Cross in the same SUV lineup. In the Japanese market which we majorly source our cars from, the CH-R is powered a choice of either the 1.2L turbocharged petrol engine or the 1.8L hybrid variant. It comes in S, S-LED, G, S-T and G-T trims where the S, S-LED and G trims are powered with the 1.2-litre turbo while S-T and G-T trims run the 1.8L. It is one of the best crossovers by Toyota especially for individuals who are after fuel economy.

name: Subaru Legacy B4 / SUNROOF
description: Subaru Legacy did a bit of an upgrade in the 6th Gen 2.5L flat four FB25 engine by uprating it to 173bhp from the 5th Generation that ended in 2013 running 169bhp. The 3.6L flat six EZ36D remained unchanged running 252bhp. The slight change in power rating might not seem like it can work a lot of magic but sure makes a change.

name: Nissan Vanette
description: The Vanette is a very practical car in a lot of dimensions. One can use it as a cargo space, another can use it commercially to carry school children. Its 1.8L engine has enough torque to handle any of these tasks.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The CX-5 has a redefined design both from the interior to the exterior and drives perfectly with the tweaked driving styles. The engine is interestingly powerful as well, a torque of 418Nm makes acceleration and overtaking an easy task!

name: Nissan Teana XL
description: Nissan Teana XL in Japan utilizes the 2.5L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine while in other markets as in Thailand, it uses the 2.0L NA Petrol engine. It is specced with Fabric seats, android infotainment display screen that is fitted with the touch screen features easing its use, dual zone climate controls gives the Co-Driver power to tune the AC as they wish, and steering wheel controls reduces distractions while driving by allowing the driver to control some of the car's features from the steering.

name: Toyota Voxy
description: An excellently reliable minivan, Toyota Voxy. It is a Minivan with two rear sliding doors opening up a 6 seats occupancy with both the third and 2nd row seats being foldable. Comfort is what sells more in this minivan. The seats have leather materials well angled for maximum sitting comfort, and the space between the floor and the car's roof allows it to accomodate all heights of individuals.

name: Toyota FJ CRUISER
description:
The FJ Cruiser has been in
production from 2006 to 2022. It
is available in two
configurations one driving the
rear wheels and the other four
wheels. It is a very rugged SUV
meant for the offroads and
comfortable for on-road. It uses
a high-mounted double wishbone
front suspension and stabilizer
bar, and a 4-link rear
suspension with lateral rod with
coil springs and stabilizer bar
A perfect build for an offroad
car. The engine is a high power
engine running a 4.0L 1GR-FE V6
petrol engine fitted with Dual
VVT-i technology producing 260hp and 367Nm of torque. This power gets stopped by 'powered' front four-piston and rear two-piston disc brakes. To keep it safe as
it is made on the body-on-frame
chassis, it is equipped with
Anti-lock brake system,
Electronic brakeforce
distribution, Brake assist, and
Vehicle Stability control.

name: Peugeot 508 1.6L
description: The 508 is a large or mid-size family car produced by Peugeot since 2010. They were produced in both sedan and station wagon variants with the Station Wagon named the 508 SW. This car favoured its passengers more with the shorter front overhang and a longer passenger compartment which makes it more comfortable. You do not miss Volvo's praise with the history it has as with the 504 and a number of models used even by the government. Its market has widely grown since inception.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The CX-5 is specced with Rear Vehicle Monitoring system, traction control system, adaptive frontlight system, i-stop function, and a petrol engine variant among other specs.

name: Toyota Mark X
description: This Mark X is specced with fabric seats that are unique for these makes, dual zone climate controls, cup holders, steering wheel controls, an interior wood trimming, and interesting drivertrain features including snow mode that prevents skidding by reducing engine power, sport mode that increases engine power, and an eco mode, a fuel efficiency feature, that serves to save on fuel consumption.

name: Volvo V60 T5
description: Volvo V60 was first introduced into the market in 2010 with the second generation beginning in 2018. It underwent a facelift in 2014 with the newer version being more sleek and appealing. This unit comes fitted with heated seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, a premium surround sound system that's arguably one of the best, and dual exhaust tailpipes.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI 1.4L
description: The 1.4L variant of the Golf TSI offers a good blend of performance, fuel economy, and reliability. The unit is specced with fabric seats, an android infotainment display screen, cup holders for both front occupants, a mechanical parking brake, and convenient side mirror indicators.

name: Nissan Sylphy
description: The Sylphy is specced with auto hazard warning, updated NissanConnect, revised steering & suspension system, fabric seat material, and dual zone climate controls.

name: Mercedes Benz E220d
description: Mercedes has always been the leading in terms of class, safety and looks. The W212 E220d is a testament to that. From its eye-catching sleek exterior design to its luxurious interior, with features such as leather seats, and advanced safety features like collision warning and lane departure warning, it is the perfect car for anyone looking for a reliable vehicle that offers a comfortable driving experience and impressive performance.

name: Subaru Forester
description: This Subaru Forester is specced with fabric seats, push-start ignition, Multifunctional steering wheel, android infotainment display system, dual zone climate controls, rear armrest with cupholders, and Subaru's eyesight system. It also has heated seats and X-Mode for offroading adventures.

name: Mitsubishi Pajero Sport
description: Pajero Sport is a Mid-size SUV produced by Mitsubishi Motors. It used the nameplate Pajero since 1996 until its 3rd Gen when it adopted the Pajero Sport or Shogun Sport. Its 3rd gen began in 2015 and major changes include the use of 4N15 2.4L Mivec engine that is slightly smaller by about 34cc from the previous 4D56. It is also more powerful by about 23% more torque doing now 430Nm from 350Nm. It also adopted Toyota's Aisin TL-80SN/TL-80NF 8-speed automatic transmission from what was used previously, its 5 speed INVECS-II automatic transmission. It also gets Mitsubishi's S-AWC all-wheel drive system that is available for 4 wheel drive variants.

name: Toyota Fielder 1.5 "G"
description: Toyota Fielder is available in a station wagon body style which means you have more space both at passenger spaces and boot space. This gives the option of using this car for multiple tasks including commercially carrying cargo whose capacity is extended because of the car's body style, commercially for moving people from one point to another as it is a very capable car, and in a corporate using it to get to work and running official errands. An excellent multi-tasker!

name: Toyota Fielder 1.5 "G"
description: Toyota Filder G coded NZE161 runs the 1.5L 1NZ-FE Naturally Aspirated petrol engine with a power rating of 109hp. There are other engine variants such as the 1.8L found in the S Trim. It is also specced with some premium safety features such as the Anti-collision warning assist and lane departure assist.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TX
description: A well rated SUV whose reliability and durability we cannot for once doubt as we have seen them traverse the whole nation during campaign trails. They easily manage to cruise through any terrain as it is fully engaged on the 4WD System and together with its high clearance of 220mm, you get a perfect offroader. Long distances with the Prado will not have you breaking your back as the seats are very comfortable.

name: Subaru Forester XT
description: This Subaru Forester is specced with half leather seats, push-start ignition, Multifunctional steering wheel, android infotainment display system, dual zone climate controls, rear armrest with cupholders, and Subaru's eyesight system. It also has heated seats and X-Mode for offroading adventures.

name: Mazda Demio
description: Mazda has constantly improved its diesel engines overtime. The 1.5L diesel engine has an impressive amount of torque that compares to sedans and even close to some SUVs. It's been quite reliable and easy to maintain. It also comes with the best price in town.

name: Toyota Premio 1.8L
description: The 2010 Toyota Premio was the first Facelift done on the 2nd Generation of Toyota Premio. These upgrades sustained the 2nd gen Premio onwards. Improvements done made the Premio look sharper and aggressive. The engine also was improved from the 2ZR-FE to Valvematic 2ZR-FE which made a lot of improvements on its fuel economy to 19Kms per Liter. This unit has an interior wood trimming, push to start button, android infotainment display screen, and climate controls.

name: Jeep Wrangler
description: This is the one of the best offroad machines to ever appear in our markets, 3rd generation Jeep wrangler that came in, in 2006 under the development of Daimler Chrysler and was developed under a clean-sheet design of the body, frame, and suspension. This generation of Wrangler Unlimited Sports came with power windows, remote power door locks, navigation, and electronically detachable sway bars on some models. The Wrangler carries the seriousness an offroader deserves. A 4WD system and a high torque engine is all you need to fulfil your offroad adventures!

name: Nissan Sylphy
description: Nissan Sylphy went into its third Gen in 2012. Its generations began in 2000 with the 4th Generation beginning in 2019. In 2012, Nissan wanted to reduce production costs which necessitated them to merge production of Nissan Sentra in its 7th Gen and Sylphy. In 2014 an update was done that included auto hazard warning, updated NissanConnect with Android and Apple Carplay, and revised steering & suspension system. This unit offers fabric seat material, and dual zone climate controls.

name: Volvo XC90
description: This is the 2nd Gen XC90 T5 that appeared in 2014 before officially launching in 2015. 1st Edition of an all-new XC90 units were produced in 2014 with a total of 1927 numbered cars selling out in only 47hours. The First edition models featured an Onyx black finish and every other feature Volvo could offer. This 2017 model also features a number of features which are a big deal including a panoramic sunroof, leather seats with third row-seating capacity with both the front and rear occupants having a heating functionality, Premium surround sound system that makes the cabin feel like a large Orchestral theatre, steering wheel controls, and all the safety systems Volvo have ever come up with including City safety and Run-off-road protection package that controls the seats comfort level and belts adjustment to deliver a comfortable offroading experience.

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: This is the ultimate crossover from Nissan, the XTRAIL performs close to the Xterra and the Pathfinder. Its sister in the North American Market was named Nissan Rogue. The 3rd gen model made a huge improvement from the previous old plain design to a better good looking urban oriented car. A hundred percent surety of you not hesitating to buy this car when you experience how it drives.

name: Subaru Outback / SUNROOF
description: This Subaru Outback is powered by a 2.5L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine, leather seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, android infotainment display system, dual zone climate controls, and a Symmetrical All Wheel Drive setup.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TZ-G
description: This Landcruiser Prado TZ-G comes with a very rare spec of the Landcruiser Prado J120 series, the 4.0L 1GR-FE V6 petrol engine. It replaced the 5VZ-FE engine while adopting a 5 speed automatic transmission in late 2005. The J150 series, 4th Gen of Landcruiser Prado was sold from 2010 after the 3nd Gen J120 ended production. The TZ-G gets a wide range of specs including cruise control, locking differentials, Downhill Assist Control, Sport & Comfort modes, 2-position memory seats, a sunroof, and 7 seats with the 3rd row being foldable.

name: Toyota Mark X
description: This Toyota Mark X is specced with 5 fabric seats, dual zone climate controls, polished metal trimming, steering wheel controls, android infotainment display screen, armrests, and fog lights.

name: Toyota Probox
description: This Toyota Probox is powered by a 1500cc naturally aspirated petrol engine producing 109hp and 141Nm of torque which is sufficient for cargo and passenger transportation. On the interior, it has fabric seats, an FM RADIO system, climate controls, and traction control.

name: Mazda CX3
description: Mazda CX3 is an excellent choice if you're looking for a reliable and affordable small crossover. It has a sleek, sporty design, great fuel economy, and plenty of features to make your everyday drives more enjoyable. It also offers impressive safety ratings, advanced technology, and a comfortable interior that makes it a great choice

name: Subaru Levorg 1.6L
description: Subaru Levorg introduced in 2014 has proven to give owners an excellent ownership experience with good performance from the 'small' 1600cc Turbocharged Petrol Engine. 'Small' is an understatement! Underrating a Levorg on the road might not turn out so well.

name: BMW 320i 2.2L
description: This is the 4th Gen of the 3 series that was produced between the years of 1998 and 2006 and succeeded the E36 series that stopped production in 2000. It came as an improvement from the previous E36 series as it was 70% more rigid than the E36. With better integrated electronics using CAN BUS system with engine, transmission, and stability control communicated via the CAN BUS. It runs a 2.2L M54B22 inline-6 petrol engine with a power rating of 210Nm of Torque.

name: Audi Q3 2.0T QUATTRO S-LINE
description: A number of Q3s in our market are the 1.4L Non Quattro versions. This is a premium one, a 2.0L TFSI QUATTRO version with power ratings of 170 horsepower and 280Nm of torque, very impressive. The half leather seats come with thigh support for the front occupants and are also powered. It is an S-LINE version which means it is also aesthetically impressive.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The W205 Mercedes Benz C200 made a debut in 2014 bringing in an all new architecture platform called the Modular Rear Architecture Platform that adopted the use of Aluminum throughout the car body structure which gives it a very light body compared to the W204 that looked and was actually heavy. Some of the standard features that came with this new Gen include 9 airbags, Collision prevention assist, attention and adaptive brake assist, and an electric parking brake among other features.

name: Smart Fortwo
description: Smart Fortwo is a city car produced by Mercedes Benz since 1998 until the year  2024. It is now in its third generation that began in 2014 and is available as a 3-door 2-seater internally designated as the C453 and a 5-door 4-seater internally designated the W453. The C453 is marketed as Fortwo while the W453 as Forfour. This car was jointly produced with Renault and was powered by a choice of two 1.0L or a 0.9L turbo petrol engine. This runs the 0.9L engine option with a power rating of 89bhp. It runs a "twinamic" dual-clutch automatic transmission different from the "soft touch" used previously. It also got to fulfil Kei Cars class requirements in Japan despite it being a non-Japanese car.

name: Volvo XC60
description: Volvo was created with a tune of Landrover's offroading capabilities and Volvo's technologies. This makes it one of the best Multipurpose, in the sense of one can operate them at different terrains and for different events, and it will never let one down. The aesthetics are on point, extremely well done, safety earns is a solid 5 star rating from both official tests and consumer reports, and performance is top notch, a marvel. The unit listed is the 2nd Gen that began production in 2017. An Inscription T5 AWD Setup Volvo XC60, quite a beauty to look at. It runs a B4204T 2000cc engine doing 251 horsepowers and 350Nm of torque in an engine orientation of inline 4 plus a turbocharger. Volvo is your next home!

name: Audi A3
description: This Audi A3 has a 1800cc engine variant that is quite strong compared to the 1400cc variant.The interior is fitted with fabric seats and Audi MMI infotainment system, multifunctional steering wheel and a dual zone climate control.

name: Porsche Cayenne
description: Cayenne S Turbo adopts an enhanced 8-speed ZF8HP shiftable automatic transmission gearbox, ventilated front and rear seats, pre-sense safety system, Carbon interior package, sports chrono package, BOSE surround sound system,soft close doors,biege leather interior and a multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Mazda CX5
description: The CX-5 has a redefined design both from the interior to the exterior and drives perfectly with the tweaked driving styles. The engine is interestingly powerful as well, a torque of 258Nm makes acceleration and overtaking an easy task!

name: Mazda Atenza
description: Mazda did an excellent work on creating the design on the Atenza which makes it among the top beautiful designs in a comparable class, in the automobiles industry. Comfort was not left out, driving the Atenza feels like an S-Class of sorts, as bumps or rubles are never a bother. The leather seats that are heated both in the front and the rear coupled with the dual zone climate controls make up a highly enjoyable ride. It goes on to have a retractable blind at the car's rear glass shield. Safety begins with lane keep assist, adaptive cruise control, and Blindspot Monitoring Assist necessary during lane change.

name: Mazda Axela
description: Mazda Axela offers a very good balance of efficiency, flexibility, and performance. Giving very efficient fuel consumptions and effective maintenance costs, flexible use scenarios in all kinds of environments, and good performance output.

name: Honda Jade
description: Honda Jade is a compact MPV first produced in 2013 mainly for the Chinese Market but has since penetrated other markets including the Japanese in 2015. It is a 5 door wagon with configurations of 5 or 4+2 individuals. Quite spacious and classy, and turns out to be a good consumer as well.

name: Subaru Outback
description: Subaru Outback's design inspired the evolution of a passenger car and a Sports Utility Vehicle which makes the Outback excel in the markets it serve. It has a stiff chassis making it more rugged and a very spacious interior that is comfortable making it very accomodating to its occupants. It a runs a big 2.5L Naturally Aspirated engine which performs well with no issues and the Symmetrical AWD system does magic on terrain aggression.

name: Ford Kuga Titanium
description: The Ford Kuga Titanium is designed to provide a smooth and comfortable ride. It features a suspension system that provides a great balance between comfort and control, while the interior is designed to be comfortable and spacious.

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: This Nissan XTRAIL came equipped with all features a top XTRAIL would come bearing. It is fitted with 7-Leather seats with heating functionality, a panoramic sunroof, 4 wheel independent suspension, disc-brakes with anti-lock braking system, and 4-wheel drive system, rear center console doubling up as armrests, lane departure warning assist, frontal collision warning system, and a panoramic sunroof.

name: Nissan XTRAIL "NT32"
description: Nissan XTRAIL NT32 is the 3rd gen of Nissan XTRAIL that has been widely used in the Kenyan Market since the entry of the first generation NT30 in 2000. It is a very capable offroader as it is fitted with optional 4WD select that enables one to drive on only two wheels to save on fuel, leather seats that are super comfortable, Nissan pure drive for environmental friendly drives, and heated seats for warming up during the cold.

name: BMW 523i
description: F10 Series of BMW 523i was first sold in 2011 with the series in general coming with major improvements that included dual Clucth transmission as used with the M5, 8 speed automatic transmission gearbox, and the turbocharged V8 engine as with the S63 engine among other specs. This unit is specced with 5 leather seats, parking sensors, Autohold brake function, auto start stop feature, and a 2.0L N20B20 inline-four turbocharged engine that was comparatively better than the N52/N53 NA six cylinder engines.

name: BMW X6 "F16" XDRIVE 35i
description: Production of the 2nd Gen BMW X6 began in 2014 with sales being done same year towards the end. It came with new improvements including a new 8 speed automatic transmission gearbox and a larger luggage compartment. The X6 became the first BMW to use Dynamic Performance Control system which works together with XDrive All Wheel Drive. Dynamic Performance Control is a drivetrain and chassis control system that work to regulate traction and correct over and understeer by actively spreading out drive forces across the rear axle. Torque vectoring happens laterally between the front and rear wheels and also from side to side at the rear which improves agility and stability. It runs a 3.0 N55 Straight 6 turbocharged petrol engine.

name: Toyota Mark X
description: Mark X has had a huge support in the car scene for its versatility among car enthusiasts. Some have trolled it, but many have loved it. The unit is powered by a 2500cc Naturally Aspirated engine producing just more than 200 horsepower which is impressive for a two wheel drive system. It is also quite comfortable with its leather covers seats and a spacious legroom for all occupants. Driving is definitely a joy with steering wheel controls to assist in manoeuvring car systems.

name: Volkswagen Touareg Hybrid
description: The Hybrid version of Volkswagen Touareg made a debut at the 2010 Geneva Motor Show and different other Motor Shows that year. It used a 3.0L V6 Supercharged Hybrid petrol engine with the engine producing 328hp and 440Nm of torque while the electric motor produces 45hp. The combined output is 375hp and 580Nm of torque. It does a quick acceleration of 0-100kph in 5.8S which is quite fast and reliable for the big body SUV!

name: Mazda CX-5 2.5L AWD
description: The new era of the CX-5 came with two famous engine in which the diesel engine has been the go-to by many consumers. The 2.5L petrol engine is a good option for those who would prefer a petrol choice to the diesel one. It has a power rating of 187hp which is quite descent for this SUV. It has some premium specs including heated steering wheel, head up display, heated seats both for the front occupants and the rear, two-position memory seats, Blindspot monitoring assist, auto start stop system, parking sensors, and and lane departure assist.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D
description: Mazda CX-5 when it was first introduced in 2012 featuring a number of great technologies and improved engines built to reduce emissions and fuel consumption. Skyactiv technologies, advanced production platform that is rigid and lightweight. An excellent car that is a super alternative to a number of crossover SUVs such as the Toyota Harrier.

name: Suzuki Swift Sport 1.6
description: Earlier in 2011 at the Australian International Motor Show, Suzuki Swift Sport was previewed by the Swift S-Concept. The major difference between the Sport and the base Swift is the engine capacity that was increased from the 1.2L to a 1.6L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine with a power rating of 134bhp. It also gets a 7 speed manual mode with paddle shifters that enhances its sporty nature.

name: Toyota Voxy
description: Toyota Voxy is a Minivan with two rear sliding doors opening up a 7 seats occupancy with both the third and 2nd row seats being foldable. Comfort is what sells more in this minivan. The seats have fabric seats well angled for maximum sitting comfort, and the space between the floor and the car's roof allows it to accomodate all heights of individuals.

name: Range Rover Classic 3.5L V8
description: The first generation Range Rovers were named as Classics to distinguish them from the predecessors. The first models were produced in only 2-door models until 1981 when the 4-door models were introduced. On introduction, it was not meant to be a luxury vehicle as they were designed with fairly basic utilitarian interiors. It used the body-on-frame design and coil springs different from the leaf springs that were popular then. It was also fitted with a permanent 4-wheel drive system, 4-wheel disc brakes, and runs a 3.5L V8 petrol engine. Definitely a true Classic!

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D AWD
description: Mazda CX-5 has proven over time to improve in its reliability over the years, hence positive customer reviews as the years go by. The new generation, 2nd since production in 2012, has grown to be a fast selling unit by Mazda. Its improving design, body size, convenience features, and safety features has made it rank among the top purchased SUVs. Mechanics and repair shops have given it a rating of 82 of 100 which makes it one of the top reliable cars as it ranks 1st of 26 Midsize SUVs in comparable class. You won't go wrong with the CX-5.

name: Volkswagen Golf 1.4L TSI
description: The 1.4L Turbocharged Petrol Engine gives a better drive feel compared to the younger brother with the 1.2L turbocharged engine. The 20Nm torque difference will give you a better head start over any car of the same class which gives the Golf TSI 1.4L some leverage.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI 1.4L
description: Volkswagen Golf TSI is the perfect starter pack to begin German life with if you are looking for a great budget car that goes easy on your pockets both on fuel and maintenance & excels in delivering reliability with durability. The 1.4L turbocharged petrol engine is a fast one and quickly dashes whenever prompted. It is also easy to maintain with a few services to be done during its service periods. It is very descent one as well with practical sense in both office and recreational activities.

name: Landrover Discovery IV
description: Discovery 4 came into production from 2009 to 2016 being an updated version of Disco 3. Upgrades included the change of front and rear lights, a newly restyled front grille and bumper that made the car much smoother as seen with the new models of Range Rover Sport from 2010. Body coloured wheel arches and bumpers matching those of Discovery 3 were retained. Fuel economy was also improved for this generation. It is specced with leather seats that are powered and heated, an analogue display clock at the dash center, Multifunctional steering wheel, hill descent assist, multiple terrain select, traction control, and an adjustable ride height.

name: Jeep Compass "MK49"
description: Jeep Compass together with the Patriot were among the first Crossover SUVs by Jeep. They carried a simpler definition of trail rated SUVs by Jeep which have been more focused on creating serious offroad cars. The Crossovers favored individuals who loved the brand but wanted something they could even go on official business with, without looking out of place in such setups.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D AWD
description: Mazda CX-5 2.2D found its way into the hearts of many Kenyan automobiles consumers. Enthusiasts have been impressed by the range of features it offers beginning from the 2200cc turbocharged diesel engine with Skyactiv technologies that is very powerful and favours long distance travellers, and excellent clearance that favours frequent offroaders.

name: Mazda Demio
description:
This is among the first models
of Mazda Demio to use the
super-high compression high fuel
efficient engine with
consumption levels of up to
30kms a liter in a perfect test
environment. It runs the 1.3L
Skyactiv-G P3-VPS engine with
power figures of 83hp and 113Nm
of torque. It features a special
equipment called the i-DM
(intelligent Drive Master) which
monitors one's driving habits
and the effects to the car's
passengers which then warns the
driver if they deviate from
their normal driving habits
hence improving the overall
driving practice

name: Toyota Premio
description: Toyota Premio is a luxurious sedan popular within a large number of individuals who liked the Corolla series. It adopts a sporty and a classy design that attracts the old monies as we have seen in our rural areas. They are quite reliable and efficient which makes them trusted by consumers who could go days without service. They are bulletproof in a way!

name: Porsche Cayenne 3.0L V6 / PANORAMIC SUNROOF
description: A combination of Porsche's build, versatility, and engineering birthed a torque house, the 3.0 V6 diesel engine, with an acceleration of about 7 seconds from 0-100kmh. Overtaking is definitely not a task. Heated seats both in the front and the rear, a classy interior wood trimming, an aftermarket sound system, and a panoramic sunroof are some of its specs.

name: Range Rover Evoque
description: Range Rover Evoque, a subcompact luxury crossover SUV meant for both urban and off-road experiences. It performs well in the city and excels as well offroading as Land Rover has done well in creating a reliable most efficient Terrain Response system including Grass, Gravel, Snow, and Sand modes. It has specially tweaked comfort to the standards Land Rover has maintained over the years and delivers great performance!

name: Isuzu FRR
description: Isuzu FRR is a large payload heavy duty truck that can accomodate up to 7  with a total gross weight of 11 Tonnes. It runs a powerhouse, 5200cc diesel engine, coupled to a manual transmission gearbox. These two combinations make it a powerful all-type cargo truck.

name: Toyota Vitz
description: Toyota Vitz, 3rd Gen XP130, features a much spacious interior compared to the previous generation, the XP90. This gives it a bonus in the comfort it offers to all of its occupants. It also looks a bit sportier as much as it is not a fully sports car as the Vitz RS variant is. The seats in this are made of fabric material coloured in a bright colour which makes the car very welcoming.

name: Nissan Skyline
description: Nissan Skyline has created a popular show for itself since its inception and use in major Movies, the unforgettable scene being with Paul Walker's Nissan Skyline R34. Its big engine has been terribly admired complimented by its premium looks that are aerodynamically optimised. The interior offers a a premium driving feel making the car overally pleasant to drive!

name: Subaru Legacy B4
description: The 6th Gen of Subaru Legacy came with an upgrade in its 2.5L flat four FB25 engine by uprating it to 173bhp from the 5th Generation that ended in 2013 running 169bhp. The 3.6L flat six EZ36D remained unchanged running 252bhp. The slight change in power rating might not seem like it can work a lot of magic but sure makes a change.

name: Mercedes Benz E250
description: The E250 has a lot of value residing in it considering what was done by Daimler in its Mid-Cycle refresh that incorporated a Blindspot assist, lane keeping assist, Pre-Safe with attention assist, and integrated LED DRLs. This unit features leather seats, dual zone climate controls, Multifunctional steering wheel, and side mirror indicators.

name: Toyota Fielder
description: Toyota Fielder is a very popular station wagon that has proven its reliability and durability over time. They have been used as family cars, commercial carriers, and even on official activities for their relevance in each of these activities. Its roomy interior gives it an edge over other station wagons for the purposes it serve. It comes with a 1.5L petrol engine with a power rating of 110hp.

name: Nissan Juke
description: Nissan Juke made a debut in 2010 as a production vehicle. In its first year of selling, it surpassed the manufacturer's expectation 10 fold and since then it has been received well in the market. It has been purchased in high numbers in Kenya also making it among best selling cars that some have criticised its shape, one that was inspired by a lot of history at Nissan. This unit comes with fabric seats, climate controls, android infotainment display screen, and a push to start button.

name: Audi A5
description: Audi's B9 generation definitely came with a new spice to it. Properly engineered curves with each serving a purpose aerodynamically, a virtual instrument cluster that definitely looks better than the traditional cluster, a sunroof that gives it a better visual look, a minimalistic modern interior, comfy bucket-styled heated leather seats, and a premium color make this A5 worth every coin!

name: Volkswagen Golf R Variant
description: The heart of Golf R reflects in its station wagon variant for family units that need more space on the interior especially the boot. It houses a 2.0L turbocharged EA888 engine that has been one of the best performing engines in recent times especially on track. This units also gets rear entertainment screens describing a proper family orientation.

name: Toyota Axio
description: An excellent car in the Toyota Corolla Lineup that a majority of users have been opting to purchase. It is a straight go-to easy car that pains its consumers less and they get to enjoy more of what Toyota has to offer in it.

name: Mazda Axela
description: The Mazda Axela is specced with fabric seats, cup holders both in the front and rear, Multifunctional steering wheel, climate controls, and a mechanical handbrake.

name: Mazda Demio 1.3L
description: Both a reliable and an excellent consumer. Mazda Demio is among the top generous cars with little to no hassle from purchasing it to maintenance. It is an excellent hatchback!

name: Toyota Porte
description: A simple spacious and room minivan by Toyota, the Porte. It is specced with sliding doors, climate controls, and foldable rear seats for extra space.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: If Mercedes' intention during its entry into the market with the W205 was to impress, then they scored a 100 percent. Half leather seats that are powered and heated, wood trimming, a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, and 3-position memory seats make up some of this car's specs. Beautifully designed exterior curves, analogue clock at the dash center, and an array of equipments make the C200 a car to behold!

name: Toyota Fielder 'G'
description: Toyota Filder G coded NZE161 runs the 1.5L 1NZ-FE Naturally Aspirated petrol engine with a power rating of 109hp. There are other engine variants such as the 1.8L found in the S Trim. It is also specced with some premium safety features such as the Anti-collision warning assist and lane departure assist.

name: Jeep Grand Cherokee 'TRAILHAWK'
description: The TRAILHAWK is a special offroad Grand Cherokee by Jeep that was based on Laredo back in 2013. Later on in 2017, the model year of the current listed unit, it was based on Grand Cherokee Limited. A few equipments separates it from the other trims, which makes it truly special for the offroads. Kevlar belted on-/-offroad tires, multi terrain select control coupled with QUADRA-LIFT air suspension system for ultimate comfort and safety of the car while offroading and on-roading, 18-inch dark grey wheels, and leather seats with microfibre stitchings. Definitely the best with the best price in town!

name: Jeep Grand Cherokee
description: The ultimate offroad machine with all equipments specifically made for the tough terrains. It carries with it excellence from the powerful 3.6L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine delivering power to an enhanced 4WD system. Super comfortable and capable even for on-roads, and perfectly engineered to last!

name: Nissan Teana XL
description: Nissan Teana XL in Japan utilizes the 2.5L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine while in other markets as in Thailand, it uses the 2.0L NA Petrol engine. It is specced with Fabric seats, android infotainment display screen that is fitted with the touch screen features easing its use, dual zone climate controls gives the Co-Driver power to tune the AC as they wish, and steering wheel controls reduces distractions while driving by allowing the driver to control some of the car's features from the steering.

name: Audi A3
description: Audi A3 is definitely a hot cake. Specced with a 1.4L Turbocharged petrol engine, you get to enjoy good power figures of up to 250Nm of torque making driving seamless and enjoyable. The fabric seats are definitely worth the comfort, and the general outlook of the A3 is worth every coin!

name: Subaru Forester NA / PANORAMIC SUNROOF
description: The Subaru Forester 2.0L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine version of the Forester is specced with a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, adaptive cruise control, Sports and Intelligent drive modes, tailgate memory height control, auto-start stop feature, XMode for handling tough terrains, dual zone climate controls, and a premium surround sound system.

name: Toyota Belta
description: Toyota Belta is the epitome of Corolla's low budget maintenance. It spends a little on fuel, mechanical maintenance and service, and is quite comfortable to anyone seeking simplicity. It has no complications, its driving is drive gear and go, and one can even service for themselves!

name: BMW X3 XDrive 20d M-SPORT / PANORAMIC SUNROOF
description: The diesel variant of BMW X3 is probably the best bet for long road trips. A powerful engine comes in handy with a comfortable and pleasurable interior that has leather seats, dual zone climate controls, a well-built music system, steering wheel controls to ease your driving, and paddles shifters to spice up the drive!

name: Nissan Sylphy
description: This is the third Gen of Nissan Sylphy that began production in 2012. Its generations began in 2000 with the 4th Generation beginning in 2019. In 2012, Nissan wanted to reduce production costs which necessitated them to merge production of Nissan Sentra in its 7th Gen and Sylphy. In 2014 an update was done that included auto hazard warning, updated NissanConnect with Android and Apple Carplay, and revised steering & suspension system. This unit offers fabric seat material, and dual zone climate controls.

name: Mazda Axela
description: The Axela is specced with fabric seats, Mazda i-stop system, Multifunctional steering wheel, android infotainment display system, dual zone climate controls, and cup holders as some of its specs.

name: Mazda Demio 1.3L
description: Mazda Demio has, before, participated in competitions for its 3rd and 4th generations being the winner in the Car of the Year Japan in 2014-2015 period and being among the top in the World Car Awards. This speaks a lot for this unit. Driving an Award winning unit sure feels majestic!

name: BMW X6 XDRIVE 35i
description:
The X6 is a mid size luxury
crossover SUV by BMW, that is
the originator of Sports
Activity Coupe because of its
sloping roof on the rear. It has
a very bold stance while
delivering all capabilities of
an SUV. With a 3.0L petrol engine, performance is guaranteed!

name: Toyota Harrier
description: Toyota Harrier has been an excellent family car since the beginning of days and still becomes an excellent SUV even as new generation models are produced. You hear of consumers who have owned it saying they can take it anywhere and easily come out, they truly mean it. Its clearance gives it an edge in any kind of terrain. Its engine also runs with zero challenges.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D
description: KF generation of the CX-5, 2nd since production in 2012, has grown to be a fast selling unit by Mazda. Its improving design, body size, convenience features, and safety features has made it rank among the top purchased SUVs. Mechanics and repair shops have given it a rating of 82 of 100 which makes it one of the top reliable cars as it ranks 1st of 26 Midsize SUVs in comparable class. You won't go wrong with the CX-5.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D
description: Probably the best crossover SUVs money can buy as seen with the consumer reviews. Be it a new car or a used car, you get the best of the car's comfort, reliability, convenience, and efficiency in fuel especially from the 2.2L diesel engine. It retains its market value overtime, and similarly giving its users constant value for their money throughout the ownership period.

name: Toyota Harrier Premium
description: A midsize crossover SUV in its 4th generation now that began in 2020, Toyota Harrier. It is a sister to the famous Lexus RX and the RAV4 XA40 Series with which the 3rd gen Toyota Harrier adopts some of its components from. Harrier is famous among family setups which Toyota understands by fitting Toyota Safety Sense P safety system which includes cruise control, lane departure assist, pre-collision system, and automatic high beam which was standard. You are assured of your safety in the Harrier.

name: Toyota Landcruiser "ZX" 200 Series 4.6L V8
