description: Toyota Landcruiser ZX is what a Toyota with everything feels like. With a Sunroof, 7 seats occupancy, front heated leather seats, an automatic transmission gearbox, side steps which is a standard equipment for this series, roof rails, fog lights, and the Old money interior trimming of wood, this is the epitome of Toyota's luxury in the actual Toyota nameplate. Driving this unit gives you more understanding of why an example of politicians really adore this car.

name: Volvo XC60
description: Volvo's powerhouse, the XC60, D4, which has a D4204T5 turbocharged diesel engine producing 400Nm of Torque. The petrol variant has 350Nm of torque. It is specced with black leather seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, a wooden trimming, and powered seats with memory function.

name: Ford Ranger
description: Ford Ranger Wildtrak is specced with a 3.2L Duratorq TDCi engine which is hell of a powerhouse. Steering wheel controls, android infotainment display screen, climate controls, heated seats, and a spacious cargo space make up the car's specs. It has excellent clearance making offroading pretty easy and on-road is also handled excellently.

name: Toyota Hilux D CAB
description: Toyota Hilux is a Cargo carriage powerhouse. It is meant for all the crazy loads one can ever think of. The 2.5L turbocharged diesel engine with the 6-Speed automatic transmission gearbox does the magic. It is powered by a 2.5L 2KD-FTV engine which is the 2nd generation of KD engine series. It has an upgraded Common Rail system that improved its fuel injection to ultra high pressures reducing emissions.

name: Audi A6 2.0L QUATTRO C7.5
description: An A6 one can mistake for an RS6. With RS6 badging and premium rims, this is one of the best good looking Audi A6s in town. This is the C7.5 generation that began sales in 2016. It adopted a different fascia and got improvements from the same line C7 gen. Quite an excellent visually and practically impressive!

name: Toyota Vitz
description: This is the 2nd facelift of Toyota Vitz which was done in 2017. Vitz is subcompact car produced by Toyota since 1999 until late 2019. It has achieved a lot of sales, more of what was projected by Toyota, especially in the early years. This increase in the number of sales were attributed by Vitz's practicality and its generosity on consumers pockets making it an excellent low budget car.

name: Nissan Elgrand
description: Highways have never been this better with Nissan Elgrand, the highway star. With a highly comfortable seat orientation accommodating 7 individuals who get recliner function, thigh and leg support which is foldable. It is also very spacious and generally super comfortable. That is one thing Nissan has perfected in doing for their vans especially.

name: Audi A5
description: The B9 is the new generation of the A5 based on the B9 platform that came after the B8 platform. The B9 platform came with major improvements with the big highlights being the new virtual instrument cluster and the impressive curves on the exterior. Specs include a Multifunctional steering wheel, half leather S-Line sport seats, adaptive headlights, Bang & Olufsen premium surround sound system, dual zone climate controls, and traction control.

name: Toyota Landcruiser 200 Series 4.6L V8
description: Toyota Landcruiser V8 4.6L, arguably one of the most versatile all round series of the Toyota Landcruiser. It is a very stable and aggressive generation that has been very much embraced and liked by many including politicians and consumers who are seeking comfort and top class convenience. You get to enjoy premium features including heated and cooled seats, multizone climate controls, parking sensors, sunroof, rear entertainment screens, leather seats, 8 seats occupancy, roof rails, side steps, and cruise control.

name: Mazda Demio 1.3L
description: A very generous car to its consumers, Mazda Demio is a very reliable and excellently performing car with the 1.3L petrol engine giving sufficient power to carry up to 5 individuals and some cargo at the back. The seats have the heating functionality which is also a plus for the comfort aspect.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The W205 was the first car to adopt the Modular Rear Architecture (MRA) Platform giving the car a much lighter body weight because of the use of Aluminum extensively throughout the body. It was available in 5 body styles spanning from sedan coded W205, station wagon/Estate coded S205, Coupe C205, cabriolet A205, and the long-wheelbase sedan coded V205. The C200 shares its turbocharged engine, M274 DE20 LA, with the C200 4MATIC, C250, and the C300 but each has different power rating with the one listed producing 181hp and 300Nm of torque.

name: Subaru Forester
description: A Naturally Aspirated Subaru Forester is here with us. For the many who prefer the Naturally Aspirated version over the turbocharged one, this is the time! The Naturally Aspirated variant produces descent power of 146hp and 196Nm of torque without a strain. The interior is also excellent with fabric seats with heating functionality as the main highlights.

name: Peugeot 208
description: A perfect French starter car, Peugeot 208. A 1.2L petrol engine, comfy fabric seats, and a generally easy car generous on fuel and maintenance.

name: Volkswagen Tiguan
description: Tiguan began production in 2007 with the first gen Tiguan being based on the PQ46 platform that was also used in the Passat, Sharan, and Ŝkoda. This platform was initially made for large cars featuring a fully independent suspension on the rear. Volkswagen Tiguan fits the class of perfect crossovers that deliver every other aspect in SUVs by Volkswagen except space. It is also a very good fuel consumer running a 1.4L turbocharged petrol engine which may sound absurd because of the body size but still does a good job.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI 1.2L
description: The 1.2L Volkswagen Golf TSI offers a good blend of performance, fuel economy, and reliability. The unit is specced with fabric seats, an android infotainment display screen, cup holders for both front occupants, an electrical parking brake quite easy to operate, and convenient side mirror indicators.

name: Volkswagen Golf Variant 1.4L TSI
description: Volkswagen marketed their cars in different body shapes and one of them was the estate variant. There is the Golf variant and that has a very spacious comfortable interior with leather seats, Autohold brake function, electric parking brake, and a flat bottomed multifunctional steering wheel among other specs. It still runs the 1.4L Turbocharged Petrol Engine driving power to two wheels only.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.5L
description: The new era of the CX-5 came with two famous engine in which the diesel engine has been the go-to by many consumers. The 2.5L petrol engine is a good option for those who would prefer a petrol choice to the diesel one. It has a power rating of 187hp which is quite descent for this SUV. It has some premium specs including heated steering wheel, head up display, heated seats both for the front occupants and the rear, two-position memory seats, Blindspot monitoring assist, auto start stop system, parking sensors, and and lane departure assist.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D
description:
The New Gen CX-5 gets to
everyone's mind for its endless
possibilities. On the road, off
the road, in executive events
and for the sport. A true
automotive marvel by Mazda!

name: Volkswagen Passat Variant 1.4L
description: One of the most appealing Passats in the market, the station wagon variant which turns out to be an excellent family station wagon. It is specced with a 1.4L rated at 200Nm of torque. It has a roomy interior with five fabric seats, dual zone climate controls, analogue clock display, and a multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Toyota Wish
description: Classified as a Multipurpose Vehicle, MPV, Toyota Wish gets to fulfil a lot of Wishes for a motorists who is looking at a car that can carry up to persons. The third row seat is a standard feature in this model. Wish lasted for only 2 generations ending in 2017 and the first generation ending in 2008. This unit is fitted with fabric seats, climate controls, android infotainment display screen, and a very spacious leg room for all the 7 occupants.

name: Porsche Cayenne 3.0L V6
description: The disel variant of the Cayenne has a high torque rating, the current standing at 580Nm of torque which makes it an excellent high force SUV as in towing. The cockpit design we never tire of has a range of equipments from the multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters and steering wheel controls, Porsche Communication Management System, offroad and onroad select modes, auto start-stop system, traction control,bucket-styled powered leather seats, and a dual zone climate control system.

name: Mitsubishi Galant GDI
description: Consumers say the Galant delivers, fuel economy and reliability are excellent. It features a 2.0L petrol engine with Gasoline direction injection system. It has a power rating of 143hp and 171Nm of torque. On its interior are fabric seats, FM Radio system, android infotainment display, wood trimming on the interior, powered windows, and an automatic transmission gearbox.

name: Land Rover Discovery IV / 3-Zone Sunroof
description: Landrover Discovery IV, a visually appealing one, with a wide array of specs, one being the three-zone sunroofs. All the occupants in each row get to have control over their sunroofs' opening and closing. You get other specs including an analogue display clock, 7 leather seats with the front seats having a heating functionality, multiple terrain modes, and a touch-screen infotainment system.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: Toyota Harrier G's, a premium SUV by Toyota that accomodates consumers who still love Toyota but would want extras of a comfortable and convenient SUV. From powered seats, eco mode that by far saves on fuel by reducing engine performance and maximising on fuel efficiency, Auto start stop feature, high clearance, dual zone climate controls, a multifunctional steering wheel, push to start button, and Traction control that is practical in handling multiple terrains. The seats are laced with Alcantara material and the G's badging. And being the G's version, it appears more sportier than other versions of Toyota Harriers. The G's is badged nearly all over the car which makes the car even more appealing.

name: Toyota Camry
description: Toyota Camry runs a powerful 2.5L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine with power rating of 178hp at 6000RPMs. The engine capacity compares to what Mark X enthusiasts enjoy under the hood. It is one of the few rich man's Toyota as we see them associated with a certain class of individuals. It is a very comfy one with leather seats in beige, and has cruise control to make the driving experience much better. Dual zone climate controls, interior wood trimming, steering wheel controls, android infotainment display, and Traction control form part of the specs.

name: Audi A6 QUATTRO C7.5
description: Audi A6 C7 series, designated Typ 4G by Audi, began production in 2011 to 2018. It drew a lot of design inspiration from the A8 and has the similar powertrain, the Modular Longitudinal platform, that longitudinal front based engines were constructed under, interior and exterior features. In 2016, sales of the C7 facelift, C7.5 began with this model being among the first to be sold. It features improved exterior styling with design curves that reduced drag effect as with the C7, advanced Matrix LED lights, improved processing capabilities of the Audi MMI infotainment system, a polished metal trimming, and on its drivertrain, holds a 2.0L turbocharged inline 4 cylinder engine with a Dual clutch, famously S-Tronic, 7 speed automatic transmission. The dual clutch transmission system performs extremely well with sporty driving as it transmits without its torque being interrupted as the clutches are just ready to engage the next gears seamlessly, better than a manual transmission!

name: Audi A5 2.0T QUATTRO S-LINE
description: The A5 is a very versatile Audi with a myriad of capabilities. It can go round the world maxing out its power while transversing every kind of terrain with one of the World's best AWD setup, Quattro!

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The C200 is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, aftermarket android infotainment display system, four-spoke steering wheel, and a mechanical footbrake.

name: Mazda Demio 1.5L
description: This diesel variant of the Demio is powered by the Skyactiv-D 1.5L diesel engine with a torque rating of 220Nm. It comfortably handles cargo of its rated payload without a struggle. It is also relatively fast and impressively does long distance travels with no hassle as the diesel engine is perfectly engineered for such adventures.

name: Mazda Axela
description: The Axela is one of the cars that is quickly gaining popularity in the Kenyan market. The reason is quite simple; it's the most practical, affordable, reliable and in many ways premium cars in it's category.

name: Volvo XC60 D4 / PANO SUNROOF
description: An excellent choice of Volvo's powerful, reliable, classy, and impressively safe SUV. The D4 is one of them which is the diesel variant powered by a 2.0L twin turbocharged diesel engine D4204T5 with a power rating of 187hp and 400Nm of Torque. It is fitted with a sunroof and a wood trimming on the interior that gives the Classic touch.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D AWD / SUNROOF
description: Mazda CX-5 2.2D, a new generation that was sold as from 2017 just after the 1st generation began in 2012. It features a totally new design and an improved set of technologies that made the CX-5 more beautiful and highly loved by consumers. There are a number of engines ranging from the 2.0L and 2.5L petrol engine & a 2.2L diesel turbocharged engine, all with Skyactiv technologies. The unit listed features the 2.2L diesel engine that is a torque monster in this class, 418Nm! It is also equipped with a good number of technologies that make it very convenient for consumers. It also has a sunroof and one of Mazda's premium color.

name: Audi Q5
description: The entry of Typ 80A Audi Q5 in 2017 when sales began came out as one of the best improvement from the previous generation Q5. It comes as a total redesign from the previous Typ 8R Q5 that began production in 2009. It features a range of new technologies that makes it a favourite of many Audi Consumers. A digital instrument cluster, redesigned steering wheel, dashboard, and center console with the design being more minimalistic than the previous model. Exterior designs became more sharper lowering drag coefficient. Both front and rear lights were also redesigned giving the car a much better admired fascia. It also was uprated just with the EA888 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine to 252hp and 370Nm of torque from the previous 222hp and 350Nm of torque.

name: BMW  X3 XDrive 20d M-SPORT
description: BMW X3 is specced with a good number of Luxury features including leather seats that are powered and have two-position memory seats with thigh support, a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, electric parking brake, Autohold brake function, dual zone climate controls, parking sensors, Camera view, and roof rails. It runs a 2.0L B47 straight-4 turbo producing 400Nm of torque.

name: Volvo XC60 T5 "Inscription" AWD
description: The best in the game when it comes to safety, and arguably among the top in comfort and power. Volvo mastered the skill and has been good in its craft. The unit listed is the petrol version of the XC60 of trim T5 with an AWD system. It has cream coloured leather seats that are powered and heated with multiple way adjustments. It also comes with a sunroof and an interior wood trimming.

name: Lexus NX200t
description: Lexus NX200t turns out to be the king in compact luxury crossover SUVs class sold by Lexus. The sporty nature of the car is complimented by the 2.0L 8AR-FTS turbocharged petrol engine that is one hell of a perfomer. It is also a very economical car attributed to by Lexus' Economy with Superior Thermal Efficient Combustion (ESTEC) direct injection with turbo (D-4ST) fuel injection. It is run by a 6-speed automatic transmission gearbox with a very smooth shift. Definitely a car you can't think twice of acquiring it.

name: Mercedes Benz E350 / SUNROOF
description: The W212 Mercedes Benz E350, specced with heated seats, a panoramic sunroof, leather powered seats, a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, blindspot monitoring assist, adaptive cruise control, and a 3.5L V6 petrol engine.

name: Nissan Patrol Nismo "Y62"  / SUNROOF
description: Nissan Patrol Nismo was introduced when the Nismo brand was being launched by Nissan at a launch event in Dubai. It got the market entry alongside other big Nismo brands including GT-R Nismo and 370Z Nismo. Nismo is the performance version of Nissan as it has been fitted with performance parts from the body to engine parts. It is quite visible that upgrades have been done to this car as Nissan fitted different red-colored body kit that includes side skirts, front and rear bumpers, and Nismo badging at the rear and at the front on the grill. The engine is also uprated having the 5.6L V8 petrol engine producing 428hp from the regular Patrol's 400hp. Its suspensions have also been upgraded with Bilstein shocks and fitted with 22-inch forged-alloy wheel. This is where the fun is at!

name: Range Rover Sport Autobiography 5.0L V8 SUPERCHARGED / PANO SUNROOF
description: The bigger brother of Range Rover Sport series of the AJ133 series, that are AJ-V8 engines produced by Jaguar. Jaguar Landrover division oversees the production of the Range Rover Sport SVR that is powered by a 5.0L V8 AJ133 Suoercharged Petrol engine that does 575 Horsepowers and 702 Nm of Torque. It is mated to an 8 speed-shiftable ZF8HP automatic transmission gearbox. Other features include Powered two tone sports leather seats, heated front & rear seats, Panoramic sunroof, Terrain response management system, adaptive cruise control, Meridian premium surround sound system, Electric tailgate, 4 Wheel Drive, and Traction control system.

name: Landrover Defender 110
description: This is the Landrover 110 series that began production in 1983. You probably wonder why the name 110, the wheelbase is 110-inches. Landrover fancily named their production models then with the wheelbase sizes as was done with the 127 also. You can almost always be sure this will give you the best memorable overlanding experiences!

name: Peugeot 2008 / MOONROOF
description: A conveniently efficient and powerul mini SUV by Peugeot. It is specced with half leather seats, climate controls, roof rails, side mirror indicators, and a multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Peugeot 508 / MOONROOF
description: 508 is a mid-size to large family car produced by the French Automaker Peugeot. The SW is the estate version of the 508 that began in 2011. It gets to share its platform with the 2nd generation Citroën C5. It has a shorter front overhang and a longer rear passenger compartment making it an excellent family car as all the individuals get to have a spacious interior and enough cargo space. This car has already won several awards including Car of the Year 2011 in Spain. Definitely a Win when you own one!

name: Volvo XC60 D4 / SUNROOF
description: Volvo introduced an even more powerful version of the XC60, D4, which has a D4204T5 turbocharged diesel engine producing 400Nm of Torque. The petrol variant has 350Nm of torque. It is specced with black leather seats, a panoramic sunroof, a multifunctional steering wheel, a wooden trimming, and powered seats with memory function.

name: Toyota SUCCEED
description: Statistics say Toyota has been selling at least 50,000 units of the Toyota Probox every year since 2008. This is not far from Toyota Succeed's sales as they have been identical since 2014. This is a loved car both commercially and for private purposes. It can serve as both a passenger or cargo vehicle or for own private use. It has 2 seats at the front and a bench setup at the rear accommodating three individuals. The boot space is also very sufficient accomodating any kind of cargo.

name: Mazda Demio 1.3L
description: The Demio runs a 1300cc Naturally aspirated petrol engine doing 94hp and 102Nm of torque. It has fabric seats, climate controls, android infotainment display system, and steering wheel controls on the interior.

name: Audi SQ5 3.0L (TFSI) QUATTRO
description: It is important to note that the SQ5 was produced as the performance version of the Audi Q5 that was first produced in 2008, coded Typ 8R. The previous versions of the SQ5 available in the Typ 8R generation used a 3.0L Supercharged V6 petrol engines, while these new generations SQ5s in the Typ 80A generations adopted a new 3.0L twin turbocharged petrol engine which turns out to be a much powerful version than the previous versions. The torque was increased to 500Nm of Torque from previously rated 469Nm of torque engine. Horsepower remained the same. Advancements are similar to what the new gen Typ 80A Audi Q5 received including a virtual instrument cluster, a de-cluttered interior making it more minimalistic, and improved leather seats with the exterior becoming more curvy and aesthetically beautiful than what was available in the previous generation. The new gen is definitely worth it!

name: Nissan Patrol LE 'Y62'  5.6L V8 / SUNROOF
description: Nissan has been on the run for long producing their best performing SUV that has been loved largely especially in the Middle East. Powerful two engine options of a 4.0L V6 and a 5.6L V8 that are petrol powered. With this unit listed, you get the bigger 5.6L V8 engine which is pure niceness ever produced by Nissan. Y62 is the 6th gen of the Patrol that was produced from 2010 but has undergone a number of facelifts to catch up with modern tech while keeping the Nissan Spirit of the Patrol. It comes in several trims options including the XE, SE, and the LE which have mini trims. There are also specially equipped editions like the Nismo that carries more power and comes out as a more aggresive variant. This is the LE trim whose engine has a VVEL DIG, Variable Valve Event and Lift and Direct Injection Gasoline that help in improving fuel consumption, performance, and efficiency while taking care of the environment in terms emissions. The engine gets a power rating of 400hp and 560Nm of torque at stock. On the interior, you get a range of features including Leather powered seats that are heated and cooled, multizone climate controls, a wooden trimming on the interior, and terrain controls for multi terrains!

name: Toyota Landcruiser 4.5L V8
description: This is a 2014 Toyota Landcruiser V8 model powered by a 4.5L 1VD-FTV Diesel turbocharged engine doing 282 horsepowers and 650Nm of Torque. The amount of torque in this vehicle felt by a single rev up is amazing. The comfort levels of this 200 series are also insane. This is one car that you do not always feel the madness of our roads. The front and rear seats offer ultimate comfort with multiple adjustment settings including base height and tilt. The seats themselves are very much welcoming that you would all the time want to sit or lie in them. With all the 8 occupants in the car having such pleasure, this would make this car a gem!

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D
description: The CX-5 can be considered as a smart car that quickly adopted market needs and incorporated them into the designs as the years came by. Until the current model years, all the consumer needs have been continously addressed with reliability, convenience, and efficiency with excellent power output.

name: Lexus RX450H / SUNROOF
description: Lexus RX450h is the only luxury crossover SUV that drives like a Suzuki Alto in its class of luxury crossovers. The hybrid system in this car is the best invention by Lexus. It is powered by a 3.5L V6 naturally aspirated petrol engine and two electric motors with one dedicated to the front wheels and the other dedicated to the rear wheels when needed. This gives the RX450h an edge over any other luxury crossover especially in urban driving as the hybrid system works optimally in city roads where the start-stop feature works. Highway driving is not much of a joy to the hybrid system as the Internal Combustion system is needed to power the high demanding acceleration.

name: Volvo XC60 T5 "Inscription" AWD
description: With the concept car appearing in 2007, sales of the XC60 first gen began in 2008 in Europe and has been Volvo's best selling car since 2009. Volvo was created with a tune of Landrover's offroading capabilities and Volvo's technologies. This makes it one of the best Multipurpose, in the sense of one can operate them at different terrains and for different events, and it will never let one down. The aesthetics are on point, extremely well done, safety earns is a solid 5 star rating from both official tests and consumer reports, and performance is top notch, a marvel. The unit listed is the 2nd Gen that began production in 2017. An Inscription T5 AWD Setup Volvo XC60, quite a beauty to look at. It runs a B4204T 2000cc engine doing 251 horsepowers and 350Nm of torque in an engine orientation of inline 4 plus a turbocharger. Volvo is your next home!

name: Ford Escape XLT
description: The XLT was the top of line trim level of the Escape early in 2001 which turned out to be the most popular trim throughout its period. It runs a 3.0L V6 petrol engine with power rating of 200hp. It gets the 4 Wheel drive system that makes it a good offroad fit. It gets 5 fabric seats and a roomy interior which is typical for such SUVs.

name: Volkswagen Golf Variant 1.4L TSI
description: Volkswagen Golf Variant has bee sold since 1993. It has also been named as a Passenger car by Volkswagen for its legroom and extended boot space. It comfortably accommodates five individuals with the seats made of fabric materials offering comfort making long distance travels smooth. The engine has also proven to be reliable and easy to maintain. Consumption is also very impressive!

name: Nissan NV200
description: Nissan NV200 is a very practical car in a lot of dimensions. One can use it as a cargo space, another can use it commercially to carry school children. Its 1.5L engine has enough torque to handle any of these tasks.

name: Suzuki Jimny 'Land Venture'
description: Jimnys are a group of four wheel drive mini SUVs that have been produced since 1970. With the latest generation, the 4th gen, being produced from 2018, production had been slightly seized for the Jimny in preparation of the entry of the 4th gen that came in same year. This is probably the most affordable Offroad capable SUV which is non problematic and comfortably handles on-road terrain as well. A perfect roadtrip and adventure car! A 660cc turns out to be an excellent fuel consumer!

name: Audi A3
description: The A3 is definitely worth your money. A versatile engine, relatively spacious interior, a powerful 1.4L turbocharged petrol engine, minimalistic sufficiently useful cockpit, and a classy subcompact sedan. The A3 works magic for a budget of less than 2.5M.

name: BMW 320d 'F30'
description: The 320d is a great choice for those seeking a reliable, fuel-efficient, and stylish vehicle. It offers a smooth ride, excellent handling, and a range of features such as cruise control, lane departure warning, and BMW's iDrive infotainment system. It is also one of the most fuel-efficient luxury cars on the market.

name: Toyota Avensis T3-X / MANUAL
description: Toyota Avensis is a mid size family car built in the United Kingdom between 1997 and 2018. It succeeded the European Carina E. It was available in T2, T3-S, T3-X, T4, T Spirit, T180 and TR trims in the UK. This is the T3-X trim which uses a 2.0L 1AZ-FSE with power rating of 147hp. It comfortably accomodates 5 individuals seated in fabric seats. Other features include dual zone climate controls, FM Radio system, and a Manual transmission gearbox.

name: Jeep Cherokee Sport 2.5L
description: There's no replacement for displacement, and being an American car, you shouldn't be surprised to know that this Jeep has a massive 2500cc engine under the hood. You are lucky enough to get airbags, but you probably won't use them because it would take a lot of force to make them deploy, something which normal traffic will not be able to do. You also get a real manual gearbox with a low range geabox. Any rhino charge fanatics in the building?

name: Toyota Fielder WXB Hybrid
description: Toyota Fielder WXB is one of the best cars to have for a number of errands that makes the driver a bit reluctant and less worried on how the car is going to end up later in the day. The engine and drivertrain system are very reliable and easy to maintain.It has a hybrid system which is very convenient when trying to achieve low fuel consumption. This unit is fitted with half leather seats, lane keep assist, Anti-collision brake assist, android infotainment display screen, climate controls, and alloy rims.

name: Toyota Probox
description: Toyota Probox has been a successful station wagon from the production year throughout the sales years that still runs to date. Toyota hasn't had to do major changes over the years as the design perfectly fits the market the Probox has been sold in. It continues to get popular among individuals who seek to use it commercially as it perfectly excels in it.

name: Volkswagen Tiguan 1.4TSI
description: Volkswagen Tiguan is a perfect Crossover that sits between the Touareg and T-Roc. It offers a very good balance between comfort, performance, and luxury. This unit comes fitted with fabric seats, Multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, android infotainment display system, parking sensors, rear retractable mini-tables for the rear occupants, electric handbrake, and side mirror indicators.

name: Mercedes Benz E350 / SUNROOF
description:
W212 is the 4th gen of Mercedes
E Class produced between 2009
and 2016. It falls under the
category of the mid cycle
updated E class that costed
Daimler AG close to £1B. This
makes it the most expensive
facelift in automotive history
Mercedes has ever done.
Therefore, you get to enjoy
premium features including
heated seats, a panoramic
sunroof, leather powered seats,
a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, blindspot monitoring assist.
three-position memory seats
analogue display clock which
makes the E Class an expensive
affair, adaptive cruise control
and a big 3.5L V6 petrol engine.

name: Citreon C4 1.6 BlueHDi
description: Citroën C4 is a French automobile that began production in 2004 towards the end. It was produced as a compact family car in its first two generations and as a subcompact Crossover SUV for its third generation. The 2nd gen within which this unit was produced made a debut in 2010. It appeared as a slightly bigger model with 5 doors as standard and the only design. Suspension geometry was slightly modified with use of new bushes, use of brake discs all round with the front being ventilated, ABS and Electronic stability program being standard. This car received a facelift later in 2015. It uses a 1.6L diesel engine with power rating of 120hp and 300Nm of torque.

name: Porsche Cayenne 3.6L V6 'Platinum Edition' with SUNROOF
description: Porsche has been producing superior performing cars since the early years of the 20th century. They have shown their expertise and highly advanced engineering in their productions. The Cayenne is one of the marvels of Porsche engineering. The 2015 Petrol Platinum Edition variant is powered by a 3600cc petrol engine that does an impressive 300 horsepower at 6300 RPMs and 400Nm of Torque at 3000 RPMs. It does a lot more better than the diesel variant in the horsepower numbers, doing about 240 horses. We can all agree on the engine's reliability and maintenance. It has beige leather, multizone climate controls, Multifunctional tilt & telescopic steering wheel, Auto start stop feature, a premium surround sound system, and differential locks.

name: Volvo S60 T3
description: Volvo S60 T3, powered by B4164T3 1600cc inline four turbocharged engine producing 148 horsepower and 240Nm of torque, is an excellent unit to use in any kind of activity from office errands to farm stuff. Very comfortable with bucket shaped leather seats and a Premium surround sound system.

name: Honda Legend 3.5L V6 Hybrid
description: Honda Legend is Honda's flagship car which is a series of mid-size luxury sedans running V6 engines. It has been in production since 1985. This is the 5th Generation which began in 2014 and ended in 2021 without a successor of this generation. It is heavily equipped with a wide range of premium specs. Heated steering wheel, adaptive cruise control, lane keep assist, Electronic stability control, parking sensors, two-position memory seats, heated seats both in the front and the rear with multizone climate controls, Blindspot monitoring assist, head up display, KRELL premium surround sound system, and a 360° camera view make up the Legend's premium specs!

name: Subaru WRX S4
description: Subaru WRX S4 is one of those good looking yet highly performing JDMs you always come along. Powered by a 2.0L turbocharged engine with stock 300 horsepower and 400Nm of Torque that has a high tuning capability, you can take this car to the track, use it to run errands, go for roadtrips, and daily it, and it will last you how good your maintenance will be. Take this as your chance to participate in high performance races!

name: Hyundai Santa Fe 2.2L Diesel / PANORAMIC SUNROOF
description: Hyundai Santa Fe was named after the city of Mexico, Santa Fe, by the South Korean automobile manufacturer. They were produced in two short wheel or long wheel bas variants which also varied with the market. Some were marketed as 7 seater units while some as 5 seater capacity units. This unit came with 7 seats all in leather and a panoramic sunroof as some of the rare equipments of this unit in the Kenyan market. It has heated and cooled front seats with the steering wheel having the heating functionality as well. You also get electronic locking differential and adaptive cruise control as some of its premium specs.

name: Ford EcoSport Titanium
description: Ford EcoSport is a very practical car with its versatility, affordability, and general efficiency from running it to maintaining it. It is powered by a 1.5L petrol engine which its owners are happy about. It comfortably accomodates 5 individuals in its fabric material seats. It is an excellent Mini SUV for Ford enthusiasts and anyone looking to get an easy going car.

name: Ford Ranger Limited 2.2L
description: One of the best comfort plus offroad car in a very sophisticated design that is an eyecatcher at a glance. Offroading tires, side steps, offroad modes, comfortable rides, and leather seats on the interior, and a high torque 2.2L turbocharged diesel engine.

name: Mazda Premacy 2.2L Diesel
description: The executive car by Mazda, the Premacy. Fitted with 6 comfortable leather seats that each individual gets to have non-shared space which is worth any long distance travel. The 2.2L diesel engine also gets to handle the roads perfectly well. The torque is sufficient and comfortably handles the car's payload. You also get a sunroof which is a plus for such a family car!

name: Toyota Landcruiser GXR 4.5L V8 / MANUAL
description: The GX-R has a very interesting spec to it, a 4.5L V8 turbocharged diesel paired to a 5 speed manual transmission gearbox which is quite a thrill. Driving a big diesel engine with a manual transmission gearbox might be a super exciting experience. It is fitted with 7 leather seats with the third row being foldable for additional space. It is also visually appealing which is a plus for an already admirable SUV.

name: Audi A4 2.0T QUATTRO
description: A4s make up perfect, unique easy go-to German cars that have high versatility yet offering good maintenance and initial purchase costs that favours many consumers who are just shifting to the German world. It runs a 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine and drives all the 4 wheels on demand via Audi's All Wheel Quattro system which is arguably one of the best systems. It has leather seats that are powered, AUDI MMI infotaiment system, Multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters and a premium sound system among other specs.

name: Audi Q7 3.0L TDI
description: Creation of the Q7 by Audi favored large family consumers. Powered by a 3000cc Turbocharged Diesel V6 Engine producing 233 horsepower and 500Nm of torque.Its 7 seats have leather material and are powered. It also has a multifunctional 4 spoke steering wheel. Its ground clearance is excellent for offroading adventures as well!

name: Toyota Rush 4WD
description: Rush is an excellent SUV in the medium sized category. It serves as an MPV for the large size body category. It is specced with 5 leather seats, climate controls, android infotainment display system, locking differential, and powered mirrors among other specs.

name: Peugeot 208
description: Peugeot has had its 2nd gen 208 in production since 2012 replacing the 207. It has been well received as its sales have gradually grown since production. This unit has 5 fabric seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, an android infotainment display screen, and climate controls among its specs.

name: Toyota Esquire
description: Well, you've probably been thinking about Toyota Noah or the Voxy, but here is greater deal, unmatched luxury and unlimited options to how one can use it. Great Family experience or amazing commercial passenger services is just a step away from next level elevation, PURCHASE!. An Auto Start Stop feature, Toyota Safety sense incorporating collision warning and lane assist are also part of this unit. Be pretty sure the 3ZR-FAE 2.0L NA engine will drive you comfortably!

name: Nissan XTRAIL Mode-Premier Autech
description: This is the 3rd gen of Nissan XTRAIL that has been widely used in the Kenyan Market since the entry of the first generation NT30 in 2000. It is a very capable offroader as it is fitted with optional 4WD select that enables one to drive on only two wheels to save on fuel, leather seats that are super comfortable, Nissan pure drive for environmental friendly drives, dual tip exhaust tailpipes, and heated seats for warming up during the cold.

name: Audi SQ5 3.0T V6 QUATTRO
description:
EN ROUTE TO THE PORT OF MOMBASA! EXPECTED TIME OF ARRIVAL 16th APRIL, 2024.

Specs include a Quattro AWD setup, Powered heated, half leather seats, Multifunctional steering wheel, Bang & Olufsen premium surround sound system, dual zone climate controls, adaptive cruise control, Blindspot Monitoring Assist, and Lane keep assist.

name: Peugeot 308 GT '2.0L Diesel'
description: The 308 GT is specially designed trim of the 308 that performs overally well with the big 2.0 diesel engine, and gives a much appealing look than the regular 308. Peugeot 308 came as a replacement of the 307. It sits below the 508 and just above the 208. It is powered by a 2000cc turbocharged diesel engine with 179hp and 400Nm of torque, a speedometer maxing at 250Km/h, cruise control, steering wheel controls, climate controls, android infotainment display system, and electric parking brake.

name: Peugeot 2008
description: Peugeot 2008, A94, first beginning production in 2013, is a subcompact crossover placed below its bigger brother, the 3008. It is powered by a 1200cc turbocharged petrol engine and drives only two wheels. This unit has half leather seats on its interior, a dual zone climate controls, and a  multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Subaru Levorg 1.6L
description: We probably don't know much about this car, but here is the thing. In 2014, Subaru thought of producing a car that's a little more interesting beginning from how they came up with the name 'Levorg' that means legacy, touring, and revolution all in one. It offered a lot of features with the basic one being the company's best feature, Symmetrical AWD except when Subaru entered British Touring Racing with the Levorg where they used rear wheel drive as per regulations. Adaptive cruise control, hill descent assist, lane keep assist, and a proper 1.6L turbocharged and intercooled direct injection flat four engine form up this car.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: Harrier is a midsize crossover SUV in its 4th generation now that began in 2020. It is a sister to the famous Lexus RX and the RAV4 XA40 Series with which the 3rd gen Toyota Harrier adopts some of its components from. Harrier is famous among family setups which Toyota understands by fitting Toyota Safety Sense P safety system which includes Adaptive cruise control, lane departure assist, pre-collision system, and automatic high beam which was standard. You are assured of your safety in the Harrier.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.5L
description: Design engineers at Mazda hit the nail in the head. Beautiful exterior designs with aerodynamically important curves, slightly minimalistic yet full equipped interior, and importantly a powerful engine in a strong durable Skyactiv Chassis.

name: Mazda CX-5 "2.0L NA"
description: Mazda CX-5 2.0L, a new generation that was sold as from 2017 just after the 1st generation began in 2012. It features a totally new design and an improved set of technologies that made the CX-5 more beautiful and highly loved by consumers. There are a number of engines ranging from the 2.0L and 2.5L petrol engine & a 2.2L diesel turbocharged engine, all with Skyactiv technologies. The unit listed features the 2.0L Naturally Aspirated petrol  engine that is easy going in this class, it is also equipped with a good number of technologies that make it very convenient for consumers!

name: Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport / 4WD WINCH
description: The Wrangler means business! Full offroad equipments fitted a winch limited to 5670KGs, approx 5 Tonnes and serious offroad drivetrain. It also has high beam lights fitted for additional vision and clarity. The Wrangler came into its 3rd generation in 2006 under the development of Daimler Chrysler and was developed under a clean-sheet design of the body, frame, and suspension. This generation came with power windows, remote power door locks, navigation, and electronically detachable sway bars on some models. The Wrangler carries the seriousness an offroader deserves. A 4WD system and a high torque engine is all you need to fulfil your offroad adventures!

name: Mercedes Benz C250
description: Mercedes-Benz W205 was produced from 2014 to 2021 with the sedan adopting W205 model code as the other models adopted different codes like A205 in the Cabriolet. Mercedes call the W205 a mini-S-Class for its large size than the W204. It features front axle four-link and rear axle five-link suspension, flat-bottomed multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, bucket-styled leather seats with thigh support and heating functionality, analogue clock on the cockpit, rear foldable armrest with deployable cup holders, and lane keep assist.

name: Toyota Wish
description: A 5-door station wagon that's a proper Family car from Toyota. With its production lasting for 14 years since 2003, the 7 seater occupancy capacity and the 2ZR-FAE 1800CC Petrol engine, this is all you need for your family from Toyota.

name: Nissan XTRAIL "HNT32" / SUNROOF
description: Nissan XTRAIL NT32 is the 3rd gen of Nissan XTRAIL that has been widely used in the Kenyan Market since the entry of the first generation NT30 in 2000. It is a very capable offroader as it is fitted with optional 4WD select that enables one to drive on only two wheels to save on fuel, leather seats that are super comfortable, single tip exhaust tailpipes, and heated seats for warming up during the cold.

name: Landrover Discovery IV / 3-ZONE SUNROOFS
description: The Discovery IV comes with a wide array of specs with the visually appealing one being the three-zone sunroofs. All the occupants in each row get to have control over their sunroofs' opening and closing. You get other specs including an analogue display clock, 7 leather seats with the front seats having a heating functionality, multiple terrain modes, and a touch-screen infotainment system.

name: Toyota Landcruiser VX-R
description: The VX-R is a serious offroading automobile. The 200 series Chassis gives it improved stability by offering a lower Center of Gravity and despite the speeds and the cornering angles, you would still be able to cruise comfortably. This is a fully loaded model with 7 leather seats occupancy with the 3rd row setting being foldable. It also has a sunroof and side steps which come as standard. It is equipped with cruise control and a number of offroading equipments including hill descent control and cruise control.

name: Volkswagen Passat
description: Volkswagen passat B7 gen came with some improvements majorly consisting of the body panels, grille, and headlights. The face of the Passat keeps on getting better with the advancements in generations. This unit is specced with fabric seats, an analogue cabin clock, interior polished metal trimming, and a Multifunctional steering wheel among other specs.

name: Mazda CX-3 1.5D
description: The CX-3 is a subcompact crossover SUV that's looks minimalistically powerful but gets to offer a lot from power output to drivetrain and comfort. With a 2WD Setup, you still get to triumph over any kind of surface while getting maximum comfort from the half leather seats.

name: Toyota Vitz
description: Vitz is subcompact car produced by Toyota since 1999 until late 2019. It has achieved a lot of sales, more of what was projected by Toyota, especially in the early years. This increase in the number of sales were attributed by Vitz's practicality and its generosity on consumers pockets making it an excellent low budget car.

name: Dodge Charger 3.6L V6
description: Dodge Charger was introduced in the early years of 1966 with the first designs adopting its shape and components from Chrysler B-body intermediate sized Dodge coronet. Production has continued since then to now the 8th generation going on sale beginning 2024. The unit listed falls under the 7th generation which that lasted between the years of 2011 and 2023. This generation came as an improved version of the previous with updates majorly being done on the interior and exterior. An aggressive designs, a more aerodynamically designed body, and the modern wrap-around tail light running through to both ends of the trunk, were the most noticeable developments. The 3.5L V6 engine available in the 6th gen was also updated to the famous bullet proof 3.6L V6 Pentastar engine, also used in Jeep Grand Cherokee, with a power rating of 292hp and 350Nm of torque. The engine is mated to a 5 speed A580 automatic transmission gearbox. This a must-have for individuals who love American muscles as it impressively carries the day for its looks and performance!

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TX/SUNROOF
description: Built for terrains off-tarmac, Toyota Landcruiser Prado TX crushes offroad terrains perfectly well while keeping the underbody safe as the body-on-frame development improved its ride height which tends to give it unstable rides while negotiating sharp corners at considerably high speeds.

name: Toyota Porte
description: A mini Multipurpose Van developed by Toyota, minimalistic and simple, being an excellent comfortable car with a high roof line and a very spacious legroom. The interior design we give it to Toyota for giving a classy and minimalistic design that is very welcoming. You might as well love this car by just looking at the interior. It also shines in its cost effective performance with engine options of 1.3L and 1.5L giving figures of up to 18Kms a liter!

name: Mercedes Benz G350d with 'Brabus Bodykit'
description: You would mistake the G350 with the famous Brabus kitted Mercedes Benz G63. The Bodykit gives it an aggressive and classy body design that is quite impressive to many and attractive to a number of Brabus Bodykit consumers. The G350 racks up 282hp and 600Nm of torque from a 3.0L inline 6 OM 656 D29TR SCR turbocharged diesel engine. The engine is very capable of pulling the weight of its own body and can comfortably maneuver any terrain with ease. It is a serious offroader and a proper onroad beast that is respected across the board. Get the experience of a lifetime with the Brabus kitted G350d!

name: SUBARU FORESTER 2.0 NON-TURBO
description: The Non Turbo version of the Subaru Forester is an easy going car if you want an SUV that is not as powerful as the Forester XT and is just powerful enough to give you the status of owning an SUV by Subaru. It is specced with fabric seats, a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, dual zone climate controls, android infotainment system and and both Sport and Intelligent driving modes.

name: Landrover Discovery IV 'XS SPEC'
description: Discovery 4 came into production from 2009 to 2016 being an updated version of Disco 3. Upgrades included the change of front and rear lights, a newly restyled front grille and bumper that made the car much smoother as seen with the new models of Range Rover Sport from 2010. Body coloured wheel arches and bumpers matching those of Discovery 3 were retained. Fuel economy was also improved for this generation. It is specced with leather seats that are powered and heated, an analogue display clock at the dash center, Multifunctional steering wheel, hill descent assist, multiple terrain select, traction control, and an adjustable ride height. This the XS Spec which means it comes with heated front seats as listed, 7 seats, climate control, cruise control, remote central locking, rear parking sensors, both front and rear heated windshields, and Harman Kardon CD Stereo multi disc player.

name: Audi Q5 2.0T
description: The Q5s never run out of fashion, you always get different units styled differently especially with the seats that are sometimes half-leather and some full leather, some would come in S-Line versions and some non S-Line but the feel of its performance and drive always catches every driver's spirit. This unit has half leather seats and is an S-Line version.

name: Toyota Auris
description: Toyota Auris gives the feel of driving a Volkswagen Golf which actually Toyota target that it competes with. The Golf and the Ford Focus in the medium cars segment are its main competitors despite the performance these two cars display. It carries some class with a lot of capability for serious racing as with the variant running the 1.2L turbocharged 8NR-FTS engine. It is the engine this car runs and is produced in the line of NR inline-four engines. It is also well spaced and quite comfortable.

name: Jeep Wrangler Unlimited SAHARA
description: Jeep Wrangler came into its 3rd generation in 2006 under the development of Daimler Chrysler and was developed under a clean-sheet design of the body, frame, and suspension. This generation came with power windows, remote power door locks, navigation, and electronically detachable sway bars on some models. The Wrangler carries the seriousness an offroader deserves. A 4WD system and a high torque engine is all you need to fulfil your offroad adventures!

name: Toyota Harrier
description: You can always bet on the Toyota Harrier to take you places for as long as you will need it. It has been excellent family car since the beginning of days and still becomes an excellent SUV even as new generation models are produced. You hear of consumers who have owned it saying they can take it anywhere and easily come out, they truly mean it. Its clearance gives it an edge in any kind of terrain. Its engine also runs with zero challenges.

name: Nissan Serena
description: The true Highway Star. It ranks among the best in comfort. They are very easy to drive and poweful enough to easily pull you in any kind of elevation without much of a struggle. The 6 seats occupancy is spacious for all occupants to enjoy their own spaces and to even stretch without having to stop. It also has cup holders and armrests among other specs.

name: Nissan Note DIG-S
description: You have probably wondered what the DIG-S means in some Nissan Notes. It means Direct Injection Gasoline-Supercharged. The Supercharger in this unit makes quite a difference in the power the Nissan Note makes. 147Nm of torque and 97hp compared to the NA version making 78hp and 106Nm does some magic!

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D AWD
description: Mazda CX-5 has proven over time to improve in its reliability over the years, hence positive customer reviews as the years go by. The new generation, 2nd since production in 2012, has grown to be a fast selling unit by Mazda. Its improving design, body size, convenience features, and safety features has made it rank among the top purchased SUVs. Mechanics and repair shops have given it a rating of 82 of 100 which makes it one of the top reliable cars as it ranks 1st of 26 Midsize SUVs in comparable class. You won't go wrong with the CX-5.

name: Peugeot 208
description: Peugeot is just at its second generation since it began production in 2012 replacing the 207. It has been well received as its sales have gradually grown since production. This unit has 5 fabric seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, an android infotainment display screen, dual zone climate control, and a moonrof among its specs.

name: Nissan DAYZ
description: Nissan DAYZ is a tall-height kei car that has been in production to majorly satisfy the economic needs of individuals who do commercial taxi services. Fuel efficiency is at the core of its marketing as that is what it excels best in. When one decides to use this unit for Taxi purposes, their clients will have an easy ride time and the driver as well gets to have an easy time all throughout because of the comfort levels the car offers.

name: Nissan DAYZ
description: Nissan DAYZ is a tall-height kei car that has been in production to majorly satisfy the economic needs of individuals who do commercial taxi services. Fuel efficiency is at the core of its marketing as that is what it excels best in. When one decides to use this unit for Taxi purposes, their clients will have an easy ride time and the driver as well gets to have an easy time all throughout because of the comfort levels the car offers.

name: Jeep Grand Cherokee 3.6 LIMITED 4×4 / PANORAMIC SUNROOF
description: Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited is what Jeep calls the 'step-up' trim of Grand Cherokee which succeeded what was in its level, the Laredo X. All the equipments available in the Laredo X including leather seats, powered front seats, a touch-screen infotainment system, a 9-speaker 506-watte Alpine surround-sound audio system, Bluetooth connectivity, dual-pane panoramic moonroof, were present in the Limited trim but additional options including heated front and rear seats & ventilated front seats, driver's memory system, and Nappa leather seats were offered. It runs the famous 3.6L V6 Pentaster petrol engine that has been known to be a bulletproof engine! The instant power from the Naturally Aspirated V6 makes this car one of the best non-problematic SUVs for all-round terrain handling.

name: Subaru Legacy B4
description: Subaru Legacy did a bit of an upgrade in the 6th Gen 2.5L flat four FB25 engine by uprating it to 173bhp from the 5th Generation that ended in 2013 running 169bhp. The 3.6L flat six EZ36D remained unchanged running 252bhp. The slight change in power rating might not seem like it can work a lot of magic but sure makes a change.

name: Mitsubishi RVR
description: Looking for a perfect Crossover? The RVR is a good one at that. With just the right body lenght and width, you can comfortably carry 5 passengers and go into any kind of squeezed road and still burn just enough fuel while going low on maintenance costs!

name: BMW X6 XDrive M50d 'N57' Tri-Turbo
description: BMW X6 began its first generation in 2008, coded E71. The X6 became the first BMW to use Dynamic Performance Control system which works together with XDrive All Wheel Drive. Dynamic Performance Control is a drivetrain and chassis control system that work to regulate traction and correct over and understeer by actively spreading out drive forces across the rear axle. Torque vectoring happens laterally between the front and rear wheels and also from side to side at the rear which improves agility and stability. The M50d badging in this car speaks of the engine type available which is the 3.0L straight 6 N57 tri-turbo spec which produces 375hp and 740Nm of torque which is quite a deal!

name: Subaru Legacy
description: Being the makers flagship car, Subaru was committed to building a non-problematic fun, safe, and reliable car. It features symmetrical AWD Setup which is standard in the Legacy. Running from 1989, it has been known to be a powerful and durable car that a lot of enthusiasts have thoroughly enjoyed. It features a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, cruise control, and fabric seats.

name: BMW X3 XDrive 25i
description: BMW X3 has maintained its standard of being a premium SUV as it was the first premium SUV in the market by BMW before beginning competition with Mercedes GLC and other SUVs of the same class. This unit here is specced with fabric seats, dual zone climate controls, Multifunctional steering wheel, side mirrror indicators and a 2.5L N52 on its powertrain.

name: Toyota Fielder "S" AeroTourer
description: Toyota Fielder S is a sporty version of the Fielder that is very instrumental in handling terrains while in Sports mode that needs one to drive at high speeds while engaging corners or obstacles. It has an 1800cc naturally aspirated engine with Valvematic technology. It has 5 seats that have fabric material, android infotainment system, steering wheel controls, climate controls, and a 2WD system.

name: Renault KADJAR
description: The Renault Kadjar is specced with half leather seats, dual zone climate controls, a multifunctional steering wheel, android infotainment display system, cruise control, cup holders, and runs a 1.2L Inline-4 Tce engine with a power rating of 130hp.

name: Toyota Landcruiser Prado TX
description: A well rated SUV whose reliability and durability we cannot for once doubt as we have seen them traverse the whole nation during campaign trails. They easily manage to cruise through any terrain as it is fully engaged on the 4WD System and together with its high clearance of 220mm, you get a perfect offroader. Long distances with the Prado will not have you breaking your back as the seats are very comfortable.

name: Porsche Cayenne 3.0 V6 'Typ 92A'
description: Porsche never gets old. Porsche has perfected the art of producing cars that are durable and are among the top high performing cars both on track and even offroad with the new development we have seen with the 911 Dakar. This is the disel variant which means it has a high torque rating, the current standing at 580Nm of torque. The cockpit design we never tire of has a range of equipments from the multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters and steering wheel controls, Porsche Communication Management System, offroad and onroad select modes, auto start-stop system, traction control, heated bucket-styled powered leather seats, a panoramic sunroof, and a dual zone climate control system.

name: Volvo V40 T5 R-Design
description: Volvo V40 is a small family car that Volvo probably took a very good time to do the design and actualize a super convenient, super performing hatchback. It has been produced since 2012 to 2019 although there was the original V40 that was produced from 1995 to 2004. A facelift was done in 2015 that featured a new fascia adopting Thor's hammer headlights, a design that was available on all V40 variants. The engine option in the T5 features a very sharp, instant, and powerful Inline-5 2500cc B5254T14 engine with a power rating of 246hp and 360Nm of torque. This is a good deal of power for such a light hatchback. Adding on it is the R-Design spec which makes the car look aesthetically sportier. This is quite some deal!

name: Volkswagen Golf GTI MK7.5 / SUNROOF
description:
EN ROUTE TO THE PORT OF MOMBASA! EXPECTED TIME OF ARRIVAL APRIL, 2024.

Specs include DCC(Dynamic Chassis Control), Sunroof, original GTI Plaid seats, Bucket style fabric seats,autonatic air conditioning,isofix child support,electric parking brake, adaptive cruise control, and a multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Volkswagen Golf GTI MK7 / SUNROOF
description:
EN ROUTE TO THE PORT OF MOMBASA! EXPECTED TIME OF ARRIVAL APRIL, 2024.

Specs include DCC(Dynamic Chassis Control), Sunroof, Bucket style fabric seats,autonatic air conditioning,isofix child support,electric parking brake, and a multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Audi A4 B9 QUATTRO ALLROAD SPEC
description: Typ 8W Audi A4 made an appearance in 2016 being the 5th Gen in the B platform. Within the B Platform, it adopts the B9 series badging. It is slightly larger than the B8 but lighter by 120Kg as Audi claims. This is the Allroad spec which is equipped for offroading activities as seen with the clearance of about 6.5 inches from the standard 5 inches of what the normal A4 offers. It is equipped with Quattro All Wheel drive setup which enables it to drive all the 4 wheels on demand whenever slip is detected on any of the wheels. It also gets the offroad driving mode which adjusts the suspensions and engine's working to provide maximum power for offroad adventures. Germans also get to be interesting not only on-road!

name: Volkswagen UP!
description: Volkswagen up! has been in production from 2013 to 2023 where production ended in October. This was part of Volkswagen's strategy to produce cars in a new class called the New Family Series which targeted city driving as the UP! is meant to be used. This is the perfect errands car and can also be used for office and group trips as it makes up an excellent fleet car. This probably the most fuel efficient car Volkswagen Engineers have ever produced. It operates at a capacity of 1000cc with power rating of 101hp. Its fuel consumption hits highs of 23Kms a liter which is pretty descent for a fast, highly reliable German car!

name: Audi A5
description: Every time you see an A5, you definitely know what that means. thrill, fun, class, executive state, and a showmaker car of sorts. The sleekness of the A5 making it a serious eyecatcher everywhere it goes. The good thing is it is able to navigate to every kind of location you would want to go and is able to represent one at any kind of event be it a race show, corporate event, or even an adventure with the 'boys'. The best part is on it price that makes it a great deal of the month. Win yourself this glorified car!

name: Volvo V60 D4 R-Design
description: The V60 is a compact executive luxury station wagon produced by Volvo Cars since 2010. It is based on the sedan version, the S60. It received a mid-life facelift in 2014 still in its first generation. There were different trims to it including a V60 Ocean Race, Polestar, and a Plu-in-hybrid trim. The V60 had an R-Design model which is aesthetically sportier than the base V60. This version is the diesel variant coded, D4, which adopts I4 D4204T14 2.0L engine power rated 187hp and 400Nm of Torque. On the interior, it is equipped with bucket-styled  leather seats that are powered with heating functionality, a multifunctional steering wheel, Blindspot Monitoring Assist called Bliss by Volvo, and a Premium surround sound system that ranks top among many cars in the same class.

name: Toyota Celica
description: This is the T230 series produced as the 7th generation lasting between 1996 and 2006. Toyota produced this car in only one body style, the liftback, which was offered with two engine options, both 1.8L engines but one runs the 1ZZ-FED I4 and the 2ZZ-GE I4. This unit runs the 1ZZ-FED engine with a power rating of 140hp. It has a sitting capacity of 4 individuals with fabric material. The front seats are styled as highly sporty bucket-styled fabric seats.

name: Mercedes Benz C200 /SUNROOF
description:
EN ROUTE TO THE PORT OF MOMBASA! EXPECTED TIME OF ARRIVAL 28th FEBRUARY, 2024.

Specs include Powered leather seats, heated front seats, daytime running LED lights, Dual zone climate controls, side mirror indicators, Push start ignition, Panoramic sunroof, and Premium surround sound system.

name: Mercedes Benz E250
description: Design inspirations for the Mercedes Benz E Class W212 were drawn from what had been done to the C-Class, S-Class, and the CLS-Class. It encompassed an aggresive and bold design different from the previous models. The car also was made more comfortable, efficient, and highly performing with the example of the 'direct control' adaptive suspension that adjusts the passenger comfort by a switch of the button. It also featured new advanced features such as the Electronic Stability program and automatic climate zone.

name: Toyota Vitz
description: Toyota used the Vitz nameplate majorly for the Japanese market and the Yaris for international markets. As a direct consumer of the Japanese market, we got the Vitz nameplate. It has been a very popular car in a lot of markets achieving over 3.5 Million sales in excess of the projected number in over 70 countries. It still continues to be among the top selling hatchbacks by the Japanese Manufacturer.

name: Nissan Note
description: Nissan Note can also add on to its large boot space by folding the rear seats leaving space for only front occupants. Its seats are in fabric materials. It has an android infotainment display screen, and climate controls.

name: Nissan Note Medalist
description: Nissan Note Medalist was actually designed specifically for the Japanese Market different from the other markets Nissan markets their Notes at. It came specced with special equipment as seen with plated door handles, seude-like cloth seats and artificial leather, piano-like center cluster finish, and genuine leather wrapped on the steering wheel.

name: Subaru Forester
description: This is the Non-Turbo version of Subaru Forester which runs the 2.0L Naturally Aspirated petrol engine with a power rating of 146hp and 196Nm of torque. On the interior, it is specced with fabric seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, an android infotainment display system, Eyesight adaptive cruise control, and an All Wheel drive setup on the drivetrain.

name: Renault Duster
description:
Renault Duster is a an excellent
crossover SUV with a good ride
height, ride quality, and perfect handling on the road. It
is a very spacious and comfy car and even more exciting being a
manual car. It features fabric
seats, climate controls, FM
RADIO, roof rails, and automatic
transmission gearbox.

name: Mercedes Benz GLC 250
description: The GLC is the equivalent of the C-Class as most of the design aspects are based off the C-Class. It replaced the GLK-Classe and the first generation came in at 2015 with the 2nd Generation beginning at 2022. It is specced with three-position memory seats that are powered and heated, Burmester premium surround sound system, 360° camera view, lane keep assist, adaptive cruise control, Blindspot Monitoring Assist, a panoramic sunroof, head up display, Auto Start Stop feature, and a flat-bottomed multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Subaru Forester 2.0 NA
description: There is some magic how the Naturally Aspirated version of the Subaru Forester that some consumers like over the turbocharged version commonly known as the XT. It is slightly less powerful than the XT but comfortably pulls without much of a struggle. It is fitted with a good number of specs available in the XT except for a few performance modes such as the S# 'Sport Plus' mode. The AWD drivetrain is standard.

name: Volvo XC60 D4 'Classic' /SUNROOF
description: The best selling car by Volvo, the XC60, has to come in a number of trims and variants that satisfy customers with different preferences. The D4 is one of them which is the diesel variant powered by a 2.0L turbocharged diesel engine D4204T5 with a power rating of 179hp and 400Nm of Torque. It is fitted with a sunroof and a wood trimming on the interior that gives the Classic touch as it is named.

name: RANGE ROVER SPORT 3.0L SDV6 / PANO SUNROOF
description: Range Rover Sport HSE, High Standard Equipment, sits above SE trim and just below the top spec 5.0L V8 Supercharged. The top of Specs fitted in the Sport HSE include a standard air suspension system that improves Range Rover's comfort and stability at high speeds and when engaging corners, an All Wheel Drive system with the drivetrain including terrain response management system and multiple offroad modes, and an eight speed automatic transmission gearbox. The infotainment system was upgraded with a 10-inch Touchscreen for convenience of car specs access with safety features including automatic emergency braking system, lane keep assist, and a blind spot warning sytem.

name: Toyota Probox
description: The best economical and relevantly commercial station wagon produced by Toyota. Durable and reliable!

name: Citroën DS4 1.6 Turbo
description: The DS 4 is a sub-compact executive luxuryDS sub-brand that was created in 2010 marking the first generation codes NX. At the beginning of the first generation, the petrol engines were as a result of a collaboration between PSA and BMW that led to the creation of the 1.6L 16 valve engine. They were produced in two engine variants for the petrol engines, the 1.6L VTi I4 that is naturally aspirated and the 1.6L THP Turbocharged I4 engine. The turbocharged engine utilises a twin-scroll turbocharger and dual head overhead cams. The DS4 has been equipped with start-stop technology with the battery being optimised to withstand 600,000 starting cycles. During the facelift of the 1st gen DS 4, DS separated fromt Citroën becoming its own brand which led to the new variants getting rid of the Citroën badging. The windows on the rear do not scroll down or open outwards which is a bit funny but some would find intriguing. The car is quite powerful, do not let the sub-compact body lie to you, it will disappear on your face!

name: Audi A5
description: Audi A5 began production in 2007 and has this series has never gotten this interesting. It has been produced under the B-Platform family of cars including the A4 and the Q5. The first generation, Typ 8T, falls under the B8 series while the 2nd Generation, Typ 8W6, falls under the B9 series. The third generation is yet to commence production where Audi seeks to replace the A4/S4 sedan with the A5/S5 fastback series. The A5 is the one of the biggest Audi's dream automobiles!

name: BMW 740i "G11" PURE EXCELLENCE
description: BMW 7 Series luxury saloons come in two versions, the G11 and the G12. The G12 is the long-wheelbase version while the G11 is the normal version of the 7 series. It came into the market on June 2015 when it made its debut and features the CLAR Platform which uses carbon-fibre-reinforced polymer as the main structural chassis components. The use of carbon fibre results in increase of torsional rigidity. The front fascia features a large kidney grille incorporating grille shutters that opens on demand for increased air flow to the engine bay which in return decreases aerodynamic drag. This unit features a range of equipments including run flat tyres, Integral Active Steering, comfort access system, soft close automatic system for doors, climate confort laminated glass and windshield, BMW Display Key which acts as a the iDrive system, Glass roof, sunblind for rear window, active seat ventilation, front and rear heated seats, 4-zone climate control, massage functions for front occupants, headlight washer system, park assistant, 360° surround view, head up display, Harman Kardon premium surround sound system, BMW Gesture control, and acoustic belt warning. Experience pure excellence!

name: Peugeot 2008 GT-Line
description: The 2008 first produced in 2013 with the first generation coded A94, is a luxurious sub-compact crossover SUV, produced by the French automaker, Peugeot. French cars have excelled in producing luxury cars that are very comfortable to drive, making them perfect for long distance drives without all the occupants getting tired of the journey. The roof has been modified to resemble like the one in the Rolls Royce. It has lit lines going through the back and breaking between each other which us an excellent substitute for lacking a moonroof. Being a GT-Line, It gets to the sportier look Peugeot does on its performance cars. It has a Facelifted fascia and a unique red color making it a highly generally attractive car.

name: Audi A3
description: Audi has shown its commitment to ensuring consumers in all markets get to own their dream A3 with the best prices despite the price regulations several countries have on the sizes of their engines. The A3 sedan has been produced in several engine capacities beginning from a 1.0L turbo engine sold in Singapore, a 1.2L TFSI engine sold in Pakistan because of import duties that go high with increased engine capacities, a 1.4L and 1.8L engine which is available with quattro AWD. Our market, primarily from Japan, gets to receive the 1.4L and the 1.2L. This unit has the 1.4L turbocharged petrol engine, a comfy minimalistic interior, and a generally powerful drivetrain.

name: Range Rover Vogue 3.0L TDV6 HSE
description: British Leyland launched the Range Rover line in 1970 and later on adding different models to it including the Sport, Velar, Vogue, and the Evoque. The unit listed is the Range Rover Vogue which was produced with a number of engine variants including the 3.0L Supercharged, turbocharged, and diesel turbocharged variants, a 4.4L diesel engine, and the mighty 5.0L V8 Supercharged petrol engine. This unit has the 3.0L TDV6 Diesel engine mated to the 8-speed ZF8HP automatic transmission gearbox. Close to half a million units have been sold since 2009 to 2016 which is a good indicator of individuals embracing luxury. The L405 series remains to be the highly preferred generation among many consumers for its boldness that catches attention at every show!

name: Mercedes Benz ML350 / PANORAMIC SUNROOF
description: This is among the last few units produced under the W166 generation with the "ML" naming before the facelifted W166 series came in with the new naming the "GLE". One of the bold cars that came with an aggresive fascia depicting a full-size SUV when it is actually a mid-size SUV but with a wide range of luxury features spanning from a multifunctional steering wheel, heated seats, dual zone climate controls, leather bucket-styled seats, an aftermarket infotainment display system with a wide screen, traction control, hill descent control, panoramic sunroof, and amrests both on the front and the rear.

name: Audi A5
description: Audi A5 competes in the same category with other luxury cars such as the BMW 428i and the Mercedes Benz C Class, especially the C200. The A5 offers top of comfort, convenience, and versatility. It is specced with leather-bucket-styled seats that are powered and have heating functionality. It is a Quattro spec meaning it drives all four wheels on demand. It appears also as a physically appealing car.

name: Volkswagen Tiguan 1.4TSI
description: Volkswagen Tiguan has been, overally, the best selling SUV in the Volkswagen Group, with over 900,000 units being produced in 2019 alone. It is an excellent compact crossover with the best offer from this car being the efficiency of the 1.4L TSI engine with a power rating of 148hp and consuming close to what a Mazda Demio does.

name: Mitsubishi Canter
description: Mitsubishi Canter falls in the category of light-duty commercial vehicles manufactured by Mitsubishi Fuso Truck and Bus Corporation which is part of Daimler Truck, that produces the popular Mercedes Benz vehicles. This unit was produced in the 8th generation that began in 2010 and runs an improved 3.0L diesel engine that easily accomodates over 2 Tonnes of payload to about 4.7 Tonnes. It drives the rear wheels through a 4×2 drive system. Canters are durable and are easy to run and maintain.

name: Mazda MPV
description: Mazda MPV is a Multipurpose Van produced since 1988 to 2016 when the last generation, the third, ended. This MPV is said to have inherited the idea of a sports car as narrated by a woman in a commercial. They are both available in front and four-wheel drive setups with the four-wheel drive system available only in the Japanese Market. It has a comfy interior well spaced with the front and rear occupants having sufficient spaces between them with the leather seats having armrests for additional comfort. It is a good alternative to the Toyota Wish and other MPVs.

name: Audi A1
description: The first generation Audi A1 began sales late in 2010 with the first body style being the three-door model. A five-door Sportback, the one listed, began production late 2011 with most of export markets receiving the car in 2012. The Sportback featured a MacPherson strut front and torsion beam rear suspension with the drivetrain consisting of a front wheel drive setup. The powertrain features a 1.0L turbocharged petrol engine with front engine setup mated to a 7-speed S-Tronic automatic transmission gearbox.

name: Mercedes Benz ML250
description: ML 250 was produced in the last production years before ML series nomenclature was changed to GLE series to match with companies naming structure. This is the W166 generation that features a 2.1L 16 Valves Inline-4 Bi-Turbo Mercedes-Benz OM651 DE 22 LA Engine with a power rating of 201hp and 500Nm of Torque. Bodywise, it appears bigger which would make some confuse it with the ML350. On the interior are half bucket-styled leather seats that are powered, parking sensors, Traction control, Multifunctional steering wheel, and Mercedes Comand Infotainment system.

name: Toyota Belta
description: The 2NZ-FE 1.3L engine used in the Toyota Belta won the International Engine of the Year award in the 1-litre to 1.4-litre category in the year 2000. This is attributed by the good performance reviews from consumers and manufacturer. It is known to be a very reliable and durable engine whose dependability has been proven over and over.

name: Mazda Atenza 2.5L
description: To begin with, Mazda did an elegant design on the Atenza which makes it among the top beautiful designs in a comparable class, in the automobiles industry. Comfort was not left out, driving the Atenza feels like an S-Class of sorts, as bumps or rubles are never a bother. The leather seats that are heated both in the front and the rear coupled with the dual zone climate controls make up a highly enjoyable ride. It goes on to have a retractable blind at the car's rear glass shield. Safety begins with lane keep assist, adaptive cruise control, and Blindspot Monitoring Assist necessary during lane change. What a Car!

name: Ford Ranger 3.2L
description: Engineered by Ford of Australia, Ford Ranger T6 that began production in 2011, specifically the worldwide marketed T6, Ford has produced versatile cars that have been able to satisfy both offroad and comfort qualities which many offroading fanatics have been seeking in offroad-capable cars.

name: Nissan DAYZ
