description: Nissan DAYZ is a tall-height kei car that has been in production to majorly satisfy the economic needs of individuals who do commercial taxi services. Fuel efficiency is at the core of its marketing as that is what it excels best in. When one decides to use this unit for Taxi purposes, their clients will have an easy ride time and the driver as well gets to have an easy time all throughout because of the comfort levels the car offers.

name: Audi Q3 2.0L Quattro
description: The Q3 is an excellent German Crossover SUV now in its 2nd Generation since the first began in 2011. Typ F3, 2nd Gen, began in 2018 and still continues until date. They are available in two engine variants,  the 1.4L and the 2.0L turbocharged petrol engines. The 2.0L version is available in this unit with a power rating of 197hp and 280Nm of torque driving from 0-100kph in 8 seconds. It is mated to Quattro All Wheel Drive system that gives the reliability of driving all four wheel on demand.

name: Nissan NV200
description: Here is a one of one undeniably GREAT PRICE deal on this 2016 Nissan NV200. One of the most practical vans that are Multipurpose and ultimately comfortable. Grab the Chance while it LASTS!

name: Toyota Harrier 'Elegance'
description: Toyota began production of the 3rd generation Harrier in 2013, coded XU60, with a facelift being done mid 2017. Available trims post-facelift included Elegance which is the base trim replacing Grand trim pre-facelift, and Progress trim that replaced the Premium trim as the flagship trim. Metal and leather package were added to both Premium and Progress trims. A limited edition called "Style NOIR" available with the Naturally aspirated Premium trim. It runs a 2.0L 3ZR-FAE with Dual VVT-i Naturally Aspirated petrol engine and a front wheel drivetrain.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI 1.2L
description: Turbocharging a small engine means you get premium power runs of bigger engine while being comfortable with low fuel consumption and pocket friendly maintenance costs. This unit additionally has the Auto Start-stop feature that saves on fuel even more. It also has traction control, fabric seats, and climate controls as some of the features.

name: Honda Fit Shuttle Hybrid
description: Honda Fit Shuttle Hybrid is surprisingly one of the best sub-compact station wagon cars to own that give an average of 34Kms a Liter as per a report by Honda. The shuttle hybrid is based on the Fit Hybrid which its smaller brother. This amazing fuel economy is achieved by reducing rolling resistance with front braking, reduced engine friction, improved control efficiency of the hybrid system, ECON mode to minimise fuel consumption, and improved aerodynamics.

name: Renault Lutecia
description: **** Renault Lutecia, a French automobile, has performed well in several markets it has been sold in from Europe as Renault Clio where it has been voted twice as to the Car of the Year Award apart from Golf which has also been voted in twice, to Japan where it has been marketed as Renault Lutecia, a name contributed by Honda because of its rights in the car's sales channel. It is powered by a 1.2L turbocharged petrol engine and is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, Android & TomTom infotainment display screen, and auto start-stop feature.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI 1.4L
description: A Golf R in disguise with the best deal in town. Running the 1.4L engine variant, this 2016 Volkswagen Golf TSI offers the best power rating in its class. It is a very practical and reliable hatch with the best performance needs. It comes with fabric seats, dual zone climate controls, and a multifunctional steering wheel that make up the comfort aspect of the car. The red colour spices it up as well giving it an interesting touch to its sportiness.

name: Subaru Legacy
description: Subaru Legacy, company's flagship, has been marketed widely in huge numbers with positive reviews coming through all the years. It is still being widely bought as of today which proves their reliability and dependability regardless of the journeys made. It has Symmetrical AWD as standard and a 2.5L Naturally Aspirated Petrol engine producing 235Nm of torque. Interior space is not compromised and the car also appears large which many of its consumers like the car for.

name: Volvo S60 T3
description: The only best selling Volvo deal in town, Volvo S60 T3, powered by a 1500cc inline-four turbocharged petrol engine running power figures of 152 horsepower and 250Nm of torque. Volvo has had a magical way of powering up their cars with small engines that end up producing great amount of power. The amount of investment Volvo does to make their consumers comfortable is amazing: comfy bucket-styled seats with heating function and 3-position memory seats with high quality leather material, top of class premium surround sound system, and quite an accomodating interior gives the S60 a 5 star rating. Safety is even non-negotiable!

description:

Specs include a Multifunctional steering wheel, Head up display, memory seats with heating function, rear amrest, sunroof, leather seats, adaptive headlights, analogue instrument cluster, Premium surround sound system, dual zone climate controls, and traction control.

description:
EN ROUTE TO THE PORT OF MOMBASA! EXPECTED TIME OF ARRIVAL 28th FEBRUARY, 2024.

description:
EN ROUTE TO THE PORT OF MOMBASA! EXPECTED TIME OF ARRIVAL MARCH, 2024.

Specs include a 360° view camera, powered leather seats, heated front seats, XDRIVE All Wheel Drive, Multifunctional steering wheel, adaptive LED headlights, daytime running LED lights, Harman Kardon premium surround sound system, and cruise control.

name: Isuzu Trooper / MANUAL
description: Isuzu Trooper was produced by Suzuki between the years of 1981 to 2002. During these years, it has greatly served its owners providing reliability, durability, and perseverance as the name Trooper means. It excels in offroad activities which it was actually meant for as it was entirely produced with optional 4WD drivetrain system. It has sufficient offroad clearance and its powertrain includes a manual transmission system.

name: Nissan Note
description: The Nissan Note is specced with fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, Traction control, Anti-collision brake assist, lane keep assist, and Auto start stop among other features.

name: BMW X3 XDrive 20d M-SPORT
description: Beginning production in 2003, BMW X3 has grown to be a highly liked Luxury SUV. It has a good number of Luxury features it is equipped with including half leather seats that are powered and have two-position memory seats with thigh support, a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, electric parking brake, Autohold brake function, dual zone climate controls, parking sensors, Camera view, and roof rails. It runs a 2.0L B47 straight-4 turbo producing 400Nm of torque.

name: Audi Q5 2.0T QUATTRO S-LINE 'Typ 80A'
description: Typ 80A Audi Q5 made its debut towards the end of 2016 as production began for 2017 sales. It comes as a total redesign from the previous Typ 8R Q5 that began production in 2009. It features a range of new technologies that makes it a favourite of many Audi Consumers. A digital instrument cluster, redesigned steering wheel, dashboard, and center console with the design being more minimalistic than the previous model. Exterior designs became more sharper lowering drag coefficient. Both front and rear lights were also redesigned giving the car a much better admired fascia. It also was uprated just with the EA888 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine to 252hp and 370Nm of torque from the previous 222hp and 350Nm of torque.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI 1.2L
description: Volkswagen Golf MK7 falls under the Compact executive hatchback segment. The 7 in the name 'Mk7' denotes the 7th generation that this model is produced under. It was produced under the MQB platform that it shares with 3rd Gen Audi A3 and Skoda Octavia. This is a perfect executive car tha consumes like a 1.0L Toyota car. Performance and consumption are at its peak with prices highly favourable for such a fast executive car.

name: Mazda Demio 1.5L
description: There are consumers who love the Mazda Demio for the only reason that is a very beautiful car with improved technologies pioneered by 'Kodo' design language. Some love it for its excellent performance and fuel economy. The new Skyactiv-D 1.5L diesel engine makes this diesel variant of Mazda Demio feel like its overpowered but it sufficiently handles what the terrains bring at it. You have different aspects to choose from!

name: Nissan Note
description: Note is a popular subcompact hatchback which also doubles up as a Mini Multipurpose Vehicle in Japan and Europe. It has also been produced in the two countries it has been marketed. It is a convenient car and has benefited a lot of individuals who have been doing city driving for their personal gains or commercially.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D
description: Mazda CX-5 just works fine for any user who would like to take their urban driving to another leve. It has a redefined design both from the interior to the exterior and drives perfectly with the tweaked driving styles. The engine is interestingly powerful as well, a torque of 418Nm makes acceleration and overtaking an easy task!

name: Toyota Fielder Hybrid
description: Toyota Fielder Hybrid turns out to be one of the best cars to have in the Corolla lineup. They were both released at the same time, in 2013, with the Corolla Axio hybrid. They are ranked as some of the most durable cars with reliability being the leading factor. They are also very fuel efficient especially with the hybrid system that runs the car when Internal Combustion is not running. Many reviews say their Toyota Hybrid Fielder does 34Km a Liter in highway and 30Kms a Liter in urban driving which is pretty amazing for such a Wagon!

name: Mercedes Benz C180 KOMPRESSOR
description: The trims offered in the C180 are more or less the same with those of Mercedes Benz C200. This Kompressor version uses a 1.6L Supercharged petrol engine. It is fitted with fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, and side mirror indicators.

name: Suzuki S Cross S×4
description: Suzuki S-Cross S×4 is now at its 3rd generation since it began production in 2006. S-Cross means a Smart Crossover SUV and the S×4 means Sports X-over 4 Seasons. This is the 2nd gen that was Facelifted in 2016 with upgrades including a new fascia described by an updated front grill, tail lights, and an improved interior with a new design fabric seats. It runs  1600cc naturally aspirated petrol engine mated to a 6 speed automatic transmission gearbox. It also has paddle shifters that allows one to drive in manual mode.

name: Mercedes Benz C200 CGI 'AVANTGARDE'
description: Avantgarde is the top trim Mercedes Benz marketed the C200 with. It was offered with Liverpool fabric/leatherette seats and optional leather. It used a different sport grille that had three wide matt-finish horizontal bars and a central Mercedes emblem that appeared boldy at the middle. An optional AMG Bodykit was also available. Upgraded sports suspension and brake piston callipers. The engine features a 1.8L turbocharged M271 CGI Inline-four engine with power rating of 270Nm of torque.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.5L AWD
description: This is the deal unit of the month, an All Wheel Drive Soul Red Metallic with a very low mileage and runs a 2.5L Naturally Aspirated Skyactiv-G petrol engine. This is the engine option that is most soughted after the 2.2 Skyactiv-D engine. The All Wheel Drive setup moreso makes it a rare deal. The Skyactiv-G engine has reduced combustion period by intensifying air flow, increasing injection pressure, and optimizing fuel injection generally. It also has reduced risk of engine knock at high compression by using the 4-2-1 engine exhaust system that merge four exhaust pipes from the 4 cylinders to two secondary pipes and finally to one main exhaust pipe.

name: Subaru Levorg 1.6L Turbo "VM" Advanced Package
description: The first gen Subaru Levorg began production in 2014 and was coded 'VM'. It is only available in two engine configuration that are turbocharged, intercooled, and direct injected. The 1.6L Turbo is fitted in this engine. There is a 2.0L Turbo engine as well. The Levorg has performed well that it has participated in racing championships in RWD configuration. This unit also comes fitted with all the features ranging from Eyesight Adaptive cruise control, side cameras, lane keep assist, Blindspot Monitoring Assist, Traction control to Hill Start to prevent gearbox strain.

name: Volkswagen Passat 1.4 TSI
description: Volkswagen passat B7 gen came with some improvements majorly consisting of the body panels, grille, and headlights. The face of the Passat keeps on getting better with the advancements in generations. This unit is specced with leather seats, an analogue cabin clock, interior wood trimming, Multifunctional steering wheel, heated seats, and powered seats with memory function.

name: Toyota Noah
description: These Vans by Toyota always offer top of class comfort. Their seats are placed high upright with a comfort-oriented posture. They hold one well in place and the armrests lets you rest on the seats. All occupants ultimately get to enjoy the drives!

name: Volkswagen Golf Variant 1.4L
description: The Volkswagen Golf Variant runs either a 1.2L or 1.4L and this unit has the bigger 1.4L turbocharged petrol engine which has enough power with no lag compared to the 1.2L. From users who have interacted with it, they attribute the preference to a reliably powerful engine, easy to maintain engine and car's components, and a generally convenient car!

name: Toyota Harrier / MODELLISTA Bodykit
description: Among the 'flavors' Toyota Harrier comes with is the Modellista bodykit which makes this car look much bolder than the regular Harriers. The Modellista bodykit includes both front and rear diffusers & side skirts that definitely gives it a substantial look. This unit also gets to be equipped with a JBL Premium surround sound system, powered boot, leather seats, cruise control, Anti-collision brake assist, and lane assist as some of its features.

name: Mazda Atenza 2.5L
description: If you are looking for a family car different from Mazda CX-5 but in the same line of Mazda's products, the Atenza is a good fit. Petrol lovers are also sorted out as this unit runs the 2.5L SKYACTIV-G petrol engine, different from the 2.2 diesel variant which we have gotten used to. The station wagon has a large boot for all the stuff you would like to fit in. Passenger spaces are also sufficient giving enough leg and head room. They get to enjoy dual zone climate controls and the driver gets to enjoy convenience from the multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D AWD
description: The new kid on the block that has grown to be very famous since it came in the later years of 2017. Its design, built quality, color codes, engine reliability and power rating, and bold stature has given it a liking, better than the older brother!

name: Nissan Serena
description: An excellent comfortable Highway Star that will give you the longest journey full of comfort, healthy backbone, convenience, safety, and happiness being this car is joyfully comfortable ride. It has 6 seats spaced well for ultimate comfort with safety features such as lane assist. It has cup holders both in the front and the rear. This car's legroom, headroom, and seats quality build is what offers it with the best rated comfort.

name: Nissan Latio
description: Nissan Latio favored consumers who were looking to get something bigger than the smaller March and the larger Nissan Sylphy.
