It has a manual transmission gearbox which gives more control to the driver on gear selection.

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: The XTRAIL is a straight go to car, easy, bold, and very outgoing in all kinds of terrains. It is specced with a 2.0L MR20DD Naturally Aspirated petrol engine with the interior having leather seats, climate controls, and a four spoke steering wheel.

name: Toyota Fielder Hybrid
description: Hybrid Synergy Drive, a new tech adopted by Toyota to supplement the power from its Internal Combustion Engine and to cut down on fuel costs especially in urban driving as it includes increased starts and stops because of road traffic. This is extreme convenience from what the car actually offers in its interior. This is just the right car for reliable and highly convenient drives!

name: Subaru Outback
description: The Name Subaru Outback was adopted Globally upon the entry of Third Generation Subaru Outback in 2003 as different names were used for different markets in the 2nd and 1st Gen. Its clearance was also improved with most markets getting upto 200mm while the US got 220mm. Some sedans were also produced in limited numbers lasting only between 2005 to 2007 as the standard production body style was the 5-door station wagon style.

name: Nissan Note Medalist
description: Nissan Note Medalist was actually designed specifically for the Japanese Market different from the other markets Nissan markets their Notes at. It came specced with special equipment as seen with plated door handles, seude-like cloth seats and artificial leather, piano-like center cluster finish, and genuine leather wrapped on the steering wheel. This is quite an exception!

name: Toyota Toyoace 3.0L
description: Toyoace was produced in the category of light to medium size truck also referred to as cab-over truck for its flat face. This is the 7th Gen that began in 2001 and has been used for various purposes from light to medium heavy works including refrigeration services and has been loved by the Refreshments industry as seen with companies selling drinks.

name: Subaru Impreza G4
description: Subaru Impreza G4 is quite an excellent car both on-road and off-road. It drives gently and also aggressively as one would wish and can comfortably carry a family in either distances. The engine is as well a good fuel consumer with the 1.6L and 2.0L engine options.

name: Mazda Axela
description: Mazda Axela handles excellently on the road, carries an attractive sporty look with less punitive bills on fuel consumption and maintenance.

name: Nissan XTRAIL /Hybrid
description: The XTRAIL already performs well with the MR20DD 2.0L Petrol engine giving excellent fuel consumptions and sufficient power to carry large cargo and families. Adding on the internal combustion engine is a parallel hybrid setup designed to rotate the axle independently or can be coupled up with the internal combustion system to rotate the axle jointly. It also on fuel economy when the power demands are low by rotating the axle by itself.

name: Landrover Discovery IV 'LANDMARK'/ 3-ZONE SUNROOF
description: Landrover Discovery 4 Landmark is that LR4 we all can purchase in a blink of an eye. It features every equipment that was optional in the LR4 series from air suspension to 3 zone sunroof. It has undergone redesigns and styling since 2009 with the introduction of two versions of the 3.0L engine, TDV6 and SDV6. This model runs the 3.0L SDV6 that initially produced 245hp but was uprated to 254hp and 600Nm of torque at 2000RPMs. All the challenges in the previous series LR3 were addressed sorting out mechanical, reliability, engine, and gearbox issues. The turbocharger system features an advanced twin-sequential turbochargers that utilizes a variable geometry turbocharger at low revs and the 2nd turbocharger activated at high speeds giving optimum power and excellent performance.

name: Mitsubishi eK Wagon
description: Mitsubishi eK Wagon is defined as an excellent minicar in the kei class, the smallest car segment, with excellent space on the interior and quite comfy fabric seats with armrests in the front, climate controls, and side mirrror indicators as some of its specs.

name: Mercedes Benz C200 "W205"
description: The W205 was the first car to adopt the Modular Rear Architecture (MRA) Platform giving the car a much lighter body weight because of the use of Aluminum extensively throughout the body. It was available in 5 body styles spanning from sedan coded W205, station wagon/Estate coded S205, Coupe C205, cabriolet A205, and the long-wheelbase sedan coded V205. The C200 shares its turbocharged engine, M274 DE20 LA, with the C200 4MATIC, C250, and the C300 but each has different power rating with the one listed producing 181hp and 300Nm of torque.

name: Mercedes Benz E300/SUNROOF
description: After careful design considerations and works that began in 2003, the final design was produced in 2009 with the unveiling happening at the North American International Auto Show. The E300 featured a 3.0L V6 naturally aspirated petrol engine that running power figures of 228hp and 300Nm of torque. This model also features a sunroof which definitely makes the E300 more interesting.

name: Audi A5
description: A very versatile Audi with a myriad of capabilities. It can go round the world maxing out its power while transversing every kind of terrain with one of the World's best AWD setup, Quattro!

name: Mitsubishi Galant Fortis Sportback
description: The Galant Fortis has gained a lot of popularity in the various markets it has been sold in throughout the production years until 2017 when they ended production. Getting yourself this would be one of many jackpots for true Mitsubishi lovers who have always fancied the Lancer or thr Galant as is it was marketed in Japan since 2007.

name: Suzuki Wagon R
description: Suzuki Wagon R despite being classified in Japan as a Kei car, meaning light and the smallest car size category, maximised its roof-floor space giving better relaxed and comfortable drives. Its assortment of specs including heated seats for the driver, Auto start stop fetaure, and headlights range adjustment gives this car much value for the Kei-car category.

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: Discover New Trails with Nissan X-TRAIL!

name: BMW 525i
description: There is just a lot to admire about a BMW. The 'eyes' probably, how low it sits, how it drives, or the excellent craftmanship of its engines.

name: Mercedes Benz GLE 450h 4MATIC
description:
CURRENTLY UNDERGOING CLEARING AT THE PORT OF MOMBASA 

It is specced with Heated seats, Air suspension setup, Multifunctional, tilt & telescopic steering wheel, Mercedes MBUX infotainment system, Downhill speed regulation system, Active parking assist sytem, Ambient lighting, Headlights with range adjustment functionality, Panoramic sunroof, Multiple climate zones, and Smartphone integration.

name: Porsche Macan S
description:
EN ROUTE TO MOMBASA!!

The Macan S produced by Porsche since early 2014 runs a very powerful Porsche 3.0L V6 twin turbocharged V6 petrol engine producing 335bhp and 460Nm of torque with an acceleration of up to 100kmh in only 4.8s. It has a sunroof and half leather seats as some of its specs.

name: Audi A4 2.0L S-LINE
description: Here is an A4 coming in a new sauce. A station wagon variant with a 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine driving the front wheels. This is an S-Line variant with heated half-leather seats with power function on the interior. You also get dual zone climate controls, Multifunctional steering wheel, and polished metal trimming on the interior.

name: Nissan Note Nismo S
description: An exceptionally interesting Nissan Note money can buy in the entire world.

name: Toyota Vitz RS 1.5L
description: Vitz RS is the performance version of Vitz. It was launched in 2005 with redesigns including deep side skirts, RS badged meshed grille, and a powerful 1.5L petrol engine with 107bhp and 147Nm of torque

name: Mercedes Benz GLC 250 4 MATIC
description: Mercedes GLC 250 replaced the GLK Class in 2015 for 2016 model years. It is a premium Compact SUV equivalent to the C Class sedan. It features a 2.0L turbocharged petrol engine, a multifunctional steering wheel, multi zone climate control, heated seats with memory function, ambient lighting, and active parking assist system.

name: Subaru Levorg
description: Subaru Levorg introduced in 2014 has proven to give owners an excellent ownership experience with good performance from the 'small' 1600cc Turbocharged Petrol Engine. 'Small' is an understatement! Underrating a Levorg on the road might not turn out so well.

name: Mercedes Benz C200/SUNROOF
description: A fully loaded Mercedes Benz C200 with a panoramic sunroof, red leather seats, dual zone climate controls, steering wheel assist, and lane assist. The C200 gives a class thrill and driving experience. It is just perfect as it is!

name: Toyota Hilux D CAB
description: Here is rugged and very agile pickup truck, a UK Spec Toyota Hilux Double Cab with manual transmission. It is still in perfect condition with all the seats well knitted together and body in good shape. It serves consumers who operate relatively heavy loads with the big space at the back and a powerful 2.5L 2KD Diesel engine.

name: Lexus GS350
description: Lexus GS was introduced in Japan as Toyota Aristo in 1991 until 2005 when it was sold as GS. This, listed, is a performance sedan that began sales in Japan at the end of 2005. GS 350 was equipped with a 3.5L 2GR-FSE V6 engine with D4-S direct injection with 6 speed Automatic transmission gearbox. On the interior, it is specced with powered leather seats, interior wood trim, and side mirror indicators.

name: FAW Fighter
description: Exceptionally reliable and quality trucks for all cargo sizes from small to large. FAW Trucks is your partner!

name: Porsche Cayenne 3.6 V6
description: Cayenne was a major leap for Porsche as it had spent a lot of years focusing on performance and luxury sedans leaving out offroading and mid & full size luxury cars. Sharing its platform, body frame, and electronics with the Touareg and Q7, it allows VAG Group enthusiasts have a wide range of SUVs to choose from. From official activities to family and road trips, Porsche Cayenne serves all purposes excellently!

name: Toyota Porte
description: Porte is a mini Multipurpose Van developed by Toyota offering an excellent comfortable car with a high roof line and a very spacious legroom. The interior design we give it to Toyota for giving a classy and minimalistic design that is very welcoming. You might as well love this car by just looking at the interior. It also shines in its cost effective performance with engine options of 1.3L and 1.5L giving figures of up to 18Kms a liter!

name: Toyota Harrier
description: Seems Toyota Harrier had a good taste of design ever since the older generation models. The 2007 model even came with powered seats that you could adjust in multiple directions at the comfort of just a button. It also had a high enough clearance that made easy for maneuvering of tough terrains. Quite comfortable and classy as well. It has never lost that taste.

name: Volkswagen Touareg 3.6 V6
description: When a car is produced with Porsche, then you know it is not a joke. The 1st Gen of Touareg was first produced in 2002 and straight up won several awards for its among it for being the best in the 4×4 car category. It shares a lot of parts with the Cayenne and the engine is their biggest similarity with it being equipped with a 3.6L Petrol V6 engine. This is a go-to car for someone who wants to use it for several purposes including offroading and for urban setups.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D AWD
description: The CX-5 can be considered as a smart car that quickly adopted market needs and incorporated them into the designs as the years came by. Until the current model years, all the consumer needs have been continously addressed with reliability, convenience, and efficiency with excellent power output.

name: Audi A6 2.0L TFSI  "C7.5"
description: This is among the first post-facelift units to be sold after the reveal at the 2014 Paris Motor Show. Entry level A6 models received a front wheel drive system with 7 speed dual clutch automatic transmission replacing the multitronic continuously variable transmission. They definitely became Much better with its reliability skyrocketing and design aesthetics attracted even more consumers.

name: Mazda Axela
description: The Axela has a lot of pros that come with its small 1.5L petrol engine that has relatively good output with torque of 144Nm, enough boot space and legroom for the car's occupants, excellent reliability, and versatility. You can't think of any other hatch from those in its class with these features.

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: XTRAIL added a taste to the front fascia giving a different vibe to what we are normally used to. And with smoked lights at the back, those who like something different from the traditional XTRAIL design have something to look up to.

name: Volkswagen Golf TSI 1.4L
description: The 1.4L Turbocharged Petrol Engine gives a better drive feel compared to the younger brother with the 1.2L turbocharged engine. The 20Nm torque difference will give you a better head start over any car of the same class which gives the Golf TSI 1.4L some leverage.

name: Honda Fit Hybrid
description: The Hybrid system in Honda consists of a petrol powered engine and a lithium-ion battery pack that is charged by a generator powered by the engine that in turn powers the drive motor when the engine is not running. This is a very efficient fuel saving and power generation mechanism that makes Honda Fit Hybrid a very reliable model.

name: Chevrolet Aveo
description: Chevrolet Aveo was produced by General Motors as from 2002. Aveo was sold in over 120 countries under seven different brands including the famous Chevrolet and Suzuki. It was sold in three body models including a 4-door sedan, 5-door hatchback, and 3-door hatchback only sold in some European hatchbacks. The unit listed is a 4-door sedan specced with fabric seats, climate controls, and a 5-speed manual transmission gearbox.

name: Porsche Cayenne GTS "Type 92A"
description: Cayenne GTS was offered in the first generation of Cayenne, E1 Gen when the chassis coded 9PA was updated in 2008. Its chassis was tweaked to be a lot more sportier with lowered sports suspension, sports exhaust system that one can open and close valves depending on how you would like them to sound, Porsche Active Suspension Management and high performance wheels. The main spice of the GTS is a very powerful and efficient 3.6L V6 engine that is twin turbocharged and direct injected. 600Nm torque can be peaked easily at 1600 RPMs and the thrilling 440 horsepower gives you a quick acceleration of 4.9s which is super fast for such an SUV.The interior has been well curated with Alcantara lacing on the roof, carbon fibre trimming on the center console, and red leather stitching with GTS embroidery on the headrests.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: Harrier is premium SUV by Toyota that accomodates consumers who still love Toyota but would want extras of a comfortable and convenient SUV. Toyota Harrier offers that. From powered seats, eco mode that by far saves on fuel by reducing engine performance and maximising on fuel efficiency, Auto start stop feature, high clearance, dual zone climate controls, a multifunctional steering wheel, push to start button, and Traction control that is practical in handling multiple terrains.

name: Volkswagen Polo GTI
description: Polo GTI is not your normal Volkswagen Polo. It is a rocket hiding in a Polo body. Introduced in 2010, it was designed with different front and rear bumpers, a roof spoiler, calipers colored in red, chrome plated twin tailpipe, a tweaked sports suspension system, and Electronic limited slip differential that assists in reducing understeer when engaging sharp corners. Earlier models came with the 1.4L engines with Turbocharger and Supercharger but the later models from 2014, when a facelift was done, were fitted with a 1.8L Turbocharged Stratified Engine mated to either a 6 speed manual or 7 speed DSG gearbox. The Manual transmission spec does 320Nm of torque while the Automatic spec maxs its torque at 250Nm.

name: Mazda Atenza 2.2D
description: SKYACTIV is a series of technologies that Mazda intended that they increase engine output and fuel efficiency. The Mazda Atenza uses a Skyactiv-D engine which is a group of diesel engines that are turbocharged. The Atenza uses SH-VPTS engine with a displacement of 2191cc. This engine was first used in CX-5s. In the Atenza, it produces 173hp and 420Nm of torque which gives the Atenza an edge over other sedans of the same class.

name: Nissan XTRAIL Hybrid
description: We all love the new gen of Nissan XTRAILs coming into the market. This one has been specced with leather seats with two tone colours of black and beige, dual zone climate controls, android infotainment display system, side mirror indicators and a camera on the left side-mirror, fog lights, and dual exhaust tailpipes.

name: Mitsubishi Pajero
description: Pajero is a full size SUV (Sport Utility Vehicle) that is very efficient in handling multiple terrains including offroad and urban setups. It runs a very capable engine and excellent drivetrain with locking diffs for offroad mode. It also works well for large family setups as a number of Pajeros come in 5 up to 7 seats!

name: Toyota Axio
description: Toyota Axio has been loved for its fuel consumption with the 1.5L being very efficient. Now, A new tech is here in the Axio to even make life in it even more pleasing, VVT-iE technology. Variable Valve Timing- intelligent by Electric Motor (VVT-iE) is a variant of dual VVT-i that uses an electrically operated actuator to control camshaft timing. It can either rotate faster or slower to adjust camshaft speed as it spins together with the intake camshaft. It improves engine accuracy and response resulting into better fuel economy, power output, and reducing on emissions.

name: Nissan Teana
description: Teana was introduced to the market as a very ambitious car. It came as a smaller sister to Murano, sat just below the Skyline, replaced the BlueBird, and with a style that adopted more of traditional homelike designs than modern technologies. Wood interior trimming, fabric seats, climate controls, and FM Radio system are some of its interior specs. It runs a 2.3L VQ23DE V6 engine that's interestingly powerful.

name: Volkswagen Jetta GTI
description: A number of individuals say if you want to avoid a number of car problems, you might as well take the Jetta. With a reliability rating of 4 of 5, it scores well in a list of compact cars. This model year car had a redesigned front bumper that reduced collision impact incase of a pedestrian collision reducing the impact on the passenger. Electronic stability program, anti-slip regulation, brake assist, and active head restraints are some of the safety features it is fitted with. On the interior are comfortable leather seats, steering wheel controls, dual zone climate controls, and an android infotainment system.

name: Toyota Esquire
description: Well, you've probably been thinking about Toyota Noah or the Voxy, but here is greater deal, unmatched luxury and unlimited options to how one can use it. Great Family experience or amazing commercial passenger services is just a step away from next level elevation, PURCHASE! Its good looking nature is attributed to the Aero Body Kit which is factory standard for this and the Voxy. An Auto Start Stop feature, Toyota Safety sense incorporating collision warning and lane assist are also part of this unit. Be pretty sure the 3ZR-FAE 2.0L NA engine will drive you comfortably!

name: BMW 523i 2.0L N20B20 "F10"
description: F10 Series of BMW 523i was first sold in 2011 with the series in general coming with major improvements that included dual Clucth transmission as used with the M5, 8 speed automatic transmission gearbox, and the turbocharged V8 engine as with the S63 engine among other specs. This unit is among the first models of the 1st year of F10 sales and is specced with 5 fabric seats, an Alcantara laced steering wheel, parking sensors, Autohold brake function, auto start stop feature, and a 2.0L N20B20 inline-four turbocharged engine that was comparatively better than the N52/N53 NA six cylinder engines.

name: BMW 320i Touring 2.0L N46NB20 "E91"
description: The unit listed was produced as a 5 door wagon or estate 320i series from the year 2004. In some markets as the North American, it was marketed as a Sports Wagon. It succeeded the E46 that was produced until 2006 for 9 years and later was succeeded by F30 and F31 series as from 2012 although the 5th Gen 3 series ended production in 2013. This unit features fabric seats, Dual zone climate controls, BMW iDrive infotainment system, multifunctional steering wheel, push-start ignition, and a speedo clock of up to 260Km/h.

name: Mitsubishi Canter FE 84
description: The Canter FE 84 is a light duty commercial truck that delivers excellent torque for sufficiently hauling the truck's cargo in line with its payload. This unit has a manual transmission which is pretty standard in such trucks because of their load capacities and can comfortably accomodate three passengers in the front.

name: Alfa Romeo Giulietta Sportiva
description: Alfa Romeo Giulietta is in the class of subcompact executive cars manufactured by the Italian Automaker. Typ 940 Gen lasted for 10 years from 2010 to 2022 with sales totalling to about half a million. It underwent the first facelift in 2013 and the 2nd in 2016. The first featured uConnect infotainment system that came in 5" or 6.5" radio navigation Touchscreen system, revised front grill and chrome plating for fog lights, and new wheels design. It runs a powerful fun to drive 1.4L Turbocharged Petrol engine with MultiAir tech that features hydraulically actuated Variable Valve Timing.

name: Subaru Legacy 2.0L
description: The 4th Gen of Subaru Legacy adopted a new design that began development early in 1999 while production began in 2003. With the chassis being stiffened, a more aggresive and a better handling car especially with sharp corners. The Japanes market received a 500cc less capacity engine from the North American market that recived 2.5L turbocharged engines. The Japanese market received a 2.0L with power figures of 240hp and 345Nm of Torque.

name: Subaru Outback
description: This is a well kept Subaru Outback with a rating of 4 of 5. All components are still intact from the engine, the fabric seats, Infotainment system, sneering wheel controls, and the body!

name: Audi Q5 2.0T S-LINE QUATTRO
description: Q5s have a very high resilience on how it handles with its users maintaining its original state and shape over the years of use. This 2014 model has been slightly used and is seeking another enthusiastic owner to continue its adventures. It is specced with half leather seats, dual zone climate controls, Multifunctional steering wheel, and a pristine black color on the exterior.

name: Toyota Avensis
description: The Avensis is related to Toyota Premio and Allion amongst other cars in the same family line as the Corolla. It has been in production from 1997 to 2018 with upgrades being done as the years and generations go by. They are only produced in models of four-door saloons and five door lift backs and estates. The unit listed is an estate version specced with beige half leather seats, a multifunctional steering wheel with paddle shifters, dual zone climate controls, a very spacious boot space, side mirror indicators, and fog lights.

name: Subaru Outback 2.5L
description: This is a car you can spec into a beast you think it can be. Its chassis and body build stands ready to be after-sale specced. It is an excellent cargo, passenger, and offroading car. Whatever you throw at it, it will gladly receive.

name: Daihatsu Mira
description: Mira in a number of aspects stands out. Practicability, convenience, ease of operation especially in monetary aspect, straightforward driving, top notch maneuverability as with tight spaces, and a very reliable 660cc engine.

name: SUBARU WRX S4
description: WRX was initially based on Impreza that was produced for World Rally Championship in 1992. STI means Subaru Technica International while the WRX means World Rally eXperimental. You probably have seen the older models bearing the name Impreza STI while the newer models just have the name WRX S4. In 2015, models in the WRX line were separated from Impreza and hence the name Subaru WRX S4. Now you know what this car was intended for!

name: Renault Lutecia RS "IV" Trophy
description: Renault Lutecia IV is the 4th gen of Lutecia that made a debut in 2012. It has been upgraded with improvements including an extended wheelbase touching also the car's width. The RS(Renault Sport) version similarly was launched in 2012 with a number of adaptations being made including the use of 6-speed EDC(Efficient Double Clucth) instead of a manual transmission, a 1.6L DIG-T Nissan MR16DDT inline four engine doing 200hp and 240Nm of torque. The unit listed is an RS Trophy version with an uprated engine doing 217bhp and 280Nm of torque. Interior features include Renault R-Link 7 inch infotainment system that incorporates Android OS and TomTom Tech system that provides navigation assistance. This is now a proper French Hatchback!

name: Isuzu Dmax D CAB 2.5D
description: Isuzu Dmax is one powerful Multipurpose pickup truck that can be used in various tasks from heavy cargo to official activities. The 2.5L turbocharged diesel engine producing up to 400Nm of Torque. It also comes with Limited Slip differential that reduces wheel spin increasing traction. It drives all the 4 Wheels giving it an edge in unforgiving terrains and the bullbar both in the rear and the front that gets to protect its body from accidental damages.

name: Audi A4 ALLROAD "B8"
description: Audi Allroad Quattro is a version of Audi's models that were meant for offroading adventures. It made a debut in 1999 with the Audi A6 avant being the first Allroad to be offered with this version. Audi A4 as well adopted this version as from 2009. This is the B8 Generation of the A4 that ended production in 2015. Allroad handles offroading way better with modifications including a wider kit, increased clearance, steel underbody to gaurd components, and roof rails for offroading equipments additions.

name: Volkswagen Sharan Typ 7N
description: The 2nd Gen of Volkswagen Sharan began production in 2010 with the first ever production of the Sharan beginning in 1995. It is considered as a Multipurpose Van because of its stature having a high roof and sufficient space for large cargo capacities and a good number of passengers. Ending its production in 2022, Sharan remains to be a very good MPV even as the Automotive world shifts from MPVs to Crossover SUVs!

name: Subaru Outback 2.5L/SUNROOF
description: Subaru Outback is among the best modern cross-over Station Wagons equipped with a wide variety of technologies spanning from Subaru's Eyesight feature that makes Adaptive cruise control possible and additionally lane keep assistance, Traction control, Symmetrical AWD which is the best in the world, highly sufficient legroom and roof height, 920 liters of boot space expandable to over 2000 liters when the back seats are folded, and to add on to this unit is the sunroof. Just a perfect SUV!

name: Mazda CX-5 2.5L
description: Design engineers at Mazda hit the nail in the head. Beautiful exterior designs with aerodynamically important curves, slightly minimalistic yet full equipped interior, well stitched leather seats with excellent comfort that are also greatly coloured in cream, and importantly a powerful engine in a strong durable Skyactiv Chassis.

name: Nissan Juke
description: The name 'Juke' originated from the word 'jukebox', that is used to play music, meaning to dance while behaving in an agile manner. It represents freedom and a daring spirit. It serves the purpose excellently. Go all out in the Nissan Juke as you take new daring paths!

name: Toyota Hiace
description: This is a very clean Toyota Hiace capable of carrying up to 14 individuals powered by a 2.7L doing close to 270Nm of torque. It is in excellent condition with every part of it in an optimum state.

name: Toyota Isis
description: Isis is a large Multi Purpose Vehicle fitted with 7 seats. It has been majorly used by families with 7 individuals capacity or less  and also by some to commercially transport persons or cargo from one point to another. Being also a very reliable Toyota, you can use the Isis for long distance purposes and it would still see you to and back!

name: Volkswagen Touareg 3.6 FSI
description: Volkswagen Touareg doubles up as a premium urban vehicle and as a serious offroader as seen with the photos in this car. Powered by a 3.6L V6 FSI engine that racks all terrains with pride, it also gives you great fuel economies and having Blue Motion technology, it really came into the market with the intention of giving high fuel efficiency and it achieves this by reducing rolling resistance that is with tires that have low resistance and improved aerodynamics, longer gear ratios as with the last two gears, and advanced engine mapping.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D AWD
description: Good things have been done to this already great car to own. A blissful music session or even a movie session watching from Mazda's infotainment system to its output in the aftermarket audio system by Pioneer music system that matches its color with the car's door panels and the center console, leather seats in black with power and memory functions, a multifunctional steering wheel, and carbon fibre trimming  on majority of the car parts make up the specs on this unit.

name: Mitsubishi Outlander
description: Definitely the best good looking aftermarket moded Mitsubishi Outlander. With an aftermarket lip-like bumper on the front, aftermarket lights, excellently stitched leather seats for all the 5 individuals, aftermarket music system, and a generally well kept car on the interior and exterior!

name: Peugeot Boxer Van
description: Boxer is a large commercial van with a cargo capacity of 11.5T and a powerful 2.2L diesel engine. On the front is a three seat carrying capacity made of fabric. It drives with manual transmission mode giving even better control while driving with large cargo carriage!

name: Range Rover Sport 3.0 SDV6 HSE
description: Range Rover Sport HSE, High Standard Equipment, sits above SE trim and just below the top spec 5.0L V8 Supercharged. The top of Specs fitted in the Sport HSE include a standard air suspension system that improves Range Rover's comfort and stability at high speeds and when engaging corners, an All Wheel Drive system with the drivetrain including terrain response management system and multiple offroad modes, and an eight speed automatic transmission gearbox. The infotainment system was upgraded with a 10-inch Touchscreen for convenience of car specs access with safety features including automatic emergency braking system, lane keep assist, and a blind spot warning sytem.

name: Nissan Juke
description: Nissan Juke is arguably one of those highly aerodynamically designed cars. With the hatch or coupe design like at the back, air flows in an airplane-wing like orientation and adding to a spoiler evens helps more with drag effect from air flow. Arguably, that is one of the reason why the Juke-R with the GTR 3.8L V6 engine was produced in just the same design as the famous Juke.

name: Subaru Forester 2.0 NA
description: A Naturally Aspirated Subaru Forester is here with us. For the many who prefer the Naturally Aspirated version over the turbocharged one, this is the time! The Naturally Aspirated variant produces descent power of 146hp and 196Nm of torque without a strain. The interior is also excellent with half leather seats as the main highlights and heated seats both in the front and rear seats also taking the day!

name: Nissan Note
description: Nissan Notes are in large numbers in our roads since majority began to purchase them. It has been very reliable and convenient for many. It runs a 1.2L engine that does very good on consumption up to 18kms a liter. The interior with 5 fabric seats that passengers can sit comfortably with the driver operating the car features from an android infotainment display screen at the center.

name: Audi A6 2.0L TFSI QUATTRO "C7.5"
description: The A6 is an all rounder. It has made a lot of improvements in tech, design, convenience, and comfort. C7.5 joins the market as an elegant piece of engineering! Experience excellent driving.

name: Subaru Forester
description: This Subaru Forester is specced with half leather seats, push-start ignition, Multifunctional steering wheel, android infotainment display system, dual zone climate controls, rear armrest with cupholders, and Subaru's eyesight system. It also has heated seats and X-Mode for offroading adventures.

name: Toyota Ractis
description: Ractis gives an interior advantage to both passengers and cargo on its height from the car floor. It can comfortably sit any person of any height and even large size cargos as it has a high roof compared with other cars of similar class. It has side mirror indicators, fabric seats, climate controls, and android infotainment system among other specs.

name: Toyota Harrier
description: Toyota Harrier shines in its class of Mid Size SUVs that is full of competing vehicles. It has been chosen by many from all economic classes as a family car and even yet an errands car. It is very reliable, convenient, and durable. It is also a premium unit that matches top cars in executive automotive car segments.

name: Mercedes Benz C200
description: The W205 Mercedes Benz C200 made a debut in 2014 bringing in an all new architecture platform called the Modular Rear Architecture Platform that adopted the use of Aluminum throughout the car body structure which gives it a very light body compared to the W204 that looked and was actually heavy. Some of the standard features that came with this new Gen include 9 airbags, Collision prevention assist, attention and adaptive brake assist, and an electric parking brake among other features.

name: Subaru Legacy
description: Subaru Legacy is Subaru's flagship car that was first produced in 1989. You receive the Symmetrical All Wheel Drive setup, and the boxer engine as standard. You can never go wrong with a flagship model.

name: Mercedes Benz E250
description: Did you know that the 2013 facelift on the Mercedes Benz E Class is arguably the most expensive facelift in the automotive industry racking up close to £1 Billion. The W212 E250 as it is a member of the E Class was also part of this facelift. Now, how much of a valuable car is this you're getting. Tafakari!

name: Nissan XTRAIL
description: This is the ultimate crossover from Nissan, the XTRAIL performs close to the Xterra and the Pathfinder. Its sister in the North American Market was named Nissan Rogue. The 3rd gen model made a huge improvement from the previous old plain design to a better good looking urban oriented car. A hundred percent surety of you not hesitating to buy this car when you experience how it drives.

name: Toyota Allion 1.8L
description: A sister to the Avensis introduced at the same time, Toyota Allion adopts a sporty design which very well accommodates Toyota Lovers who are into sports. It is a very reliable car whose durability matches how one uses and maintains it.

name: Daihatsu Mira
description: Produced since 1980, Daihatsu Mira was produced for commercial purposes as a city vehicle. Its usage with Uber and Bolt cases are the perfect examples of its commercial use. The engine also is an excellent use case, with a 660cc displacement capacity, fuel consumption levels are at its best.

name: Volvo XC60 T5 "Inscription" AWD
description: Volvo for a long time have mastered their game with small production engines but great power. The XC60 runs a 2.0L engine with front engine layout and an All wheel drive system. Its power figures are 251hp and 350Nm of torque similar to a Typ 80A Q5. Its design aspect is also receives a hats off!

name: Toyota Hilux D CAB
description: Much has been said of the 3.0L 1KD D-4D engine by toyota. Its reliability and durability wraps up great praise for the Toyota Hilux Double Cab. It can haul heavy loads and not break down, it can tow other vehicles in need of towing and it can comfortably carry an extra bunch of passengers at the back!

name: Ford Ranger 3.2L(Raptor Kitted)
description: Offroad king in a very sophisticated design that is an eyecatcher at a glance. Offroading tires, side steps, offroad modes, comfortable rides in offroad fitted suspensions and half leather seats on the interior, and a high torque 3.2L turbocharged Duratorq diesel engine.

name: Audi Q5 2.0T QUATTRO "Typ 80A"
description:
ENROUTE TO MOMBASA.
It is important to note that the 2nd Gen Audi Q5 Typ 80A shares a platform with the A4 and A5 B9 versions, the Audi MLB Evo platform. Some would refer the Q5 2nd Gen as the B9 because of the platform. This has leather seats with heating functionality, parking sensors, Audi drive select, Audi MMI Infotainment sytem, and a multifunctional steering wheel as some of its specs!

name: Toyota Succeed
description: The Succeed can double up as multi purpose car, from a passenger vehicle to a daily office vehicle, its convenience preceeds it. It is fitted with fabric seats, android infotainment display system, climate controls, and traction control system.

name: Mazda Demio
description: The Demio runs a 1300cc Naturally aspirated petrol engine doing 94hp and 102Nm of torque. Coloured in red, this would favour those who like the red color a lot. It has fabric seats, climate controls, android infotainment display system, and steering wheel controls on the interior

name: Audi A6 2.0L TFSI
description: A White-brown coloured A6, on the outside is a White factory paint, and on the interior are brown leather seats. Quite a color spec. It is fitted with an Audi MMI Infotainment system, dual zone climate controls, leather seats, and a dual exhaust tailpipe.

name: Peugeot 2008
description: Here is another red coloured Peugeot 2008, giving  you full options on the colors. It is specced with half leather seats, climate controls, roof rails, side mirror indicators, and a multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Peugeot 308
description: The peugeot 308 came as a replacement of the 307. It sits below the 508 and just above the 208. It is powered by a 1200cc turbocharged petrol engine with 128hp and 230Nm of torque, a speedometer maxing at 250Km/h, cruise control, steering wheel controls, climate controls, android infotainment display system, and electric parking brake.

name: Honda Fit Hybrid
description: The Honda Fit hybrid is a very forgiving car especially when it comes its fuel economy. With the 1.5L hybrid engine, you get up to 18Km/L on the minimum. You also get sufficient legroom and enjoyable drives with the half leather seats!

name: Mitsubishi Fuso F1
description: This is medium duty truck powered by a 4000cc turbocharged diesel engine mated to a manual transmission gearbox. Its cabin can accommodate 3 persons with the seats being manuall operated. The occupants get to enjoy music from a FM Radio system fitted in. It has a load carrying capacity close to 10 Tonnes which makes it very capable of carrying any kind of laod+

name: Peugeot 208
description: We are receiving a lot of good reviews on this car from our clients, some of them say the steering wheeel is enjoyable and easy to steer, some enjoy the beautiful fabric seats, and some enjoy the smooth rides. We would like to hear what your reviews are as well.

name: Audi Q5
description: The Q5s never run out of fashion, you always get different units styled differently especially with the seats that are sometimes half-leather and some full leather, some would come in S-Line versions and some non S-Line but the feel of its performance and drive always catches every driver's spirit. This unit has half leather seats and is an S-Line versions.

name: Audi Q7 3.0TDI
description: Audi favored large family consumers by introducing the 7 seater Audi Q7. Powered by a 3000cc Turbocharged Diesel V6 Engine producing 233 horsepower and 500Nm of torque.Its 7 seats have leather material and are powered. It also has a multifunctional 4 spoke steering wheel. Its ground clearance is excellent for offroading adventures as well!

name: Isuzu NQR 5.0L
description: Isuzu are big on heavy automobiles. This is an Isuzu NQR locally assembled at their plant here in Kenya. It is powered by a 5000cc Turbocharged diesel engine that can haul extremely large cargos including cement, sand, and any other heavy commodity. It has a manual transmission which gives the driver more control over power output and driving terrains.

name: Suzuki Solio
description: This is the 2nd Gen Suzuki Solio that was based on the Wagon R. It has been produced since 1997. It runs a 1.24L engine that is naturally aspirated and can carry 4 passengers comfortably in 4 fabric seats. It has an Automatic transmission gearbox, climate controls, and an FM Radio system among its specs.

name: Volkswagen Passat TSI
description: The Station Wagon variant of Volkswagen Passat is not an everyday sight. We've brought you one of them, a 2016 Volkswagen Passat TSI Variant with 5 fabric seats, android infotainment display screen, Multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, side mirror indicators, and roof rails.

name: Toyota Fielder "S"
description: Toyota Fielder S is a sporty version of the Fielder that is very instrumental in handling terrains while in Sports mode that needs one to drive at high speeds while engaging corners or obstacles. It has an 1800cc naturally aspirated engine with Valvematic technology. It has 5 seats that have fabric material, android infotainment system, steering wheel controls, climate controls, and a 4WD system.

name: Mitsubishi Galant Fortis Sportback  2.0 Ralliart
description: Here is an excellent Mitsubishi Galant Fortis Sportback that's in a perfect condition. It is specced with 5 Fabric seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, android infotainment system, paddle shifters, cup holders, and a very spacious boot space.

name: Mercedes Benz GLC 250 4 MATIC
description: The Mercedes Benz GLC250 4 MATIC carries a different taste of what SUVs give. Brown leather stitchings on the dash, door panels, and seats that are half fabric, a revised grill, side steps, ambient lighting, and sufficient interior space make this an excellent unit!

name: Audi Q5 2.0T S-LINE QUATTRO "Typ 8R"
description: 2016 was the last year of production for the Q5 Type 8R which was the first generation of the Q5. Earlier in 2012, a facelift was done to improve on its general design and engine power which saw an uprated engine, the 2.0L EA888, producing 222 horsepower and 350Nm of torque from the previous figure of 208 horsepowers. Q5s have never failed its owners since its inception, and this even motivated Audi to go into the next gen Q5, Typ 80A, in 2017 with production beginning September 2016.

name: Audi A5 2.0T QUATTRO S-Line
description: Audi A5 has a very huge tuning potential. The Kenyan Car scene with some famous tuners has shown us what this beast is capable of. It runs an EA888 2.0L petrol engine coded CDNC with  a quattro drivertrain. Its stock power figures are 208 horses and 350 Nm of torque which can be uprated even to 800 horses as some tuners have shown. Quite a fancy comfortable car with leather powered seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, cup holders, an S-Line trimming, and performance oriented design cue with the exhauts being dual tailpipes.

name: Volvo XC60 D4/SUNROOF
description: Volvo introduced an even more powerful version of the XC60, D4, which has a D4204T5 turbocharged diesel engine producing 400Nm of Torque. The petrol variant has 350Nm of torque. It is specced with cream leather seats, a panoramic sunroof, a multifunctional steering wheel, a wooden trimming, and powered seats with memory function.

name: Toyota Hiace 2.7L
description: You rarely find a Toyota Hiace this clean. Looks like it is fresh from the factory, from the body paint to seats. Its powertrain is from a 2.7L petrol engine driving 2 Wheeels. It has 14 seats carrying capacity with the seats having fabric material. It has no scratches and no dents giving it a very good rating of its state!

name: Volvo S60 T3
description: Volvo S60 T3, powered by B4164T3 1600cc inline four turbocharged engine producing 148 horsepower and 240Nm of torque, is an excellent unit to use in any kind of activity from office errands to farm stuff. Very comfortable with buckey shaped bright leather seats and a Premium surround sound system, and very adventurous with a Sunroof.

name: Toyota Vanguard
description: A very efficient alternative to the RAV4, Toyota Vanguard. Running on a 2.4L power house, it is convenient enough to carry large loads of cargo and a good number of up to 5 occupants in its fabric seats. They can be enjoying some good music from an FM Radio system as the driver controls car systems with steering wheel controls. Experience more with the purchase of this unit!

name: Nissan Latio
description: This Nissan Latio is still very fresh and looking quite new judging from its very well maintained exterior and interior. It has 5 fabric seats, climate controls, and side panel indicators that compliment the front and rear positioned indicators among its specs

name: Landrover Discovery IV/ SUNROOF
description: Landrover Discovery has a very rich history of evolution since 1989 when the First Series of the 1st generation was introduced. This is the second generation (L319), Discovery 4, also known as LR4, which was produced from 2009 to 2016. This unit is the last of its generation. Powered by a 3.0L SDV6 engine producing 254 horsepower and 600Nm of torque. It is mated to a ZF 8HP70 automatic transmission gearbox which came as a standard transmission from 2014. It was much upgraded in 2012 to include powerful brakes from Ranger Rover Sport, thicker anti-roll bars for better road handling and a better stability control system that handles issues with understeer as soon as it occurs. It still has fully independent air suspension and electronically locking differentials. This is a pure Marvel!

name: Toyota Landcruiser "ZX"
description: Here is a fully specced Toyota Landcruiser ZX with Sunroof, 7 seats occupancy, front heated leather seats, an automatic transmission gearbox, side steps which is a standard equipment for this series, roof rails, fog lights, and the Old money interior trimming of wood. Driving this unit gives you more understanding of why an example of politicians really adore this car.

name: Audi Q3 2.0L Quattro
description: A number of Q3s in our market are the 1.4L Non Quattro versions. This is a premium one, a 2.0L TFSI QUATTRO version with power ratings of 217 horsepower and 350Nm of torque, very impressive. The fabric seats come with thigh support for the front occupants and are also powered. This is an updated version that came to the market in 2015 with redesigns of front lights, grille, and its exterior face. Upgrades also included parking sensors in the front and rear, and full LED headlights.

name: Toyota Mark X G's
description: The hottest Saloon in town, Toyota Mark X G's, also known as GR Sport from 2016. This unit is based on the 250s base model with a 2.5L V6 engine. One can notice the difference between this and other variants by its 3-piece bodykit complimented by a rear upper spoiler, clear smoked tail lamps, forged 19' wheels, a magic air suspension that lowers and rises by remote command, red stitchings on the interior, and Upgraded Alcantara seats. It also is fitted with quad exhaust tailpipes. This is a huge moment for Mark X enthusiasts to purchase this unit!

name: Mazda Verisa
description: Mazda Verisa has been in production since 2004. Sadly, it came to an end in 2015 with the last model receiving an update in 2009. This 2008 model received an update in 2006. Brown fabric seats would welcome you into an interior with climate controls, cup holders, and an android infotainment display system. Maintainance has also been on point in this unit.

name: Audi A6 2.0L TFSI
description: An Audi A6 in dark Blue, easily mistaken as a black color. A lot about this car is very unique, from the color to its sleekness and design. A rear diffuser, leather powered seats, S-Line styling, and power from the 2.0L engine make up this worthy unit!

name: Mercedes Benz GLC 250 4 MATIC /SUNROOF
description: A high spec Mercedes Benz GLC 250 4 Matic with sunroof with an updated redesigned grill. In its interior are bucket styled leather seats with thigh support, Multifunctional tilt and telescopic steering wheel, smartphone integration, active parking assist, and a premium surround sound system.

name: SUBARU WRX S4
description: This is one of those good looking yet highly performing JDMs you always come along. Powered by a 2.0L turbocharged engine with stock 300 horsepower and 400Nm of Torque that has a high tuning capability, you can take this car to the track, use it to run errands, go for roadtrips, and daily it, and it will last you how good your maintenance will be. Take this as your chance to participate in high performance races!

name: Audi A4 2.0L
description: This one of the rare colored A4s in wine red and adding to the sauce is the 2.0L engine. This is a one time opportunity of getting a 2.0L Audi A4 with leather seats, dual zone climate controls, and a multifunctional steering wheel at an incredible 2.25M cash price.

name: Mazda Atenza 2.2D
description: An all black unit from the exterior body color to the interior. It is fitted with leather seats in black as well. A little touch of art on this unit and it will be the talk of the town!

name: Mazda Atenza 2.2D
description: Mazda Atenza shares a lot with its bigger brother, the CX-5. The interior resembles the CX-5 in nearly all factors you would even think you are in a CX-5. The body size brings out the difference and the sleekness which the Atenza has really embraced. It will always have you looking back in traffic at it.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D
description: Mazda was very intentional in delivering different tastes of one of their best selling cars, the CX-5. This model is coloured in light blue with a dark grey variant interior. The seats are fabric grey, climate controls are dual, an android infotainment system, and a multifunctional steering wheel all in grey. It runs a 2.2L diesel engine with excellent handling.

name: Subaru Outback 'EyeSight Package 2.5'
description: Subaru Outback in its fifth "BS" Generation that began its sales in 2015. The 5th generation was inspired by it accommodating passengers with the sporting spirit. The Chassis also was made more stiff with the drag factor in it being far reduced by mounting side mirrors on the front door panels. In its interior are heated leather seats, dual zone climate controls, a multifunctional steering wheel, and an android infotainment system.

name: Volvo V60 T3
description: Volvo V60 was first introduced into the market in 2010 with the second generation beginning in 2018. It underwent a facelift in 2014 with the newer version being more sleek and appealing. This unit comes fitted with a a Sunroof, heated seats, a multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, a premium surround sound system that's arguably one of the best, and dual exhaust tailpipes.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D
description: Diesel powered cars are loved for their torque that you are going to need in instances of carrying heavy loads, towing, and the basic overtaking. This is a 2.2L diesel powered Mazda CX-5 with a torque figure of 418Nm, about 200Nm less than a J200 Landcruiser series diesel variant. Leather seats that are powered with memory seats and cup holders for all occupants make very enjoyable drives. It also has dual zone climate controls and an android infotainment display system for access to car controls.

name: Mazda Axela 1.5L
description: Mazda Axela, now in its third generation since its first Gen models production in the tear 2003, has undergone a lot of changes with the major one being the Skyactiv chassis that replaced Ford's C1 platform. This unit has a 1500cc naturally aspirated petrol engine with a 2WD drivetrain. Fabric seats,climate controls, android infotainment display system, steering wheel controls, and cup holders make up the interior.

name: Nissan DAYZ
description: Nissan DAYZ is a very efficient car for running the daily constant errands as with the Uber business. It is a very spacious, Comfortable, and convenient car. This unit has beige fabric seats with a tone of brown color on its edges. Powered by a 660cc, consumption levels are extremely good in this unit with up to 20Kms a liter on the minimum.

name: Toyota Landcruiser VX 4.5L "V8" AT
description: This is one of those eye catchers when it comes to Landcruiser 200 series especially the early production models that began in 2007 after the end of 100 series. This is a 2008 model powered by a 4.5L 1VD-FTV Diesel turbocharged engine doing 282 horsepowers and 650Nm of Torque. The amount of torque in this vehicle felt by a single rev up is amazing. You can almost instantly feel how powerful the VX V8 Model is. It has a rear view camera as a standard feature, 10 airbags, CRAWL terrain feature, downhill assist control, Multi Terrain ABS, Kinetic Dynamic Suspension System, and leather seats all became standard in the VX having not been there in the 100 series. It also has 7 seats carrying capacity. And of all, it was bought locally! Such a unit.

name: Lexus RX300
description: Lexus RX300 is powered by a 3000cc V6 naturally aspirated petrol engine producing 204 horsepower and 283Nm of torque. It is still a performer 10 years later after its production. It is very well maintained with leather seats, FM Radio system, climate controls, and steering wheel controls.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D
description: The CX-5, listed, powered by a diesel 2.2L engine with a turbocharger is quite a powerful car and a reliable one at that. Its owners over the years have really loved this since when it was introduced in 2012. This unit has a multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, powered leather seats unlike the traditional manually controlled seats, fog lights, and roof rails.

name: Audi Q5 2.0T QUATTRO "Typ 8R"
description: Audi Q5 Type 8R is the first generation of the Q5 that began production in 2008 with the 2nd Generation beginning in 2017. The first generation was done a facelift in 2012 and carried through all the models after then to 2016. Front and rear lights were redesigned and the engines uprated with the increasing need for power and efficiency. The unit listed has beige leather seats that are powered and heated. A multifunctional steering wheel, Audi MMI infotainment system that was updated in the facelift. Its finishing was done in wood that has always been refreshing.

name: Peugeot 3008 GT-Line
description: Peugeot, manufactured in France, first produced the 3008 in 2008 and launched Mid 2009 succeeding Peugeot 4007 and 4008. It is a compact crossover SUV that shares its platform with the 308 which is its smaller counterpart. This unit is the 2nd Generation Peugeot 3008, P84, that succeeded the T84 that ended production in 2015. P84 did a lot of improvements beginning with Peugeot's iCockpit featuring a virtual instrument cluster. The 8 inch display screen with a touch functionality is the center hub of all the car controls. Car controls were designed angularly towards the driver which eases the driver's focus when selecting any control feature. It is also offers a thrilling driving experience. This is a high performance variant with a number of features including lane assist, Blindspot assist, and an exhilarating quick drive.

name: Mazda CX-5 2.2D
description: Mazda CX-5 is a crossover SUV produced by Mazda since 2012. It has only been produced for two generations the 2nd one beginning in 2017. This is the first generation named KE. It is powered by a 2.2L diesel engine producing some great torque of 418Nm. It interior is graced by a bright interior with cream powered leather seats, cup holders, Multifunctional steering wheel, android infotainment display screen, side mirror indicators, and memory seats quite convenient with two different users.

name: Audi Q5 2.0T S-LINE QUATTRO
description: Audi Q5 With Quattro All Wheel Drive is the car you need in this weather. Quattro distributes power to all wheels depending on their power needs. This feature by Audi prevents skidding in the a wet terrain. The unit has half leather seats, dual zone climate controls, hill descent control, a multifunctional steering wheel among other features.

name: Mercedes Benz C180
description: The C180 was well articulated by the manufacturer in its design aspects. The curves on the exterior, well curated cabin with a Mercedes command infotainment display system, steering wheel controls, cup holders, an analogue clock, a touchscreen infotainment system control that is complimented by steering wheel controls, paddle shifters to use in manual driving mode, and cabin vents that can be moved like a joystick depending on the user's wish. Quite an art!

name: Nissan March
description: Nissan March is a minimalistic cool car with a very direct approach when driving it. Fabric seats, two tone in this unit, android infotainment display screen that's important in controlling some components of the car such as the radio, climate controls, Traction control that ensures the car doesn't lose traction slipping off, and Electrically folding side mirrors.

name: Nissan Note
description: With a premium low mileage of 45K kms, the Nissan Note is a new as one would never expect of 2016 model from Japan. The unit will give you over 100,000Kms of mileage before you begin doing any serious service. Needless to say you need to maintain it well regularly. Its fabric seats are still wrapped in factory polythene. A push to start button, climate controls, lane assist, Anti collision system, and traction control are among the premium features you will find in this unit.

name: BMW 535i "F10"
description: The 6th generation of BMW 5 series lasted between the years of 2010 to 2017 where different series including the F10, listed here, F11, F07, and the F18, were also produced. The F10 is a 4 door sedan while the other series' are in different body forms. The 535i under the F10 series was among the first cars in the F10 lineup to be specced with an 8 speed dual clutch automatic transmission gearbox, electric power steering, and an LCD instrument cluster. It packs up over 300 horsepowers in the hood produced by a 3000cc inline 6 twin scroll turbocharged engine. A twin scroll turbocharger basically has two exhaust gas openings in its household caller scrolls. This unit is cool but also can get power angry as you wish!

name: Nissan March
description: The best priced Nissan March in the market. Comes with a 1200cc naturally aspirated engine on the hood. In its interior is an android infotainment display screen, climate controls, cup holders, and a traction control feature among other features.

name: Toyota Axio
description: The newer models of Toyota Axio look very good compared to the older models. The redesigns worked on a lot of parts, the major one being the face, front bumper. It has bight fabric seats, climate controls, android infotainment display screen, and cup holders that are very useful especially in the mornings.

name: Toyota Vitz
description: This Toyota Vitz is specced with fog lights that gives the advantage of increased vision, side mirror indicators to alert motorists from all side of the side one wants to drive to, alloy rims that last a lifetime, fabric seats, Electrically folding side mirrors, an android infotainment display screen that you can access car functions from, and climate controls.

name: Toyota Succeed
description: Toyota Succeed came to the market as a commercial vehicle that makes it very efficient in conducting business between various towns and long distances. It has a 2 wheel drive drivertrain that sends power, received from a 1500cc engine, to 2 Wheels all the time. It is fitted with fabric seats with the rear seats covered with leather material. Other features include an android infotainment display screen, climate controls, powered windows, and a foot brake that is powerful compared to the handbrake.

name: Toyota Harrier/PANORAMIC SUNROOF
description: This is a highly specced Toyota Harrier that has a Panoramic sunroof, powered leather seats, dual zone climate controls, steering wheel controls, interior wood trimming, push to start button, cup holders, armrests, alloy rims, fog lights and side mirror indicators.

name: Subaru Forester 2.0 NA
description: The Forester is quite a decent car that plays role in different worlds, from Family purposes to entertainment escapades during the weekends. This is a Non Turbo model that is highly reliable. Other specs include fabric seats, dual zone climate controls, steering wheel controls, paddle shifters, push to start button, dual exhaust tailpipe, and side mirror indicators

name: Porsche Cayenne Platinum Edition
description: Porsche has been producing superior performing cars since the early years of the 20th century. They have shown their expertise and highly advanced engineering in their productions. The Cayenne is one of the marvels of Porsche engineering. The 2014 Petrol Platinum Edition variant is powered by a 3600cc petrol engine that does an impressive 300 horsepower at 6300 RPMs and 400Nm of Torque at 3000 RPMs. It does a lot more better than the diesel variant in the horsepower numbers, doing about 240 horses. We can all agree on the engine's reliability and maintenance. It has beige leather, dual zone climate controls, Multifunctional tilt & telescopic steering wheel, Auto start stop feature, a premium surround sound system, and differential locks.

name: Toyota Fielder
description: Toyota Fielder will give you a very high longevity as long as you would like to own it. This has undergone some few modifications including aftermarket rims, an aftermarket sound system that's quite a deal. It also features an android infotainment display screen, climate controls, side mirror indicators, and roof rails

name: Peugeot 308
description: Peugeot 308 scored a very good reliability score among reviewers and users. It is very reliable with good maintenance and will with no doubt take you miles. It is powered by a 1200cc turbocharged engine that's quite powerful doing over 230Nm of Torque. It has fabric seats, steering wheel controls, paddle shifters, climate controls, android infotainment display screen, and side mirror indicators. It is quite spacious and very comfortable.

name: LEXUS IS300h
description: Lexus IS has been in production since 1999 with a lot of redesigns done on the models since then, the Lexus IS 300h in our stock is a Third Gen of the IS series called the XE30 that began in 2013 to 2020. It is quite modern with improved lamps, front, and a number of updates in the interior. It has beige half leather seats, cup holders, steering wheel controls, paddle shifters, analogue clock, android infotainment display screen, dual zone climate controls, and a hybrid setup that packs up extra power.

name: Mazda Axela
description: Heads up display gives one of the safest ways to drive allowing one to focus on the road. it display the current car speed "virtually" on the road. Fabric seats, dual zone climate controls, steering wheel controls, fog lights, and side mirror indicators all work to achieve a pleasurable drive.

name: Audi SQ5/PANORAMIC SUNROOF
description:
Enroute to the Port of Mombasa.

A panoramic sunroof, two tone leather interior with front heated seats, dual zone climate controls, a multifunctional steering wheel, cup holders, and armrests. These gives the SQ5 a premium rating and a great experience to its users.

name: Mercedes Benz GLE 350d Coupe
description:
Enroute to the Port of Mombasa. 

The GLE350d is one of the premium models produced by Mercedes. It comes fully loaded with a panoramic sunroof, leather seats with heated and memory function, Mercedes speedtronic cruise control system, active parking assist system, ambient lighting, multiple climate controls, and engine immobilizer among other features.

name: Mercedes Benz E250
description: One of the  best deals in town! The Mercedes Benz E250 fitted with half leather seats, multifunctional steering wheel, dual zone climate controls, side mirror indicators, and Mercedes Command infotainment system.

name: Lexus RX450H
description: The RX450h is known for its reliablity, convenience, and class. Many of its users have appreciated how good the Lexus has been. It comes with beige fabric seats, climate controls, multifunctional steering wheel, and amrests.

name: Daihatsu Move
description: The best minimalist car we can call. A 650cc engine that gives a good deal of fuel economy, a spacious enough interior, beige fabric seats, and quality car controls. This is the best choice for this kind of economy.

name: Honda Fit
description: The Honda fit Non hybrid version is powered by a 1300cc naturally aspirated engine that produces 97 horsepower and 130Nm of torque. In its interior are fabric seats, climate controls, steering wheel controls, android infotainment display screen, and an Eco drive mode that saves on fuel by reducing the engine performance.

name: Subaru Outback EyeSight Package 2.5
description: The famous Subaru Outback dreaded by many, but you can own it! It is powered by a 2500cc naturally aspirated engine that can last a lifetime without complications and has the World's best symmetrical All wheel Drive system that easily manages any kind of terrain in any kind of weather. The interior is fitted with fabric seats with seat heating feature for both rear and front seats, dual zone climate controls, and a multifunctional steering wheel.

name: Ford Ranger
description: A locally manufactured Ford Ranger powered by a 2500cc diesel engine mated to a manual transmission gearbox in a 4WD drive system. It has a 5 seats capacity with fabric material and a spacious cargo space.

name: Honda Fit Shuttle Hybrid
description: A very fun to drive, well spacious, highly accommodating, well powered car. The Honda Fit shuttle with an hybrid setup has Honda giving its fans the best in their station wagon models. The interior is fitted with half leather seats that are quite comfortable. An android infotainment display screen gives access to all car systems that you can control some from the steering wheel

name: Toyota Sienta
description: This yellow coloured Toyota Sienta is very catchy. No eye would miss the beautifully designed fog lights, headlamps, sporty alloy rims, and well shaped tail lights with nice blue strips finishing at the rear!

name: Honda Vezel Hybrid
description: Many would appreciate the hybrid system in the Vezel in such economic times. The car is an extremely impressive consumer. A 1500cc naturally aspirated engine with a hybrid setup has made driving easier, no matter the fuel economy crisis!

name: Jeep Grand Cherokee "LAREDO"
description: The Laredo came into the market as an averagely equipped Jeep model. With standard features including power windows, steering wheel controls, android infotainment display screen, paddles shifters, and dual zone climate controls, the Laredo is 4×4 beast that can handle what every road has to offer!

name: Mazda Atenza 2.2D
description: Station Wagons have introduced a different cars taste from the traditional sedan and SUV models. This Grey Mazda Atenza 2.2.2D is one of the best models Mazda has created. The unit comes with fabric material seats. Dual zone climate controls, steering wheel controls, fog lights, cup holders, roof rails, and a very interactive android infotainment display screen.

name: Mazda Atenza 2.2D
description: Mazda developed some powerful station wagons, one of them being the Atenza. The 2.2L diesel turbocharged engine produces over 170 horsepower and a great deal of over 300Nm of torque. This shows the leves of dedication Mazda has undertaken on its developments. You can never go wrong with this model

name: Toyota Auris "Turbo"
description: The turbocharged version of the Toyota Auris has received quite a number of positive reviews from its users. The 1200cc capacity engine does magic in its strength and handling, very addictive. The design cue is on point. Reliability and convenience had Toyota outdoing themselves

name: Toyota Sienta
description: The Sienta does amazing things that are not shown by its design, a 7 seats carrying capacity is incredible for a 1.5L naturally aspirated engine. Comfort wasn't forgotten for all the occupants as the Sienta has leather seats and a good climate controls system. You can count on it

name: BMW X3 XDRIVE20D
description: The BMW X3 XDrive 20d, a 2.0L diesel variant, is the best bet for the long road trips. A powerful engine comes in handy with a comfortable and pleasurable interior that has leather seats, dual zone climate controls, a well-built music system, steering wheel controls to ease your driving, and paddles shifters to spice up the drive!

name: Suzuki Swift
description: Suzuki Swift is a compact car that has been highly ranked by motorists for its agile handling, sporty design, fuel efficiency, a practical comfortable interior, and high safety measures including stability control feature. This comes with a choice of fabric seats, android infotainment display screen, and climate controls.

name: Mazda Demio 1.5L
description: Mazda has constantly improved its diesel engines overtime. The 1.5L diesel engine has an impressive amount of torque that compares to sedans and even close to some SUVs. It's been quite reliable and easy to maintain. It also comes with the best price in town.

name: Nissan Skyline 200GT
description: This here is one of the best value for money cars in the market. A Nissan on the outside and a Mercedes-Benz W205 C200 underneath. It comes with Mercedes' M274 petrol engine and the 7 G-tronic transmission that seamlessly transitions. The interior styling is very welcoming and comfy. Leather seats, steering wheel controls, dual zone climate controls, and a well integrated android infotaiment display screen make a very interesting vehicle.
